NK073(pu)006:1: // u pa de sha da r+sha kam m+aa la s+ya
NK073(pu)006:2: b+ha sham da n+t+ra nawa&&& r+tha ra t+n+aa lo ko
NK073(pu)006:3: n+aa ma bi dza ha ra ti sma //
NK073(pu)006:6: // man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba'i bshad pa rgyud don
NK073(pu)006:7: rin po che snang byed ces bya ba bzhugs so
NK073(pu)006:9: // mnyam nyid mtha' bral nam mkha'i ngang nyid las //
NK073(pu)006:10: rang byung rang gsal ye shes rin po che //
NK073(pu)006:11: gdul bya'i blo bzhin 'char ba chu zla bzhin //
NK073(pu)006:12: drug pa'i skyes bu bla mar bcas la 'dud //
NK073(pu)006:14: brjod bya don dang brjod byed tshig go //
NK073(pu)006:16: kun nas nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i chos dang /
NK073(pu)006:18: de yang gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK073(pu)006:19: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros /
NK073(pu)006:20: ces pa la sogs pa shwa lo ka gcig gis 'khor ba'i rgyu dang /
NK073(pu)006:24: mya ngan las 'das pa'ang de nyid las /
NK073(pu)006:25: stod nyid bdag med rang rig ye mkhyen thugs /
NK073(pu)006:26: ces pa la sogs pa shwa lo ka gcig gis mya ngan las 'das pa'i gzhi dang /
NK073(pu)006:28: rnam grangs kyi ngos nas ngo bo bstan pas rgyas par gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:29: brjod byed kyi tshig la gsum gyis bstan pa'i don gyi khog dbubs pa la gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:30: gang zag 'jug ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:31: don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i phyir bshad pa'i thabs so //
NK073(pu)006:32: dang po ngos bzung ba ni gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:35: de la spyir bstan pa ni spyir khams gsum gyi
NK073(pu)006:36: sems can thams cad rgyu ma rig pa gnyis las
NK073(pu)006:37: byung / rkyen las dang nyon mongs pas bsgrubs te /
NK073(pu)006:38: 'bras bu'i ngo bo gnas khams gsum na 'gro ba rigs drug bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams /
NK073(pu)006:39: spyi dang bye brag gi sdug bsngal gyis nyen te /
NK073(pu)006:40: las kyi sbyang ba dag sgo gsum kun nas gdung ba rnams la /
NK073(pu)006:41: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi yul bral gyi ye shes chen pos /
NK073(pu)006:42: me long ngam chu zla'i gzugs brnyan ltar yar yul du ma grub pa'i gdul bya rnams la /
NK073(pu)006:43: gzigs tshul gsum dbyer med pas gzigs te /
NK073(pu)006:44: spro bsdu dang bral ba'i thugs rje chen po /
NK073(pu)006:45: gdul bya'i ngos nas skye lugs bzhis skyes te /
NK073(pu)006:46: don mdzad pa'ang gsum gyi nang nas 'dir don dam
NK073(pu)006:47: nges pa'i theg pa 'ba' zhig la bzung ste don
NK073(pu)006:48: ston na / rgyu 'bras gnyis las rgyu'i dbang du ste /
NK073(pu)006:49: ston pa sprul pa'i skus gzigs tshul bzhis gdul bya
NK073(pu)006:50: la gzigs nas 'dzam bu'i gling du chos gsungs pa'ang
NK073(pu)006:51: gsum ste / gnyen po'i sgo nas gsungs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:52: dbye ba'i thabs su gsungs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:53: bsdu ba'i thabs su gsungs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:54: de la gnyen po'i sgo nas gsungs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:55: nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por
NK073(pu)006:56: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs te
NK073(pu)006:57: / gdul bya la dug gsum cha mnyam pa dang bzhi la dgongs te /
NK073(pu)006:58: 'dod chags kyi gnyen por rnam par dbye ba'i mi
NK073(pu)006:59: gtsang ba bsgom pa 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri
NK073(pu)006:60: chig stong ste 'dod chags kyi dbye ba rnams la
NK073(pu)006:61: dgongs pa'o // zhe sdang gi gnyen por ting nge
NK073(pu)006:62: 'dzin shas che ba mdo sde nyis khri chig stong
NK073(pu)006:64: gti mug gi gnyen por rnam par dbye ba mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong /
NK073(pu)006:65: dug gsum cha mnyam pa la dgongs nas sde snod
NK073(pu)006:66: gsum cha mnyam pa nyi khri chig stong ste des
NK073(pu)006:67: na rnam grangs brgyad khri bzhi stong ngo //
NK073(pu)006:68: grangs de dag kyang gdul bya'i blo rtog la snang gi /
NK073(pu)006:69: ston pa rang ngo la rgya chad pa med de nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:70: zhes rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa kun nas gsungs so //
NK073(pu)006:71: sgo'i tshad kyang theg pa che chung gi bzhed pa
NK073(pu)006:72: slob dpon so sos bzhed pa gzhan du shes te
NK073(pu)006:73: / rgyu'i theg pa 'ba' zhig gi snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:74: dbye ba'i thabs su gsung pa ni 'dir 'bring du bstan pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:75: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong de yang gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis su 'dus te /
NK073(pu)006:76: mdo'i sde dang dbyangs kyis bsnyad pa'i sde la sogs pa bcu gnyis so //
NK073(pu)006:77: de dag la mdo sde zhes kyang bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:78: 'khor rnam gnyis sder langs pas ston pa la mdor bsdus pas zhus pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:80: 'bel gtam rgyas pas tshig sder langs pa gcig gis don mdor bsdus pa ston pas so //
NK073(pu)006:81: mdo sde bcu gnyis gzhan na gsal lo //
NK073(pu)006:82: da ni tha ma bsdu ba'i thabs su gsungs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:83: yan lag bcu gnyis po de yang /
NK073(pu)006:84: sde snod rin po che gsum du bsdus te /
NK073(pu)006:85: ston pa zhal mi bzhugs pa'i dus su 'khor rnams kyis so //
NK073(pu)006:86: de'ang ston pa 'das nas chos bsdu ba mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK073(pu)006:87: kun dga' bos mdo sde bsdus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:89: 'od srung chen pos mngon pa bsdus pa la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:90: sde snod gsum re re la gsum gsum tshang ste /
NK073(pu)006:91: 'dul ba la yang srung ba 'ba' zhig ston pa ni 'dul ba'i 'dul ba /
NK073(pu)006:92: shes rab kyi cha ston pa ni 'dul ba'i mngon pa /
NK073(pu)006:93: ting nge 'dzin gtsor ston pa ni 'dul ba'i mdo sde'o //
NK073(pu)006:95: 'o na rgyu'i theg pa sde snod rin po che gsum gyis bstan pa de ltar yin na /
NK073(pu)006:96: gsang sngags ci ltar bzhed zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:97: sngon gyi mkhas pa rnams bzhed gzhung mi 'dra ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:98: jo bo a ro la sogs pa rnams kyis mngon par bsdus te /
NK073(pu)006:99: mngon pa phung po khams dang skye mched kyi dbye ba rgya che bar ston la /
NK073(pu)006:100: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga na phung po khams
NK073(pu)006:101: dang skye mched kyi dbye ba de ltar ston pas
NK073(pu)006:102: so ce'o // yang mkhas pa la las 'dul bar bsdu skad de /
NK073(pu)006:103: 'dul ba na bsrung bya'i rnam grangs rgya che la
NK073(pu)006:104: gsang sngags na dam tshig sa ya 'bum sde ston
NK073(pu)006:105: pas so ce'o // de gnyis la lung ngos gsal du ston pa med do //
NK073(pu)006:106: yang sngon gyi mkhas pa nas da ltar gyi gsang sngags pa shas che bas mdo sder bsdus te /
NK073(pu)006:109: mdo sde 'di ni mnyam par gyis /
NK073(pu)006:111: mdo sde 'di yi gzi brjid kyis /
NK073(pu)006:113: u pa ya rnam snang mngon byang nas /
NK073(pu)006:115: mdo sde'i dbang po'i rgyal po zhes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:117: theg pa che la mngon dga' bas /
NK073(pu)006:118: mdo sde 'di ni bshad par bya /
NK073(pu)006:120: ma h+aa yo ga nges brjod bla ma nas /
NK073(pu)006:121: gsang sngags mdo sde'i rgyal po'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i zhes bshad pas /
NK073(pu)006:122: de ltar nges so zhes pa ni da ltar gyi gsang sngags pa thams cad kyis bzhed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:123: de la bla ma dam pa bde bar gshegs pa chen po'i zhal nas /
NK073(pu)006:124: mngon pa dang 'dul bar bsdu ba rnam pa gnyis ni lung med pa'i mthong snang phra mo ste /
NK073(pu)006:125: chos mthun pa'i ngos nas ni glang po che byi bar bsdu ba dang mtshungs la /
NK073(pu)006:126: mdo sder bsdu ba'ang lung phra mo dang shes rab
NK073(pu)006:127: phra mo la brten te byis pa'i blo lta bu'o
NK073(pu)006:129: rgyu 'bras kyis lta spyod kyi khyad par dang /
NK073(pu)006:130: ston pa'i snang tshul gyi khyad par dang /
NK073(pu)006:131: gdul bya dbang po rab 'bring gi khyad par ma rtogs te phyogs phran bu tsam brjod pa'o gsungs /
NK073(pu)006:132: bzhed pa gsum po de ni rgyal po gcig la
NK073(pu)006:133: mtho dman mang pos so so nas nga'i rgyal ba'i
NK073(pu)006:134: rgyal po zer ba'am nor bu rin po che ras
NK073(pu)006:135: kha dog sna tshogs kyis gnas skabs su bsgyur ba'i
NK073(pu)006:137: des na 'dul bar bsdu ba'am shin tu mi 'thad de /
NK073(pu)006:138: 'dul ba dang gsang sngags gnyis lam gyi gnas skabs
NK073(pu)006:139: na 'gal rkyen rgya che bas srung ba tsam zhig
NK073(pu)006:140: gis 'dul bar bsdu mi nus so //
NK073(pu)006:141: mngon pa yang phung khams skye mched rgya che bar
NK073(pu)006:142: ston kyang de dag spang bya'i ngos nas ston la
NK073(pu)006:143: / gsang sngags kyis de dag blang bya 'bras bu'i ngo bor bstan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:144: gzhan lta ba dang spyod pa dang ting nge 'dzin dang 'bras bu grub pa'i yin dang /
NK073(pu)006:145: gzhi 'jug pa'i sgo dbang la brten pa rnams kyis rnam pa thams cad du mi mtshungs so //
NK073(pu)006:146: mdo sder bsdu ba'am gong ma rnams kyis kyang mi mtshungs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:147: ting nge 'dzin gtsor ston kyang ngo bo mi 'dra bas /
NK073(pu)006:148: spu rangs kyi rgyal po rtse lde khams kyi sprang po rtse lde mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:150: rnam 'joms na mdo sde ces pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:151: kri ya mdo sngags mtshams su byang bas mdo sde zhes bya /
NK073(pu)006:152: rgyud ces bya gzungs zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:153: ston pa sprul sku nyid yin kyang bden pa dbyer med la 'jug pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:154: lha'i sku la dmigs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:155: mi tshe bdun gyis sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyong bar mi mtshungs so //
NK073(pu)006:156: rnam snang mngon byang na mdo sder brjod pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:157: mdo sde'i dbang po rgyal po zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:158: sde snod gsum gyi dbang po'am rgyal po'am lam stegs sam bcud lta bur khas blangs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:159: yo ga nas mdo sde brjod pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:160: theg pa che la mngon dga' zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:161: mthong snang gi chos thams cad spangs pa med par /
NK073(pu)006:162: sku gsung thugs su shes pa'i sgo nas 'jug na 'bras bu la skyol bar byed pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:163: thabs che la tshegs chung lam myur bar theg pa chen po zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:164: gsang sngags yin la de nyid ni tshig mdor bsdus don sder langs pas mdo sde zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:165: nges brjod nas gsang sngags mdo sde /
NK073(pu)006:166: gsang sngags kyi don 'khor 'das thams cad sems nyid
NK073(pu)006:167: rang rig tu ston par byed pa'i don rgya che
NK073(pu)006:168: ba de tshig mdor bsdus pa nyung ngus ston te
NK073(pu)006:169: / sems sam rang rig gam lhan cig skyes pa lta bu bas /
NK073(pu)006:170: mdo sder mi 'dus te tshig gis 'jigs pas lung mang po ma bkod do //
NK073(pu)006:171: 'o na gsang sngags kyi theg pa ci lta bu yin zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:172: spyir gnas chos kyi dbyings don gyi 'og min na
NK073(pu)006:173: 'khor mthar phyin pa mthar lam pa rtsal chen rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:174: pa'i skyes bu rnams kyi ngo la snang ba'i ston
NK073(pu)006:175: pa rigs kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang
NK073(pu)006:176: po khyad par gyi longs sku chu dang me long
NK073(pu)006:177: dwangs pa ltar dag ba'i 'khor rnams kyi snang ba
NK073(pu)006:178: la lhun grub tu bzhugs te /
NK073(pu)006:179: dus chos kyi dbyings la skad cig ma dang bral
NK073(pu)006:180: bas dus gsum mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la skye
NK073(pu)006:181: 'gro dang bsdu gshegs mi mnga' ste /
NK073(pu)006:182: de'i rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen po
NK073(pu)006:183: lhag pa'i chos sku nyid ngo bo gang du'ang ma
NK073(pu)006:185: gdul bya'i ngo bzhin cir yang mi 'gags par 'char te /
NK073(pu)006:186: blo yang rab kyi ngo bo rtogs pa'i rig pa
NK073(pu)006:187: skad cig gis 'bras bu sangs rgyas su lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:188: grub par byed pa rdzogs pa chen por snang /
NK073(pu)006:189: blo de las cung zhan pa'i dbyings dang ye shes
NK073(pu)006:190: rgyu 'bras su 'dzin pa tsam la lung a nu
NK073(pu)006:191: yo gar snang / de bas cung zhan pa'i bsgom
NK073(pu)006:192: lam mtho dman pa rnams la ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK073(pu)006:194: rig pa skad cig la gnas tha dad 'og min dang gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi gnas dang /
NK073(pu)006:196: ri rab kyi khong seng dang /
NK073(pu)006:197: lang ka srin po'i yul dang /
NK073(pu)006:199: gnod sbyin gyi gnas dang de la sogs te so
NK073(pu)006:200: so'i gnas sna tshogs su so sor ston par snang
NK073(pu)006:201: nas so so'i bstan pa gsungs te /
NK073(pu)006:202: bsdud pa pos so sor bsdus pa'i dus su thams
NK073(pu)006:203: cad mkhyen pa rang ngo la mnyam pa las rdul
NK073(pu)006:204: phra rab tsam yang ma dmigs te /
NK073(pu)006:205: 'byung 'jug med pa nam mkha' lta bu nyid /
NK073(pu)006:206: mkhyen pa dang thugs rje dang mdzad pa la snga
NK073(pu)006:207: phyi med par lhun grub tu bzhugs pas ngo bo
NK073(pu)006:208: nyid kyi rgyun nam mkhar lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:210: de'ang ma h+aa yo ga pa thabs kyi rgyud /
NK073(pu)006:212: dbyer med kyi rgyud gsum la /
NK073(pu)006:214: thabs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:215: shes rab kyi rgyud mnyam sbyor dang /
NK073(pu)006:216: zla gsang rnams 'og min du gsungs /
NK073(pu)006:217: shes rab kyi rgyud gzhan ma bung che ba 'dzam
NK073(pu)006:218: bu gling gru gsum chos kyi 'byung gnas su byin
NK073(pu)006:219: gyis brlabs nas / so sor rgyas par gsungs pa
NK073(pu)006:220: rnams so so'i lo rgyus bzhin te gdul bya'i snang
NK073(pu)006:221: gyis brlabs nas / ba'o // thabs kyi rgyud gzhan
NK073(pu)006:222: ma rnams ri rab kyi zom dang lha ma yin
NK073(pu)006:223: gyi gnas dang gnod sbyin gyi gnas rnams su gsungs
NK073(pu)006:225: yo ga ni 'og min du gdul bya des 'dul
NK073(pu)006:226: ba rnams la rnam snang chen por snang nas 'bum
NK073(pu)006:227: sde gsungs pa'o // u pa ya dang kri ya
NK073(pu)006:228: ni dbang bsgyur gyi khang bzang dang sum cu rtsa
NK073(pu)006:229: gsum dang ri rab ngos dang /
NK073(pu)006:230: 'dzam bu gling gi gnas so so la sogs pa
NK073(pu)006:231: rnams su ston pa so so rnams kyis gsungs pa
NK073(pu)006:232: rang rang gi gzhung gi lo rgyus bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:233: de bas na gsang sngags phyi nang drug tu snang
NK073(pu)006:234: ba yang gdul bya'i blo rab 'bring drug gi snang
NK073(pu)006:236: 'on kyang thabs cad mkhyen pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi
NK073(pu)006:237: thugs rje'i rgyun rang snang ba kho nar zad do
NK073(pu)006:238: // de ltar chos kyi dbyings mtha' dbus med pa'i ngang las /
NK073(pu)006:239: mtha' thug pa med pa'i gdul bya rnam las 'gro
NK073(pu)006:240: 'ong dang spro bsdu bral ba'i ston pa rang snang
NK073(pu)006:241: ba yang ngo bo nyid kyi longs sku chen po
NK073(pu)006:242: drug pa'i drug pa ston pa nyid kyi che ba'i
NK073(pu)006:243: yon tan gyi rtsal rang snang ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:245: de las bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang
NK073(pu)006:246: gsung dang thugs rdo rje las rig pa'i skyes bu
NK073(pu)006:248: 'thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis s+n+rel zhi dang
NK073(pu)006:249: yas man gyi 'jig rten gyi khams phyogs bcu mtha'
NK073(pu)006:251: stong gsum gyi stong chen po re rer thug pa
NK073(pu)006:252: chen po re res 'dul ba rnams bzhis 'gro ba
NK073(pu)006:254: zhes pa la sogs pas gsang sngags kyi byin rlabs
NK073(pu)006:255: las nyi ma'i zer gyi tshul du sde snod rin
NK073(pu)006:257: 'og min du ngo bo nyid kyi bstan pa gsang sngags kyi don rtogs pa'i shes rab med de /
NK073(pu)006:258: mos pas spyod pa'i sa pa rigs drug la snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:259: dgos pa ni 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po byon
NK073(pu)006:260: na yul khams thams cad chas su zhugs pa dang
NK073(pu)006:261: 'dra bar mthar thug pa'i theg pa snang bar 'gyur
NK073(pu)006:262: ba'i gzhi 'am rten nam snod dag par bya ba
NK073(pu)006:263: lta bu'i phyir sde snod gsum snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:264: de yang 'og min du ni gsang sngags kyi bstan
NK073(pu)006:265: pa snga la snod dag pa dang ldan nas bcud
NK073(pu)006:267: mi yul du ni gsang sngags phyi pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:268: kha cig gis rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis gzhi
NK073(pu)006:269: lam 'bras bu gsum la tha dad de 'brel ba
NK073(pu)006:270: med pas / gsang sngags ni dbang po rnon pa'i spyod yul dang /
NK073(pu)006:271: mtshan nyid ni dbang po btul po'i spyod yul lo //
NK073(pu)006:272: ces brjod de de ltar na 'gro ba rnams kyi
NK073(pu)006:273: shes rgyud gzhi nas tha dad de chos nyid du
NK073(pu)006:276: gzhi nas rang rgyud rno brtul med //
NK073(pu)006:277: gzhi nas rang rgyud rno brtul na //
NK073(pu)006:278: de bzhin nyid du gcig mi rung //
NK073(pu)006:281: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK073(pu)006:282: shin tu sbyang la rab gnas shing //
NK073(pu)006:283: dkyil 'khor ma lus brnyes pa yi //
NK073(pu)006:287: thos bsam bsgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK073(pu)006:288: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyi bzung //
NK073(pu)006:290: sbyangs pa med pa'i gang zag la /
NK073(pu)006:291: gsang sngags rtogs pa'i skal ba med /
NK073(pu)006:292: des na sde snod gsum gyi don la sbyangs pas gsang sngags mthong bas na /
NK073(pu)006:294: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK073(pu)006:295: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK073(pu)006:298: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK073(pu)006:299: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK073(pu)006:302: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK073(pu)006:303: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK073(pu)006:305: des na rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa'i gnas thabs nam /
NK073(pu)006:306: dper na ri bo'i rgyal po lta bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:307: ri bo mchog rab la ri bdun dang lcags ris
NK073(pu)006:308: bskor ba'i mtho dman gyi bye brag gi dpe dang
NK073(pu)006:309: / 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po la /
NK073(pu)006:310: mkhar la sogs pa'i rgyal po dang blon po dang 'bangs dang rim pas bskor ba'i dpes /
NK073(pu)006:311: rim pa bzhin du 'og ma rnams 'khor dang snod dang lam stegs lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:312: dkyus kyi 'bru gnon pa'i skabs su yang theg pa'i bshad pa la /
NK073(pu)006:313: skas kyi rim pa'i dpe dang /
NK073(pu)006:314: rta dang glang dang rkyang gi dpe dang khang pa sgo mang gi dpes rgyas par ston to //
NK073(pu)006:315: des na gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK073(pu)006:316: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK073(pu)006:317: dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK073(pu)006:318: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK073(pu)006:319: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK073(pu)006:320: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK073(pu)006:321: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK073(pu)006:322: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK073(pu)006:327: ro myong ba gsum gyi dpes mtshon nas zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:328: nyan thos kyi dka' thub gtsang sbra dag spyod spong
NK073(pu)006:329: len lus ngag gi bya ba gtso che ba snod
NK073(pu)006:331: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba ces pa phyi rgyud sde gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:332: kri ya lus ngag yid gsum 'dul ba gtsor che ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:333: u pa ya las ting nge 'dzin gtso che bas dgongs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:334: gsang ba ni yo ga ste /
NK073(pu)006:335: chos nyid stong pa nyid gsang ba gsum /
NK073(pu)006:336: spyod pa gtsang spra gtsor len pas 'dul ba dang mthun la /
NK073(pu)006:337: de'i thog tu lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs
NK073(pu)006:338: su bsgrub pa nyams su len pa bcud blugs pa
NK073(pu)006:340: de lta bu'i don la brten te thob bya'i ngo
NK073(pu)006:341: bo 'khor 'das dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin sems nyid
NK073(pu)006:344: dbyer med pa kun tu bzang po gsum lhun gyis grub la /
NK073(pu)006:345: gong gi don de nyid las gzhan du ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:346: der snang ba ni chos thams cad bdag nyid chen
NK073(pu)006:347: po las mi gzhan pas ngo bo la rgyu 'bras
NK073(pu)006:348: ma dmigs kyang 'og ma la stos na 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:349: lta bur snang bas ro myong ba lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:350: tshig bsnol te mngon pa dang zhes pas mngon pa'i sde snod te /
NK073(pu)006:351: gzhi chos can du phung po dang khams dang skye mched kyi rnam grangs rnams /
NK073(pu)006:352: rtsa ba dang yan lag dang nyid lag la sogs pa phra mor 'byed pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:353: 'dir de lta bu'i shes rab dang ldan pa snod lta bu la /
NK073(pu)006:354: sku dang zhes pas ma h+aa yo ga ste /
NK073(pu)006:355: zhus len phra men 'phel rgyas kyis bstan par snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:356: phung po lnga snang la ma dmigs rigs lnga /
NK073(pu)006:357: 'byung ba lnga snang la ma dmigs yum lnga /
NK073(pu)006:358: khams dang skye mched sems dpa' dang sems ma'i rang bzhin yin pa bzhin rtogs nas /
NK073(pu)006:359: ye nas de lta bu'i ngang las dus gsum du
NK073(pu)006:360: 'da' nyams med par gnas pa la ni bsgom pa
NK073(pu)006:361: ces bya ste / bcud blugs pa lta bu yin la /
NK073(pu)006:362: de'i ngang las phung po khams dang skye mched ma 'dres pa kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:363: yongs su rdzogs pas bzang mo //
NK073(pu)006:364: dbyer med pa byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa'i dus su yul yul can nam /
NK073(pu)006:365: shes bya shes byed dbyer med par rang rig mtha'
NK073(pu)006:366: dbus bral ba nam mkha' lta bu lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:367: pa ni mthar phyin pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:368: rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtogs pa /
NK073(pu)006:369: zhes bya bas ro myong ba lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:370: mdo sde zhes pa theg pa de nyid kyi las
NK073(pu)006:371: gsum gyi mtha' dbye nas mi dge ba spong zhing
NK073(pu)006:372: / dge rtsa dang du len pa'i ngang las bden pa gnyis bzung ste /
NK073(pu)006:373: don dam pa'i bden pa nam mkha'i ngos lta bu mnyam bzhag /
NK073(pu)006:374: rjes la sgyu ma lta bu la gnas nas bslab pa gsum gcig gi rgyur gcig gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:375: gcig gis gcig bskyed pa nyid la dam du byed pa ni snod lta bu yin la /
NK073(pu)006:376: gsung ces pas a nu yo ga ste /
NK073(pu)006:377: bstan pa kha gsal 'jug bde ba nyid la /
NK073(pu)006:378: gdug bya rnams kyi lam du gyur pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:379: rgyu chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba las /
NK073(pu)006:380: 'bras bu rig pa'i ye shes phyi nang gi chos thams cad du rang snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:381: snang tsam nyid na rig pa nyid lhar snang ba
NK073(pu)006:382: las ma togs par bar skabs kyi bsgyur byed mi
NK073(pu)006:383: mnga' ste / des na dbyings ye shes skad cig
NK073(pu)006:384: ma snga phyi med kyang rgyu 'bras tsam du smras
NK073(pu)006:385: nas de'i ting nge 'dzin grtsor byed pa ni bcud
NK073(pu)006:387: de'i sgo nas rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don
NK073(pu)006:388: mthong ba med par mngon du gyur pa ni ro
NK073(pu)006:390: des na rdzogs pa chen po la ni mthar thug
NK073(pu)006:391: pa'i don chos thams cad kyi de kho na nyid
NK073(pu)006:392: rang rig ye shes phyogs 'dzin phra ba'am ma grub
NK073(pu)006:393: pa'i ngang las zhen 'dzin rdul phra rab tsam yang
NK073(pu)006:394: mi gnas te / gtan nas zad nas mtha' dbus
NK073(pu)006:395: dang bral ba lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang las chos
NK073(pu)006:396: thams cad der 'du shing de las snang ba dang
NK073(pu)006:397: der 'dzin dang bral zhing cha shas dang du ma
NK073(pu)006:400: de lta bu'i rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa'i bsdu tshul
NK073(pu)006:401: bstan pa'i dgos pa yang 'dir theg pa dgu ston
NK073(pu)006:402: pa la / rgyu'i theg pa ni gsum du bsdus
NK073(pu)006:403: pas 'bras bu gar bsdu cha med pa rnams kyi
NK073(pu)006:404: pa la / ngo dang / yang gong ma bzhin
NK073(pu)006:405: du sde snod gsum du bsdu bar bzhed pa rnams
NK073(pu)006:406: pa la / ngo dang / ni / rgyal po
NK073(pu)006:407: dmangs su bsdu ba dang 'dra bas de dag gi
NK073(pu)006:408: phyogs shes par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:409: bdag gi bla ma bde bar gshegs pa rin po ches gsungs so //
NK073(pu)006:410: des na gsang sngags ni shas che bar longs sku'i bstan pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:411: mtshan nyid ni sprul bsdu 'ba' zhig gi bstan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:412: 'o na gsang sngags ni brjod pa'i rnam grangs tshig gi tshogs su yod la /
NK073(pu)006:413: longs skus ni rnams pa thams cad du mi gsungs te /
NK073(pu)006:414: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la /
NK073(pu)006:415: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK073(pu)006:416: zhes pas ston pa dang bstan par yang ma 'dzom mo zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:417: longs sku chen po brjod pa dang bral ba chos
NK073(pu)006:418: sku'i ngang las mi g.yo bar mnyam par bzhag pa
NK073(pu)006:419: 'ba' zhig lta bu'ang gdul bya'i snang ba yin la
NK073(pu)006:420: / byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyang bar byed pa /
NK073(pu)006:421: skus chos ston pa'i tshul yang gdul bya'i snang ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:422: des na gdul bya'i ngos nas chos gsungs pa yang mi 'gal la /
NK073(pu)006:423: yang rnam snang de nyid ni thun mong gi longs sku yin la /
NK073(pu)006:424: 'dir ni rigs lnga dbyer med drug pa'i ngo bo ste /
NK073(pu)006:425: longs spyod rdzoogs pa chen po yin pas ma 'gags
NK073(pu)006:426: pa dang ma dmigs pa'i ngos nas 'khor 'das gnyis
NK073(pu)006:428: zhes 'chad na gdul bya'i snang ba'i ngos nas chos gsungs pa yang mi 'gal te /
NK073(pu)006:429: drug pa'i lhub grub kyi sku'i mdzad pa las /
NK073(pu)006:430: ba spu'i rtsa ba re re nas kyang sprul pa'i
NK073(pu)006:431: sku ston 'khor gdul bya dang bcas pa grangs med
NK073(pu)006:432: pa phyogs bcur thug pa med pa 'phro zhes kun
NK073(pu)006:433: 'dus kyis gleng gzhi dang dgongs 'dus gleng bslang ba'i
NK073(pu)006:435: gsang ba'i snying po'i thun mong bcas gzhi'i le'u las /
NK073(pu)006:436: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje las byung ngo ces 'byung bas /
NK073(pu)006:437: sku gsung thugs rdo rje dbyer med pa ni drug pa'i sku'o //
NK073(pu)006:438: des na sprul pa'i sku'i mdzad pa thams cad kyang drug pa'i sku'i mi 'gags pa'i rtsal dang /
NK073(pu)006:439: gdul bya'i snang ba gnyis skad cig ma la lhun grub tu bzhugs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:440: don des na gdul bya ci tsam du gdul byed snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:441: gdul bya 'khor ba dongs sprugs thams cad rang byung
NK073(pu)006:442: gi ye shes 'ba' zhig tu lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK073(pu)006:443: dus su gdul bya med pas /
NK073(pu)006:444: de la ltos pa'i gdul byed kyang med de /
NK073(pu)006:445: des na sangs rgyas ces pa'i gdags gzhi dang bral bas sgra tsam yang ma grub po /
NK073(pu)006:446: ltos pa'i dbang gis tha snyad mi gnas kyang ngo
NK073(pu)006:447: bo nyid lhun grub kyi sku la ni chad pa
NK073(pu)006:448: mi manga'o // 'on kyang gdul bya'i mthun snang du 'char ba ni me long gzugs brnyan lta bu /
NK073(pu)006:449: de'ang 'gro 'ong dang spro bsdus dang bral ba ni chu zla lta bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:450: yul du ma grub rang sems nyid der snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:451: 'on kyang drug pa'i sku la tshig tu gsungs pa mi 'gags kyang /
NK073(pu)006:452: drug pa'i lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams lam mthar phyin
NK073(pu)006:453: pa sha stag yin pas tshig gis 'dul ba'i skye
NK073(pu)006:454: bos dben pas / bzhin dang me long gi tshul
NK073(pu)006:455: du ston pa'i dgongs pa nyid 'khor gyi rig pa
NK073(pu)006:456: la lhun gyis grub nas dgongs pa dbyer med du
NK073(pu)006:457: gyur pa la ma 'gags pa'i ngos nas bstan pa
NK073(pu)006:458: bos dben pas / zhes brjod de / shar tshul
NK073(pu)006:459: gyi ngos nas longs sku'i gsung me long zhes brjod
NK073(pu)006:460: bos dben pas / zhes brjod de / la /
NK073(pu)006:461: rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i ngos nas chos sku'i gsung
NK073(pu)006:464: de lta bu'i bstan pa de go phye ba'i 'khor
NK073(pu)006:465: lha mo skal ldan rnams la snang ba'i tshul ni
NK073(pu)006:466: / ston pa'i thugs nyid brjod pa tshig sprul pa po ting tshogs rnams su snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:467: gdul bya'i snang ba la sdud pa pos bsdus zhes dkyus kyi tshig tu bkod zhes kyang brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:468: des na po ti rnams rig can gyi khang thog tu babs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:469: so so'i gnas nas snang tshul la sogs pa rnams rgyus par shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:470: rim pa des na sde snod gsum du bsdur mi btub par bshad do //
NK073(pu)006:471: ngos bzung ba bye brag tu bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:472: gzhung 'di nyid theg pa che chung gnyis las chen po'o //
NK073(pu)006:473: de nyid las rgyu 'bras gnyis las 'dir 'bras bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:474: de la'ang phyi nang gnyis las 'di nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:475: nang pa la'ang bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK073(pu)006:476: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga dang /
NK073(pu)006:477: rdzogs pa chen po a ti gsum las 'di ma h+aa'o //
NK073(pu)006:478: 'o na 'dir ma h+aa yo ga yin na /
NK073(pu)006:479: theg pa 'og ma rnams dang theg pa gnyis po'ang ston pa ci zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:481: 'du ba mdo sde chos mngon dang /
NK073(pu)006:482: zhes pa gong du bstan pa ltar gyis theg pa thams cad 'di las 'byung zhing 'dir 'dus te /
NK073(pu)006:484: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK073(pu)006:485: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK073(pu)006:486: zhes pas 'bras bu tshol ba la zhugs pa /
NK073(pu)006:487: thams cad 'di nyid kyi thog tu dbab pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:488: nye bas mthong ba dang nye bas brgyud de mthong
NK073(pu)006:489: ba dang rim pas brgyud de mthong ba'i thabs su
NK073(pu)006:490: bstan pa dang / 'og ma rnams ni bre nang
NK073(pu)006:491: du phul shong ba'i theg pa yar ldan gyi dpe
NK073(pu)006:492: bstan pa dang / dang / gong ma gsum ni gcig gis gcig 'byin par ston te /
NK073(pu)006:493: bdud rtsi chen po'i rgyud las /
NK073(pu)006:494: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag kyang //
NK073(pu)006:495: 'bangs dang rje'u dang rgyal po'i rtsal //
NK073(pu)006:496: khyad par rtsal 'phang thag ring yang //
NK073(pu)006:497: gcig la gcig brten gcig gi ngang //
NK073(pu)006:499: spyir theg pa thams cad kyi spyi lung yin te brjod bya'i don thams cad kyang rang bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:500: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros shing 'dus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:501: brjod byed kyi tshig thams cad kyang rgyud 'di nyid
NK073(pu)006:502: gsung ba'i dus su gdul bya blo mtho dman thams
NK073(pu)006:503: cad la theg pa thams cad snang ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:504: des na rgyud 'di ni rgyud kyi rgyal po la sogs pa'i che ba bdun /
NK073(pu)006:505: shin tu gsang ba man ngag gi le'u bstan pas kyang gsal lo //
NK073(pu)006:506: de lta bu'i chos de la yang bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis las /
NK073(pu)006:507: bka' la'ang bzhir dbye ba gzhan du shes te /
NK073(pu)006:508: de la brten pa ni bstan bcos so //
NK073(pu)006:513: rtsod pa lhung len bzhir yang 'chad la /
NK073(pu)006:514: 'dir ni rgyud kyi tshig la 'jug pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:515: sgrub pa'i thabs la 'jug pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:516: rgyud kyi tshig la 'jug pa ni 'grel pa dang khog dbubs dang sa gcod rnams so //
NK073(pu)006:517: sgrub pa'i thabs la 'jug pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:518: bslab cing nyams su blang ba sgrub pa'i ngo bo ste /
NK073(pu)006:519: slob dpon sgegs pa'i rdo rjes /
NK073(pu)006:520: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam dang //
NK073(pu)006:521: phrin las sgrub pa'i las rim gyis //
NK073(pu)006:522: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya /
NK073(pu)006:523: zhes pas bdun du byas pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:524: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mchod pa bsnan pas brgyad du byas pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:525: slob dpon b+hi ma las sngags dang phyag rgya gnyis bsnan pas bcur byas pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:526: de yang de kho na nyid lta ba'i man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:527: zin chags med pa spyod pa'i man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:528: bkod pa dkyil 'khor gyi man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:529: mi 'da' ba dam tshig gi man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:530: rol pa phrin las kyi man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:531: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa'i man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:532: mi ga yo ba ting nge 'dzin gyi man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:533: gnas su stobs pa mchod pa'i man ngag dang /
NK073(pu)006:534: 'ching zlos sngags dang phyag rgya'i mang ngag go //
NK073(pu)006:536: de la yang shes rab spyan 'byed la sogs pa grangs mang yang /
NK073(pu)006:537: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba
NK073(pu)006:538: rnams so sor ma 'dres par khrigs chags su bstan
NK073(pu)006:540: de ni spyi dang bye brag gi ngos nas dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:541: gnyis pa de bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:542: man ngag thams cad rtsis mgos klad nas gzhom /
NK073(pu)006:543: zhes pas 'di la don gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:544: dang po rtsis mgo rnam pa lngas bshad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:545: khung smos pas yid ches par bya ba'i phyir slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:546: bstan pa la mtshan nges shing don gyi mdo tsam
NK073(pu)006:547: rtogs par bya ba'i phyir mtshan ci las btags pa
NK073(pu)006:548: dang / bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung
NK073(pu)006:549: tshugs par bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas btus te
NK073(pu)006:551: rtsom pa la don yod par bya ba'i phyir dgos ched su'i don du mdzad pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:552: shes shing khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir dbu zhabs su don dus bstan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:553: de la dang po mdzad pa'i slob dpon ni /
NK073(pu)006:554: bstan bcos mdzad pa'i tshad gsum ka dang ldan te /
NK073(pu)006:555: rab chos nyid bden pa'i don mthong /
NK073(pu)006:556: zhes pa dang po yan chad la 'jog kyang /
NK073(pu)006:557: 'dir ni rtsa chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bu mthar lam pa sangs rgyas ma rag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:558: 'bring yi dam lha'i zhal mthong zhes pa yo ga
NK073(pu)006:559: man chad pa dag gis yi dam lha yi zhal
NK073(pu)006:560: mthong ba ni / tshogs lam chen po bar yang brjod na /
NK073(pu)006:561: 'dir sku gsum dbyer med he ru ka lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:562: lung gi khrag thung dgu dang /
NK073(pu)006:563: de la sogs pa rgyal po dkyil 'khor ma lus pa mthong bas /
NK073(pu)006:564: sgom lam gyi rmi lam dang sgra snyan dang dngos
NK073(pu)006:565: su lung bstan pa rnam pa gsum yang rdzogs par
NK073(pu)006:566: nges te / nyid mthar lam la bzhugs pa'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:567: tha ma rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:568: gzhi bzhag yin pas na gsum ka 'dzom pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:569: de yang sku che ba'i yon tan gyi ngos nas pad+ma las brdzun te skyes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:570: dam pa'i chos la zhugs nas sang kra ha gsan
NK073(pu)006:571: pa'i dus su yo ga sum cu rtsa gsum gyi
NK073(pu)006:573: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad grub pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:574: mes sbyangs pas ma tshig pa la thams cad ngo mtshar du gyur pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:575: bod yul du byon nas mi ma yin thams cad
NK073(pu)006:576: btul nas bod la phan btags pa la sogs te
NK073(pu)006:577: / rgyas par gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:578: bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par
NK073(pu)006:579: bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gar
NK073(pu)006:580: gtogs na / rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying po
NK073(pu)006:581: las btus shing de'i dbang gis phyogs ni de nyid
NK073(pu)006:582: de tan tra sde bco brgyad kyi rtsa ba yin
NK073(pu)006:583: pas ma h+aa yo ga ces kyang brjod la /
NK073(pu)006:584: don gyi rtsa ba'i bzhag so a ti yo ga yin pas a ti yo gar bsdu'o //
NK073(pu)006:585: 'o na lta ba thams cad ston pas theg pa spyi'i lung yang zer la /
NK073(pu)006:586: rdzogs chen gcig tu smra ba ci zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:587: de ni rgyal khams kyi lo rgyus brjod pa mang po brjod kyang /
NK073(pu)006:588: rgyal po de'i zhing khams zer ba min pa 'bangs
NK073(pu)006:589: so so'i zhing khams so so zhes mi smos pa
NK073(pu)006:590: bzhin / thams cad rdzogs pa chen po las snang zhing rdzogs chen du 'dus la /
NK073(pu)006:593: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK073(pu)006:594: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK073(pu)006:596: 'di mdzad pa'i tshul ni rdzogs pa chen po'i lo rgyus las kyang bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:597: 'dir ni slob dpon gyis sngon du mchims phu dang
NK073(pu)006:598: sman lung gnyis su gsang ba'i snying po tshar gnyis
NK073(pu)006:600: der bsam yas rab gnas mdzad pa'i gong du rje 'bangs nyer lnga 'tshogs nas /
NK073(pu)006:601: rgyud kyi le'u bcu gsum pa'i /
NK073(pu)006:602: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog /
NK073(pu)006:603: la sogs pa'i the tsom dris pa'i lan du gral du dkyus 'di nyid mdzad pa lags skad do //
NK073(pu)006:604: gang zag gang gi don du mdzad na phyi rabs
NK073(pu)006:605: pa lam pa rnams kyis 'di nyid kyi don lta
NK073(pu)006:606: ba'i ngo bo shes shing khong du chud pa'i phyir
NK073(pu)006:608: rgya che ba mos pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:609: chung ba la mos pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:611: de la dang po ni 'jig rten phyal pa nas
NK073(pu)006:612: a ti'i khyad par gyi lta khyad la sogs bskol
NK073(pu)006:613: mdo drug gam brgyad kyis ston pa de /
NK073(pu)006:614: 'dir bstan pas de gdar sha gcod pa'i phyir theg
NK073(pu)006:615: pa thams cad la mkhas par 'gyur bas rgya che
NK073(pu)006:616: ba la mos pa'i don to //
NK073(pu)006:617: chung ba la mos pa'i don yang lta ba'i rnam
NK073(pu)006:618: grangs de dag dkyus nyung ngu 'dir bsdus te bstan
NK073(pu)006:619: pas / de nyams su blangs pas shes pas lta ba thams cad la mkhas te /
NK073(pu)006:620: des na gzhung mang po blo la mi shongs pa' don du byung bas rgya chung ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:621: don la mos pa'i don du'ang mdzad de /
NK073(pu)006:622: tshig tshogs la skrags cing don gcig pu la mos
NK073(pu)006:623: pa rnams rang gi blo tshod dang mthun pa'i lta
NK073(pu)006:624: ba'i dgos pa nyams su lon nas mthar rdzogs pa
NK073(pu)006:625: chen po'i don mngon du snang ba'i phyir gzhung nyung
NK073(pu)006:627: gang zag gcig gi lam mthar thos pas so //
NK073(pu)006:628: mtshan bstan pa ni spyir lnga ste /
NK073(pu)006:633: yul lag btags pa dang rnam pa lnga las don las btags pa ste de la 'ang bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:634: don gyi gtso bo las btags pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:635: rnam grangs las btags pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:636: don mdor bsdus pa las btags pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:637: don rang gi ngo bo las btags pa las /
NK073(pu)006:638: 'dir rang gi ngo bo las btags pas lta ba ces pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:639: dpe las btags pas phreg ba ces so //
NK073(pu)006:640: dbu zhabs su don bsdus bstan pa ni gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:642: gnyis pa rtsis mgo rnam pa lnga po de dkyus gzhung nas ji ltar bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:644: bskyud byang zhes pa sdebs sbyor spangs te zhu ba thad sor lan btab pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:646: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK073(pu)006:647: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags /
NK073(pu)006:648: zhes pa la sogs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying po yin par bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:649: mtshan ci las btags pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:650: zhabs nas lta ba'i gsang ba 'di /
NK073(pu)006:651: zhes pa'i dpe don gnyis kyis bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:652: gang gi ched du mdzad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:653: gsang sngags kyi rigs su byung zhing skal ldan gyi don du mdzad de /
NK073(pu)006:654: gzhung las skyes mchog yod na 'phrad gyur cig /
NK073(pu)006:656: yang slob dpon smros pa ni gsang sngags byin rlabs
NK073(pu)006:657: kyi lam pa yin pas bka' drin chen po rjes
NK073(pu)006:659: mos gus rgyun mi chad pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:660: mtshan ni phyogs la mgo mi rmongs shing don mdor bsdus pa rtogs par bya ba'i dgos pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:661: don ched ni nyan pa po spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK073(pu)006:662: snod dang bcud du 'dzom pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:663: dbu zhabs su don bsdus bstan pa'i sa gcod kyi dgos pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:664: dper na rta dkyus kyis bya 'drongs na dkyus 'jug
NK073(pu)006:665: de las rjes su mi 'da' ba dang 'dra bar
NK073(pu)006:666: / sa gcod glo glor sa gcod na bstan pa'i
NK073(pu)006:667: dkyus mi 'khyams shing mgo mi rmongs pa'i don no
NK073(pu)006:668: / // des na don de dag gis ni bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:669: des gong ma spyi dang bye brag rnam pa gnyis kyis dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:670: de gnyis bsdoms pas ni dgos pa'i don kyis khog dbubs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:671: spyi don gnyis pa dkyus kyi sa gcod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:672: gsum pa tshig gi 'bru gnon pa gnyis thun mong du khre'u ru ston to //
NK073(pu)006:674: sa gcod pa la spyi don gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:678: de la klad kyi don la gnyis kyi mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:679: lta ba dang theg pa la sogs pa khyad par du bsdus pa'i bskyud byang zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:680: 'dir shugs las bshad par dam bcas pa nyid kyang gsal te /
NK073(pu)006:681: de yang lta ba ni 'jig rten pa'i lta ba bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:682: 'das pa'i lta ba dgu dang bcu gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:683: de la 'jig rten pa'i lta ba bzhi ni /
NK073(pu)006:684: ma rtogs pa phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:685: log par rtogs pa mur thug pa dang mu stegs pa gnyis dang bzhi'o //
NK073(pu)006:687: nyan thos rang rgyal byang sems dang gsum /
NK073(pu)006:689: gsang sngags nang pa gsum dang spyir bcu gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:690: 'di la la dag gis lta ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:691: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba bzhi ste rang rang gi
NK073(pu)006:692: ma thong snang de la 'bras bu med cing 'khor
NK073(pu)006:693: ba las mi ldog pa'i don gyi na lta ba
NK073(pu)006:694: ces bya ste / theg pa ni theg pa dgu
NK073(pu)006:695: pos rten gyi gang zag gang yin pa de theg
NK073(pu)006:696: pa de nyid kyi sgor zhugs te bar du chud
NK073(pu)006:697: ma zos shing rang gi 'bras bu la sbyor zhing
NK073(pu)006:698: skyol bar byed pas na theg pa zhes bya ste
NK073(pu)006:699: ces bya ste / / nang tshan dgu'i lta ba'i zhes brjod la /
NK073(pu)006:700: sogs khongs su spyod pa bsdu ba rnam pa thams cad du mthun /
NK073(pu)006:701: de lta bu de la lta ba'i brtag bya'i ngo bo ni so so'i mthong snang gi chos so //
NK073(pu)006:702: rtogs par bya ba'i thabs ni /
NK073(pu)006:703: theg pa so so'i gzhal bya'i gtan tshigs rnams so //
NK073(pu)006:704: lta ba'i ngo bo ni lam gyi gnas skabs so //
NK073(pu)006:705: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab dang /
NK073(pu)006:706: des don rnyed nas mi dmigs pa'i shes rab gnyis so //
NK073(pu)006:707: bye brag ni gong du bstan pa'i lta ba bcu gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:708: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta rim dgu'i nges tshig ni /
NK073(pu)006:709: mthong bya'i don gang yin pa de rig pa la lhun gyis grub nas /
NK073(pu)006:710: yo ga man chad rnams ni zhen 'dzin dang bcas la /
NK073(pu)006:711: nang pa ni yul med rang gsal gyi nyams rnyed pa tsam mo //
NK073(pu)006:712: lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs ni /
NK073(pu)006:713: dad pa bskyed pa dang mos gus che ba dang //
NK073(pu)006:714: rgyu 'bras phra ba'i phra ba la'ang 'dzem pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:715: dkar po'i las phra ba'ang len cing nag po'i las phra ba'ang spong pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:717: phyal pa nas rdzogs pa chen po'i bar bcu gsum
NK073(pu)006:718: gyi gong 'og gi khyad par gong nas gong du
NK073(pu)006:720: yon tan ni lam gyi gzhi zin ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:721: lta ba med pa'i skyon ni /
NK073(pu)006:722: rnam par dkar ba'i chos spyod bcu la 'bad kyang
NK073(pu)006:723: zag bcas 'ba' zhig tu snang gi byang chub la
NK073(pu)006:724: mi reg pa'o // de ltar dgu po de ni theg pa dgu'i lta ba'i khyad par brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:725: dang zhes pas lta ba'i khyad par bcu gsum du dbyer yang /
NK073(pu)006:726: gong ma bzhi pos 'khor ba las sgrol bar mi nus pas /
NK073(pu)006:727: rgyu'i theg pas nyams su blangs te khams gsum las
NK073(pu)006:728: 'das shing 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i nus pa dang
NK073(pu)006:729: ldan pas / theg pa zhes smos te /
NK073(pu)006:730: de yang theg pa'i nges tshig ni /
NK073(pu)006:734: 'dir theg pa'i don gyis na theg pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:735: de'ang dpe bzhi'i ngos nas ston te /
NK073(pu)006:736: sdug bsngal las sgrol ba'i dpe gru gzings lta bu dang /
NK073(pu)006:737: 'og ma rnams gong ma las yar ldan gyi dpe glang po che lta bu dang /
NK073(pu)006:738: gdul bya'i blo tshod dang sbyar ba'i dpe rta lta bu dang /
NK073(pu)006:739: brtson 'grus kyi dpe rkyal mkhan lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:740: de la gru gzings kyi dpe ni /
NK073(pu)006:741: theg po'i ngo bo ni nyan thos kyi theg pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:742: de'i sgor 'jug pa'i rten gyi gang zag ni /
NK073(pu)006:743: 'di theg pa'i don gyis na theg pa ste rten no //
NK073(pu)006:744: 'dis theg pa'i don gyis na theg pa ste nyan thos kyi theg pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:745: 'di las theg pa'i don gyis na theg pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:746: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba bzhis bsdus pa'i khams gsum gyi chos thams cad do //
NK073(pu)006:747: 'dir theg pa'i don gyis na theg pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:748: dgra bcom pa zung bzhi ya brgyad do //
NK073(pu)006:749: gang zag dbang po'i tha ma'i 'bring rang rgyal ba'i rten gyi gang zag ni /
NK073(pu)006:751: rang rgyal brten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis lugs 'byung ldog ni /
NK073(pu)006:752: 'dis theg pa don gyis ste gru gzings lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:753: khams gsum gyi thog tu nyan thos bsnan pas ni 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:754: rang sangs rgyas yid bzhin bde mchog gis ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:755: gang zag dbang po tha ma'i rab ni /
NK073(pu)006:756: 'di theg pa ste mi lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:757: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa bden pa gnyis ni 'dis theg pa ste gru gzings lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:758: khams gsum gyi thog tu dman pa gnyis ni /
NK073(pu)006:759: 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:760: mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa bcu gcig kun tu
NK073(pu)006:761: 'od kyis ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta bu'o
NK073(pu)006:762: // dbang po 'bring gi tha ma kri ya'i rten
NK073(pu)006:763: gyi gang zag ni 'di theg pa ste mi lta
NK073(pu)006:764: // bu'o // des 'jug pa'i yul kri ya'i theg
NK073(pu)006:765: pa ni 'dis theg pa ste gru gzings lta bu'o
NK073(pu)006:766: // bu'o // // khams gsum dang dman pa gsum
NK073(pu)006:767: dang lam ring ba rnams ni 'di las theg pa
NK073(pu)006:769: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:771: u pa ya'i rten gyi gang zag ni 'di theg pa ste mi lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:772: u pa ya'i theg pa ni 'dis theg pa ste gru gzings lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:773: khams gsum dang kri ya man chad ni 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:774: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gis ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:775: dbang po 'bring gi rab ni 'di theg pa ste mi lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:776: de 'jug pa'i yul yo ga'i theg pa ni 'dis theg pa ste gru gzings lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:777: khams gsum u pa ya dang bcas pa ni 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:778: stug po bkod pa'i sa mngon du byas pa ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:779: dbang po rab kyi tha ma ni 'di theg pa ste mi lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:780: ma ha'i theg pa ni 'dis theg pa ste gru gzings lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:781: khams gsum yo ga man chad dang bcas pa ni 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:782: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:783: dbang po rab kyi 'bring gi rten gyi gang zag ni 'di theg pa ste mi lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:784: des 'jug pa'i yul a nu yo ga ni 'dis theg pa ste gru gzings lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:785: khams gsum ma h+aa yo ga man chad ni 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:786: a nu yo ga'i bdal ba chos nyid kyi sa ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:787: dbang po yang rab kyi rten gyi gang zag ni 'di theg pa ste mi lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:788: de'i 'jug pa'i yul rdzogs pa chen po ni 'dis theg pa ste gru gzings lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:789: khams gsum gyi thog tu theg pa brgyad po ni 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:790: kun tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i sa mngon
NK073(pu)006:791: du byas pa ni 'dir theg pa ste skams lta
NK073(pu)006:792: bu'o // des na dpe gru gzings de la spang
NK073(pu)006:793: bcos legs par byas pa'i rten 'brel 'dzom pa dang
NK073(pu)006:794: bu'o // / nang du zhugs pa'i mi rnams kyis
NK073(pu)006:795: thabs gzabs te gru bca' ba'i thabs la 'bad pa
NK073(pu)006:796: bu'o // / dang / mnyan pa mkhas pas ma
NK073(pu)006:797: yengs par mnyan na chu las brgal te pha mthar
NK073(pu)006:798: bu'o // / dang / phyin la / bcos ma
NK073(pu)006:799: legs pa dang nang gi mi rnams brtson 'grus chung
NK073(pu)006:800: ste gru ma bcos mnyan pa med na chud za
NK073(pu)006:802: chu nang du 'chi ba bzhin theg pa so so'i
NK073(pu)006:803: sgor zhugs nas lta spyod sgom pa rnams le lo
NK073(pu)006:804: dang snyoms las kyis phyal bar dor na /
NK073(pu)006:805: theg par zhugs pa ltar snang yang 'bras bu la
NK073(pu)006:806: mi sbyor ste 'khor ba'i khams su zag par 'gyur
NK073(pu)006:807: ro // gru'i bcas thams cad tshang zhing skyes bu
NK073(pu)006:808: brtson 'grus dang ldan yang mnyan pa mkhan med na
NK073(pu)006:809: chu las phar brgal ba'i thabs med pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:810: theg pa'i bcas thams cad rdzogs nas rten gyi gang
NK073(pu)006:811: zag brtson 'grus dang ldan yang skya ba 'dzin pa
NK073(pu)006:812: dang / 'dra ba'i rdo rje slob dpon med na 'khor ba las brgal bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK073(pu)006:813: des na gru gzings kyi dpes bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:814: theg pa yar ldan glang po che'i dpes bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:815: mi khur bcu rgyab khal dang bcas pa glang po che 'phra bu gcig gi rgyab na shongs la /
NK073(pu)006:819: thal dkar la sogs pa rnams /
NK073(pu)006:820: 'og ma 'og ma rgyab khal dang bcas pa bcu
NK073(pu)006:821: bcu gong ma gong ma re re'i khal la rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:822: / dpe de bzhin du nyan thos theg pa rgyud dang bcas pa rang rgyal la rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:823: de rgyu dang 'bras bu bcas pa byang chub sems dpa' la rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:824: de rgyu dang 'bras bu bcas pa rnams kri ya la rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:825: de rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa u pa ya la rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:826: de rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa yo ga la rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:827: de bzhin du nang pa rnam gsum yang 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:828: dang bcas pa rim pa bzhin rdzogs pa chen po
NK073(pu)006:829: la rdzogs te / dper na gsang sngags nang pa
NK073(pu)006:830: lta bu gcig tu zhugs kyang yo ga man chad
NK073(pu)006:831: rnams spangs nas bzhag pa lta bu ma yin te
NK073(pu)006:832: la rdzogs te / / ngo bo nyid kyis gong ma la lhun gyis rdzogs la /
NK073(pu)006:833: 'og ma la ma brten par gong ma mi mthong
NK073(pu)006:834: ba ni theg pa dgu rim pa bzhin du skas
NK073(pu)006:836: 'on kyang thad sor 'dus pa'i dus su gdul bya'i blo tshod dang sbyar ba'i dpes bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:837: rta mgyogs pa gcig la skyes bu rtsal dang ldan
NK073(pu)006:838: pa gcig gis zhon na thogs pa med par gnas
NK073(pu)006:839: su phyin la / rtsal chung gcig gis zhon na
NK073(pu)006:840: gnas su mi phyin pa'i thog tu bar ma dor
NK073(pu)006:842: de bzhin theg pa'i mthar thug a ti lta bu gcig la /
NK073(pu)006:843: dbang po'i bye brag dgur na bstan pa'i blo yang rab lta bu gcig gis nyams su blangs na /
NK073(pu)006:844: rtogs pa'i rig pa skad cig la 'bras bu sangs rgyas su snang la /
NK073(pu)006:845: rtsal chung dang 'dra ba'i nyan thos dag rang rgyal gyi rten gyi gang zag gcig zhugs na /
NK073(pu)006:846: shes rab kyi snod bcud mi 'dzom pa'i dbang gis nyan thos rang gi 'bras bu'ang med la /
NK073(pu)006:847: a ti'i don yang mi snang bas bar ma dor chud za ba lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:848: rta bul ba la mi rtsal chen gyis zhon na'ang gnas su myur bar mi phyin la /
NK073(pu)006:849: rtsal chung gis zhon na rkyen du 'dzom bar ma
NK073(pu)006:850: dor chud mi za zhing dal bus gnas su skyal
NK073(pu)006:851: bar byed pa dang 'dra bar nyan thos kyi theg
NK073(pu)006:852: pa lta bu la dbang po yang rab gcig zhugs
NK073(pu)006:853: kyang / bcud kyis snod mi tshim pa'i dbang gis 'bras bu sangs rgyas myur du mi snang la /
NK073(pu)006:854: rtsal chung dang 'dra ba'i nyan thos kyi gang zag
NK073(pu)006:855: gis nyams su blangs na de nyid kyi 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:856: snang bas snod bcud 'dzom ste chud mi za ba'o
NK073(pu)006:857: // des na theg pa rim pa dgu kun gyi gong 'og rim pa bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK073(pu)006:858: brtson 'grus kyi dpe rkyal gyi bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:859: chu la rkyal ba yang brtson 'grus drag pos rkyal na thad du gcod la /
NK073(pu)006:860: brtson 'grus zhan pas rkyal na gzhol phyogs su gcod pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:861: rten gyi gang zag theg pa gang gi sgor zhugs kyang /
NK073(pu)006:862: so so'i gzhung bzhis brtson 'grus drag pos nyams su blangs na /
NK073(pu)006:863: 'bras bu la myur bar sbyor la /
NK073(pu)006:864: brtson 'grus zhan par gyur na lam myur bar mi
NK073(pu)006:865: chod cing 'bras bu la myur bar mi sbyor bas
NK073(pu)006:866: / brtson 'grus kyi dpe rkyal gyis bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:867: la la dag rkyal pa'i dpe ni /
NK073(pu)006:868: gsang sngags nang pa'i lam gyi dpe yin te /
NK073(pu)006:869: chu srog gcod pa'i ngo bo yin pa las de nyid la bslab te /
NK073(pu)006:870: byang nas chu la bde blag tu dbang bsgyur te
NK073(pu)006:871: chu'i 'jigs pa las thar nas pha rol du 'gro
NK073(pu)006:872: ste / gzhan yang de las 'dren pa dang 'dra bar /
NK073(pu)006:873: khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa dug gsum dang dug
NK073(pu)006:874: lnga rgya mtsho chen po dang 'dra bar rgya che
NK073(pu)006:875: la gting zab pa dang brgal dka' ba des /
NK073(pu)006:876: 'gro ba rnams kyi thar pa'i srog gcod par byed pa nyid /
NK073(pu)006:877: rkyal dang 'dra ba'i thun mong ma yin pa'i theg
NK073(pu)006:878: pa de'i nang du yang nyon mongs nyid thabs kyi
NK073(pu)006:879: khyad par lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyis dngos
NK073(pu)006:880: su nyams su blangs pas chu'i 'jigs pa las thar
NK073(pu)006:881: ba bzhin ma spangs gnas su dag pa rang byung
NK073(pu)006:882: ye shes su lhun gyis grub nas /
NK073(pu)006:883: gzhan yang de nyid la sbyor bar byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:884: des na nang pa nyid kyi dpes bshad do //
NK073(pu)006:885: theg pa khang pa sgo mang gi dpes bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:886: khang pa la sgo mang po yod kyang gang la zhugs kyang nang du phyin pa dang 'dra bar /
NK073(pu)006:887: theg pa dgu gang gi sgo nas zhugs kyang 'bras
NK073(pu)006:888: bu mthar thug mngon du ma byas kyi bar du
NK073(pu)006:889: lam gyi ngo bo yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:890: dus nye ring tsam min pa bar ma dor dus 'da' ba med pa'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:891: des na khang pa sgo mang gi dpe dang /
NK073(pu)006:892: yar ldan glang po'i dpe dang /
NK073(pu)006:893: rim pa bzhin du 'dzegs pa skal kyi dpe rnams tha dad par mi bsam ste /
NK073(pu)006:894: ston pa'i lung dang dam pa'i man ngag thams cad las gsungs so //
NK073(pu)006:895: des don gyi gtso bo lta ba rgyas par bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:896: sogs kyis spyod pa ston te /
NK073(pu)006:897: 'jig rten pa log pa'i dka' thub 'chad pa rnams dang /
NK073(pu)006:898: 'jig rten las 'das pa theg pa dgu'i spyod pa rnams ston te /
NK073(pu)006:899: dkyus su 'chad par 'gyur bas shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:900: khyad par zhes pa gong ma'i lta ba bcu gsum
NK073(pu)006:901: po de dag skas kyi gdang bu ltar 'og ma
NK073(pu)006:902: las gong ma lta ba la sogs pa khyad par
NK073(pu)006:904: de'ang ltar pa'i phreng ba ces pas lta ba'i khyad
NK073(pu)006:905: par rnams so sor ma 'dres par phreng bzhin khrigs
NK073(pu)006:907: g.yu thang la sogs pa ltar gong mas 'og ma
NK073(pu)006:908: dngos su sun mi 'don pas phreng ba ces smos
NK073(pu)006:909: so // 'on gser gyi ri bdun ri rab dang bcas pa'i mtshan nyid brjod pa'i skabs su /
NK073(pu)006:910: 'og ma las gong ma ci ltar 'phags pa rtogs pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:911: 'dir yang rnam grangs gnas tshul phreng ba bzhin bstan pas /
NK073(pu)006:912: nang tshan gyi khyad par skas kyi gdang bu ltar rtogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:913: theg pa dgu re re la'ang 'jug sgo la sogs
NK073(pu)006:914: pa'i rnam grangs bzhi'am lnga'am rgyas par bcu gnyis la
NK073(pu)006:915: sogs par so sor bstan pas khyad par ce'o //
NK073(pu)006:917: spyir de rnams rgyas par ston pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:918: chos kyi sgo mo brgya khri bzhi stong yin la /
NK073(pu)006:919: de gsang ba'i snying por bsdus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:920: de shin tu gsang ba man ngag gi le'ura bsdus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:923: man ngag sbas pas rgyud na 'thor ba slob dpon gyis gzhung 'di nyid du bsdus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:924: 'dir yang don ma bsdus rgyas par bstan kyang tshig nyung bas bsdus pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:925: bskyud byang zhes pa don la brjed byang ste /
NK073(pu)006:926: rgyal 'bangs nyer lnga la sogs pa rnams kyis zhus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:927: de dag gi brjed kyis dogs pas tshig gi tshogs su bkod pas sam /
NK073(pu)006:928: yang na bstan bcos gzhan bzhin du rtsom pa'i 'dun
NK073(pu)006:929: pa sngon du ma btang bar zhus pa'i tshig de
NK073(pu)006:931: tha snyad sdebs sbyor ma byas pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:932: yang na slob dpon nyid kyi khengs pa bskyungs te /
NK073(pu)006:933: slob dpon blo gros mi zad pa bzhin bdag rang nyid kyi brjed byang tsam yin te /
NK073(pu)006:934: slob dpon nyid mthar lam pa yin pas don de
NK073(pu)006:935: nyid la brgyud de gzhan don du'ang 'gyur bar bstan
NK073(pu)006:936: des na mtshan bstan zhar la bshad pa dam bca'
NK073(pu)006:938: 'o na de ltar yin na bstan bcos gzhan la ni /
NK073(pu)006:939: dang po phyag 'tshal nas bshad par dam 'cha' ba yin la /
NK073(pu)006:940: 'dir dam bcas nas phyag 'atsala ba ma 'gal lam zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:941: de'ang bstan bcos rtsom pa'i dam bca' ba'i go cha sngon du song nas /
NK073(pu)006:942: de'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs zhi ba'i phyir phyag 'tshal ba shin tu 'thad de /
NK073(pu)006:943: dpe na 'jig rten pas phyir pa byed pa'i sbyor ba rjogs te /
NK073(pu)006:944: dngos gzhi la 'jug pa'i tshe rlung g.yor ba lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:945: klad don gyi gnyis pa phyag 'tshal ba la gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:946: mtshan gyi kha byang du bzhag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:947: gzhung mdzes pa'i rgyan du bzhag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:948: de la kha byang ltar na /
NK073(pu)006:949: 'dul ba 'chad na thams cad mkhyen pa phyag 'tshal na 'dul ba bshad par mngon la /
NK073(pu)006:950: 'jam dpal na mngon pa sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' la na mdo sde'o //
NK073(pu)006:951: rigs gsum la na kri ya /
NK073(pu)006:952: rigs bzhi la na u pa ya /
NK073(pu)006:953: rnam snang la na yo ga /
NK073(pu)006:954: rdo rje sems dpa' la na ma h+aa yo ga /
NK073(pu)006:955: bcom ldan 'das dpal sgron byed thugs rje'i rgyal po la na a nu yo ga /
NK073(pu)006:956: kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo zer na rdzogs pa chen po 'chad par mngon no //
NK073(pu)006:958: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nu dang rdo rje chos phyag 'tshal lo //
NK073(pu)006:959: zhes pas bcom ldan 'das ni theg pa sbyir mthun la /
NK073(pu)006:960: 'jam dpal ni mtshan nyid stong pa'i kha byang /
NK073(pu)006:961: rdo rje chos ni gsang sngags ston pa'i kha byang ste /
NK073(pu)006:962: des na dkyus kyi kha byang du bstan no //
NK073(pu)006:963: gzhung mdzes par byed pa'i rgyan la gnyis kyis phyag
NK073(pu)006:964: 'tshal ba'i gnas tshig gi don du bstan pa ni
NK073(pu)006:965: / bcom ldan 'das ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:966: 'di yang gzhung gi don gyis 'jig rten pa la ni bcom ldan 'das mi mnga' la /
NK073(pu)006:967: theg pa rim pa dgu dang sbyar na /
NK073(pu)006:968: dang po rgyu'i theg pa ltar na /
NK073(pu)006:969: nyan thos dang rang rgyal ba mthong sgom gyi lam gyis nyon mongs pa che 'bring rnams spangs pas /
NK073(pu)006:970: khams gsum las 'das te 'khor ba'i mtha' la mi gnas pa tsam /
NK073(pu)006:971: rang don lhun gyis grub pas bcom pa dang ldan yang 'das pa mi mnga' ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:972: byang chub sems dpa' gang gis tshogs lam du sems bskyed /
NK073(pu)006:973: sbyor lam du drod bzod bzhis bdag gnyis sbyangs nas /
NK073(pu)006:974: sa dang po la bden pa mthong bas las dang
NK073(pu)006:975: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa bcom kyang gnas skabs pa
NK073(pu)006:976: ste / shes bya'i sgrib pa mnga' bas so //
NK073(pu)006:977: sgom lam du shes bya'i sgrib pa rags pa bcom ste /
NK073(pu)006:978: sa bcu rim pa bzhin du bgrod nas pha rol
NK073(pu)006:979: tu phyin pa bcu rim pa bzhin du sbyangs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:980: tshul gyis sa bcu mthar phyin pa la /
NK073(pu)006:981: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis shes bya'i
NK073(pu)006:982: sgrib pa phra ba'i phra ba'ang skad cig ma dang
NK073(pu)006:984: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa la spang bya phra ba'ang mi mnga' bas bcom zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:985: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes zhes kyang bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:986: de'i ngang la rang don gyi bdud bzhi bcom lugs ni /
NK073(pu)006:987: 'dzin pa phra ba'ang mi mnga' yul dang yul can med pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:988: des 'bras bu nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga
NK073(pu)006:989: gtan nas bral te nam mkhar dngos po mi snang
NK073(pu)006:990: ba bzhin phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:991: de nyid la rgyu rkyen ma grub bas skad cig ma dang bral te 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:992: nam mkha' la gnyen po med pa bzhin chos nyid
NK073(pu)006:993: la gnyen po'i chos ma grub pas lha'i bu'i bdud
NK073(pu)006:994: bcom la / de'ang zhi ba phyogs gcig pa la gnas pa min te /
NK073(pu)006:995: ji lta ba de nyid las ma g.yos par ji
NK073(pu)006:996: snyed mkhyen pa'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas
NK073(pu)006:997: gdul bya'i don thogs chag med pas ldan zhes bya
NK073(pu)006:998: / de nyid bcom pas 'khor ba'i mtha' las 'das
NK073(pu)006:999: shing de la mi gnas pa mya ngan las 'das
NK073(pu)006:1001: gang gi ldan pa'i don gyi thugs rjes 'char tshul gyi /
NK073(pu)006:1003: bzhi bcom drug ldan mtha' gnyis las 'das pa'i don sprul pa'i sku'i mdzad pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1004: mthar phyin pa'i sangs rgyas kyi gzigs pa bzhis lho'i 'dzam bu'i gling pa /
NK073(pu)006:1005: dge sdig stobs che ba las kyi sa pa yin pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1006: yul bcu drug gi rgyal po la sh+aakya'i rigs mchog tu gyur pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1007: thun mong ma yin pa'i yab yum gnyis dang /
NK073(pu)006:1008: 'khor spyir gdul bya skal ldan mang zhing khyad par
NK073(pu)006:1009: du log par zhugs pa'i mu stegs 'khor tshogs mang
NK073(pu)006:1010: po dus gcig 'dul bar gzigs pas gdul bya'i don
NK073(pu)006:1011: dpag tu med pa grub pa'i don la gzigs pa
NK073(pu)006:1012: dang bzhi'o // de nas dpyid zla ra ba'i tshes
NK073(pu)006:1013: brgyad la yum gyi lhums su zhugs nas gdul bya
NK073(pu)006:1014: dang mthun pa'i mdzad pa rnams rgyas par byas nas
NK073(pu)006:1016: nee ra dza nar dka' thub rdzogs te dka' spyad kyis sku 'khogs par gyur pa la /
NK073(pu)006:1017: legs skyes mas 'o thug drangs nas sku mtshan dpe
NK073(pu)006:1018: can gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa ltar gyur pas
NK073(pu)006:1020: bcom ldan 'das tshe'i 'du byed la mnga' brnyes te /
NK073(pu)006:1021: bzhed pa bskal pa dpag tu med pa bzhugs la /
NK073(pu)006:1022: skad cig las mya ngan las 'da' bar bzhed na'ang mnga' brnyed te /
NK073(pu)006:1023: rang dbang thob pa'i 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1024: ngang las gdul bya le lo can la phan gdags
NK073(pu)006:1025: pa'i phyir 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa la /
NK073(pu)006:1026: mgar ba'i bus zhus pas lo gnyis shol bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1027: lha'i bu'i bdud ni bcom ldan 'das byang chub kyi
NK073(pu)006:1028: shing drung rdo rje'i gdan la sangs rgyas pa la
NK073(pu)006:1029: / snyigs ma'i dus kyi 'gro ba rnams kyis bskur ba 'debs pa de thugs su chud nas /
NK073(pu)006:1030: de bsal ba'i phyir zhal gyi mdzod spu la sogs pa sku'i gnas nas /
NK073(pu)006:1031: 'od zer bye ba drug cu drug cu phyungs nas /
NK073(pu)006:1032: lo ka pa dregs pa can zil gyis mnan te
NK073(pu)006:1033: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha'i bu dregs pa can
NK073(pu)006:1034: dag / de la phrag dog skyes nas 'dod pa'i dbang phyug la dris pa la /
NK073(pu)006:1035: dge sbyong go'u ta ma shing grib la 'dug pa'i 'od yin no //
NK073(pu)006:1036: 'di ma brlag na 'u bu cag gi 'dod khams
NK073(pu)006:1037: stong par 'od zer nas lha'i bu bye ba dung
NK073(pu)006:1039: 'khor ni za bar 'dod steng du mtshon cha'i char pa bab pa las /
NK073(pu)006:1040: bcom ldan 'das byams pa'i ting nge 'dzin las ma g.yos pas mtshon cha me tog tu gyur /
NK073(pu)006:1041: sgra mi snyan pa rnams dkon mchog gi sgra gyur nas /
NK073(pu)006:1042: sdig can mya ngan gyi khang bur zhugs pa ni lha'i bu'i bdud bcom pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1043: nyon mongs pa'i bdud ni sdig can gyi bu mo
NK073(pu)006:1044: dpal 'byor dang me tog mda' can la sogs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1045: dpung bye ba tsam me tog dang rgyan gyis brgyan
NK073(pu)006:1046: te / bslu brid kyi tshogs bslu ba byas kyang /
NK073(pu)006:1047: bcom ldan 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos pa'i bden pa'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK073(pu)006:1052: slar bcom ldan 'das la skyabs su mchis pas /
NK073(pu)006:1053: snga ma kho bzhin du gyur pa ni nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1055: dbang phyug ni tshogs gnyis mthar phyin pa'i dbang gis
NK073(pu)006:1056: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la mnga' mdzad cing
NK073(pu)006:1057: dbang bsgyur ba'o // gzugs bzang ba ni mtshan bzang
NK073(pu)006:1058: po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad bzang po
NK073(pu)006:1059: brgyad cus mthar phyin par spras pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1061: rtogs pas bdag don mthar phyin cing gdul bya'i don lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1063: che ba'i yon tan sangs rgyas kyi zhing dang sems can gyi gnas su rgyas la /
NK073(pu)006:1064: mo'u 'gal gyi bus gsung gi mtha' ma rtogs pa'ang bsdu'o //
NK073(pu)006:1065: ye shes ni ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa phra ba'i phra ba'ang mkhyen pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1066: brtson 'grus ni 'bad pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis
NK073(pu)006:1067: skad cig ma tsam yang mi g.yo ba ra gdul
NK073(pu)006:1069: 'das ni gong ma dang mthun no //
NK073(pu)006:1070: yo ga man chad kyi bcom ldan 'das gzugs sku'i mdzad pa de nyid la 'jog pa yin yang /
NK073(pu)006:1071: 'dir gsang sngags rnying ma'i bzhed dus u pa ya
NK073(pu)006:1072: zhar la gtang nas kri ya dang yo ga gnyis
NK073(pu)006:1073: ya'ang ldan te / kri ya'i ltar na /
NK073(pu)006:1074: a b+hi ra h'u kham zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1075: kham kha sa me'i sgras drangs na /
NK073(pu)006:1077: bden pa dbyer med kyi don chos nyid ma byung
NK073(pu)006:1078: ma skyes stong zhing bdag med nam mkha' ltar rtogs
NK073(pu)006:1079: pa'i dus na bdud bzhi bcom ste /
NK073(pu)006:1080: a a nu sa ta sarba d+harma'i sgras drangs na /
NK073(pu)006:1081: chos nyid ma skyes pas skye ba med pa'i don
NK073(pu)006:1082: mtha' dang bral ba nam mkha' lta bu'i don rtogs
NK073(pu)006:1083: pa'i ngang la phung po ma grub pas phung po'i
NK073(pu)006:1084: bdud bcom / b+hi ba yu zhes pa'i sgras drangs na /
NK073(pu)006:1085: rnam par rtog pa bcas te /
NK073(pu)006:1086: de ni bar chad kyi lha'i bu'i bdud yin te /
NK073(pu)006:1087: rnam rtog gis rnam grol thub tu mi ster zhing de'i gegs su gyur pas /
NK073(pu)006:1088: dpe de ni gong ma lta bu'i rtogs pa dang
NK073(pu)006:1089: ldan pa'i dus na rnam par rtog pa ming yang
NK073(pu)006:1090: med pas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1091: ra ra ga'i sgras cags pa'i rgyus /
NK073(pu)006:1093: nyon mongs pa'i bdud yin te gzung 'dzin khrag zhag
NK073(pu)006:1094: dang 'dra ba nyon mongs pa'i ngo bo phyed dka'
NK073(pu)006:1095: ba ni / rnam grol thob tu mi ster ba
NK073(pu)006:1096: nyid gong ma ltar stong zhing bdag med pa nam
NK073(pu)006:1097: mkhar ltar rtogs pa'i dus na ming yang med pas
NK073(pu)006:1099: h'u ha he tu'i sgras rgyu zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:1100: rgyu las dang nyon mongs pas 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi phung por smin te /
NK073(pu)006:1101: skad cig ma dang bcas pas skye 'jig can ni 'chi bdag gi bdud yin la /
NK073(pu)006:1102: de'ang gong ma ltar chos nyid kyi don rtogs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1103: dus na rgyu dag pas 'bras bu phung po mi
NK073(pu)006:1104: gnas des 'chi bdag gi bdud dag go //
NK073(pu)006:1105: de'i ngang la yo byad dang khrus dang gtsang sbra
NK073(pu)006:1106: dang lha drug gis rigs gsum gyi skur snang ba
NK073(pu)006:1107: dang ldan / de tsam na bcom pa'i don gyis 'khor ba'i mtha' las 'das /
NK073(pu)006:1108: ldan pa'i don gyis mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' las 'das so //
NK073(pu)006:1109: yo ga ltar na bcom ldan 'das ni /
NK073(pu)006:1110: b+ha ga nan b+hi ga nan ma ra ya ta tan /
NK073(pu)006:1114: ma ra ya ni bcom pa'am bsad pa /
NK073(pu)006:1116: de kho na nyid ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1117: de yang dang po la ta tan bshad na de kho na nyid la yang gsum te /
NK073(pu)006:1118: chos kyi dbyings rgyu rkyen ma grub pa stong zhing bdag med te mtha' brgyad dang bral ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:1119: spros pa dang bral ba'i de kho na nyid ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1120: de lta bu'i ngang las ma g.yos gzhin du chu'i
NK073(pu)006:1121: gzugs brnyan bzhin mngon par byang chub pa lnga'i sgo
NK073(pu)006:1122: nas lha'i sku phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan pa mtshan
NK073(pu)006:1123: ma'i rnam par gsal ba ni mchog dang thun mong
NK073(pu)006:1124: gi dngos grub thams cad de las snang ba'i mi
NK073(pu)006:1125: bslu ba'i de kho na nyid ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1126: de ltar gong gi de kho na nyid gnyis po
NK073(pu)006:1127: de me long dang gzugs brnyan bzhin ye nas dbyer
NK073(pu)006:1128: med de mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis
NK073(pu)006:1129: su med pa ni de kho na nyid chen po
NK073(pu)006:1130: zhes bya'o // de lta bu'i rtogs pa'i gding dang ldan pa'i dus su /
NK073(pu)006:1131: bdag gnyis kyi 'dzin pa dang bral bas bdud ni bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1132: de'i dbang gis bdag 'dzin gyis bar du ma chod par bgegs ni bsad /
NK073(pu)006:1133: de kho na nyid gsum dbyer med pa'i don dang ldan la /
NK073(pu)006:1134: de kho na nyid chen po'i don gyis mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas pas 'das so //
NK073(pu)006:1135: ma h+aa yo ga ltar na gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:1136: lta ba'i ngos nas phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su rtogs /
NK073(pu)006:1137: 'byung ba lnga yum lnga'i gang du rtogs te rtog
NK073(pu)006:1138: tshogs lhar dag nas tha mal pa'i phung po ma
NK073(pu)006:1139: dmigs pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1140: de'i ngang la rab yul lhar dag pas chags sdang
NK073(pu)006:1141: gi yul yul can gtan nas ma grub pas nyon
NK073(pu)006:1143: lha dang lha mo las ma gtogs pa'i gzhan pa phra ba'ang ma dmigs pa lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1144: snod bcud lha dang lha mor sangs rgyas pa'i ngang
NK073(pu)006:1145: las skad cig ma dang bral bas mi rtag pa
NK073(pu)006:1146: med do // 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom mo //
NK073(pu)006:1147: yang na ma h+aa yo ga rang gzhung gi spyod pa ltar na /
NK073(pu)006:1148: b+ha ga wa na zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1149: bcom ldan 'das zhes bya skal ldan zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1150: de ni b+ha ga'i sgras mkha' dbyings cis bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1151: yum gyi mkha' chos kyi dbyings rtogs pa dang ldan pa'i dus na /
NK073(pu)006:1153: ting nge 'dzin gyis phyag rgya chen po bzhi dang ldan pas dngos su bdud bzhi bcom pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1154: de'ang sku phyag rgya chen po ni rtogs pa sngon
NK073(pu)006:1155: du song ba dang ldan pa'i skyes bus ting nge
NK073(pu)006:1156: 'dzin gyis nyams su blang ba'i dus su yab yum
NK073(pu)006:1157: so so na lha dang lha mo'i sku phyag rgyar
NK073(pu)006:1158: gsal bar bsgom pa'i ngang la tha mal pa'i phung
NK073(pu)006:1159: po ming yang med pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1160: gzungs ma dam tshig gi mu tra'i lus la ye
NK073(pu)006:1161: shes kyi lha mo snang la rang bzhin med pa
NK073(pu)006:1162: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon ltar gsal bas /
NK073(pu)006:1163: phar yang ma chags te yul ma grub pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1164: tshur yang mi gos te bsgom par bya ba'i gnas
NK073(pu)006:1165: mi mthun pa dang gnyen po ma grub bas lha'i
NK073(pu)006:1167: ma skyes pa chos kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK073(pu)006:1168: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa bde ba chen po dang ldan pa'i dus na /
NK073(pu)006:1169: rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin du ldan pa'i ngang
NK073(pu)006:1170: la tha mal pa'i nyon mongs pa mi 'byung bas
NK073(pu)006:1171: de nyid bcom / 'phro 'du phrin las kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK073(pu)006:1172: gong ma'i ngang las lhag pa byang chub kyi sems
NK073(pu)006:1173: kyi 'phro 'dus thun mong dang thun mong ma yin
NK073(pu)006:1174: pa'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyis 'gro don byas kyang
NK073(pu)006:1175: sprul pa la skye 'chi mi mnga' bas /
NK073(pu)006:1177: phyag rgya bzhi'i don dang ldan pas ni ldan /
NK073(pu)006:1179: thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i bde ba'i ro sku nyams su bstar ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:1180: 'das pa'i mtha' la mi gnas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1181: de nyid ni skye ba med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas 'khor ba'i mtha' la mi gnas /
NK073(pu)006:1182: lung ltar na chos thams cad chos kyi dbyings spros
NK073(pu)006:1183: pa med pa gang gi ngo bor mi gnas shing
NK073(pu)006:1184: de las snang yang de nyid du lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:1186: dbyings kyi cha dang 'gags pa med pa'i longs spyod
NK073(pu)006:1187: rang byung ye shes kyi cha rtogs ma rtogs kyis
NK073(pu)006:1188: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad du snang ba dang
NK073(pu)006:1189: rang ldan pa ye shes kyi cha de tsam nyid
NK073(pu)006:1190: na dbyings ye shes gnyis kyis mtha' gnyis las 'das
NK073(pu)006:1192: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po byang chub sems kyi
NK073(pu)006:1193: ngang la phung po ngar snang yang ngo bo la
NK073(pu)006:1194: grub pa med pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1195: de'i ngang la gzung 'dzin gtan nas mi gnas pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1196: de lta bu'i rang byung ye shes gnyen po dang bral bas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1197: rang byung ye shes la skad cig ma dang bral bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:1198: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po sems kyi chos nyid
NK073(pu)006:1199: kyi ngang la rtogs pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1200: chos dang / ma rtog pa 'khor ba'i chos su
NK073(pu)006:1201: snang ba thams cad lhun gyis grub pas rang ldan
NK073(pu)006:1202: chos dang / / de lta bu'i ngang la phyogs zhen phra ba'ang mi gnas pas 'das so //
NK073(pu)006:1203: 'jam dpal gzhon nu ni mtshan nyid kyi kha byang yin la /
NK073(pu)006:1204: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje chos la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK073(pu)006:1206: gsang sngags phyi nang gi sdud pa po yin pas de'i kha byang du nges so //
NK073(pu)006:1208: don 'jam pa dang rtags 'jam pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:1209: don ni thugs chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin chos
NK073(pu)006:1210: nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang la mtha'i skyon
NK073(pu)006:1211: gyi zug du mi mnga' bas 'jam pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1212: rtags ni sku dngos su snang ba yang sku'i mi dge ba gsum dang /
NK073(pu)006:1214: thugs kyi gsum gtan nas mi gnas te /
NK073(pu)006:1215: de mi mthun pa'i phyogs ma grub pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1216: gzhon nu mtshan dpe dang ldan pa sha rgyas pa'i cha byad du bzhugs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1217: dpal ni bdag don du chos nyid ci lta ba bzhin rtogs pa'i ngang las ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK073(pu)006:1218: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa brnyes pa ni bdag gi dpal lo //
NK073(pu)006:1219: de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams la don de kho
NK073(pu)006:1220: na nyid ston cing yon tan de dag thob par
NK073(pu)006:1221: byed pa ni gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK073(pu)006:1222: gzhon nu ni don de nyid la skad cig ma
NK073(pu)006:1223: mi mnga' bas ngo bo nyid kyi rtag pa chen
NK073(pu)006:1224: po ste / bsgres rgud mi mnga' ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1225: rtags 'khor ba na bzhugs shing 'gro don mdzad na'ang
NK073(pu)006:1226: 'khor ba'i nyes skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags su
NK073(pu)006:1227: khye'u lo brgyad pa'i cha byad du mdzad nas 'khor
NK073(pu)006:1228: ba ma stongs sems can ma zad kyi bar du
NK073(pu)006:1229: 'gro don mdzad pas na gzhon nu'o //
NK073(pu)006:1230: gnas de nyid la'ang phyag 'atsala ba ngo bo nyid spyi don du bston pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1231: 'og ma dang bsdom ste 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK073(pu)006:1232: de zhes bsdud pa po ste /
NK073(pu)006:1233: gang zhe na rdo rje chos so //
NK073(pu)006:1234: rdo rje ni chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma
NK073(pu)006:1235: thams cad dang bral ba nam mkhar lta bur dus
NK073(pu)006:1236: gsum du mi 'gyur bas rdo rje dang /
NK073(pu)006:1237: de nyid rang snang bas gsal la 'gags pa med
NK073(pu)006:1238: pa rang byung gi ye shes kyis gnyis snang gi
NK073(pu)006:1239: chos thams cad nyid kyi dbyings su 'joms pas rdo
NK073(pu)006:1240: rje dang / de de gnyis kyang dbyings gang gi
NK073(pu)006:1241: dbyings na rig pa'i ye shes dngos po thams cad
NK073(pu)006:1242: dang bral ba nyid mi dmigs pa'i mtshan nyid can
NK073(pu)006:1244: de nyid gsal la 'gag pa med pa rang gsal bas rang byung gi ye shes dang /
NK073(pu)006:1245: de ye nas dbyer med pa mar dang chu'i dpe
NK073(pu)006:1246: bzhin bzhugs te mi phyed pa'i don kyi rdo rje
NK073(pu)006:1248: drug pa'i thugs lhag pa'i chos sku chen po ste /
NK073(pu)006:1249: rdo rje'i chos bdun dang yang ldan par shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1250: chos ni dbye ba med par mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1251: rtogs ma rtogs kyi snang bas 'khor 'das gnyis te
NK073(pu)006:1252: / de nyid rdo rje lta bu'i thugs rang byung
NK073(pu)006:1253: gi ye shes gnyis su med pa'i ngang las ma
NK073(pu)006:1254: g.yos shing mi phyed par bzhugs pas snying rje chen
NK073(pu)006:1256: thugs rjes gdung thag 'khor ba'i mthar la rje /
NK073(pu)006:1258: des na rdo rje dang chos kyang ye nas dbyer
NK073(pu)006:1259: med pa'i ngo bo drug pa'i dgongs pa nyid gdul
NK073(pu)006:1260: bya'i ngo la bstan pa'i ston par yang snang la
NK073(pu)006:1261: / de nyid du sdud par yang snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:1262: ston pa'i thugs ye shes nyid bstan par snang ba yang sdud par nus pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:1263: de'i go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du gsang sngags
NK073(pu)006:1264: phyi nang gi sdud pa por snang ba la rdo
NK073(pu)006:1266: la lar ni rgyud kyi ston par yang snang /
NK073(pu)006:1267: la lar ni dal gyi gtso bor yang snang bas so //
NK073(pu)006:1269: gong ma'i phyag 'tshal ba'i yul gnyis gzhi'i don te /
NK073(pu)006:1270: de la phyag 'tshal ba'i ngo bo spyi don du bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:1271: gang gis 'tshal na sngon byung du slob dpon pad+ma /
NK073(pu)006:1272: rjes 'jug rnal 'byor pa thams cad do //
NK073(pu)006:1274: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nu dang /
NK073(pu)006:1275: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje chos gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:1276: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis kyi kha byang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:1278: spyod pa ya rabs kyi phyag theg pa 'og ma dang mthun pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1279: sgrub pa thabs kyi phyag gzhung 'di nyid thos bsam sgom gsum gyis nyams su len pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1280: rtogs pa don gyi phyag mjal ba ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1281: mthar thug pa'i lta ba'i ngo bo dang /
NK073(pu)006:1282: phyag 'tshal ba'i gnas ye nas dbyer med pa nyid rig pa la gding du gyur pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1284: chu la chu dang mar la mar /
NK073(pu)006:1287: ci'i phyir phyag 'tshal ba la gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:1289: khyad par du 'tshal ba'i dgos ched do //
NK073(pu)006:1291: dang po ni 'jig rten pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1292: tshul mthun pas mos can drangs pa'i dgos ched de /
NK073(pu)006:1293: 'jig rten pa'i ya rab d+r+wa ma dag bya ba
NK073(pu)006:1294: gang dang gang byed kyang rang mos pa'i lha la
NK073(pu)006:1296: bya ba chud mi za ba dang tshul bstun pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1298: phyag 'tshal ba sngon du song bas bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:1299: des snang mun gyi dpes bsod nams ma yin pa dag nas /
NK073(pu)006:1300: des bskyed pa'i bar chod mi 'byung bar thugs dgongs mthar phyin pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1301: de ltar dgos pa gnyis dang ldan pa'i phyag de
NK073(pu)006:1302: slob dpon nyid kyis mdzad pas cho ga yi ge'i
NK073(pu)006:1303: dkyus su bkod mi dgos so zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:1304: dkyus su bkod pa'i dgos pa ni gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:1305: dang po slob dpon ya rab kyi tshul can du shes par bya ba'i phyir te /
NK073(pu)006:1306: slob dpon gyi dam bca' ba phyag dang bcas pa sngon du song bas /
NK073(pu)006:1307: phyi rabs pa gang zag gang zag gi rjes su
NK073(pu)006:1308: 'a jug pa rnams de la brten te 'jug nas
NK073(pu)006:1309: dkyus kyi don mthong bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1310: phyag gi yul gnyis bkod pas de la brten te
NK073(pu)006:1311: gang zag chos kyi rjes su 'brang ba rnams kyang
NK073(pu)006:1312: / don 'di mthar thug pa'i ngo bo yin par shes nas 'jug pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1314: phyi rab kyi nyan bshad mkhan tshogs sogs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1315: slob dpon nyid rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bu yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:1316: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor mun pa gzhi bral ltar /
NK073(pu)006:1317: bar chod gtan ma dmigs kyang phyag gi mchod pa la don dam mdzad pa'i /
NK073(pu)006:1318: phyi rabs pa rnams kyis de la brten te nyan
NK073(pu)006:1319: pa la sogs pa'i skabs su yon tan thams cad
NK073(pu)006:1320: kyi rtsa ba'i bla ma la rag las pas /
NK073(pu)006:1321: phyi rabs pa rnams kyis de la brten te nyan
NK073(pu)006:1322: pa la sogs pa'i skabs su yon tan thams cad
NK073(pu)006:1323: kyi rtsa ba'i bla ma la rag las pas /
NK073(pu)006:1324: thabs ci'i sgo nas kyang tshogs gsogs pa la 'bad par gdams pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1325: khyad par du phyag 'tshal ba'i 'thad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1326: 'jam dpal gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal bas gzhung gi kha byang ni gong du bstan /
NK073(pu)006:1327: 'dir shes rab kyi lha yin pas bshad pa bzhin
NK073(pu)006:1328: du 'tshal na shes rab rno ba'i dgos pa dang
NK073(pu)006:1330: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung mi 'gags
NK073(pu)006:1331: pa'i ngo bo yin pas gsung byin gyis rlobs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1333: de yang gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi khyad par shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1334: des na phyag 'tshal ba dkyus kyi rgyan du bkod pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1335: gling bzhi'i rgyan nyi ma yin pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:1336: yul thams cad kyi rgyan ri bo yin pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:1337: mi thams cad kyi rgyan rgyal po yin par bzhin du /
