NK073(pu)006:1338: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis kyi bstan pa'i bdag
NK073(pu)006:1339: po klad du phyungs pas bstan chos mdzes pa'i rgyan
NK073(pu)006:1340: du nges so // 'jig rten pa'i lta ba la mdor bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1342: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1343: de'ang 'jig rten na snod 'jig chags stong gnas bzhi gcig la gcig brten pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1344: bcud skye rga na 'chi bzhi gcig la gcig brten pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1345: de gnyis kyang snod 'jig 'jig 'dra ba la bcud 'jig 'jig 'dra ba brten pas 'jig rten ste /
NK073(pu)006:1346: de lta bu mthar thug pa med pa'i khams ni
NK073(pu)006:1347: byed pa med par rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa
NK073(pu)006:1348: ste / sa byed pa med par sra zhing brtan pa'i mtshan nya da 'dzin /
NK073(pu)006:1349: chu gsher ba me dro ba la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1350: yang na rgya che zhing grangs mang bas kyang khams te /
NK073(pu)006:1352: bcud kyi sems can grangs mang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1353: rgya che ba dang brtsegs pas kyang khams zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1354: phan tshun za 'og yas man dong tse 'dra bas kyang khams zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1355: phyogs dang ris su chad pas kyang khams te /
NK073(pu)006:1361: de la sogs te zhib bu rnams gcig gis gcig mi mthong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1362: bcud 'gro ba rigs drug kyang so sor chad de spyod yul du ma gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1363: na zhes pa gnas gzhi'i don te snod do //
NK073(pu)006:1364: de'i bcud ni sems can zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1365: sems kyi mtshan nyid rnam par dag pas don ma
NK073(pu)006:1366: rtogs te tshogs brgyad kyi shes pa dngos por bzung
NK073(pu)006:1367: ba can / yang na sems ni tshogs brgyad la bya la /
NK073(pu)006:1368: can ni de nyid lus dang ngags su ldan pa'i don to //
NK073(pu)006:1369: phyin ci log ces pa yang dag pa'i don ma rtogs te /
NK073(pu)006:1370: dper na pha la dgrar mthong ba dang 'dra ba gzung 'dzin gtan nas ma grub pa las /
NK073(pu)006:1371: yul yul can gnyis su brtags pa ni yang dag
NK073(pu)006:1372: pa'i don las gol bas na phyin ci log go
NK073(pu)006:1373: // lta ba ni de la zhen pa'i 'dzin pa dang ma bral ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1374: grangs med ces bye ba spyir sems can gyi grang kyang rtsis gyis mi chod la /
NK073(pu)006:1375: de dag so so'i blo ngo la rnam rtog gi
NK073(pu)006:1376: lta ba'i grangs dpag tu med pa gcig yod de
NK073(pu)006:1377: / de'i shas phra ba mu stegs pa la'ang su
NK073(pu)006:1378: ma brgya drug cu la sogs pa dpag tu med
NK073(pu)006:1380: 'dir bstan pa mdor bsdu na so so mtshan nyid mi 'dra ba'i rnam grangs bzhir 'dus te /
NK073(pu)006:1383: rgyu 'bras dang dge sdig gang gi'ang phyogs su'ang brten pa med de /
NK073(pu)006:1384: phyogs bsgrub med pa so so'i skye bo phyug ba dang glang lta bu ste shin tu dman pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1386: dge sdig rgyu 'bras kyi don ma go yang tshe
NK073(pu)006:1387: 'di'i khe grags dang btsan phyug don du gnyen ba
NK073(pu)006:1388: tsam mo // mur thug ni grub mtha' la brten pa'i mtha' chad par lta ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1390: grub mtha' la zhugs pa'i lta ba can no //
NK073(pu)006:1393: de la phyal pa zhes pa la sogs pa mdor
NK073(pu)006:1394: bstan gyi skabs su bzhir phyes pa de las phyal
NK073(pu)006:1396: blo'i rten sa med pa'i don gyis na phyal pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1397: don la zhe 'dod kyi gtan sgo med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1398: de ni chos thams cad ces pa ma rtogs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1399: chos khams gsum gyi dge mi dge'i chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:1400: / rgyu dang 'bras bu yod med ma rtogs te ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:1401: rgyu dge ba las 'bras bu mtho ris 'byung bar yang ma rtogs te blo mi 'jig /
NK073(pu)006:1402: rgyu mi dge ba las 'bras bu ngan song yod
NK073(pu)006:1403: par ma rtogs te blo mi 'jug ste phyi ma'i
NK073(pu)006:1404: rgyu 'bras lkog tu gyur pas so //
NK073(pu)006:1405: 'di la yang rgyu 'bras bskyed pa'i cha thams cad
NK073(pu)006:1406: la blo 'jug pa med pas phal pa'i sems brgyad
NK073(pu)006:1407: kyi dang po'ang mgo ma zug pa ste 'di dang
NK073(pu)006:1408: phyi ma'i rgyu 'bras thams cad la blo zhugs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1409: stobs med pas kun tu rmongs zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1410: so so'i skye bo glang lta bu ste 'jig rten pa rnams kyi nang gi dman pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1411: de ni lha la med de mngon par shes pa dang ldan pas so //
NK073(pu)006:1412: mi dang lha ma yin la shas tsam yod /
NK073(pu)006:1413: ngan song gsum la shas che ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1415: zhes pa tshe snga phyi la sogs rgyu 'bras mgo ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:1416: gong ma dang 'dra bas yang dag pa'i don las
NK073(pu)006:1417: rgyang ring du song bas tshe 'di'i phan pa bsgrub
NK073(pu)006:1418: pa ste / de yang tshe snga phyi rtag par lta ba ltar yod par yang ma rtogs /
NK073(pu)006:1419: chad par lta ba ltar med pa yang ma rtog shing gang du 'ang blo ma zhugs la /
NK073(pu)006:1420: tshe 'di nyid gcig pu la phan bsod kyi rgyu 'bras tsam gcig zhe phugs su bzhag pas /
NK073(pu)006:1421: btsan pa ni rigs rgyud mang bas kha drag pa lta bu /
NK073(pu)006:1422: phyug pa ni nor mang bas longs spyod che ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1423: mthu ni rang ngo mthong ba dang khe drag che ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1424: stobs ni nus phod che ba dang nyams rtsal che ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1425: bsgrub pa ni 'bras bu grol ma de dag 'dod
NK073(pu)006:1426: pa'i phyir te 'jig rten pa'i lha'i gsang tshig lo
NK073(pu)006:1427: ma can gyi gsang sngags ste gar sha'i ngan sngags
NK073(pu)006:1430: sa bdag mchog pa dang g.yang len la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:1431: rang gis shes na byed gzhan la'ang bcol bas des
NK073(pu)006:1432: 'bras bu gong ma rnams bsgrub pa la brten pa'o
NK073(pu)006:1434: zhes pa gong ma gnyis ni ma rtogs pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:1435: 'dir ni log par rtog pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1436: gong ma phyal pa'i skabs su ni rgyu 'bras yod med la blo ma zhugs pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:1437: 'dir ni chos thams cad ces pa dge sdig dang 'khor 'das te /
NK073(pu)006:1438: rgyu dge ba las 'bras bu mtho ris dang /
NK073(pu)006:1439: mi dge ba las ngan song dang 'khor ba dang
NK073(pu)006:1440: 'das par 'byung ba gtan nas med par lta ste
NK073(pu)006:1441: / chu bskos pa brag la thug pa lta bu la mur thug ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1442: tshe 'di nyid la spyod yul du gyur pa'i chos
NK073(pu)006:1443: thams cad rgyu rkyen med par glo bur bar skyes
NK073(pu)006:1444: la / shi nas kyang glo bur du thim ste /
NK073(pu)006:1445: phyi ma med par chad par lta ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1446: des na bzang mo ma shi bar du bde bar 'tsho //
NK073(pu)006:1447: shi nas de yi sbyod yul med /
NK073(pu)006:1448: lus kyang thal ba bzhin song na /
NK073(pu)006:1449: slar skye ba lta ga la yod /
NK073(pu)006:1451: des na skye ba yang spang la sha mong brdol
NK073(pu)006:1452: ba dang chu la chu bur bzhin thod rgal du
NK073(pu)006:1454: skye ba phyis len bya ba'ang rdzun te mi 'den /
NK073(pu)006:1455: skye ba phyis len par brjod pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1456: dper na thang po che la spyang ki'i rjes bcad
NK073(pu)006:1457: pa dang mtshungs te rtsar phyin pa su'angasa med zer
NK073(pu)006:1458: nas / mang ston pas ni mang bstan pa //
NK073(pu)006:1459: sbyang ku dag gi rjes gcod 'dra /
NK073(pu)006:1461: mu stegs pa ni zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1462: rang blos bzhag pa'i lta ba ngan pa la mu bcas nas /
NK073(pu)006:1463: de nyid la 'bras bu sgrub pa'i lam gyi stegs su byed pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:1464: yang na lta ba la mu 'dzin cing /
NK073(pu)006:1465: spyod pa la stegs bcas te 'di yang ngo bo ni bdag yod par lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:1466: rang bzhin ni yang dag pa'i don la log par lta ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1467: mtshan nyid ni bdag rtag chos bdag lus gtsang tshor ba bde ba bzhi'o //
NK073(pu)006:1468: rkyen dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang bral te /
NK073(pu)006:1469: sdig pa'i grogs po dag sangs rgyas kyi bka' la
NK073(pu)006:1470: rang byin gyis zhugs pa dang dpyod blos rang dgar
NK073(pu)006:1472: 'di la ni mtho ris ngan song dge mi dge
NK073(pu)006:1473: tshe snga phyi spang blang shes nas 'dod tshod kyi
NK073(pu)006:1474: bsgrub bya bsgrub pa'ang yod de /
NK073(pu)006:1475: chos thams cad kun tu brtags pa'i bdag rtag pa cig yod par lta ste /
NK073(pu)006:1476: zhes pa snod bcud kyi chos thams cad la dngos
NK073(pu)006:1477: po med kyang rang gi log rtog gi blos kun
NK073(pu)006:1478: tu brtags te chos dang gang zag gi bdag gnyis
NK073(pu)006:1479: rtag pa dus gsum du mi 'gyur bar yod par
NK073(pu)006:1480: lta ba ni kun gyi thun mong ste /
NK073(pu)006:1482: rgyu yod la 'bras bu med par lta ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:1483: lta ba ces pa rgyu ni sems can la gang
NK073(pu)006:1484: zag gi bdag gtsang la gsal ba me long ngo
NK073(pu)006:1485: gnyis pa lta bu che theb bong tsam /
NK073(pu)006:1488: phra rta rnga tsam gcig yod pa la /
NK073(pu)006:1489: yul ni dngos po rtag pa rang rgyud du lta ste /
NK073(pu)006:1490: des na 'gro ba kun la rdul mun pa snying stobs gsum dang ldan pas /
NK073(pu)006:1491: de gsum cha mnyam na bdag dag ste /
NK073(pu)006:1492: cha ma mnyam pa'i dbang gis bdag dag par ma
NK073(pu)006:1493: nus pa slar khams gsum sems can du snang ba
NK073(pu)006:1494: ni / snying stobs shas che na dmyal ba /
NK073(pu)006:1495: mun pa shas che na byol song /
NK073(pu)006:1496: rdul shas che na yi dwags /
NK073(pu)006:1497: gnyis po la rdul shas chung na mi /
NK073(pu)006:1499: mun pa chung bas lha min du snang te 'khor ba snang la /
NK073(pu)006:1500: de gsum cha mnyam par byas na /
NK073(pu)006:1501: gang zag ni bdag ste dag pas 'bras bu'i ngo bo gtso bo bem po la thim pas /
NK073(pu)006:1502: rig pa med pas gang du'ang mi snang zhing bem po ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1503: dngos po med pa nam mkhar dwangs pa lta bu nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor 'dod pas na /
NK073(pu)006:1507: gsum gyi las kyis bskyed pa'i sems can ni dngos su yod par 'dod la /
NK073(pu)006:1508: de las byung ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK073(pu)006:1509: gtso bo bem po la thim pas dngos po med cing gzhan du skyer mi btub bas na /
NK073(pu)006:1510: rgyu yod 'bras bu med ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1511: 'di la mu stegs pa zag bcas kyi 'du shes
NK073(pu)006:1512: pa dag gis mthong bas khams gnyis po shi nas
NK073(pu)006:1513: gzugs med du skye ba khams gnyis po lus la
NK073(pu)006:1514: brten pas mngon shes kyi spyod yul du gyur la
NK073(pu)006:1515: / gzugs med pa ming bzhi'i phung po ma mthong bas rgyu yod 'bras bu med ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1516: yang gnas skabs kyi rgyu yod 'bras bu med par lta ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:1518: byed pa po rgyur smra ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:1519: gang zag gi bdag dngos po can gcig yod pa gong dang mthun la /
NK073(pu)006:1520: des byas pa'i 'bras bu mtho ris dang ngan song bya ba med de /
NK073(pu)006:1521: sngar mtho ris dang lha mir skyes pa de phyis kyang der skye la /
NK073(pu)006:1522: sngar ngan song du skyes pa de phyis kyang der skye bar zad de /
NK073(pu)006:1523: skye ba barje bsor du yang mi gtub ste /
NK073(pu)006:1526: nas la gror mi btub pa bzhin zhe'o //
NK073(pu)006:1527: des na mtho ris dang ngan song bya ba ni dge sdig las kyis ma byas te /
NK073(pu)006:1528: dper na rdza chag bye'u 'phur bzhin zhe'o //
NK073(pu)006:1529: rgyu med la 'bras bu yod pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1530: gong gi gang zag gi bdag de dag pa dang
NK073(pu)006:1531: gsum po cha mnyam nas gtso bo bem po la
NK073(pu)006:1532: thim pa'i phyir / lo ma dang shun pa sdong
NK073(pu)006:1533: bu tsam la brten cing ri brag tu gnas bcas
NK073(pu)006:1534: thim pa'i phyir / te / dge ba rgyu dang
NK073(pu)006:1535: gsang tshig tsam la brten nas bsgrub pas g.yeng dag
NK073(pu)006:1536: pa'i stobs kyis sems gnas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1537: lus gtsang ba'i stobs kyis mngon shes 'aphra'u 'char nas ngan song mtho ris su 'pho /
NK073(pu)006:1538: mtho ris ngan song du 'pho ba tsam mthong bas las kyis 'phen pa ni ma rtogs /
NK073(pu)006:1539: khyi la sogs pa las 'gas mtho ris su 'gro /
NK073(pu)006:1540: 'gas ngan song du 'gro ba la sogs pa 'di
NK073(pu)006:1541: rnams la byed pa po gcig yod ces rtogs te
NK073(pu)006:1543: dbang phyug gis byed ces zer ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1545: 'jig rten na dbang che ba su yod ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:1546: des kyang dbang phyug tshangs pa brgya byin yod byas pas /
NK073(pu)006:1547: khos spyi'i byed pa po de dag go zhes rtog ste /
NK073(pu)006:1548: gong gi lha de dag gang dang gang yin pa la dad pas mchog ste /
NK073(pu)006:1549: bsgrub pas stes dbang gis ri bdun kha la gnas
NK073(pu)006:1550: pa'i lha'i bu rnams 'dzam bu'i gling du ltas mo
NK073(pu)006:1551: la babs pa / la las glang po zhon pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1554: rta ngang pa zhon pa la sogs pa mthong nas
NK073(pu)006:1555: 'di dag bdag gis sgrub pa'i lha'o zhes rtog ste
NK073(pu)006:1556: / glang po can brgya byin du bzung /
NK073(pu)006:1557: rma bya can tshangs pa la sogs par bzung zhing dad pa dang 'dun pas gnas te /
NK073(pu)006:1558: lha'i bu de dag mtsho la rkyal ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1559: chu la 'dzul ba dang zas mi dgos pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1560: bla gab can la mi gnas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1561: shing gi drung na gnas pa la sogs pa spyod
NK073(pu)006:1562: lam rnams rang rang gi lhas grub pa'i gdams ngag
NK073(pu)006:1564: la la ma pham dang g+aad+g+aa la 'phur ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1565: shing drung na gnas pa dang zas gcod pa la
NK073(pu)006:1566: sogs pa'i brtul zhugs dag nyams su blangs te 'di
NK073(pu)006:1567: dag ni / nas 'dod pas sa bon yug po btab pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:1568: mtho ris 'dod pas mi dge ba sna tshogs bsags
NK073(pu)006:1569: pas rgyu bsod nams bsags pa med pas 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:1570: phya dang dbang phyug gis byed pas yod par lta
NK073(pu)006:1571: ba'o // yang kho'i mngon shes kyis gzugs med sems
NK073(pu)006:1572: can shi ba khams gnyis por skye bar mthong bas
NK073(pu)006:1573: des kyang rgyu med 'bras bu yod par gdags so
NK073(pu)006:1574: ba'o // // zhar la de dag gi rang bzhin
NK073(pu)006:1575: rgyur smra ba ces gdags te rgyu dge sdig med
NK073(pu)006:1576: pa las 'bras bu mtho ris dang ngan song du
NK073(pu)006:1579: gnam babs sam 'dod rgyal gyis skye ba rnams byed ces brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:1580: rgyu 'bras log par lta ba dang zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1581: 'bras bu mtho ris thob par 'dod pas rgyu mi dge ba bsgrub ste /
NK073(pu)006:1582: srog gi mchod sbyin byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1583: dbyug gu gsum pa dang g.yang la mchongs pa la sogs pa'i log lta 'dzin pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1584: 'bras bu thar par 'dod pas rgyu chos dang gang zag gnyis su bzung ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1585: 'bras bu 'das pa 'dod pas rgyu 'jig rten pa'i lha bsgrub ste log par lta ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1587: rgyu 'bras kyi don ma rtogs par log lta khong du bcug nas /
NK073(pu)006:1588: log pa'i lta ba brtul zhugs 'chal ba'i spyod pa sna tshogs byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1589: yang dbang phyug rgyur lta ba ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1590: mtho ris dang ngan song du skye ba /
NK073(pu)006:1591: las dge sdig gis ma bsgrub /
NK073(pu)006:1594: byed pa po'am bsko ba po ces pas bskos te /
NK073(pu)006:1595: de dag mgu na ni mtho ris su skye bar byed la /
NK073(pu)006:1596: de dag ma dga' na ngan song du skye bar byed pas de dag dga' bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:1597: ba glang la sogs pa srog gi mchod sbyin byed do //
NK073(pu)006:1598: des na las dge sdig ngo ma shes pa'i log lta ste /
NK073(pu)006:1600: skye ba po la shes pa yod min te /
NK073(pu)006:1601: 'di na bde dang sdug bsngal rang dbang med /
NK073(pu)006:1602: dbang phyug gis btang yang na mtho ris dang /
NK073(pu)006:1603: yang na ngan song dag tu ltung bar 'gyur /
NK073(pu)006:1606: 'di dag ni ma rig pa'i lta ba'o zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1607: gong du smos pa'i lta ba bzhi po 'di dag ni /
NK073(pu)006:1608: ma dag pa log pa'i lta ba gzung 'dzin phyin ci log gi shes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1609: rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa las byung
NK073(pu)006:1610: ba dang skabs su yang dag la sgrib pas na
NK073(pu)006:1612: de nyid du 'dzin pa dang bral ba ni gti mug can gyi log pa'i lta ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1613: yang dag pa'i lam bstan pa 'di'i skabs su ma
NK073(pu)006:1614: rig pa'i lta ba de dag bstan pa la dgos
NK073(pu)006:1616: dper na zas kha mo ma zos na mngar ba mi tshor ba dang 'dra ste /
NK073(pu)006:1617: lta ba ngan pa 'di dag bstan pas yang dag pa'i lam la nges shes skye ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1618: cha yod dug la mi rig bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:1619: log lta gnyis su ga la 'gyur /
NK073(pu)006:1620: zhes pas 'jig rten pa'i lta ba rnams bstan bshad kyi sgo nas shes na /
NK073(pu)006:1621: de dag la 'jug par mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1622: skyes bu lam la mkhas na lam gyi gol sa
NK073(pu)006:1623: la mkhas dgos pa'i phyir bstan pa gal che bar
NK073(pu)006:1624: gdams pa'o // 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba bstan pa'i rnams grangs spyir bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1626: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1627: de la 'jig rten zhes pa snod bcud kyi mtshan nyid rnams gong du bshad pa bzhin la /
NK073(pu)006:1628: 'das pa ni des ma reg cing ma zin pas
NK073(pu)006:1629: ma gos pas na mun pa las 'das pa'i snang
NK073(pu)006:1631: 'khor ba ma grub pa'i nyan thos rang rgyal /
NK073(pu)006:1632: sangs rgyas kyi sa dang gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:1633: lam ni 'bras bu de dag nyid grub par bya
NK073(pu)006:1634: ba'i thabs te so so'i 'bras bu'i rnam par thar
NK073(pu)006:1635: pa'i lam du gyur pa theg pa rim pa dagu'o
NK073(pu)006:1636: // de nyid gzhi 'bras bu grub pa'i lam du
NK073(pu)006:1637: mthun pas dbye ba'i gzhir bzhag pas lam la zhes
NK073(pu)006:1638: // so // grangs kyi dbye ba ni rnam pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:1639: gsal ba'i dbye ba'i ngos nas bstan na /
NK073(pu)006:1640: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1642: zhes pa la lam gyi ngo bo don dam pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1643: 'bras bu sku gsum nyid bshad pa'i rgyud mtshan du
NK073(pu)006:1644: yid la byed pas kyang mtshan nyid du bshad la
NK073(pu)006:1645: / yang na mtshan nyid ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:1646: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid ces te /
NK073(pu)006:1647: spyi'i mtshan nyid mi rtag pa da nga sdug bsngal ba /
NK073(pu)006:1648: rang gi mtshan nyid ni stong zhing bdag med par bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:1649: de'ang spyi'i mtshan nyid ni 'khor ba'i chos kyi mtshan nyid yin la /
NK073(pu)006:1650: rang gi mtshan nyid ni mya ngan las 'das pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1651: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad snod bcud gnyis su 'dus la /
NK073(pu)006:1652: de'ang 'byung ba lngar 'dus te sa ni sra zhing
NK073(pu)006:1653: brtan pa la sogs te 'byung ba so so'i mtshan
NK073(pu)006:1655: bcud kyi 'jig rten ni phung po lngar 'dus te /
NK073(pu)006:1656: de'ang gzugs ni gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba'i mtshan nyid /
NK073(pu)006:1657: tshor ba nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid /
NK073(pu)006:1658: 'du shes yul la gcod pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK073(pu)006:1659: 'du byed mngon par 'du byed pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK073(pu)006:1660: rnam par shes pa rnam par rig pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:1661: rang gi mtshan nyid rnam par byang ba ni pha rol tu phyin pa drug tu 'dus te /
NK073(pu)006:1662: de yang sbyin pa gtong ba'i mtshan nyid /
NK073(pu)006:1663: tshul khrims nyams pa med pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK073(pu)006:1666: bsam gtan g.yeng ba med pa /
NK073(pu)006:1667: shes rab ni chos kyi mthar rtogs pa'i mtshan nyid can te /
NK073(pu)006:1668: 'bras bu thams cad mkhyen pa'ang mngon sum pa'i mtshan nyid la sogs pa'i gsal bar ston pas /
NK073(pu)006:1669: gong gi rnam par 'byed pa rnams kyis kun nas nyon mongs pa ni spong /
NK073(pu)006:1670: rnam par byang ba ni bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:1671: des 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i theg pa ni bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:1672: rdo rje'i zhes pa 'bras bu'i sgo nas gsungs pa yin te /
NK073(pu)006:1673: rgyu spyad pa'i 'bras bu la mi ltos par rdo rje lta bu gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:1674: lnga bshad pa nyid kyi don rtogs nas bsgom pa
NK073(pu)006:1675: tsam gyis 'bras bu sangs rgyas par grub pa yin
NK073(pu)006:1676: te / theg pa'i sgra'ang bshad pa ltar yin la
NK073(pu)006:1677: de nyid la ni nges pa'i don gtan la phebs
NK073(pu)006:1678: te / pa zhes bya'o // yang na rdo rje ni /
NK073(pu)006:1679: rnal 'byor pa'i lus ngag yid gsum yi dam lha'i
NK073(pu)006:1680: sku gsung thugs rdo rjer gnyis su med par bsgrubs
NK073(pu)006:1681: te tshe gcig gis 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'o
NK073(pu)006:1682: // de gnyis ni lta ba dang sgom pa gnyis kyi tshul lo /
NK073(pu)006:1683: yang na legs nyes thams cad stobs che bas na rdo rje ste /
NK073(pu)006:1684: lta spyod sgom pa cha rkyen 'tshogs pa'i sgrub pa nyams su blangs na /
NK073(pu)006:1685: lam gyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs sgrib pa rnam pa
NK073(pu)006:1686: gsum dus gcig mi gnas par mdzad pas kyang rdo
NK073(pu)006:1687: rje'o // de nyid kyi 'bras bu'i ngo bo rdo
NK073(pu)006:1688: rje lta bu rnam gsum mngon du byed pas kyang
NK073(pu)006:1689: rje'o // rdo rje'o // gzhung bzhin ma sgrub ste
NK073(pu)006:1690: 'gal na lus ngag yid gsum gtan du brlag ste
NK073(pu)006:1691: rje'o // rdo rje'o // / dmyal ba'i yang gting du 'joms pas kyang rdo rje /
NK073(pu)006:1692: sdug bsngal la glag med cing ngal bso ba'i skabs med pas kyang rdo rje'o //
NK073(pu)006:1693: bye brag tu phye ba'i mdor bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1694: mtshan nyid kyi zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1695: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa de rang la yang /
NK073(pu)006:1696: grangs kyi dbye ba rnams pa gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:1698: gsal ba'i dbye ba'i ngos nas /
NK073(pu)006:1699: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1700: zhes pa thos pa'i shes rab kyi ngos nas dge
NK073(pu)006:1701: ba'i bshes gnyen la nyan la rna ba'i dbang pos
NK073(pu)006:1702: thos pa don du gnyen pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:1703: yang na thos sgrogs zhes brjod pas ston pa'i spyan
NK073(pu)006:1704: sngar na mdo sde bcu gnyis thos nas kha bton
NK073(pu)006:1705: du byed cing gzhan la sgrogs kyang /
NK073(pu)006:1706: rang nyid la nyan thos kyi gzhung min pa nyams su ma myong bas na nyan thos zhes so //
NK073(pu)006:1707: theg pa ni rang gi nyan thos kyi chos te
NK073(pu)006:1708: nyan thos kyi 'bras bu la sbyor bar byed pa'o
NK073(pu)006:1709: // des na nyan thos thog mar yang dge ba'i bshes gnyen la mnyan /
NK073(pu)006:1710: 'bras bu thob ka'ang dge ba'i bshes gnyen la rag las te /
NK073(pu)006:1711: 'phags pa rta thul gyi gdams ngag gis /
NK073(pu)006:1713: moo'u 'gal gyi bu gnyis 'bras bu thob pa la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1714: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1715: sngon du dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten te thos bsam gyi lam la sbyangs kyang /
NK073(pu)006:1716: 'bras bu thob ka na slob dpon dang mjal ba'i smon lam ni ma btab /
NK073(pu)006:1717: sngon dge ba'i bshes gnyen la thos bsam gyi sgo
NK073(pu)006:1718: nas chos nyid kyi don kun gzhi la stobs su
NK073(pu)006:1719: gyur pas don go ba'i stobs dang ni ldan la
NK073(pu)006:1720: / smon lam ma btab pa'i dbang gis ni dge
NK073(pu)006:1721: ba'i bshes dang ma mjal yang rten 'brel rtogs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:1722: rgyu rkyen chos gang gis nus te rtogs nas /
NK073(pu)006:1723: rang byang chub byon pa'i dus slob dpon dang mjal ba'i smon lam ma btab pa'i stobs kyis /
NK073(pu)006:1724: sangs rgyas snga ma'i bstan pa nub /
NK073(pu)006:1725: phyi ma ma byon pa'i bar ma snang la /
NK073(pu)006:1726: sangs rgyas byon pa'i rtags mthong nas zhi ba la
NK073(pu)006:1727: thim nas lus kyi rdzu 'phrul gyis 'gro ba'i don
NK073(pu)006:1728: byed pa'o // byang chub sems dpa' zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1729: las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa byang nas de'i stobs kyis sa'i khyad par rnams bsgrub pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1730: sems bskyed pa nas sa bcu'i bar ro //
NK073(pu)006:1731: de yang byang chub sems dpa' zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1732: bdag gis byang chub thob par sems bskyed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1733: byang chub kyi phyir sems bskyed pa ni sems can thams cad kyi phyir sems bskyed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1735: sems can gyi don du 'gyur na yan lag gi dang po mgo dang /
NK073(pu)006:1736: dbang po'i dwangs ma mig gtong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1738: sgrib gnyis spangs pas rnam dag byang //
NK073(pu)006:1739: shes bya rtogs pas ye shes chub //
NK073(pu)006:1740: bdag dang gzhan gyi don la sems //
NK073(pu)006:1741: rig pa'i rtsal dang blos rtogs dpa' //
NK073(pu)006:1743: de'i theg pa ni spang blang gi sgo nas chos
NK073(pu)006:1744: nyid kyi rtogs pas 'bras bu la skyol bar byed
NK073(pu)006:1745: pas so // rgyas par nyan thos kyi theg pa
NK073(pu)006:1746: la brgyad kyi dang po gang zag dang 'jug sgo
NK073(pu)006:1747: thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1748: de la zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1749: gang gi gsum du dbye ba'i gzhi de las nyan thos bkar nas bshad na /
NK073(pu)006:1750: nyan thos kyi theg pa zhes pa nyan thos kyi theg pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:1751: mu stegs pa'i nga gtsang skyid rtag bzhi las ldog ste /
NK073(pu)006:1759: lam bsgom par bya ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:1760: theg pa de nyid nyags su blang ba la ni zhugs /
NK073(pu)006:1763: zhugs pa zhes pas rten gyi gang zag bstan te rten gyi dbang po rab 'bring gsum /
NK073(pu)006:1764: re re la'ang gsum gsum du byas pa'i tha ma'i tha ma /
NK073(pu)006:1765: dad pa dang brtson 'grus che zhing /
NK073(pu)006:1766: shes rab snying rje'i spobs pa chung ste mtha' gnyis dang bral ba'i don la 'jug mi nus shing /
NK073(pu)006:1767: gzhan don dang du len pa ma bzod de rang nyid zhi ba 'ba' zhig ched du gnyer ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:1768: lta ba ces pa rtogs pa'i lta ba ste 'di
NK073(pu)006:1769: la yang mi mthun pa'i phyogs ma grub par bstan
NK073(pu)006:1770: pa dang / ngo bo dmigs su bstan pa gnyis las /
NK073(pu)006:1771: mi mthun pa'i phyogs ma grub par bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1773: mtho ris ngan song ngam phyi dang nang ngam snod
NK073(pu)006:1774: bcud kyi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa gzhal bya yul du
NK073(pu)006:1776: mu stegs pa la sogs pa zhes pas gang zag mu stegs dang /
NK073(pu)006:1777: sogs khongs su chad pa'am gsum po bsdus pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1778: las zhes pas rten des sgro dang skur ba kun brtags pa'i /
NK073(pu)006:1779: zhes pa sgro ni med pa la kun brtags te
NK073(pu)006:1780: don dam pa'i bden pa spros pa'i mtshan ma dang
NK073(pu)006:1781: bral ba las gzung 'dzin yul dang yul can kyis
NK073(pu)006:1782: nga dang bdag tu kun brtags pa'i dbang gis tshig
NK073(pu)006:1783: gung bsdebs te / rtag pa la sogs pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1784: dngos po rdzas can du ma grub pa la der bzung ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1785: sogs khog su rtag pa'i bye brag rnams kun bsdus te /
NK073(pu)006:1786: des na dngos po yod par brtags pa'i cha rnams dang /
NK073(pu)006:1788: sems kyi rtsal las dge sdig gi 'bras bu mtho
NK073(pu)006:1789: ris dang ngan song chud mi za bar 'byin pa
NK073(pu)006:1790: la / chad lta bas de med ces skur ba
NK073(pu)006:1791: btab ste mtha' chad par kun tu brtags pa'i dbang
NK073(pu)006:1792: gis rgyu 'bras dang tshe snga phyi dang mtho ris
NK073(pu)006:1793: ngan song ye med ces chad par lta ba dang
NK073(pu)006:1794: la / / gnyis ni gzhi la ye ma grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:1795: blo nor gyi log brtags kyi shes pa 'ba' zhig
NK073(pu)006:1796: gis brtags pa las snang ba thag pa las sprul
NK073(pu)006:1797: du mthong ba bzhin du med ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:1798: dper na skyes bu shes pa rtsing ba gcig dang
NK073(pu)006:1799: nam mkha' ma dwangs pa dang thag pa khra bo
NK073(pu)006:1800: dang gsum 'phrad na sbrul du mthong ste /
NK073(pu)006:1801: de blo zhib pas brtag na sbrul gyi rang bzhin
NK073(pu)006:1802: ni 'khril ba dang rlan pa dang 'dzin par byed
NK073(pu)006:1803: pa yin na / thag pa la de gang yang med par sbrul du mthong ba bzhin du /
NK073(pu)006:1804: mu stegs pas rtag chad gnyis med bzhin du nan
NK073(pu)006:1805: gyis brtags pa yang skyes bu shes rab rtsing ba
NK073(pu)006:1806: dang / lhan cig skyes pa'i bag chags ma dag
NK073(pu)006:1807: pa dang sems nyid cir yang snang ba'i gzhi thag
NK073(pu)006:1808: pa khra bo lta bu las sbrul bzhin rtag chad
NK073(pu)006:1810: nyan thos pa blo zhib pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1812: de gnyis kyis thag pa la thag par mthong ste
NK073(pu)006:1813: sbrul du ma grub pa bzhin gzhi nas bral bar
NK073(pu)006:1814: shes te rtag chad du mthong ba'i 'khrul gzhi tsam
NK073(pu)006:1815: yod kyang ngo bo la ma grub par thag chod
NK073(pu)006:1816: do // lta ba rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:1817: phung po dang zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:1818: gzugs la sogs pa'i phung po lnga ste /
NK073(pu)006:1819: de yang nyan thos la blo rno brtul gnyis gyis /
NK073(pu)006:1820: bye brag pa dang mdo sde pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:1821: bye brag pas rnam shes phung po ma gtogs pa'i phung po bzhir 'dod la /
NK073(pu)006:1822: mdo sde pas lngar 'dod pa'i dbang gis dkyus su grangs ma smos pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1823: skye mched kyang bye brag pas dbang lnga yul lnga bcur 'dod /
NK073(pu)006:1824: mdo sde pas de'i thog tu yid kyi dbang po dang /
NK073(pu)006:1825: yid kyi yul chos 'dus byas la bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:1826: 'dus ma byas la bzhi dang brgyad gcig tu byas pas bcu gnyis su 'dod /
NK073(pu)006:1827: khams kyang blo brtul gyis dbang lnga yul lnga rnam shes lnga dang bco lngar 'dod do //
NK073(pu)006:1828: mdo sde pas dbang drug yul drug rnam shes drug ste bco brgyad du 'dod do //
NK073(pu)006:1829: 'byung ba'ang bye brag pas nam mkha' ma gtogs pa bzhir 'dod /
NK073(pu)006:1831: des na phung po khams dang skye mched dang /
NK073(pu)006:1832: sogs pa ni gang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:1833: de bskyed par byed pa'i 'byung ba chen po bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:1834: de dag dngos po rags par snang zhing so so'i
NK073(pu)006:1835: bya ba byed pa'i nus pa dang ldan pa'i snang
NK073(pu)006:1836: tshod ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:1838: zhes pa de dag rnam par gzhig na rdul phra
NK073(pu)006:1839: rab rab cha shas med pa'i sil bur ni don
NK073(pu)006:1840: dam par ro // de la bye brag pas rdul phra rab de ma 'dres pa'i sil bur /
NK073(pu)006:1841: bar snang mun dang bcas par 'dod de /
NK073(pu)006:1842: g.yag rnga dang ne'u seng bzhin zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:1843: ne'u seng rgyang nas btas pas sngo leb be ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1844: cha shas sil bur ma 'dres par 'dod pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1845: mdo sde bas gzung ba don dam pa'i bden pa
NK073(pu)006:1846: yul rdul phra rab de 'byar yang ma 'byar la
NK073(pu)006:1847: / bar yang med par 'dod de dper na dras
NK073(pu)006:1848: ka byas pa'i po sti'am shing lo ltar bar na
NK073(pu)006:1849: mun ba'i skye mched ni med /
NK073(pu)006:1850: 'byar ni ma 'byar bar 'dus pa'i tshul du yod zer te /
NK073(pu)006:1852: bar med rnam par nas kyang rung //
NK073(pu)006:1854: rnam par shes pa ni don dam pa med par lta bas zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1855: rnam par shes pa dngos por snang ba ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa /
NK073(pu)006:1856: de nyid skad cig ma'i shes pa 'phags pa'i spyod yul du gyur pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1857: dus gsum gyi chas gzhig na ma grub kyang /
NK073(pu)006:1858: skad cig ma phra ba tsam gcig don dam par blta ste /
NK073(pu)006:1859: kun rdzob tu ma grub pas don dam par med par lta zhes kyang smos so /
NK073(pu)006:1860: yang skad cig ma phra ba yod pas don dam par yang yod par lta /
NK073(pu)006:1861: kun rdzob tu ma grub pas don dam par med par lta zhes kyang smos so //
NK073(pu)006:1862: yang skad cig ma phra ba yod pas don dam par yang yod par lta /
NK073(pu)006:1863: zhes kyang smos te gang ltar yang khyad med do //
NK073(pu)006:1864: bsam gtan gyi rim pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1867: ting nge 'dzin ni bden pa bzhi'i ngos nas nyams su len te /
NK073(pu)006:1868: de'ang 'phags pa ni khams gsum gyi chos kyis ma gos pa la 'phags pa zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:1869: de'i thabs bden pa bzhi la yang 'phags pa zhes brjod la /
NK073(pu)006:1871: sdug bsngal dang kun 'byung dang 'gog pa dang lam mo //
NK073(pu)006:1873: sdug bsngal kun 'byung gnyis ni 'khor ba'i chos su bden la /
NK073(pu)006:1874: 'gog pa dang lam gnyis mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos su bden pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1880: sdug bsngal ni gsum dang brgyad de bcu gcig go //
NK073(pu)006:1881: kun 'byung ni sdug bsngal de dag dug gsum las
NK073(pu)006:1882: 'byung bas de dug gsum tsher ma bzhin du spang
NK073(pu)006:1883: ba'o // 'gog pa mngon du bya ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:1884: dus gsum spang ba'i don du 'gog pa mngon du bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:1885: mig gis gzugs mthong na yul gyi dbang gis dug gsum skye bar byed dgos pa sa /
NK073(pu)006:1886: mig yul la mi blta nas btsum pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1887: sna yul la mi 'phro nas bsrub pa dang rna ba yul la 'phro dogs nas btsang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1888: lces zas za gcig la 'khor ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:1889: lus kyis phyag dar khrod dang shing shun dang tshem bu gyon pa la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1890: de dag ni sngon du sbyangs yun ring thung gi dbang gis gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:1891: dang po pa rnams kyis ni /
NK073(pu)006:1892: lus dran pa nye bar bzhag pa'i mtshan nyid kyis gzhig pa rnams sems kyis sngon du bsam nas /
NK073(pu)006:1893: rnam par bam pa la sogs pa yang yang bsgoms
NK073(pu)006:1894: pas goms pa'i mthu phung po la mi chags pa
NK073(pu)006:1895: 'byung / sems dran pa nye bar bzhag pa ni
NK073(pu)006:1896: kun 'byung gi rang bzhin yin te tshogs drug gi
NK073(pu)006:1897: 'byung / phyir mi gtong / tshor ba dran pa
NK073(pu)006:1898: nye bar bzhag pa ni sdug bsngal gyi mtshan nyid
NK073(pu)006:1900: chos dran pa nye bar bzhag pa kun 'byung gi
NK073(pu)006:1901: yul sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin can de tshogs drug
NK073(pu)006:1903: de nas 'bring la slob tshul ni /
NK073(pu)006:1904: khyad par du kun 'byung bkag ste /
NK073(pu)006:1905: rlung phyi nang du rgyu ba la shes pa gtad de sems bkag go //
NK073(pu)006:1906: de goms pa ni bzod 'bring ngo //
NK073(pu)006:1908: tshor ba 'di dag sdug bsngal te 'di cis lan na las kyis lan /
NK073(pu)006:1909: las kun 'byung gis bsags pas sdug bsngal shes par byed /
NK073(pu)006:1910: kun 'byung bkag nas de lta bu'i lam rgyud la bsten /
NK073(pu)006:1911: bkag pas khegs pa ni 'gog pa ste 'bras bu'i ngo bo'o //
NK073(pu)006:1912: de ltar bshad pa yang spyir nyan thos la ting nge 'dzin gyi bye brag mang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:1914: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi bsgom pa'i rim pas zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:1915: dang po lam bsgom pa'i ngo po bden pa gsum sngon du song ba'i bzhi pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1916: ye shes bcu drug gi chas rig pa'i cha sbyangs zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:1917: ye shes bcu drug ni shes pa brgyad dang bzod pa brgyad de bcu drug la /
NK073(pu)006:1918: sdug bsngal la chos shes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1919: sdug bsngal la rjes su chos shes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1920: sdug bsngal la bzod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1921: sdug bsngal la rjes su bzod pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1922: de rim pa bzhin du sbyangs pa la ni rim pa yis zhes so //
NK073(pu)006:1924: shes bzod bcu drug gi ting nge 'dzin goms pa des /
NK073(pu)006:1925: khams gsum gyi nyon mongs 'dod chags dang /
NK073(pu)006:1927: gti mug dag cha sbyangs nas 'bras bu bzhi grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:1933: de la rgyun du zhugs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1934: ye shes bcu drug gi khams gsum gyi nyon mongs brgyad cu rtsa brgyad mthong bas spang ste /
NK073(pu)006:1935: gnyen po ye shes kyi rgyun du zhugs te nyon
NK073(pu)006:1936: mongs pa'i rtog pa rags pas mngon du bar ma
NK073(pu)006:1937: chod pa rgyun du zhugs pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1942: ma rig pa bzhi yod pas /
NK073(pu)006:1943: gsum ni gzugs khams bsam gtan gsum pa man chad du sbyangs /
NK073(pu)006:1945: phyir 'dod khams su khong khro sbyangs du 'ong ste
NK073(pu)006:1946: 'dod khams kyi lha mir skye ba blangs nas khong
NK073(pu)006:1948: lan gcig phyir 'ong ba zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:1950: gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhi pa las thar nas /
NK073(pu)006:1951: gzugs med pa'i nam mkha' mtha' yas dang /
NK073(pu)006:1953: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched gsum du skyes nas
NK073(pu)006:1954: phyin chad 'dod khams dang gzugs khams su skye ba
NK073(pu)006:1955: mi len pas phyir mi 'ong ba zhes bya'o de
NK073(pu)006:1956: nas yod min med min nas srid pa'i rtse mo
NK073(pu)006:1957: la nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa phra mo yan chad
NK073(pu)006:1958: sbyangs te khams gsum las tal gyis thal nas ting
NK073(pu)006:1959: nge 'dzin gyi skad cig mas phyi ma la dgra
NK073(pu)006:1961: dper na dgra bsad na phyis mi ldang ba bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:1962: nyon mongs pa phra mo yan chad sbyangs pas sa
NK073(pu)006:1963: bon tsam yang ma lus pas dgra bcom pa zhes
NK073(pu)006:1964: bya'o // bsrung ba'i tshul khrims ni /
NK073(pu)006:1966: dge tshul gyi spong pa bcu gsum 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK073(pu)006:1967: dge slong gi brgya phrag phyed dang gsum /
NK073(pu)006:1969: don la so sor thar pa ris bdun no //
NK073(pu)006:1971: sems can la gnod pa gzhi dang bcas pa las ldog pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1972: rang gi rgyu la rnam par dkar ba'i chos spyod pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1973: ngo bo sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis so //
NK073(pu)006:1974: yun ni bskal pa chen po brgyad 'grub bo //
NK073(pu)006:1975: 'bras bu thob tshul ni bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:1979: dper mar me rgyun zad lta bu zer /
NK073(pu)006:1981: dus mnyam du thob pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1982: bzhag nas skad cig ma 'ga' na thob pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:1983: yang srid de'u blangs kyi sar thob pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:1984: 'di la'ang las zad pa'i skye rgyun chad /
NK073(pu)006:1985: smon lam ma btab pas rang dbang med /
NK073(pu)006:1986: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes bslang ba las ma gtogs pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' yin /
NK073(pu)006:1987: 'bras bu thob nas bskal pa nyi khri na bde
NK073(pu)006:1988: gshegs thugs rnga'i 'od kyis bslangs nas sems bskyed de
NK073(pu)006:1989: sa bcu rim gyis spyod par bshad do //
NK073(pu)006:1990: rang sangs rgyas la lngas bstan pa'i /
NK073(pu)006:1992: 'jug sgo dang gang zag thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:1993: rang byang chub ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1995: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug pa zhib tu 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK073(pu)006:1996: zhugs pa zhes pas rten de rnams kyis rten gyi gang zag kun bsdus pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1997: dbang po tha ma'i 'bring rang byang chub kyi 'bras bu mngon du byed par nus pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:1998: dad brtson rnams nyan thos dang mthun la /
NK073(pu)006:1999: shes rab de las cung 'phags te /
NK073(pu)006:2000: gzugs kyi phung po chos kyi phyogs gcig bdag med par rtogs pa'i shes rab dang ldan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2002: rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2003: de la gnyis kyi log pa'i lta ba dgag pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2004: chos thams cad mu stegs ces pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:2005: lta gzhi nyan thos dang mthun pas nyan thos kyi
NK073(pu)006:2006: skabs su bshad pa ltar phyi nang gi chos thams
NK073(pu)006:2007: cad la mu stegs la sogs pa'i log rtog gi
NK073(pu)006:2008: tshogs kyis yod med kyi sgro dang skur ba dang
NK073(pu)006:2009: blo la kun tu brtags pa'i bdag rtag pa dang
NK073(pu)006:2010: / chad pa dang phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen rnyes med pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2011: thag sbrul gyi dpes nyan thos dag mthun la /
NK073(pu)006:2012: yang nyan thos dang mthun zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2013: zhes pas yul rags par snang ba kun rdzob kyi bden pa /
NK073(pu)006:2014: rdul phra rab don dam pa /
NK073(pu)006:2015: 'dzin byed kyi shes pa'ang rags par snang ba kun rdzob /
NK073(pu)006:2016: de yang skad cig ma cha shas dang bral ba 'phags pa'i spyod yul du gyur pa /
NK073(pu)006:2017: don dam pa mthun pa'i thog tu nyan thos kyi
NK073(pu)006:2018: de las rang sangs rgyas lhag pa'i khyad par du
NK073(pu)006:2019: / gzugs kyi phung po chos kyi phyogs gcig ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:2020: phung po lnga la gzugs kyi phung po chos kyi
NK073(pu)006:2021: bdag gi phyogs gcig yin pas de rdul phra rab
NK073(pu)006:2022: kyang phyogs chas gzhig nas ma grub par bdag med
NK073(pu)006:2023: par rtogs pa la rtogs zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:2024: de la mkhas pa chen po a ro ye shes 'byung gnas kyis /
NK073(pu)006:2026: rgyu'i gzugs bzhi 'bras bu'i gzugs bcu gcig las /
NK073(pu)006:2027: bcu bzhi la ni bdag med par ma rtogs te /
NK073(pu)006:2028: rdul phra rab nyan thos dang mthun /
NK073(pu)006:2029: chos kyi phyogs gcig ces pas rnam par rig byed
NK073(pu)006:2030: ma yin pa'i gzugs yid kyi yul chos la bdag
NK073(pu)006:2032: de la rnam par rig byed ma yin zhes pa'i nges tshig gang yin na /
NK073(pu)006:2033: dge ba dang mi dge ba'i las kyi bag chags
NK073(pu)006:2034: dang ni ldan na dbang po rnam shes kyis mthong
NK073(pu)006:2035: zhing rig par byar med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2036: 'o na de las khyad par du gzugs zhes ci'i phyir brjod na /
NK073(pu)006:2037: gzhon du rung ba'i phyir te /
NK073(pu)006:2038: dge mi dge gang gi'ang rig byed ma yin pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2039: de la dge bar rig byed ma yin pa ni
NK073(pu)006:2040: sngar tshul khrims ma nos na dge bar gyur la
NK073(pu)006:2041: / phyi'i de'i 'gal rkyen spyad na sngar gyi dge ba'i bag chags de zhig pas so //
NK073(pu)006:2042: mi dge ba'ang de dang mtshungs pas gzugs zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2044: gzugs kyi phung po chos kyi phyogs gcig ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:2045: gzugs bco lnga las rnam par rig byed ma yin pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2046: ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs yin pas stong par ma shes te /
NK073(pu)006:2047: bcu bzhi pa la chos kyi phyogs gcig ces smos pas bdag med par rtogs so //
NK073(pu)006:2048: gzung ba'i rtog pa nyams phyir dang /
NK073(pu)006:2049: 'dzin pa'i rtog pa ma spangs phyir /
NK073(pu)006:2051: de la kha che pan che na re /
NK073(pu)006:2052: phyi gzung ba'i yul thams cad med par shes pa ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:2053: gzung ba'i rtog pa nyams phyir dang /
NK073(pu)006:2054: zer bas rags pa ni med par shes te phra
NK073(pu)006:2055: rab la med zer mi nus pas gsungs skad de
NK073(pu)006:2056: / de ni nyan thos dang yang khyad med do //
NK073(pu)006:2057: bsam gtan gyi rtogs tshul ni /
NK073(pu)006:2058: rang byang chub kyi 'bras bu thob pa'i dus na'ang
NK073(pu)006:2059: zhes pa la sogs te 'dir nyan thos dang khyad
NK073(pu)006:2060: par yod ste / nyan thos ni dang po yang dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten la /
NK073(pu)006:2061: 'bras bu len pa'i dus na'ang dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten pa yin na /
NK073(pu)006:2063: sngon gyi sbyangs pa mtha' phyin pas rang gis dngos
NK073(pu)006:2064: po gang la rten 'brel gyi don rtogs te 'bras
NK073(pu)006:2065: bu thob pas / rang byang chub ces bya la /
NK073(pu)006:2066: 'bras bu thob pa'i dus na'ang zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2067: 'bras bu rgyu gtan la dbab ste /
NK073(pu)006:2068: 'bras bu yid bzhin bde mchog gis thob ste /
NK073(pu)006:2069: mngon du bya ba'i dus kyi tshe skabs gang la rag na /
NK073(pu)006:2070: bsgom pa la rag las pas de'i dus su yang /
NK073(pu)006:2071: nyan thos ltar dge ba'i bshes gnyen la mi ltos te /
NK073(pu)006:2072: sngon goms pa'i stobs su zhugs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2073: dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang mi 'bral ba'i smon lam ma btab pa gnyis kyis so //
NK073(pu)006:2074: sngon goms pa'i shugs kyis zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2075: tshe snga ma la rten 'brel rtog dpyod goms pa stobs su gyur pa'i shugs /
NK073(pu)006:2076: nyi ma gling bzhir rang bzhin gyis 'khor ba dang
NK073(pu)006:2077: 'dra ba'i shes rab kyis bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:2079: rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2080: ting nge 'dzin bsam gtan mar me shi ba lta
NK073(pu)006:2081: bu ste rus pa mthong bas bltas pa la rten
NK073(pu)006:2082: 'brel rtogs te / rten 'brel la yang phyir dang nang gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:2083: nang ni rus pa shi ba las byung /
NK073(pu)006:2085: de na ba nas rim pa bzhin du ma rig pa'i bar du rtsad bcad de /
NK073(pu)006:2086: gtugs pa la ni rten 'brel lugs las bzlog pa zhes bya /
NK073(pu)006:2087: des ma rig pa bkag pas 'du byed 'gag nas /
NK073(pu)006:2088: rga shi'i bar du 'gags par rtogs pas ma rig pa bkag pa'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:2089: bsam gtan mar me rgyud zad pa lta bu la mnyam par bzhag ste /
NK073(pu)006:2090: dper na mar ma zad na me mi zad pa bzhin du /
NK073(pu)006:2091: me yod kyi bar la g.yo ba mi rtag mar
NK073(pu)006:2092: zad na dus mnyam du zad pa bzhin ma rig
NK073(pu)006:2093: pa zad pas rga shi'i bar zad par rtogs te
NK073(pu)006:2094: / ma rig pa bkag pa'i phyir 'gog pa'i ting nge 'dzin yang dang yang du goms pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2095: rten 'brel bcu gcig gnyis kyi sgo nas chos nyid
NK073(pu)006:2096: spros pa dang bral ba zab mo'i don rkyen gyis
NK073(pu)006:2097: rtogs nas / 'bras bu'i thob tshul ni /
NK073(pu)006:2098: rang byang chub kyi zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2099: gong gi rtogs pa'i don la bsgom pa mthar phyin
NK073(pu)006:2100: nas rang byang chub kyi 'bras bu dpa' bo 'jigs
NK073(pu)006:2105: smad na chu 'brugs pa'i rtsal dang ldan pa yin bzhin bde mchog gi sa thob pa yin no //
NK073(pu)006:2106: 'di yang srung ba'i tshul khrims ni nyan thos dang mthun /
NK073(pu)006:2107: spyod pa'i khyad par ni nyan thos dang mthun pa
NK073(pu)006:2108: las khyad par du ting nge 'dzin la brtson par
NK073(pu)006:2111: bse ru bskal pa brgya yi rgyus /
NK073(pu)006:2112: zhes pas nyan thos dang mthun no //
NK073(pu)006:2113: 'di la skyon gsum yon tan gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:2114: spobs pa chung zhing smon lam med pas theg chen la 'jug mi nus /
NK073(pu)006:2115: slob dpon la brten mi nus /
NK073(pu)006:2116: grogs tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa la'ang brten mi nus /
NK073(pu)006:2117: yon tan skye ba barjesa tsa kho rang gi grub mtha' rang shugs kyi zin /
NK073(pu)006:2118: sdig pa'i chos ngang gis 'gags gcig pur gnas shing bsam gtan la brtson pa che /
NK073(pu)006:2119: 'bras bu nyan thos las khyad par ni /
NK073(pu)006:2120: gzugs phung bdag med rtogs pa'i stobs kyis thub pa'i bstan pa mi gnas pa'i dus su /
NK073(pu)006:2122: lus kyis rdzu 'phrul ya ma zung gis 'gro don byed /
NK073(pu)006:2123: de yang bem rig cir ston yang sngar sbyangs pa
NK073(pu)006:2124: chung bas pan+di ta dang 'khor los bsgyur bar ston
NK073(pu)006:2125: mi nus / phyis bder gshegs byon pa'i rtags snang
NK073(pu)006:2126: na shes rab kyi spobs pa chung bas zad par
NK073(pu)006:2128: mdo sde nas bskal chen khri 'das nas ston pa
NK073(pu)006:2129: byon la khad kyi sngon rol du nyid dang mthun
NK073(pu)006:2130: pa'i sprul sku 'char nas des bgro gling gi tshul
NK073(pu)006:2131: du theg chen la btsud de sems bskyed nas sangs
NK073(pu)006:2132: rgyas thob par bshad skad do //
NK073(pu)006:2133: des na de yan chad du ma rtogs pa phyal ba rgyang 'phen gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:2134: log par rtogs pa mur thug dang /
NK073(pu)006:2136: theg chung 'di gnyis la ni phyogs rtogs zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:2137: lus sems 'brel med du lta ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2138: gzhan don sems bskyed med pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2139: shes rab kyis don dam phyogs kyang shas phra ba bas ma rtogs pas theg chung zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2140: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la bzhi'i dang po
NK073(pu)006:2141: 'jug sgo dang gang zag thung mong du bstan pa
NK073(pu)006:2142: ni / byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la zhugs pa rnams kyis zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2143: dang por 'jug pa'i sgo ni byang chub sems dpa' zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:2144: 'dir lam lnga dang sbyar te 'bru mnan na /
NK073(pu)006:2145: tshogs lam du bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pas /
NK073(pu)006:2146: kun gzhi la bsags pa'i bag chags ngan pa'i tshogs dus thog ma med pa nas ldan pa rnams /
NK073(pu)006:2147: tshogs lam mthar phyin pa'i dus su /
NK073(pu)006:2148: gtan nas byang ste sbyangs yag pas nad kyi lhag
NK073(pu)006:2149: ma ma lus pa bzhin song bas ni bya la
NK073(pu)006:2150: / tshogs lam mthar phyin pa'i yon tan rnams chub pas chub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2151: bsags sbyangs de nyid la sems rab tu gnas shing bstun te dpa' bas sems dapa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2152: sbyor lam du nges 'byed cha bzhis bdag gnyis dag
NK073(pu)006:2153: ste nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa rtsa ba nas byang
NK073(pu)006:2154: zhing bdag med gnyis mngon du gyur pas chub pa'o
NK073(pu)006:2155: // sems ni de nyid gnyen po'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK073(pu)006:2156: des spang bya spong bas dpa' ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2157: de nyid mtha' phyin pas mthong lam nyid yin na /
NK073(pu)006:2158: mthong lam du 'khor ba'i chos rgyu 'bras ril byang
NK073(pu)006:2159: zhing don dam pa'i bden pa khong du chub ste
NK073(pu)006:2160: / mnyam bzhag rang don ting nge 'dzin la sems shing /
NK073(pu)006:2161: rjes sgyu ma lta bus 'gro don la sems te mdzad pas don la brtul bas dpa' ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2162: sa lnga ba'i bar shes sgrib rags pa byang ste /
NK073(pu)006:2163: bden pa dbyer med chub la de nyid las mi 'gyur ba la sems dpa' brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:2164: brgyad pa'i bar la phra ba byang la /
NK073(pu)006:2165: bcu pa'i bar phra ba'i phra ba 'ang byang ste /
NK073(pu)006:2166: mun pa dag nas snang bar gyur pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:2167: yon tan rnams chub cing de las mi g.yo ba
NK073(pu)006:2168: nyid sems dpa' ba'i ngang la 'gro don la ci
NK073(pu)006:2169: ltar yang skrag pa med pas dpa' ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2170: theg pa zhes pa gong du bshad ste /
NK073(pu)006:2171: zhugs pa ni 'jug pa'i sgo ste ngo bo bden pa gnyis so //
NK073(pu)006:2172: zhugs pa rnams kyis zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2173: gang zhugs pa'i gang zag bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2174: dbang po tha ma'i rab bden pa gnyis rtogs pa'i shes rab dang ldan la /
NK073(pu)006:2175: brtson 'grus rab dang ldan pas dka' ba spyod pa la skyo ba chung ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2177: lta ba ces pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2178: de yang kun rdzob dang don dam pa gnyis las /
NK073(pu)006:2179: dang por don dam pa bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2180: kun nas nyon mongs pa zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2181: snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i khams gsum 'khor ba'i chos
NK073(pu)006:2182: thams cad ni gzung 'dzin gnyis kyis nyen pa'i dbang
NK073(pu)006:2183: gis / dus gnas phyogs kun nas nyon mongs shing sdug bsngal te /
NK073(pu)006:2184: de yang spyi'i mtshan nyid mi rtag sdug bsngal yang rang gi mtshan nyid stong zhing bdag med de /
NK073(pu)006:2185: yul ni rdul phra rab yin la de phyogs cha drug gis gzhig na ma grub pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2186: shes pa ni skad cig ma yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2187: de yang dus gsum gyi chas gzhig na ma grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2188: de nyid spros pa'i mtshan nyid thams cad dang bral
NK073(pu)006:2189: ba la ni don dam par 'khor ba'i chos thams
NK073(pu)006:2190: cad kun rdzob tu snang yang spros mtha' brgyad dang
NK073(pu)006:2191: bral ba rang bzhin med pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2192: rnam par byang ba'i chos thams cad ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:2193: khams gsum mam sdug bsngal lam mya ngan las 'das
NK073(pu)006:2194: te 'khor ba'i rnam pa ma grub par tha snyad
NK073(pu)006:2195: du byang ba ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:2196: de mi 'gags par snang ba'i chos thams cad ni gzugs sku gnyis yon tan dang bcas pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:2197: des gsungs pa'i lam gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:2198: kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje dang gdul bya'i
NK073(pu)006:2199: rgyud dag pa'i byin rlabs gnyis 'dzom pa las me
NK073(pu)006:2200: long gi gzugs brnyan bzhin rang 'char gyi /
NK073(pu)006:2201: dper na 'ja' nam mkhar dbyer med pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:2202: don dam pa'i ngang du rang bzhin med /
NK073(pu)006:2203: de nyid kyi tha snyad las kyang 'das pa yin zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2204: de ni mi bslu ba'i phyir don dam pa'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2205: de ltar don dam pa bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:2206: da ni kun rdzob bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2207: kun rdzob tu ni zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2208: dngos po ma grub kyang nan gyis bartagagasa pa nyid
NK073(pu)006:2209: kyis 'khrul pa nyes pa dang bcas par snang ba'o
NK073(pu)006:2210: // de ni sgyu ma tsam zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2211: sgyu ma ni mkhan pos de nyid kyi rgyu rkyen 'tshogs nas snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:2212: blta mkhan gyi dbang po'i dgos pa skong ba don yang ngo bo ma grub pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:2213: 'dir 'gro ba rnams kyi rig pa sgyu ma mkhan dang 'dra bas /
NK073(pu)006:2214: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa gnyis sgyu ma'i rgyu dang /
NK073(pu)006:2215: las dang nyon mongs pa sgyu ma'i rkyen 'dzom pa
NK073(pu)006:2216: las khams gsum gyi chos thams cad so so'i bya
NK073(pu)006:2217: ba byed pa ltad mo ba'i dbang po'i dgos pa
NK073(pu)006:2219: de yang 'khor ba'i chos kyang 'khrul snang gi ngo
NK073(pu)006:2220: la ma grub bzhin snang ba sgyu ma lta bu
NK073(pu)006:2221: ste / tsam gyi sgras de tsam du yang ma dmigs par bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:2222: mtshan nyid ma 'dres par so sor yod ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:2223: rgyu dkar ba'i las kyis 'bras bu mtho ris su ma 'dres par yod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2224: sdig pa sgyu ma tsam gyi las kyis ngan song
NK073(pu)006:2225: sgyu ma lta bu dge ba dang mtshan nyid mtshan
NK073(pu)006:2226: nyid ma 'dres par so so yod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2227: rgyu dge ba rang yang bye brag mtshan nyid ma 'dres par so sor yod bzhin du /
NK073(pu)006:2228: de'i 'bras bu mtho ris kyang so sor ma 'dres par zhib par gnas la /
NK073(pu)006:2229: rnam par byang ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK073(pu)006:2230: ma 'gags pa'i mtshan nyid thams cad kyang mtshan nyid
NK073(pu)006:2231: ma 'dres par gdul bya dang mthun pa'i sku gsum
NK073(pu)006:2232: gyi mdzad pa so sor yod te /
NK073(pu)006:2233: so so'i bya ba byed pa ni gtan du ma
NK073(pu)006:2234: yin te mi rtag cing mi brten pa kun rdzob
NK073(pu)006:2235: ces bya'o // 'o na 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kun rdzob yin na /
NK073(pu)006:2236: mya ngan las 'das pa la kun rdzob ces gdags pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:2237: bde bar gshegs pa'i ngo bo rang byung gi ye
NK073(pu)006:2238: shes chos kyi sku la ni kun rdzob kyi gdags
NK073(pu)006:2239: gzhi bral te ye shes 'ba' zhig gi snang ba
NK073(pu)006:2241: sku gnyis kyi mdzad pa che yan dang bcas pa
NK073(pu)006:2242: thams cad ni gdul bya 'ba' zhig gi snang ba
NK073(pu)006:2243: ste / thams cad mkhyen pa rang ngo la rdul gyi cha yang ma dmigs te /
NK073(pu)006:2244: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba'i tha snyad kyang ma grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2245: des na gdul bya'i ngos kyi snang ba thams cad
NK073(pu)006:2246: la dag ma dag gis kun rdzob ces brjod do
NK073(pu)006:2247: // de ltar bden pa gnyis de la yang don drug gis bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2248: bden pa gnyis kyi ngo bo dang /
NK073(pu)006:2254: de la dang po kun rdzob bden pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:2255: khams gsum gyi 'khrul pa'i ngo la snang ba'i bem rig gis bsdus pa'i dngos po thams cad do //
NK073(pu)006:2257: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK073(pu)006:2259: de la sngon gyi mkhas pa rnams kyis /
NK073(pu)006:2260: nang rig pas bsdus pa thams cad ni /
NK073(pu)006:2261: nam zhig byang chub la reg pa'i rang bzhin yin te /
NK073(pu)006:2263: byang chub kyi snying po can yin te /
NK073(pu)006:2264: sad snga phyi tsam la rag las pas yang dag
NK073(pu)006:2265: pa'i don byed nus pas yang dag ces bya la
NK073(pu)006:2266: / da lta gzung 'dzin 'khrul chos su snang bas kun rdzob /
NK073(pu)006:2267: yul bem pa'i cha thams cad ni 'bras bu la
NK073(pu)006:2268: reg pa'i bya ba mi byed pas log pa zhes
NK073(pu)006:2269: bya ste / thad sor 'khrul chos kun rdzob bo //
NK073(pu)006:2271: snang la don byed nus pa chu 'thungs pas skom pa sel ba lta bu dang /
NK073(pu)006:2272: snang la don mi nus pa chu zla dang 'ja' tshon lta bu dang /
NK073(pu)006:2273: mi snang pa don byed mi nus pa ri bong rwa dang mo gsham gyi bu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:2274: snang la don byed nus pa'ang cha bzhis 'grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:2275: mu stegs kyi rdzas can gyi brtags pa ma grub pas brtag na dben pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2276: bum pas chu skyor ba la sogs pa so so'i don byed nus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2277: 'gro ba drug so so'i dbang po'i ngo la mthun par snang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2278: 'byung ba la sogs pa so so'i gzhan dbang rten cing 'brel pas 'byung bas bskyed ce'o //
NK073(pu)006:2279: de la gsar bshad 'gas bem rig gang ltar rung
NK073(pu)006:2280: gong gi chos bzhi ldan ni yang dag kun rdzob
NK073(pu)006:2281: yin la / chos bzhi gcig tsam ma tshang ba yang log pa'i kun rdzob bo //
NK073(pu)006:2283: kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK073(pu)006:2284: skad cig ma dang bcas pas mi rtag cing /
NK073(pu)006:2285: bdag 'dzin gyis bskyed pas sdug bsngal ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2286: ngo bo 'khrul chos la longs spyod cing 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid can no //
NK073(pu)006:2287: sgra 'jug pa'i rgyu mtshan dang mthun dpe thun mong ba sdeb ste bshad na /
NK073(pu)006:2290: bardzabasa pa'i don gyis na kun rdzob ste /
NK073(pu)006:2291: dpe ni rnyogs ma dwangs pa'i chu gsal ba la zla ba'i gzugs brnyan 'char ba de /
NK073(pu)006:2292: skyes bu gang dang gang gis bardzabasa te rnyogs na /
NK073(pu)006:2293: chu'i rnyogs ma des zla ba'i gzugs brnyan yang bsgribs pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:2294: don dam bden pa spros mtha' brgyad ngang gis bral bas dwangs pa'i bdag nyid can la /
NK073(pu)006:2295: thams cad mkhyen pa'i che yon zla ba'i gzugs brnyan
NK073(pu)006:2296: dang 'dra ba 'char du rung ba de 'khrul rtog
NK073(pu)006:2297: dbang yul gyi chos kun rdzob kyis bsgribs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2298: bsgribs pa'i don gyis na kun bsgribs te /
NK073(pu)006:2299: gong ma'i don des don dam bden pa yang dag ma mthong bas /
NK073(pu)006:2300: dper na mig rab rib can gyis 'khrul pa'i yul dngos por ma mthong ba bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:2301: don de la bden pa zhes pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2302: kun brtags can 'khrul pa la longs spyod pa'i dus su bden pa ltar snang ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2303: dper na mig nad can la skra shad kyi 'khor lo bden pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:2305: khams gsum sems can la rags par snang /
NK073(pu)006:2306: bdag med rtogs pa'i mgo zug pa la phra bar snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2307: don dam pa'i bden pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:2308: spros mtha' brgyad kyi dben pa 'khrul pa can gyi spyod yul ma yin pa /
NK073(pu)006:2309: ye shes dam pa'i spyod yul dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2310: dbye ba ni rnam grangs dang /
NK073(pu)006:2312: rnam grangs ni chos can so so'i bye brag thams
NK073(pu)006:2313: cad nyan thos kyi rdul dang skad cig mar btags
NK073(pu)006:2314: pa la sogs pa so sor ma grub pa'i ngos
NK073(pu)006:2315: nas btags te / don dam pa'i ngo bo la
NK073(pu)006:2316: du ma med kyang chos can ma grub pa'i ngos
NK073(pu)006:2317: nas btags te / nas snang ba'o // ming gi rnam grangs ni /
NK073(pu)006:2321: yang dag pa la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2322: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam pa ni rang gi ngo bo ste /
NK073(pu)006:2323: ming gi rnam grangs kyi tha snyad thams cad dang bral ba /
NK073(pu)006:2324: thos pa dang bsam pa'i shes rab kyis reg par ma nus pa /
NK073(pu)006:2325: sgom pa'i shes rab mthar phyin pa'i ngo bo ye shes dam pa'i yul lo //
NK073(pu)006:2326: mtshan nyid ni stong zhing bdag med pa shes brjod thams cad kyi yul las 'das pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2328: pa pa ra mi ta na /
NK073(pu)006:2329: don dam pa ste ngo bo mi 'gyur /
NK073(pu)006:2330: rtogs pas mi bslu kun rdzob thams cad kyang de nyid du dbyer med la /
NK073(pu)006:2331: 'gyur ldog mi mnga' ba'i phyir na'ang bden pa'i sgra 'jug go //
NK073(pu)006:2333: phyogs tsam mthun pa'i dpe mang yang /
NK073(pu)006:2335: kun rdzob kyi dngos po thams cad la khyab kyang des ngo bo la gos pa med pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2336: yod med kyi spros pa'i mtha' mi rnyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2337: rang bzhin la dngos po 'khrul brtags kyi chos kyis dben pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2338: yul gang la snang na mthong lam yang chad pa la ji bzhin par snang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:2339: 'o na bden pa gnyis pa de gcig gam tha dad ce na /
NK073(pu)006:2340: rnam pa kun tu tha dad na'ang mdo las skyon bzhi 'byung ste /
NK073(pu)006:2341: kun rdzob dang de'i rang bzhin don dam pa la chos nyid kyi 'brel pa med pa'i skyon dang /
NK073(pu)006:2342: don dam rtogs kyang 'khrul ba zil gyis mi non pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2343: des na 'phags pa'i thugs rje dang gdul bya'i bsags
NK073(pu)006:2344: pa gnyis 'khor 'das so sor 'gyur ba'i skyon dang
NK073(pu)006:2345: / bden pa mthong yang tha dad pa mun snang
NK073(pu)006:2346: bzhin gang zag gis dus gcig la gnyis ka tha
NK073(pu)006:2347: dad du mthong ba'i skyon no //
NK073(pu)006:2349: rnam pa tha dad du gcig pa'i dbang gis don
NK073(pu)006:2350: dam pa mthong bas grol ba bzhin kun rdzob mthong
NK073(pu)006:2353: don dam mthong bas kyang 'ching ba dang 'phags pa'i
NK073(pu)006:2354: ngo la stong zhing bdag med pa bzhin sems can
NK073(pu)006:2355: gyi ngo la'ang de dang 'dra ste 'bad med grol
NK073(pu)006:2356: ba dang / sems can gyi ngo la kun brtags
NK073(pu)006:2357: 'khrul pa rang rgyud snang ba bzhin 'phags pa la
NK073(pu)006:2358: 'ang de dang 'dra ste grol thar med pa'i skyon
NK073(pu)006:2359: ba dang / no // 'on kyang 'gal ba sdum pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2360: mkhas pa snga ma kun ni /
NK073(pu)006:2361: ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad ste /
NK073(pu)006:2362: de 'ang lam bgrod tshul la ltos na /
NK073(pu)006:2363: tshogs lam man chad du kun rdzob rang rgyud du snang /
NK073(pu)006:2364: sbyor lam du bdag med mgo zug nas phyogs re mthong /
NK073(pu)006:2365: mthong lam du don dam rang gi mtshad nyid mthong /
NK073(pu)006:2366: drug pa mngon du gyur nas bden pa dbyer med mthong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2367: gang zag la ltos na rtogs ma rtogs gnyis ngo
NK073(pu)006:2368: bo la lhan cig kyang rtogs pa la don dam
NK073(pu)006:2369: du snang / ma rtogs pa la 'khrul par snang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:2371: de nyid dam gzhan du brjod du med ces bshad de /
NK073(pu)006:2372: gcig pa ni bkag gnyis su ni khas mi len
NK073(pu)006:2373: pas kun rdzob dbang po'i mngon sum du snang ba
NK073(pu)006:2374: de nyid don dam ma yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2375: de las gzhan du'ang don dam du ni brjod du med ce'o //
NK073(pu)006:2376: des na byang chub sems dpa'i rtogs pa'i lta ba bden pa gnyis kyi rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2378: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu spyod ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2379: spyad ces pas spyod pa'i khyad par yang bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2380: de la spyir 'dir pha rol tu phyin pa bcu
NK073(pu)006:2381: zhes pas spyod pa'i dngos gzhi mthar phyin pa dang
NK073(pu)006:2384: pha rol phyin pa bcu re re spyad pa mthar
NK073(pu)006:2385: phyin pa stobs su gyur pa 'bras bu re re
NK073(pu)006:2387: pha rol tu phyin pa de dang de spyad pas 'bras bu de dang de thob pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2388: sa de thob pas pha rol tu phyin pa de
NK073(pu)006:2389: stobs su gyur pa mthar thug pa zhes pa bstan
NK073(pu)006:2390: te / des na dang po rten gyi gang zag
NK073(pu)006:2391: gcig gis snying rje chen pos khams gsum gyi sems
NK073(pu)006:2392: can rjes su dran nas de dag gi don du
NK073(pu)006:2393: te / sems bskyed nas / tshogs lam bzhi gsum bcu gnyis nyams su blangs pa'i dus nas /
NK073(pu)006:2394: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu phra rags nyams su
NK073(pu)006:2395: blangs nas sbyin pa'angasa zang zing phra ba sbyin pa
NK073(pu)006:2396: tsam yan chod / tshul khrims ni bslab pa rin
NK073(pu)006:2397: po che gsum khas blang tshad tsam la dri mas
NK073(pu)006:2399: bzod pa'ang go cha'i brtson 'grus dang ldan pa'i sgo
NK073(pu)006:2400: nas bsgom brtson 'grus kyang dran pa dang shes bzhin
NK073(pu)006:2401: ma yengs pa'i ngos nas rtsom /
NK073(pu)006:2402: bsam gtan yang don spyi yid kyi yul du byas pa tsam gyi ngos nas bsgom /
NK073(pu)006:2403: shes rab kyang bdag med la mos pas so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis 'jug /
NK073(pu)006:2404: des na lam stobs su gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:2405: sbyor lam du nges 'byed cha bzhis chos dang gang
NK073(pu)006:2406: zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i dus su yang pha
NK073(pu)006:2407: rol tu phyin pa drug stobs su gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:2408: de la pha rol tu phyin pa re re la'ang rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK073(pu)006:2412: 'bras bus gang thob pa dang bzhi bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:2413: de la sbyin pa rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:2414: dngos po gang la'ang ma chags par gtong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2416: zang zing dang chos dang skyabs so //
NK073(pu)006:2421: de la gtong ba ni 'phral gyi gos dang zas nor phra mo gtong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2422: de dag ni tshogs lam nas ldan te stobs su gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2424: rgyal srid dang bu smad la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2425: bzod thob yan chod kyi spyod yul lo //
NK073(pu)006:2427: rang gi lus dang mig dang srog dang sha khrag gtong ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2429: de na sbyin pa gsum ka'i nus stobs mthong lam nas rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:2431: yi ge sbyin pa nas shes rgyud dgrol ba'i bar te /
NK073(pu)006:2432: tshogs sbyor mthong gsum la ci tsam nus pa'i stobs brtsa ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2433: gzhan grol ba'i rkyen du 'gyur ba las ma gtogs pa rnyed pa la stos pa med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2435: 'khor ba las skyabs pa ni chos kyi sbyin pa dang yang mthun la /
NK073(pu)006:2436: gnod pa las skyabs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2437: gzhan sdug bsngal dang bral bar byed pa'i rnam grangs so //
NK073(pu)006:2439: gsod par nges pa'i dgra dang shan pa'i lag nas srog bslu ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2440: de yang lam mtho dman gnas skabs dang sbyar ro //
NK073(pu)006:2441: mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni ser sna ste /
NK073(pu)006:2442: de dag la sgyid lug nas mi brtson pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2443: sbyin pa la slar 'gyod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2444: de dag gi dngos po'i bye brag rnams gtong mi bra ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2446: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i blo ste /
NK073(pu)006:2448: sbyin par byed pa po dang /
NK073(pu)006:2449: rdzas gsum don dam par rang bzhin med par shes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2450: de'ang las dang po pa'i dus su blos gzhan rgyas 'debs tsam yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2451: mthar phyin pa'i dus su yul yul can 'dzom pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK073(pu)006:2452: gnyen po bskyed mi dgos par lhun grub tu 'char ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2453: de'i 'bras bu ni dang po rab tu dga' ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2454: mtshan de la yang rgyu mtshan gsum gyis spang bya spong ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:2455: khams gsum gyi dri ma gtan nas dag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2457: don dam pa'i bden pa mthong bas rtogs pa la spros pa'i dri ma med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2458: mthong bya ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhal mngon du mthong nas chos gsan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2459: yang rnam pa gcig tu sbyin pa'i pha rol tu
NK073(pu)006:2460: phyin pa'i stobs rdzogs pa'i sa yin pas sbyin pa'i
NK073(pu)006:2461: zang zing gis yul dga' zhing /
NK073(pu)006:2462: bsod nams kyis bdag dga' ba'i 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir yang rab tu dga' ba'i sa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2463: de ltar rtogs shing mthong ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK073(pu)006:2464: dri ma sbyong bar byed pas na sa gnyis pa
NK073(pu)006:2465: yin te / sa der tshul khrims kyi pha rol
NK073(pu)006:2466: tu phyin pa'i stobs rdzogs te de'ang tshul khrims rang
NK073(pu)006:2467: gi ngo bo ni 'chal ba'i dri ma med pa'o
NK073(pu)006:2469: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK073(pu)006:2472: de yang lam mtho dman gyi rim pa bzhin du blos rtsal dang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2473: mi mthun phyogs ni 'chal ba'i dri ma ste log pa'i zhe 'dod dang bcas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2474: 'grub byed kyi yan lag ni 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2475: de'i rgyas theb pa la blo tshod kyi rim pa bzhin du'o //
NK073(pu)006:2476: 'bras bu'i ngo bo dri ma med pa zhes pa
NK073(pu)006:2477: yang ting nge 'dzin gyi dri ma dag par byed
NK073(pu)006:2478: pa'i phyir dang / tshul khrims kyi stobs rdzogs nas 'chal ba'i dri ma gtan nas dag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2479: pha rol tu phyin pa'i nges tshig kyang de nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:2480: de ltar ting nge 'dzin gyi dri ma spangs nas
NK073(pu)006:2481: rtsal yongs su sbyong bas sa gsum pa 'od byed
NK073(pu)006:2482: pa'i sa ste / der bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa'i stobs rdzogs pa yin te /
NK073(pu)006:2483: de yang bzod pa rang gi ngo bo 'khrugs pa med pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2484: lam gyi bye brag gis mtho dman grangs mang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:2485: rnam grangs ni chos nyid zab mo rtogs pas sa de la nyams nga ba med pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2486: bdag gzhan gyi don du lus ngag gi sdug bsngal khyad du gsod de /
NK073(pu)006:2487: don bsgrub pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2488: gzhan gyis sdug bsngal bar gtses kyang de nyid chos kyi 'grub byed du mthong ste yid mi 'khrugs /
NK073(pu)006:2489: lan mi 'debs pa'i bzod pa dang gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:2490: mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni gong ma gsum la bzod mi nus nas sems 'khrugs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2491: 'grub byed kyi yan lag ni 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2492: las dang po pas rtogs pa'i rgyas 'debs nas tha mar rang shar 'byung ba'i bar ro //
NK073(pu)006:2493: 'bras bu ni gsum pa la bzod pa'i stobs rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:2494: pa'i phyir 'od byed pa zhes bya ste ting nge
NK073(pu)006:2497: de nas ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal sems can gyi
NK073(pu)006:2498: don du kun tu 'phro zhing sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK073(pu)006:2499: sbyong ba ni 'od 'phro ba ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:2500: de la brtson 'grus kyi stobs rdzogs so //
NK073(pu)006:2501: de la brtson 'grus rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:2502: bsgrub par bya ba'i don la sgyid lug pa med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2503: rnam grangs ni dkar po dge ba'i phyogs thams cad
NK073(pu)006:2504: la brtson pa lam gyi gegs su gyur pa rnams
NK073(pu)006:2505: spong ba la brtson pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2506: sems can gyi don du brtson pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2507: mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni snyoms las sgyid lug dang bcas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2508: 'grub byed kyi yan lag ni 'khor gsum dag pa'i rgyas thebs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2509: 'bras bu ni bzhi pa 'od 'phro ba ste ting
NK073(pu)006:2510: nge 'dzin rtsal 'byongs pa tshad du phyin pa dang
NK073(pu)006:2511: / gzhan don gyi mdzad pa thams cad rgyu de la rdzogs pas /
NK073(pu)006:2512: brtson 'grus kyi 'bras bu yang yin la brtson 'grus mthar phyin pa yang yin no //
NK073(pu)006:2513: de man chad kyi sa bzhi po dag ni shes
NK073(pu)006:2514: bya'i sgrib pa rags pa mi gnas pa yin te
NK073(pu)006:2515: / de nyid lam yin pa'i phyir ched 'dzin gyi sgo nas lam 'grod pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2516: rim gyis 'jug pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir yang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:2517: de yang rigs pa la lnga ste /
NK073(pu)006:2518: bden pa gnyis so sor cha 'byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2519: mi mthun pa dang gnyen po'i bye brag dang /
NK073(pu)006:2520: mnyam rjes kyi bye brag dang /
NK073(pu)006:2521: mnyam bzhag la yang don dam pa'i bden pa'i bden
NK073(pu)006:2522: pa ye shes dam pa'i yul smra bsam las 'das
NK073(pu)006:2523: pa shes rab kyi spyod yul byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2524: spang bya'i nyon mongs pas mi gos kyang bag tshab dang bcas pa /
NK073(pu)006:2525: de dag lnga pa dang bcu pa'i bar du rim gyis sbyongs te /
NK073(pu)006:2526: de yang sa lnga pa la bden pa dbyer med
NK073(pu)006:2527: du slob pa'ang kun rdzob dang don dam mtshan nyid
NK073(pu)006:2528: mi 'dra ba gnyis skad cig la mgo snyoms pa
NK073(pu)006:2530: phye 'gam pa dang gling bu 'bud pa gnyis skyes bu gcig la ma 'dzoms pa yin kyang /
NK073(pu)006:2531: dbyer med zung 'jug don gyi ngo bo yin gyis mi sbyong kha med la /
NK073(pu)006:2532: shin tu dka' ba'i phyir na sbyong dka' ba zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2533: de ni bsam gtan gyi grogs ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK073(pu)006:2534: stang gis gtso che bas bsam gtan gyi pha rol
NK073(pu)006:2536: ngo bo ni rigs pa yul la ma 'brel pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2537: rnam grangs ni mi dge ba'i stobs gnon pa'i bsam gtan dang /
NK073(pu)006:2538: yon tan gong du bskyed pa'i bsam gtan /
NK073(pu)006:2539: dge ba'i chos zag med nye bar sgrub pa'i bsam gtan no //
NK073(pu)006:2540: de gsum yang zhi gnas dang lhag mthong las mtha' gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:2541: zhi gnas kyis mngon shes la sogs pa 'phags pa'i che yon bsgrub /
NK073(pu)006:2542: lhag mthong gis srid pa'i nyes pa 'joms /
NK073(pu)006:2543: las mthas sems can gyi don phun sum tshogs par 'gyur /
NK073(pu)006:2544: mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni yul gyi phyir rnam par g.yeng ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2545: 'grub byed kyi yan lag ni 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa ste bsgom bya bsgom byed med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2546: 'bras bu ni mthar phyin pas lnga pa sbyong dka' ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2547: bden pa dbyer med slob nas mi mthun gnyen po dbyer med mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2548: des na pha rol tu phyin pa'i 'bras bu yang yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2549: de nyid kyi stobs kyang der rdzogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2550: sa drug pa la shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stobs su gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:2551: de yang shes rab kyi ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:2552: thogs pa med par shes bya la 'jug pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2553: rnam grangs ni spyi'i mtshan nyid stong zhing bdag med par shes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2554: rang gi mtshan nyid dngos po'i rgyu rkyen mi 'gags par shes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2555: de gnyis zung 'jug tu shes pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2556: mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni shes rab 'chal ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2557: phyogs su 'dzin pa log rtog gi tshogs so //
NK073(pu)006:2558: 'grub byed kyi yan lag ni 'khor gsum yongs su
NK073(pu)006:2559: dag pa ste shes rab rang gi ngo bo nyid
NK073(pu)006:2560: de / 'og ma rnams kyi rgyal 'debs ni 'di'i lam tsam yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2561: 'di nyid ni don gyi ngo bo'o //
NK073(pu)006:2562: 'bras bu bden pa dbyer med kyi don mngon du gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:2563: shes rab kyi stobs mthar phyin cing shes bya'i rtsal rdzogs pa'i phyir mngon du gyur pas /
NK073(pu)006:2564: sa der ni shes bya'i sgrib pa rags pa gsum gong du bstan pa ltar nyid mi gnas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2565: sa bdun pa ring du song ba yan chad du
NK073(pu)006:2566: 'bras bu'i pha rol tu phyin pa bzhi yin pas
NK073(pu)006:2568: thabs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni sems can
NK073(pu)006:2569: gyi don du spang bar bya ba'i nyon mongs pa
NK073(pu)006:2570: nyid la spyod kyang bag tsha ba med cing bdag
NK073(pu)006:2571: gzhan gyi don du gyur pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2572: de'i phyir thabs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stobs su gyur pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:2573: sa brgyad pa la stobs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa nyid brtan cing stobs su gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:2574: de la byang chub sems dpa' de mnyam par bzhag
NK073(pu)006:2575: pa'i chos sangs rgyas kyi rdzu 'phrul las ma gtogs
NK073(pu)006:2576: pa lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten rnams dang nyan
NK073(pu)006:2577: thos rang rgyal dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi
NK073(pu)006:2578: cho 'phrul gyis kyang g.yo bar mi nus te /
NK073(pu)006:2579: snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin gang la mnyam par bzhag
NK073(pu)006:2580: kyang de la ci byas kyang g.yo mi nus so
NK073(pu)006:2581: // de'i phyir mtha' dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:2582: lhun gyis grub pas mi g.yo ba ces kyang bya
NK073(pu)006:2583: // / stobs kyi pha rol du phyin pa zhes kyang bya /
NK073(pu)006:2584: zhi ba'i mthar mi ldog pa'i phyir mi ldog pa'i sa zhes bya /
NK073(pu)006:2585: 'gro don bya ba'i phyir sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes bskul bar mdo sde nas bshad do //
NK073(pu)006:2586: sa dgu pa la smon lam gyi pha rol tu
NK073(pu)006:2587: phyin yongs su rdzogs te so so yang dag par
NK073(pu)006:2588: rig pa bzhis bdag gzhan gyi don thams cad lhun
NK073(pu)006:2589: gyis grub ste / gzhan don gyi mdzad pa la rtsol ba mi dgos la /
NK073(pu)006:2590: mnyam bzhag gi ting nge 'dzin yang yul bral gyi
NK073(pu)006:2591: ye shes chen po brnyes pas rtsol ba dang bral
NK073(pu)006:2592: te / so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi
NK073(pu)006:2593: mngon du gyur pas legs pa'i blo gros zhes bya
NK073(pu)006:2594: te / ste / bdag gzhan gyi don thams cad
NK073(pu)006:2595: rtsol ba dang bral bar shar bas na smon lam
NK073(pu)006:2596: gyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2597: sa bcu pa la ye shes kyi pha rol tu
NK073(pu)006:2598: phyin pa stobs su gyur te sa dang pha rol
NK073(pu)006:2599: tu phyin pa kun gyi stobs rdzogs pa'i phyir ro
NK073(pu)006:2600: / byang chub sems dpa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa'i phyir chos kyi sprin zhes kyang bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:2601: pha rol tu phyin pa na sa bcu pa ni
NK073(pu)006:2602: de bzhin gshegs pa'am de bzhin nyid du'ang gsungs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:2603: phyir / sangs rgyas kyi sa nyid du'ang brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:2604: de'i dus su mthar thug pa med pa'i sangs rgyas
NK073(pu)006:2605: rnams kyis chos gsungs pa rnams kyang ma gsan pa'ang
NK073(pu)006:2606: med / chog shes pa dang dub pa'ang mi mnga' ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2607: sems can mtha' yas pa'i don mdzad kyang sgyid lug pa mi mnga' ste /
NK073(pu)006:2608: bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni zad 'phel med
NK073(pu)006:2609: pa'i chos kyi dbyings rtogs pa'i stobs mnga' ba'i phyir
NK073(pu)006:2610: / tshad med pa'i stobs dang ldan ni //
NK073(pu)006:2611: de'i phyir dpe las mtshan du gsol ba chos kyi sprin no //
NK073(pu)006:2612: ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa'i mkhyen pa rnam
NK073(pu)006:2613: gnyis stobs tshad du phyin pa ye shes kyi pha
NK073(pu)006:2615: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK073(pu)006:2616: las kyi mdzad pa thams cad kyang mi lcog pa
NK073(pu)006:2617: med de lhun gyis grub pa yin pas byang chub
NK073(pu)006:2619: sa bcu rgyun gyi tha ma zhe'am /
NK073(pu)006:2620: kun tu 'od kyi sa zhes bya bar rigs lnga'i
NK073(pu)006:2621: sangs rgyas longs sku chen po dbang bskur zhes mdo
NK073(pu)006:2622: sde zab mo rnams nas 'byung ngo //
NK073(pu)006:2623: des na pha rol tu phyin pa spyad pa'i 'bras bu'ang rim pa bzhin du sa bcu yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2624: sa bcu so so'i gnas skabs su pha rol tu phyin pa de'i stobs su gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2625: des na spyod pa'i dngos por kha tshon bcad pa
NK073(pu)006:2626: ni lam mtho dman gyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK073(pu)006:2627: kyi spyod pa'i dngos po gang ltar spyad kyang pha
NK073(pu)006:2628: rol tu phyin pa bcu 'am drug po de las
NK073(pu)006:2630: des na smon pa'i skabs su gtong ma de bu
NK073(pu)006:2631: gang tsam la'ang pha rol tu phyin pa drug tshang
NK073(pu)006:2632: bar lung man ngag rnams las gsugs so //
NK073(pu)006:2633: sa bcu zhes pas sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin yang bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2634: sa dang po la ting nge 'dzin rang gi ngo bo nyid mngon du gyur la /
NK073(pu)006:2635: de man chad kyi ting nge 'dzin ni lta ba la mos pa'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK073(pu)006:2636: chos nyid rang gi ngo bo mngon du mthong ba'i
NK073(pu)006:2637: ting nge 'dzin nam mkha'i dkyil lta bu la rab
NK073(pu)006:2638: tu dga' bar ming btags pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2639: shes bya'i sgrib pa rags pa dag pa mgo zug
NK073(pu)006:2640: pas na ting nge 'dzin la dri ma med pa
NK073(pu)006:2641: dang / gsum pa la ting 'dzin rang gi rtsal sbyong bas 'od byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2642: sa bzhi pa la ting nge 'dzin stobs rdzogs pa ste 'od 'phro ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2643: lnga pa la bden pa dbyer med la slob pas sbyong dka' ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2644: drug pa bden pa dbyer med kyi don mngon du gyur pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2645: bdun pa de nyid la'ang ched 'dzin dang bral bas ring du song ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2646: brgyad pa ting nge 'dzin de nyid la mnyam bzhag
NK073(pu)006:2647: stobs su gyur pas nam mkhar ltar mi g.yo ba
NK073(pu)006:2648: dang / dgu la so so yang dag pa bzhi'i
NK073(pu)006:2649: sgo nas zhi gnas dang lhag ma thong dbyer med
NK073(pu)006:2650: pa mthar phyin te shes bya'i sgrib pa phra mo
NK073(pu)006:2651: spong ba legs pa'i blo gros dang /
NK073(pu)006:2652: bcu pa phra ba'i phra ba rig cing rtogs dka'
NK073(pu)006:2653: ba'i dus su 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad kyi
NK073(pu)006:2654: dgongs pa dang mdzad pa thams cad phyogs med du
NK073(pu)006:2655: 'char te lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2656: bshad pa ltar chos kyi sprin zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2657: des ni ting nge 'dzin bstan no //
NK073(pu)006:2658: rim gyis bgrod pas zhes pas yun bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2659: rten gyi gang zag sems bskyed pa nas bzung ste /
NK073(pu)006:2660: 'dir tshogs lam bzhi gsum bcu gnyis kyang rim pa
NK073(pu)006:2661: bzhin du 'grod pas mthar phyin te las kyi sgrib
NK073(pu)006:2662: pa dag / sprul sku'i zhal mthong /
NK073(pu)006:2663: sbyor lam nges 'byed cha bzhi yang rim gyis bgrod
NK073(pu)006:2664: de mthar skad cig ma la mthong lam mngon du
NK073(pu)006:2665: gyur / nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag /
NK073(pu)006:2666: longs sku mthong ba'i mgo zug /
NK073(pu)006:2667: de man chad du bskal pa grangs med gcig /
NK073(pu)006:2668: de nas gong ltar gnyis pa na sa bcu rim gyis bgrod de /
NK073(pu)006:2669: skas kyi rim pa dang 'dra bar 'og ma la ma brten par gong ma mi skye la /
NK073(pu)006:2670: 'og ma la ma brten par gong ma la mi 'jug ste rim pa bzhin du bgrod pa'i mthus /
NK073(pu)006:2671: dgu pa man chad la shes bya'i sgrib pa rags
NK073(pu)006:2672: pa dag par byed pas lam gyi ngo bo'ang ting
NK073(pu)006:2673: nge 'dzin yin la gzhan thams cad de'i grogs su
NK073(pu)006:2674: 'gyur te des na grangs med gcig /
NK073(pu)006:2675: de nas bcu pa chos kyi sprin shes bya'i sgrib
NK073(pu)006:2676: pa phra ba sbyang ba'i phyir bgrod pa'i mtha' ste
NK073(pu)006:2677: yun bskal pa grangs med gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:2678: yang na mthong lam man chod dang /
NK073(pu)006:2684: dge ba chos sdud pa gsum ste /
