NK073(pu)006:2685: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa nyi shu pa la sogs pa rnams su rgyas par ro //
NK073(pu)006:2686: 'bras bu ni bla na med pa'i byang chub tu grub par 'dod pa yin no //
NK073(pu)006:2687: zhes te bla na med pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2689: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:2690: de'i tshe chos thams cad gnyis su med pa'i rang
NK073(pu)006:2691: bzhin nam mkha' ltar 'gyur ba med cing phyi nang
NK073(pu)006:2692: gi dngos po dang mi mthun pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2693: gnyen po'i chos thams cad kyang des bcom zhing yul yul can dbyer med /
NK073(pu)006:2694: shes bya shes byed dbyer med pas mtshan ma mi
NK073(pu)006:2695: gnas pas rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin no
NK073(pu)006:2696: // 'dzin pa'i cha phra ba'i phra ba'ang mi gnas pas kun tu 'od ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2697: thob bya'i 'bras bu lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:2698: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pas chos kyi sku zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2700: byang chub ces pa spangs dang rtogs pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:2701: spangs pa mthar phyin pas shes bya'i sgrib pa phra ba'i phra ba'ang mi gnas pas byang /
NK073(pu)006:2702: rtogs pa mthar phyin te gnyen po che ba'i che
NK073(pu)006:2703: ba rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du
NK073(pu)006:2704: gyur pas chub / grub par zhes pa ngo bo
NK073(pu)006:2705: la grub bya grub byed med kyang lam pa'i blo
NK073(pu)006:2706: gyur pas chub / ngo'i snang ba'o // 'dod pa yin no zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2707: spyir gdul bya dbang po mtho dman gyi bye brag gis lam nye ring grangs mang bas /
NK073(pu)006:2708: 'dir theg pa chen po blo dman la lam ring
NK073(pu)006:2709: ba'i 'dod pas yun dang lta ba dang spyod pa
NK073(pu)006:2710: dang rim gyis 'jug pa rnams dang /
NK073(pu)006:2711: 'bras bu yang lhun grub ma brjod pas /
NK073(pu)006:2712: spros bral 'ba' zhig tu ston pa rnams lam pa'i blo'i 'dod pa yin zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2714: mtshan nyid kyi gzhung ston pa'i skabs su de nyid kyi rang gzhung mi smra nas /
NK073(pu)006:2715: nang pa'i tshig 'dod pa brjod pa ci zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:2716: de ni bden te lam mtshan nyid rang gzhung smos pa yin kyang /
NK073(pu)006:2717: khung spyi lung gsang sngags yin pa'i dbang gis ma
NK073(pu)006:2718: drangs pa'i tshig gis de bas lhag pa yod kyang
NK073(pu)006:2719: khos de ltar 'dod pa yin no zhes pa lta
NK073(pu)006:2720: bu'o // des na 'di'i dkyus su nyan thos dang
NK073(pu)006:2721: rang rgyal gnyis la grub pa yin no zhes bstan
NK073(pu)006:2722: bu'o // pa ni / rang gzhung de nyid las gzhan gang na'ang mi mnga' ba'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:2723: 'dir theg pa chen po thams cad 'bras bu sangs rgyas su mthun la /
NK073(pu)006:2724: sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo ni lhun grub kyi ye
NK073(pu)006:2725: shes yin pa la lam pa'i blo'i 'dod tshod yin
NK073(pu)006:2727: de la ni yang dag nyid ma rtogs zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2728: yang dag pa ni rang rig byang chub kyi sems
NK073(pu)006:2729: bden pa dbyer med kyi ngo bo gsang sngags kyi
NK073(pu)006:2730: bdag nyid sgro skur dang bral ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:2731: de la bden pa yan bkar du dmigs shing yul
NK073(pu)006:2732: du tshol te rang rig gi don ma myong ba'o
NK073(pu)006:2733: // gsang sngags la mdor bstan pa ni //
NK073(pu)006:2734: rdo rje'i theg pa zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:2735: rdo rje'i theg pa'i 'bras bu bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:2736: gzhi de nyid bstan pa la yang /
NK073(pu)006:2737: grangs kyi dbye ba ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:2738: bya ba rgyud kyi theg pa zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:2739: kri ya lus ngag gtsor ston cing las dang bya ba dang gza' dang dus tshigs gtso ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2740: rgyud ni rgyu'i theg pa dang mi 'dra ste /
NK073(pu)006:2741: gzhi lam 'bras bu 'brel pas na rgyud ste /
NK073(pu)006:2742: gzhi sems kyi mtshan nyid dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba de /
NK073(pu)006:2743: lam kri ya'i gzhung gis phun sum tshogs pa nyams su blangs kyang /
NK073(pu)006:2744: gzhi de nyid las ma g.yos shing /
NK073(pu)006:2745: lam du rigs gsum la gtsor 'dzin pa nyid /
NK073(pu)006:2746: 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje 'chang gis mngon du gyur yang /
NK073(pu)006:2747: gzhi'i don de nyid lhun gyis grub pas na rgyud kyi nges pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2748: des 'bras bu la skyol bar byed pa'i bstan pa la ni /
NK073(pu)006:2751: u pa ya ste lta sgom yo ga'i rjes su
NK073(pu)006:2752: 'jug pa spyod pa kri ya'i rjes su 'jug pa
NK073(pu)006:2753: nyid rgyud dang theg pa bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:2754: rnal 'byor ni yo ga ste lta ba phyi gzung
NK073(pu)006:2755: ba'i yul ma skyes pa'i don dam pa'i rnal ma
NK073(pu)006:2756: la / nang 'dzin pa'i sems bdag med pa'i rig
NK073(pu)006:2757: pa'i blo 'byor te yul sems stong pa kha sprod
NK073(pu)006:2759: ting nge 'dzin sems dag pa mtha' bral gyi ngang
NK073(pu)006:2760: la byang chub pa lnga'i sgo nas lha'i sku bsgom
NK073(pu)006:2762: spyod pa zhar la smos pa'o /
NK073(pu)006:2763: rgyas pa la gsum gyi kri ya'i 'jug sgo dang gang zag thun mong du bstan pa ni //
NK073(pu)006:2764: de la zhes pa gsang sngags la gsum du dbyes pa'i gzhi de las /
NK073(pu)006:2765: kri ya bkar nas ston pa'i 'jug pa'i sgo ni /
NK073(pu)006:2766: bya ba rgyud kyi theg pa zhes pa kri ya ste 'bras bu gong bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:2767: yul de la zhugs pa rnams kyi zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2768: rten gyi gang zag bstan te dbang po rab 'bring
NK073(pu)006:2769: dgu'i 'bring gi tha ma brtson pa che zhing khrus
NK073(pu)006:2770: dang gtsang sbra dag sbyod la dga' ba bram ze
NK073(pu)006:2771: lta bu'o // rnams ni sa snga phyi kun bsdus pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2772: lta ba ni zhes pa la sogs pa rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:2773: 'dir 'og ma ltar lta ba'i ngo bo yang rdul
NK073(pu)006:2774: phra rab dang skad cig mas gzhig nas ma grub
NK073(pu)006:2775: pa'i don dam par mi byed de /
NK073(pu)006:2776: 'dir sems kyi rang bzhin rnam par dag pa yod
NK073(pu)006:2777: med rtags chad kyi mtha' bzhi ma spangs ngang gis
NK073(pu)006:2778: bral ba nyid ni dngos gzhi thams cad dang bral
NK073(pu)006:2779: zhing dus gsum du mi 'gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:2781: skye 'gag med pa la zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2782: de lta bu'i ngang las chu thams cad gsher ba dang mtshungs pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:2783: yul sems dang phyi nang gi chos thams cad rgyu rkyen ngang gis ma dmigs pas /
NK073(pu)006:2784: skye ba ma dmigs la rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i
NK073(pu)006:2785: don gyis 'gags pa dang bral bas dngos po med
NK073(pu)006:2786: pas skye 'gags med pa'i ngang las ces pa don
NK073(pu)006:2788: 'o na kun rdzob tsam du ci ltar yin ce na /
NK073(pu)006:2789: kun rdzob tsam du ni bltas nas dor bya min te /
NK073(pu)006:2790: rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed pa ltar snang ba'i kun rdzob 'di nyid lha'i gzugs zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2791: sku gsum thugs gsum gyi 'bras bu bsgrub pa'i rgyu'i ngo bo ltar bur gnas te /
NK073(pu)006:2792: dper na mkhar khu sku ma yin kyang mkhar khu min pa'i gzhan las sku ma grub pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:2793: mthong tsam sku ma yin kyang lta spyod sgom gsum gyi ngos nas sems dag par byas nas /
NK073(pu)006:2794: mkhar khu las skur snang ba bzhin 'khrul pa dag pa nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bo 'dod de /
NK073(pu)006:2795: des nang rgyud nas lhar lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:2797: lha'i gzugs kyi skur bsgom zhing zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:2798: dben la gtsang ba'i gnas su sngon 'gro'i cho ga
NK073(pu)006:2799: mtho dman la tshogs bsags pa rnam pa gnyis sngon
NK073(pu)006:2800: du song nas lha drug gi tshul gyis dam tshig
NK073(pu)006:2802: dang po s+w+aa b+ha ba'i sngags kyis stong par byas te /
NK073(pu)006:2803: stong pa chos nyid kyi lha don dam pa skye 'gag med pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin la /
NK073(pu)006:2804: kun rdzob du stong pa'i ngang las sa bon gang
NK073(pu)006:2805: yin pa'i sgra grags pa sgra brnyan gyi lha dang
NK073(pu)006:2806: / yig 'bru dngos su byung ba gsum yig 'bru'i lha dang /
NK073(pu)006:2807: de'i zhabs su gdan nyi zla byung ba gdan gyi lha dang /
NK073(pu)006:2808: de'i steng du sa bon las thugs phyag mtshan du byung ba thugs phyag rgya'i lha dang /
NK073(pu)006:2809: de las rigs gsum gang mos kyi skur snang ba sku phyag rgya'i lha dang /
NK073(pu)006:2810: de'i sku gsung thugs rlabs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:2811: dper na 'bangs gcig gis rje rgyal po gcig gdan
NK073(pu)006:2812: drangs nas bsnyen bkur gyi ched du gnas khang phyag
NK073(pu)006:2814: nyid kyang rgyan gyis legs par brgyad te /
NK073(pu)006:2815: rgyal po mnyes par bya ba'i phyir dang 'dra bar
NK073(pu)006:2816: ye shes pa spyan drangs pa la dam tshig sems
NK073(pu)006:2817: dpas dngos grub re ba'i phyir bsnyen bkur ba'i tshul
NK073(pu)006:2818: ni / de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs pa yang /
NK073(pu)006:2819: gnas 'og min nas drangs de mdun gyi nam mkha' la ye shes pa'i gdan khri'i zhabs dang /
NK073(pu)006:2820: dam tshig sems dpa'i spyi bo'i thad sogs bsam nas bar yang khri gang gi tha so'o //
NK073(pu)006:2821: dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rtags su rang gis lha'i lus 'dzin nas phyag dang /
NK073(pu)006:2823: pu tsa la sogs pa'i tshogs bsags pa rnams tshar nas /
NK073(pu)006:2825: dmigs pa gsum yan lag bzhi'i tshul du 'o //
NK073(pu)006:2826: zhes gsungs pas dmigs pa gsum ni lha ye shes
NK073(pu)006:2827: sems dpa'i spyi bo'i thad kar bzhugs par dmigs pa
NK073(pu)006:2828: dang / de'i thugs kar byang chub tu sems bskyed
NK073(pu)006:2829: pa mthar phyin pa'i gzugs brnyan zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK073(pu)006:2830: gsung yig 'bru dang bcas par dmigs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2831: bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i mu drar gsal bar dmigs pa dang gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:2832: yan lag ni bzlas pa la bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:2833: gtan tshigs ni lus kyi yan lag gis las thams cad sgrub pa dang 'dra bar /
NK073(pu)006:2834: sngags kyi bzlas brjod kyis las thams cad 'grub cing dngos grub thams cad thob par byed do //
NK073(pu)006:2835: de ltar bdag dang ye shes sems dpa' rje bran
NK073(pu)006:2836: gyi tshul du gsal nas bzlas pa byed pa'i tshe
NK073(pu)006:2838: dbugs phyin 'gro ba'i dus lha la dmigs pa /
NK073(pu)006:2839: nang du 'dren pa'i su bdag gi thugs kar dmigs so //
NK073(pu)006:2840: de ni ting nge 'dzin mi g.yo zhing brtan pa'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:2841: bzlas pa'i 'od zer yang 'gal me'i 'khor lo'i tshul du ste /
NK073(pu)006:2842: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes sems dpa'i thus kar thim nas thugs dam bskul /
NK073(pu)006:2843: yang bdag gi thugs kar thim pas dngos grub stsol bar bsam pa'i ka ra ra bya ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2844: de nas tshar nas ye shes sems dpa' gshegs su gsol /
NK073(pu)006:2845: dam tshig sems dpa'i spyod lam gyis gnas so //
NK073(pu)006:2847: sku'i gzugs brnyan dang zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:2848: 'dir bya ba rgyud kyi gtan tshigs kyis las bya
NK073(pu)006:2849: ba dang rten 'brel thams cad 'tshogs pa las 'bras
NK073(pu)006:2851: dper na 'jig rten gyi zhing bzang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2852: rgyu sa bon skyon med pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2854: so nam legs par byas nas bar cad med pa'i ston thog bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:2855: des na rigs gsum gyi lha gang la dad pa'i gzugs brnyan ni /
NK073(pu)006:2858: ris su bri pa'i bye brag rnams kyang srog chags las ma byung ba dang ma 'bags pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2859: dung dang ba so dang tshon rtsi'i sbyin pa la sogs pa spang bar bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2861: dar gyi dog pa 'jur mdud med pa yi //
NK073(pu)006:2862: tha ga mas btags 'jam la snyoms pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2863: kha tshar ma nyams ras la bri bar bya /
NK073(pu)006:2866: rigs gsum gyi thugs kyi gzugs brnyan te /
NK073(pu)006:2867: 'chang ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK073(pu)006:2868: 'dzin pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK073(pu)006:2869: bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang gsum /
NK073(pu)006:2870: de la 'chang ba ni rnal 'byor pa'i rdo rje dril bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:2871: 'dzin pa ni ye shes sems dpa'i thugs mtshan pad+ma rdo rje ral gri la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2872: bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya ni /
NK073(pu)006:2873: dam tshig ye shes kyi thugs kar ting nge 'dzin gyis thugs mtshan bsgom pa la bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2874: bzlas brjod ces pa gong ma gnyis sku dang thugs kyi gzugs brnyan te /
NK073(pu)006:2875: 'di gsung gi gzug brnyan la dam tshig kyang yin te /
NK073(pu)006:2880: dang po bzlas pa'i gong du dam du bcas pa de nyid las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2882: bzlas brjod byed pa'i tshe glang dang sprid pa dang glo lu ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2883: mchil snabs dor ba la sogs pa'ang spangs na mi
NK073(pu)006:2884: tshig gis bar ma chod pa lta ci smos te
NK073(pu)006:2885: / dper brgya rtsa brgyad dam bcas nas brgya rtsa
NK073(pu)006:2886: bdun nas mi tshig gis chod na gzhi nas bzla
NK073(pu)006:2888: sngags kyi grangs dam du bcas pa de nyid mthar phyin te 'byongs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2889: bzlas brjod byed pa'i tshul ni /
NK073(pu)006:2891: bzlas brjod byed tshe mi dal mi myur zhing /
NK073(pu)006:2892: mi tshig ma 'dres gzhan du ma yengs sems //
NK073(pu)006:2893: ha cang sgra cher ma yin shub bur min //
NK073(pu)006:2894: gug skyed klad kor tshag shad zur phyin cing //
NK073(pu)006:2895: gsang sngags dag cing cho ga yongs su rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:2897: gtsang spra dang zhes pas spyod pa'i khyad par ste //
NK073(pu)006:2898: spyod pa rnams kyi gtso bo nye reg dang 'thor 'thung ste /
NK073(pu)006:2899: chu phud ma nyams pa'i nang du dri bzang sbyar
NK073(pu)006:2900: ba mdun du bzhag la lag pa g.yon pa'i srin
NK073(pu)006:2901: theb sprad rdo rje tshang bar bcug ste /
NK073(pu)006:2902: srin theb la nyi zla'i dal bsam la de'i bar
NK073(pu)006:2903: du yi ge a dkar po gcig bsam pa'i 'phro
NK073(pu)006:2904: 'du las dri chab de nyid a'i rang bzhin du
NK073(pu)006:2906: de nas dri chab lag mthil g.yas g.yon du theg
NK073(pu)006:2907: le zlum por byung ste zla dal du bsam la
NK073(pu)006:2908: lag mthil kha sprod pa'i bar du a dkar po
NK073(pu)006:2909: yungs 'bru tsam sha dag gis gang bar bsgom /
NK073(pu)006:2910: de bdag gi mgo la byugs pas lus skye ba med pa chos kyi dbyings su byin gyis brlab /
NK073(pu)006:2911: lce la bzhag pas kyang de bzhin du brlab /
NK073(pu)006:2912: thugs kar byugs pas kyang de bzhin brlab //
NK073(pu)006:2913: de nas rnal 'byor ba rnams la reg pas kyang gong ma bzhin byin gyis brlab po //
NK073(pu)006:2914: de nas phyogs bcur gtong bas stong gsum thams cad gong ma bzhin du brlab bo //
NK073(pu)006:2915: de nas lhag ma bdag nyid kyi kyang btung /
NK073(pu)006:2916: rnal 'byor pa gzhan ma rnams kyis kyang lus bkru ba la sogs pa bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:2923: ro bag la sogs pa thams cad kyis kyang ma gos pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2924: sman lnga la sogs pa gtsang ba blangs te mdor na dag spyod thams cad do //
NK073(pu)006:2926: dus bzang po la 'jug pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:2927: de yang bya ba'i dus dang ba'i dus gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:2928: bya ba'i dus ni nyin gcig bzhin du bya ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2929: de ma nus na zla ba gcig la dus bzang drug la bya ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2930: de ma nus na zla re la lan re bya ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2931: yang tshes brgyad dang bcu bzhi dang /
NK073(pu)006:2933: 'jug pa'i dus kyang bzang ba'i dus gcig la 'jug pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2934: gza' dang rgyu skar la sogs pa zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2937: rgyu skar ni mgo dang rgyal ba lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:2938: sogs khongs su rtsis kyi la nyi bzang ngan thams cad bsdu'o //
NK073(pu)006:2939: grub pa'i tshul ni gtsor yo byad dang zhes pa
NK073(pu)006:2940: la sogs pa ste gong du smos pa'i yo byad
NK073(pu)006:2941: rnams thams cad tshogs pa las dngos grub snang ste
NK073(pu)006:2942: dper na rtsa dang dur mo dang rdo dang skyes
NK073(pu)006:2943: bu'i rtsol ba rnams bsdongs pa las me snang ba
NK073(pu)006:2944: dang 'dra bar gtsor yo byad ni /
NK073(pu)006:2945: gong du smos pa rnams kyang yin la khyad par
NK073(pu)006:2946: du dkar gsum mngar gsum la sogs te cha rkyen
NK073(pu)006:2947: nyer lnga'o // rgyu rkyen zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:2950: yang na rgyu ting nge 'dzin rkyen yo byad ste /
NK073(pu)006:2951: dper na sa 'og na gser yod kyang rkyen rko
NK073(pu)006:2952: ba'i mthun rkyen ma tshogs na mi snang la tshogs
NK073(pu)006:2954: rgyu ting nge 'dzin gser dang 'dra ba de /
NK073(pu)006:2955: rkyen yo byad la sogs pa gong ma rnams 'tshogs
NK073(pu)006:2956: pa las snang ba'i stobs kyis dngos grub rab 'bring
NK073(pu)006:2957: rnams snang bas na rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:2958: mthu ni rgyu rkyen rnams 'tshogs na mi 'dod kyang snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:2959: rang dbang med par 'char ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:2960: dper na pho mo'i rkyen dang rnam par shes pa
NK073(pu)006:2961: 'dzom pas dbang med du lus su snang ba lta
NK073(pu)006:2962: bu'o // tshul khrims 'og ma kun gyi steng du sdom pa gsum ldan gyi ngo bo yin te /
NK073(pu)006:2963: byang chub sems dpa' bzhin rkang lag sbyin pa la sogs pa mi dgos te /
NK073(pu)006:2964: dang po sku gsung thugs kyi dbang blangs pas de'i dam tshig ni dag pa gsum bsrungs ste /
NK073(pu)006:2965: lus kyi mi dge ba gsum spong /
NK073(pu)006:2969: ngag gi mi dge ba bzhi spong /
NK073(pu)006:2971: mi tshig dang me chus bzlas pa'i bar mi bcad /
NK073(pu)006:2973: bdag dang ye shes la bying rmugs ngang rgod 'thor spong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:2974: bzhan yang kri ya'i dam tshig bdun bsrung ste /
NK073(pu)006:2975: dkon mchog gsum mi spong pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2976: byang chub sems mi spong ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2977: rdo rje slob dpon gtsug gi nor bu bzhin du bkur ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2978: lta spyod mthun pa'i grogs la gdung sems rgyun mi bcad pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2979: yi dam lha rgyun du bsgom zhing bzlas brjod dag par bya ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2980: sha chang dang sgog tsong la sogs pa dri nga ba'i kha zas mi za ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:2981: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK073(pu)006:2982: lha la phul ba'i rnying pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2983: lha'i grib ma mi 'gom pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:2984: nye reg dang 'thor 'thung bya ba bdun no //
NK073(pu)006:2986: yul dang 'bras bu gnyis ka ston te /
NK073(pu)006:2987: de'ang yun nam grub ce na /
NK073(pu)006:2989: dag spyod gtsang spra can 'di mi tshe bdun /
NK073(pu)006:2991: 'di sgrub pa'i gang zag de thang lhod ma shor
NK073(pu)006:2992: na mi tshe bdun rim pa bzhin du barjesa pa'ang
NK073(pu)006:2993: goms pa stobs su gyur pas bden pa mthong ba'i
NK073(pu)006:2994: lam thad sor phyin pa'i tshe /
NK073(pu)006:2995: lhag bcas kyi kri ya'i rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK073(pu)006:2996: khams gsum gyi 'jigs pa dang bral nas sngar bsgoms
NK073(pu)006:2997: pa'i lha gang yin pa de'i cha lugs kyis sum
NK073(pu)006:2999: dga' ldan du gnas shing ting nge 'dzin gyis sems can gyi don byed /
NK073(pu)006:3000: rgyal ba mang po la chos nyan te sgom lam sa mtho dman dang mnyam mo //
NK073(pu)006:3001: de nas blo dman na'ang mi lo stong drug brgyas
NK073(pu)006:3002: shes bya'i sgrib pa byang nas kri ya rdo rje
NK073(pu)006:3004: 'bras bu sangs rgyas mngon du 'grub po //
NK073(pu)006:3005: de la dkyus kyi sku'i gzugs brnyan dang rgyu rkyen
NK073(pu)006:3006: 'tshogs pa'i bar thams cad kyang bya ba ngos nas
NK073(pu)006:3008: bya ba'i rgyud ces pa'i nges tshig yin no //
NK073(pu)006:3009: de la ni 'dul ba ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3010: lus ngag gi byed spyod thams cad gtsor len pas
NK073(pu)006:3011: sems 'dul zhing 'bras bu thob par byed pas bya
NK073(pu)006:3013: u pa ya la bzhis ston pas /
NK073(pu)006:3014: 'jug sgo dang gang zag thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3015: gnyis ga'i rgyud ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3016: de'ang gnyi ga'i rgyud kyi theg pa la zhes pas 'jug sgo dngos bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3017: 'bras bu mdor bstan gyi skabs su bstan pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3018: zhugs pa rnams kyis zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3019: rten gyi gang zag bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3020: dbang po 'bring gi 'bring brtson 'grus dang rgyu rkyen
NK073(pu)006:3021: rnams kyang 'bring du gyur pa u pa ya'i theg
NK073(pu)006:3023: rnams ni gang zag rnams bsdus pa'i tshig go //
NK073(pu)006:3025: don dam par skye 'gag med pa las zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:3026: u pa ya'i rtogs pa'i lta ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:3027: don dam pa dang kun rdzob gnyis te phyi nang
NK073(pu)006:3028: gi chos thams cad sems nyid ma skyes pa'i dbyings
NK073(pu)006:3029: don dam pa'i ngo bo skye 'gag gnyis gcig ma
NK073(pu)006:3030: grub pas cig shos kyang mi mnga' ba'i ngang ni
NK073(pu)006:3031: don dam pa'o // kun rdzob tu lha'i gzugs kyi sku zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3032: phyi nang yul sems kyi dngos po rgyu rkyen gyis
NK073(pu)006:3033: bskyed pa ma 'gag pa 'di nyid kri ya ltar
NK073(pu)006:3034: brgyud nas lhar snang ba ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:3035: snang tsam nyid na gzugs sku'i ngo bo nyid yin
NK073(pu)006:3036: pa'ang lugs ma dod nas sgrom las ma phyung ba
NK073(pu)006:3037: lta bu la rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi skur
NK073(pu)006:3038: bzhed de / de'ang ting nge 'dzin la rag las pa'i tshul lo //
NK073(pu)006:3039: de ltar don dam kun rdzob gnyis kyang me long
NK073(pu)006:3040: dang gzugs brnyan bzhin dbyer med pa'i ngo bo las
NK073(pu)006:3041: / ting nge 'dzin skur bsgom pa gtso che bas /
NK073(pu)006:3042: ting nge'i ngo la bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul dang ldan pas na /
NK073(pu)006:3044: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi lha'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom ste //
NK073(pu)006:3045: de yang bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK073(pu)006:3046: de kho na nyid rnam pa bzhi dang ldan par bsgom zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3047: de la de kho na nyid bzhi ni //
NK073(pu)006:3048: bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK073(pu)006:3049: lha'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK073(pu)006:3050: bzlas pa'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK073(pu)006:3051: ting nge 'dzin gyi de kho na nyid dang zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3052: dang por bdag gi de kho na nyid ni dam tshig sems dpa' bskyed pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3053: bskyed tshul gong 'og gang ltar min kyang bdag gi de kho na nyid ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3054: lha'i de kho na nyid ni ye shes pa spyan drangs nas smin mtshams kyi thad sor bzhugs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3055: ting nge'i de kho na nyid ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3056: bdag dang mdun gyi ye shes sems dpa' gnyis ka'i
NK073(pu)006:3057: thugs ka nas zla ba dang yig 'bru dang dam
NK073(pu)006:3058: tshig sems dpa'i thugs kar bzlas pa'i sngags gsal ba
NK073(pu)006:3059: bsgom pa'o // bzlas pa'i de kho na nyid ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3060: dbugs dang sprad pa'i sngags kyi phreng bas phar spros thugs dam bskul //
NK073(pu)006:3061: tshur 'dus dngos grub stsol ba la bzlas pa'i skyon bcu spang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:3062: slob dpon a ro ye shes 'byung gnas kyis ni /
NK073(pu)006:3063: de kho na nyid rnam pa bzhi zhes smos pas /
NK073(pu)006:3064: gong gi bzhi po de ma 'gags par snang yang
NK073(pu)006:3065: stong zhing bdag med par rtogs pa la bshad do
NK073(pu)006:3066: // 'dir ni dkyus su de nyid ces smos pas /
NK073(pu)006:3067: dama pa bde bar gshegas pas /
NK073(pu)006:3068: bdag dang lha dang ting nge 'dzin dang bzlas pa
NK073(pu)006:3069: bzhi gnas skabs de dang de nyid kyi rnam grangs
NK073(pu)006:3070: bzhi po la bzung ngo skad /
NK073(pu)006:3071: des na de bzhi gcig tu 'dzom pa'i sa ma ti ni /
NK073(pu)006:3072: gnyis ka'i rgyud kyi rang gzhung ngo //
NK073(pu)006:3073: yo byad dang rgyu rkyen la sogs pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:3074: kri ya'i skabs su smos pa ltar yo byad rnams dang /
NK073(pu)006:3078: rkyen yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3079: sogs khongs su skol mdo brgyad kun bsdu'o //
NK073(pu)006:3081: 'dis theg pa'i nges tshig kyang bstan te theg pa 'dis rang sa mi zin pas /
NK073(pu)006:3082: lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin yo ga la brten la /
NK073(pu)006:3083: bsrung ba'i tshul khrims dang spyod pa la sogs pa
NK073(pu)006:3084: rnams kri ya la brten pa'i dbang gis kri ya
NK073(pu)006:3085: bzhin du yo byad gtso che ba'ang ma yin /
NK073(pu)006:3086: yo ga bzhin du ting nge 'dzin gtso che ba'ang ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:3087: ting nge 'dzin dang yo byad phun sum tshogs pa
NK073(pu)006:3088: gnyis ka cha mnyam pa las 'bras bu snang bar
NK073(pu)006:3089: 'dod do // spyod pa'i khyad par ni /
NK073(pu)006:3090: yo byad dang rgyu rkyen dang zhes pas kyang bstan la kri ya dang mthun no //
NK073(pu)006:3091: bsrung ba'i dam tshig kyang de nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:3092: grub pa'i zhes pas shugs la dus kyang bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3093: lta spyod gong 'go can 'di mi tshe lnga /
NK073(pu)006:3094: rten des sgrub pa bar ma chad pas stobs su gyur pas rig 'dzin mngon du byas te /
NK073(pu)006:3095: zag med la sbyor ba'i dus su gang bsgoms pa
NK073(pu)006:3096: de nyid kyi lha mngon du snang zhing kri ya
NK073(pu)006:3098: ring na'ang lo stong drug brgya'i ring la shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyang ba ni yin no //
NK073(pu)006:3099: 'bras bu ni sangs rgyas kyi sa la rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gis zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3100: sgrib pa phra ba'i phra ba'ang dag nas lam pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3101: mthong snang gis 'bras bu la ming der btags kyang
NK073(pu)006:3102: / sku gsum lhun grub la dbye ba med do //
NK073(pu)006:3103: des na theg pa dgu spyi lung bdun du bsdus pa'i dbang gis phyogs rtogs zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3104: nyan thos la bzhag gi rang sangs rgyas la rtogs
NK073(pu)006:3105: pa lhag po yod kyang de'i zhar byung du bartsi'o
NK073(pu)006:3106: // u pa ya'ang lta spyod gong 'og gi rjes
NK073(pu)006:3107: su 'brang bas rang sa mi zin pas des na
NK073(pu)006:3108: // / rang sangs rgyas dang de gnyis spyi lung
NK073(pu)006:3109: du mi brtsi ba'i dbang gis spyi lung bdun zhes
NK073(pu)006:3110: // / bya ste / shin tu gsang ba man
NK073(pu)006:3111: ngag gi le'u du'ang 'dul ba ces pa kri ya
NK073(pu)006:3112: dang dgongs pa zhes yo ga bstan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3113: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi mdor bstan ni /
NK073(pu)006:3114: rnal 'byor rgyud ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3115: de la rnal 'byor zhes pa 'dir mdor bstan gyi skabs yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:3116: gsang sngags phyi nang kun dang sbyar te yo ga'i skabs na /
NK073(pu)006:3117: phyi gzung ba'i yul ma skyes pa don dam pa'i rnal ma la /
NK073(pu)006:3118: nang 'dzin pa'i sems bdag med pa la rig pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3119: blo 'byor te stong pa kha sbyor gyi rnal 'byor
NK073(pu)006:3120: ro // ma h+aa yo ga'i gnas skabs su dbang po lnga ma 'gags pa thabs /
NK073(pu)006:3121: yul lnga ma 'gags pa shes rab tu 'byor ba'am /
NK073(pu)006:3122: phung po lnga ma 'gags pa thabs dang /
NK073(pu)006:3123: 'byung ba lnga ma 'gags pa shes rab tu 'byor pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:3124: phung po khams dang skye mched ma 'gags pa thabs la /
NK073(pu)006:3125: de dag rang bzhin med pa shes rab tu 'byor ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:3126: a nu yo ga'i skabs na phyi nang chos thams
NK073(pu)006:3127: cad ma byung ma skyes skye ba med pa chos
NK073(pu)006:3128: kyi dbyings dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba'i rnal ma
NK073(pu)006:3129: la / chos thams cad gsal la ma 'gags pa
NK073(pu)006:3130: 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa thams cad rang rig
NK073(pu)006:3131: pa'i ye shes te chu dang gzugs brnyan ltar skad
NK073(pu)006:3132: cig ma la lhun gyis grub pas 'byor pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3133: rdzogs pa chen po ltar na byang chub kyi sems
NK073(pu)006:3134: rang byung gi ye shes chen po nyid gsal la
NK073(pu)006:3135: ma 'gags par snang ba 'khor 'das sam snod bcud
NK073(pu)006:3136: kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad snang ba'i dus nyid
NK073(pu)006:3137: na yul dang yul can nam phyogs su 'dzin pa
NK073(pu)006:3138: phra ba'i phra ba'ang mi mnga' bas gzung 'dzin gtan
NK073(pu)006:3140: kun tu bzang por lhun gyis grub la /
NK073(pu)006:3141: de nyid chos dbyings las ma g.yos shing de la der 'dzin dang bral ba nyid /
NK073(pu)006:3142: mtshan ma dang bral bas bzang mor brjod la /
NK073(pu)006:3143: de chu dang mar gyi dpe bzhin dbyer med pa
NK073(pu)006:3144: nyid la byang chub sems bde ba chen po zhes
NK073(pu)006:3145: bya ste / de ni lam pa'i blos byas pa lta bu ma yin ste /
NK073(pu)006:3146: ye nas de ltar bzhugs pa'i rnal ma ma bcos par /
NK073(pu)006:3147: rdzogs pa chen po'i don la rtogs pa'i blo gyur
NK073(pu)006:3148: pa rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa ni
NK073(pu)006:3149: 'byor zhes bya'o // rgyud ni bzhi po gang ltar
NK073(pu)006:3150: yang 'bras bu'i theg pa yin pas gzhi lam 'bras
NK073(pu)006:3151: bu gsum gyi 'brel ba so sor brtsi bar bya
NK073(pu)006:3154: 'bru gong du bshad de nyams su blangs te zhugs
NK073(pu)006:3155: pa rten gyi gang zag rnams kyi lta ba ni
NK073(pu)006:3156: / zhes pa lam gyi gzhi sngon du 'gro ba ste mig dang 'dra bas dang por smos so //
NK073(pu)006:3158: zhes pas grangs kyi dbye ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:3159: gsal ba'i dbye ba'i ngos nas rnal 'byor phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3160: rnal 'byor nang ba thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3161: zhes pa rnal 'byor ni bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3162: phyi pa dang nang pa gnyis bsdebs te bshad na /
NK073(pu)006:3163: lta bas phyi nang du gyur pa /
NK073(pu)006:3164: spyod pas phyi nang du gyur pa /
NK073(pu)006:3165: ting nge 'dzin gyis phyi nang du gyur la /
NK073(pu)006:3166: dngos grub len tshul gyis phyi nang du gyur pa /
NK073(pu)006:3167: yun gyis phyi nang du gyur pa dang lnga'o //
NK073(pu)006:3168: de la lta bas phyi nang du gyur pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3169: yo ga bdag gis 'khor 'das dbyer med rang rig
NK073(pu)006:3170: chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i don ma rtogs te
NK073(pu)006:3171: gzung yul kha sprod stong pa mtshan ma med pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3172: ngang las kun rdzob lhar byin gyis rlobs pa'i gzhi
NK073(pu)006:3173: tsam du lta bas phyi pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3174: nang pas lta ba bdag nyid chen po'i rtogs pa la yang /
NK073(pu)006:3175: ma h+aa pas mtsho dwangs pa las gzugs brnyan 'char ba nyid /
NK073(pu)006:3176: mtsho nyid kyi cho 'phrul gzugs snyan du snang ba las ma gtogs pa gzhan med pas bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:3177: phyi nang gi chos thams cad sems nyid du gcig pa la /
NK073(pu)006:3178: sems nyid cho 'phrul phung po khams dang skye mched
NK073(pu)006:3179: rnams su snang ba nyid lha'i dkyil 'khor yin pa
NK073(pu)006:3180: la de nyid du bsgom pa tsam lta ba'i ngo
NK073(pu)006:3181: bo'i / des na nang ba ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3185: mtshan med ni yo ga bas chos nyid mtha' brgyad dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin gtsor byed pas /
NK073(pu)006:3186: bdag nyid chen po ma rtogs te phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3187: nang pas rigs pa rang gsal yul bral gyi ting
NK073(pu)006:3188: nge 'dzin zhe 'dod phra ba'ang mi mnga' bar rang
NK073(pu)006:3189: rig ngo bo yin pas nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3190: mtshan bcas la lha'i sku mngon byang lngas bskyed pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3191: cho 'phrul bzhis bskyed pa ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3192: yab rkyang du bsgom pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3193: yum zhal sbyor ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3194: 'khor thugs kha nas spro ba ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3195: gsang gnas nas spro ba ni nang pa'o /
NK073(pu)006:3196: zhi ba 'ba' zhig bsgom pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3197: zhi khro gnyis ka bsgom pa ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3199: zhi ba'i rgyan cha rnams dang ldan pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3200: dpal chas rnams bsgom pa ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3201: rdzogs rim kyang sna rtse dang snying ga dang smin
NK073(pu)006:3202: mtshams kyi thig le tsam la brten pa ni phyi
NK073(pu)006:3203: pa yin la / 'khor lo bzhi dang chags lam gyi thabs rnams ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3204: spyod pas phyi nang du gyur pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3205: cha rkyen nyer lnga la sogs pa dag gtsang rnams la spyod pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3206: spyod pa'i dngos po nyi shu la spyod pa ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3207: mchod pa lnga dang brgyad dang rin po che sna
NK073(pu)006:3208: bdun dang 'dod yon lnga dang dag gtsang gi spyod
NK073(pu)006:3209: pa rnams la gtsor byed pa ni phyi pa yin
NK073(pu)006:3210: la / phyi'i mchod pa de rnams kyi steng du
NK073(pu)006:3211: nang gi mchod pa gtong ma dang bdud rtsi dang
NK073(pu)006:3212: dug gsum gyi mchod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3213: gsang ba'i mchod pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa rnams nyams su len pa ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3215: ye shes mnyes pas bdag dag /
NK073(pu)006:3216: bdag dag pas dngos grub snod du rung bar rtsol ba ni phyi pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3217: bsnyen sgrub rnams pa bzhi'i sgo nas dngos grub rang la shar bar lta ba ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3219: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang man chad len pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3220: zab mo'i dbang gsum len pa ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3221: de'i dbang gis dam tshig la'ang phyi nang de ltar mtshungs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3223: barje nas thob pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3224: de nyid kyis thob pa ni nang pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3225: thub pa zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku
NK073(pu)006:3226: gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar bsgoms pas mi mthun pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3227: dbang du mi gtong bas thub ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3228: ting nge 'dzin gtso che ba'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:3229: yang na lta ba phyi par gyur ba'i dbang gis
NK073(pu)006:3230: bsrung bya'i ngo bo la phra ba'i phra ba las
NK073(pu)006:3232: rtogs pa stobs chung ba'i dbang gis so //
NK073(pu)006:3233: rgyud dang theg pa ni bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3234: rnal 'byor nang pa ni bshad zin te thabs zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:3236: che ba dang mang ba dang yas pa dang yangs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3237: de dag kyang rgyas pa gzhan du shes par byas la /
NK073(pu)006:3238: 'dir ni dper na btsan dug gis srog gcod ba'i bdag nyid yin pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3239: sman pa mkhas pa gcig gis rdzas dang sngags kyis btul te zos na /
NK073(pu)006:3240: dug tu mi 'gyur ba'i thog nad gzhan gyis mi
NK073(pu)006:3241: tshugs shing bcud len du 'gyur ba dang 'dra bar
NK073(pu)006:3242: / dug dang 'dra ba'i nyon mongs pa lngas khams
NK073(pu)006:3243: gsum gyi thar pa'i srog gcod par byed pa ste
NK073(pu)006:3244: / / nang pa'i theg pa gsum gyis lta ba'i sgo nas rtogs pa gding du gyur /
NK073(pu)006:3245: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas stobs zhugs te /
NK073(pu)006:3246: spyod pa blang dor med pas bstangs pa na thar
NK073(pu)006:3247: pa'i 'bras bu mi gcod pa'i thogs tu 'bras bu'i
NK073(pu)006:3250: dug gsum sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub pa
NK073(pu)006:3251: ni thabs che ste dug la bdud rtsir byas pa
NK073(pu)006:3252: lta bu'o // spyod pa'i dngos po'ang de dang mtshungs so //
NK073(pu)006:3253: rgyud dang theg pa'ang bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3255: phyi pa'i 'jug sgo dang gang zag thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3256: de la zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3257: rnal 'byor la gnyis su phyes pa'i gzhi de las phyi pa bkar te bshad na /
NK073(pu)006:3259: rnal 'byor phyi rgyud kyi theg pa la zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:3260: rnal 'byor yo ga'i bstan pa'am theg pa ste 'bru gnon gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3261: zhugs pa rnams kyis zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3262: rten gyi gang zag bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3263: 'dir shes rab dang longs spyod che zhing gos rgyan
NK073(pu)006:3264: dang rol mo dang spros pa la dga' ba 'byor
NK073(pu)006:3265: pa tshogs pa rgyal rigs lta bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:3266: yo ga'i theg pa gzhung bzhin nyams su len pa'i stobs dang ldan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3268: lta ba ni zhes pas lta ba bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3269: de'ang gzhan phyogs dgag pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3270: phyii'i yo byad la gtsor mi 'dzin pas zhes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3271: de sngon du bstan pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3272: bstan ma thag pa'i kri ya nyid phyi'i yo byad la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:3273: rgyu rkyen tshogs pa'i mthu las grub pa'o zhes smos pas de'i zhen pa bcad pa'i phyir te /
NK073(pu)006:3274: 'dir kri ya'i rten la yo ga bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3275: khyad che ba'i dbang gis de smos mi dgos pa la nye ba'i dbang gis zhen pa dgag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3277: sems kyi rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin 'ba' zhig gtsor
NK073(pu)006:3278: byas pa nyid kyis 'grub par gsungs te bshad pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3279: rnal 'byor gyi tshig gis kyang gsal lo //
NK073(pu)006:3280: lta ba rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:3281: don dam par zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:3282: chos thams cad kyi de kho na nyid chos kyi
NK073(pu)006:3283: dbyings kyi ye shes don gyi ngo bo mi 'gyur
NK073(pu)006:3284: zhing mtshan nyid thams cad dang bral ba'i don dam
NK073(pu)006:3285: pa'i ngang la / rgyu rkyen skad cig ma dang bral bas skye ba'i phung por ma grub /
NK073(pu)006:3286: des 'gags pa ngang gis dag ste /
NK073(pu)006:3287: tha snyad du med ces te don dam pa'i ngo bo nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:3288: 'o na kun rdzob 'di ci ltar yin ce na /
NK073(pu)006:3289: lha dang lha mo zhes pa snang tsam nyid da
NK073(pu)006:3290: lta nas rnam snang rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs
NK073(pu)006:3291: kyi ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK073(pu)006:3292: de yang dngos su snang ba cer re ni khas mi len te /
NK073(pu)006:3293: dper na lugs ma dod nas yod kyang sgrom nas phyung dgos pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:3294: 'dir yang gdod nas yin kyang mngon byang lnga'i ting
NK073(pu)006:3295: nge 'dzin gyis kha phye ba'i tshul du 'dod do
NK073(pu)006:3296: // des na g.yu thang las kyang /
NK073(pu)006:3297: rang rig dngos stong mtshan ma gnyis //
NK073(pu)006:3298: dbyer med dbyings dang ye shes la //
NK073(pu)006:3299: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings kyi lha /
NK073(pu)006:3301: ting nge 'dzin ni de dag dang 'dra ba'i rgyud
NK073(pu)006:3302: yongs su dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes pa la
NK073(pu)006:3303: sogs te / de dag dang 'dra ba'i zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3304: lta ba'i rjes su zhugs pa'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK073(pu)006:3305: lta ba'i don dam kun rdzob rnam pa gnyis kyi rtogs tshul la ni /
NK073(pu)006:3307: de nyid nyams su blang ba ni 'dra ba'i zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:3308: kri ya ltar rje bran du mi blta /
NK073(pu)006:3309: thams cad kyi byed pa po sems rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa lha'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3310: bsrung 'khor dang rdzas dang kha lag byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK073(pu)006:3311: rten sprul pa dang tshogs bsags pa thams cad rang
NK073(pu)006:3312: gi byin brlabs su blta zhing mngon byang lngas sku
NK073(pu)006:3313: bskyed de / des na sems rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK073(pu)006:3314: par dag pa skad cig ma'i rgyun dang bral te
NK073(pu)006:3315: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyun nam mkha' lta bu la
NK073(pu)006:3316: ni yongs su dag pa zhes so //
NK073(pu)006:3318: mngon byang lnga'i ting nge 'dzin te de yang /
NK073(pu)006:3319: +amo tsi tra pra ti be tang ka ro ya mi /
NK073(pu)006:3321: bdag gi sems nyid skye 'gag med pa'i yongs su
NK073(pu)006:3322: dag pa'i ngang ni byang chub pa lnga po ste
NK073(pu)006:3323: sems so sor rtog pa'i rig pas byang chub pa
NK073(pu)006:3324: zhes bya'o // sems bskyed pa las mngon par byang chub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3325: bdag gi sems gong ma bzhin skye ba med pa
NK073(pu)006:3326: de kun rdzob de'i gzugs brnyan yi ge a dkar
NK073(pu)006:3328: bo d+h+ai tsi t+ta u pa ta ya mi /
NK073(pu)006:3329: zhes brjod pas zla ba tshes gnyis pa gcig tu bsam la /
NK073(pu)006:3330: de je che je che nya gang ba gcig tu bsgom mo //
NK073(pu)006:3331: de yang zla ba tshes pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3332: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i rtags yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3333: nyar rdzogs pa ni bsod dang ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3334: des na chos kyi skur gnas pa las /
NK073(pu)006:3335: mngon par byang chub pa rgyu byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid zla ba'i dkyil 'khor las /
NK073(pu)006:3336: 'bras bu byang chub sems kyi ngo bo h'u dkar po 'bur gyis byung ste bsgom pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3337: chos kyi sku'i gzugs brnyan yin no //
NK073(pu)006:3338: de nas brtan pa las mngon par byang chub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3339: yi ge h'u de 'phros shing 'dus pa las phyag
NK073(pu)006:3340: mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga pa gyen du 'greng ba
NK073(pu)006:3342: ye shes lnga mtha' gnyis su mi 'gyur ba'i rtags so //
NK073(pu)006:3343: de nas sku mthar phyin pa las mngon par byang chub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3345: +amo ya tha sta tha badz+ra a hmo /
NK073(pu)006:3346: zhes brjod pas bdag rnam par snang mdzad rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur par bsam la /
NK073(pu)006:3347: 'phags pa zhes pa 'khor ba dang ngan song dang
NK073(pu)006:3348: mtha' gnyis kyi skyon las 'phags pas rnam snang chen
NK073(pu)006:3349: po / gzugs kyi sku ni gnyis las gsang sngags kyi sgo nas longs spyod rdzogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3350: phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan par bsgom /
NK073(pu)006:3351: zhes pa ni sku phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK073(pu)006:3352: lha dran pa'i rgyud cha bas yig 'bru dang phyag
NK073(pu)006:3353: mtshan la sogs pa ma 'gags pa'i ngos nas sku
NK073(pu)006:3354: yin yang ltar dmigs pa mi skye bas sku zhes
NK073(pu)006:3355: bya'o // thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya ni /
NK073(pu)006:3358: ye shes lnga thugs su chud pa'i rtags su rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK073(pu)006:3359: 'gro ba'i rgyud la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK073(pu)006:3360: rtags 'khor lo gdul bya'i re ba rkong ba'i rtags
NK073(pu)006:3361: rin po che 'khor ba'i chos ma spyod kyang nyes
NK073(pu)006:3362: pas ma gos pa'i rtags pad+ma 'gro don lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:3363: grub pa'i rtags rgya gram bsnams pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3365: gsum chos kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK073(pu)006:3366: ljags kyi steng du rdo rje rtse lnga pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK073(pu)006:3367: byang chub sems dpa'i gsum chos kyi phyag rgya so sor bsgom pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3368: 'phro 'du phrin las kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK073(pu)006:3369: thugs ka na zla ba'i steng du rdo rje rgya gram bsgom pa las /
NK073(pu)006:3370: 'od zer gyis 'phags pa spyan drangs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3371: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i 'phro 'du'i bye brag rnams kyi gzhi rtsa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3372: yang na de ltar 'phags pa'i gzugs kyi sku bsgoms nas ye shes sems dpa' bstim pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3374: dbang po sgo sprad mnyam par bzhag /
NK073(pu)006:3376: de yang dam du 'dzin pa bya ba yar blangs
NK073(pu)006:3377: te lcags kyus phyag rgyas ye shes sems dpa'i thugs
NK073(pu)006:3380: zhags pa'i phyag rgyas so so'i gdan la bzhugs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3381: dbang po sgo sprad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3382: lcags sgrogs kyi phyag rgyas ye shes dang dam tshig sgo sprad nas gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:3384: dril bu'i phyag rgyas ye shes dam tshig dbyer med
NK073(pu)006:3385: ste chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin du bsam
NK073(pu)006:3386: mo // phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan par zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3387: de nas dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK073(pu)006:3389: sku phyag rgya chen po gsum bca' zhig bsgom pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3390: rgyas 'debs bzhi dang bral na mchod pas dngos grub mi snang zhing /
NK073(pu)006:3391: rgyas 'debs kyi byin brlabs kyis mthar thug gi dngos
NK073(pu)006:3392: grub thams cad stsol ba'i nus pa dang ldan pa'o
NK073(pu)006:3394: kri ya bzhin las dang bya ba gtsor mi che
NK073(pu)006:3395: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'ba' zhig gtso che ba'o
NK073(pu)006:3401: man chod rnams yongs bsdoms pa'i steng du yo ga spyi'i dam tshig bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:3402: khyad par gyi dam tshig lnga ste /
NK073(pu)006:3403: spyi'i bzhin rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK073(pu)006:3404: mched dang lcam dral la gdung sems rgyun du bya ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3405: mchod pa'i yo byad phud ma nyams shing gtsang bar bya ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3406: nyan thos rang rgyud pa dang lhan cig mig gnas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3407: 'chad ba'i dbang ma thob par chos mi bshad pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3410: sdom pa gsum dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa
NK073(pu)006:3411: la rgyun du gnas pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3413: rtags rdo rje dril bu dang /
NK073(pu)006:3414: don shes rab snying rje dang mi 'bral ba rdo rje'i rigs /
NK073(pu)006:3415: spyin pa rnam bzhi rtag tu sbyin pa rin po che'i rigs /
NK073(pu)006:3416: theg pa phyi nang gi thos bsam la 'bad pa pad+ma'i rigs /
NK073(pu)006:3417: phrin las kyis 'gro don byed pa dang 'phas pa mchod pa las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig go //
NK073(pu)006:3418: yun ni mi tshe gsum gyis zag med rig 'dzin gyi sar sbyor la /
NK073(pu)006:3419: de nas ring ltar thogs na'ang mi lo stong drug
NK073(pu)006:3420: brgyad 'bras bu stug po bkod pa sangs rgyas kyis
NK073(pu)006:3422: de ni rgyud las dgongs pa zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3423: ting nge 'dzin gtso che ba rnal 'byor rgyud kyi theg pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3424: gsang sngags nang pa'i mdor bstan ni /
NK073(pu)006:3425: rnal 'byor nang pa zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3426: de la rnal 'byor pa thabs kyi theg pa la zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3428: zhugs pa rnams kyis zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3429: rten gyi gang zag gnyis 'dir theg pa la dbye
NK073(pu)006:3430: ba byung bas gsum gsum du gnas kyang gsum ka
NK073(pu)006:3431: nang par mthun pas gcig tu bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3432: de yang mgo nas mar so so rang rang gi skabs su 'chad par shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3433: de yan chad kyi 'bru gnon ni bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3436: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag kyang rje'u dang 'bangs dang rgyal pa'i tshul //
NK073(pu)006:3437: khyad par rtsal 'phang thag ring yang //
NK073(pu)006:3438: gcig la gcig bsten gcig gi ngang //
NK073(pu)006:3445: a ti la yang gsum du ston pas /
NK073(pu)006:3446: ma h+aa rang gzhung gi don ston pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3447: ma h+aa'i rdzogs tshul rnams ni /
NK073(pu)006:3449: ma h+aa'i nang du mnyam rdzogs ston pa rnams ni /
NK073(pu)006:3451: 'di'i rdzogs chen ma h+aa yo ga rang gi rdzogs chen yin pas 'jug pa'i sgo /
NK073(pu)006:3452: thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3453: rten gyi gang zag kyang thun mong dang lta ba'am dus gcig tu bstan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3454: 'di'i rdzogs chen gyi skabs su gtan tshigs gsum dang /
NK073(pu)006:3456: mtshan nyid gsum la sogs pa rnams kyang /
NK073(pu)006:3457: gsang snying nyid kyi lung gis bstan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3459: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po nas gzhug slob dpon
NK073(pu)006:3460: gyi mtshan nyid bstan pa'i bar gyi shin tu gsang
NK073(pu)006:3461: ba man ngag gi le'u'i don gyis gtan la phab
NK073(pu)006:3464: 'dir rten gyi gang zag dang 'jug pa'i sgo thun
NK073(pu)006:3465: mong du bstan pa ni spyir bshad pa yin la
NK073(pu)006:3466: / de'i shugs la so sor phye ste bshad pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3467: skabs su de dag yong bar gsal bas don gyis
NK073(pu)006:3468: / shes te / gsang ba'i snying po theg pa spyi'i lung yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:3469: snang ba gsum rgyas par bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3470: de yang ma h+aa dang a nu gnyis ni /
NK073(pu)006:3471: gsang ba ces pas bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3472: yo ga phyin chod kyi mi rtogs pa'i lta spyod gnyis dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:3474: rdzogs pa chen po bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3475: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis kun tu bzang po'i
NK073(pu)006:3476: sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub pa dbang po'i
NK073(pu)006:3477: mngon sum du snang ba nyid yin pa la /
NK073(pu)006:3478: gsang ba bzhis chod cing lung dang man ngag rnam pa gnyis dang bral bas ma mthong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:3479: des na bskyed pa la ma h+aa /
NK073(pu)006:3481: rdzogs pa chen po a ti gsum so sor 'acada ces so //
NK073(pu)006:3482: 'o na rdzogs pa chen po 'chad pa'i skabs na /
NK073(pu)006:3483: rtogs pa bzhi dang mtshan nyid gsum la sogs pa
NK073(pu)006:3484: gsang ba'i snying po'i gtan tshigs rnams 'byung ba ci
NK073(pu)006:3485: zhe na / gsang ba'i snying po spyi lung yin pas don rdzogs pa chen po 'chad kyang /
NK073(pu)006:3486: dper na rgyal po chen po'i thugs dgongs bsgrubs na /
NK073(pu)006:3487: blon po mchog tu gyur pas gtan la 'bebs pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3489: 'dir spyir bstan pa'i skabs te so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyi yul gyi lta ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3490: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyi yul gyi lta ba la /
NK073(pu)006:3491: 'dir so sor rtog pa'i shes rab ste /
NK073(pu)006:3492: don spyi yid kyi yul du byas pa tsam la brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:3493: de la'ang 'dir rnam pa gsum ste zhes pa grangs kyi dbye ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:3496: bskyed pa'i tshul dang zhes pa ma h+aa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3497: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dpe rgya mtsho'i gzugs
NK073(pu)006:3498: brnyan rgya mtsho'i gcig pa bzhin sems rang rig tu
NK073(pu)006:3499: gcig la / rang rig gi cho 'phrul nyid phung
NK073(pu)006:3500: po khams dang skye mched du rang snang yang dbyer
NK073(pu)006:3502: lha'i dkyil 'khor yang ting nge 'dzin bzhir cho 'phrul
NK073(pu)006:3503: bzhis bskyed pa'i don nyams su blangs nas 'jug par
NK073(pu)006:3504: byed pas na tshul dang zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3506: chos thams cad ma byung ma skyes skye ba med
NK073(pu)006:3507: pa chos kyi dbyings spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang
NK073(pu)006:3509: de mi 'gags pa'i rang byung gi ye shes phung
NK073(pu)006:3510: khams skye mched snang ba'ang rang rig pa nyid snang
NK073(pu)006:3511: ste / cho 'phrul zhes kyang mi brjod pas dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa lhun gyis rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:3512: de'i dbang gis lha'i sku bskyed pa yang rim gyis bskyed mi dgos te /
NK073(pu)006:3513: rig pa la gcig char rdzogs pa'i tshul du 'jug
NK073(pu)006:3514: cing bsgom pas gnas skabs kyis 'char ba ces kyang
NK073(pu)006:3515: 'dogs so // rdzogs pa chen po zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:3516: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bsal spang med par
NK073(pu)006:3517: rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngang du rdzogs pa
NK073(pu)006:3518: / de yang ma 'gag pa sku gsung thugs mi
NK073(pu)006:3519: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor lhun gyis grub pa
NK073(pu)006:3521: rang rig byang sems su lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3522: yongs su rdzogs pa de nyid dus la res mo
NK073(pu)006:3523: dang phyogs la snga phyi med pas chen po zhes
NK073(pu)006:3524: bya ste / mtha'i phyogs zhen phra ba'i phra ba'ang mi gnas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3525: de lta bu'i don ye nas yin pa mngon du gyur pa la ni /
NK073(pu)006:3527: rgyas par ma h+aa bstan pa la /
NK073(pu)006:3528: de la zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:3529: gong du gsum du dbye ba'i gzhi de las ma h+aa yo ga bshad pas na /
NK073(pu)006:3530: bskyed pa'i tshul ni zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:3531: 'dir 'jug sgo la sogs pa dmigs kyis bsal na /
NK073(pu)006:3532: 'jug pa'i sgo nii bskyed pa'i tshul ma h+aa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3533: dkyil 'khor rten dang brten pa rim gyis bskyed pa'i tshul gyis mnyam su blang ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:3534: lta ba rig pa nyid cho 'phrul la brgyud de
NK073(pu)006:3535: phung po khams skye mched du snang bar rtogs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3536: tshul gyis so // des na snang ba thams cad rig pa'i cho phrul ltar snang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3537: dkyil 'khor yang zhi khro gnyis la rigs lnga re res gtso bo byas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3538: gdul bya dang mthun par snod bcud rim pa bzhin du bskyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3539: lha ched 'dzin che ba dang spyod pa blang dor med pa ched du blang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3540: spyod pa'i dngos pos zag med nyams su myong bar byed pa rnams te ma h+aa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3543: 'byor pa dang brtson 'grus dang brtul zhugs che ba /
NK073(pu)006:3544: shes rab gong ma gnyis tsam mi nus pas ma ha'i don rtogs pa'i shes rab dang ldan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3545: de ni ting nge 'dzin ston pa'i shugs kyis shes te rten no //
NK073(pu)006:3546: rten des rtogs pa'i lta ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:3547: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i tshad ma
NK073(pu)006:3548: rnams kyi gzhal ba yo ga man chad kyi spyod
NK073(pu)006:3553: lhag pa'i don dam pa 'khor 'das thams cad kyi
NK073(pu)006:3554: ngo bo sems nyid mtha' bral ci'ang ma yin pa
NK073(pu)006:3556: dbyings ye shes gnyis te dkor bdun lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3558: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK073(pu)006:3561: rig pa de nyid kyi 'phrul ma grub bzhin cir
NK073(pu)006:3562: yang mi 'gags par 'char bas don byed nus pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3563: mtshan nyid dang ldan pas sgyu ma lta bu ste
NK073(pu)006:3564: / phung po khams dang skye mched rigs lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:3566: sems dpa' dang sems ma'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa mnyam pa nyid du 'char ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:3568: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis /
NK073(pu)006:3569: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing /
NK073(pu)006:3571: dbyer med kyi don de gnyis tshig la snga phyi byung yang /
NK073(pu)006:3572: don la dbyer med pa chu dang gsher pa'am mar dang snum bzhin te /
NK073(pu)006:3573: gcig chod du chod pa'i dus su gzhal ba'i ngos nas gong ma gnyis yin kyang /
NK073(pu)006:3574: rtogs pa'i ngos nas phyogs kyi zhe 'dod phra ba'ang med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3575: dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK073(pu)006:3577: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su /
NK073(pu)006:3578: bdag dang gzhan du dbyer med de /
NK073(pu)006:3579: rnam dag dbyings nyid tshul gcig go //
NK073(pu)006:3581: lta ba gtan la phebs pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:3583: lta dang lta bar bya med pa'i /
NK073(pu)006:3584: ye shes sgron ma spring pa yi //
NK073(pu)006:3585: phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams cad mthong /
NK073(pu)006:3588: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3589: de yang de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK073(pu)006:3591: rgyu ting rnam pa gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:3592: lhag pa'i don dam sems nyid cir yang ma yin
NK073(pu)006:3593: pa tha snyad thams cad dang bral ba'i ngo bo
NK073(pu)006:3594: yin pa'i rtags su de ting bsgom /
NK073(pu)006:3595: sems spros pa dang bral ba de ting nyid cho
NK073(pu)006:3596: 'phrul snang ba'i ngo bo nyid cir du bzhugs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3597: phyir / rig pa gsal la 'gags pa med pa
NK073(pu)006:3598: phyi nang gi chos thams cad du snang ba kun
NK073(pu)006:3599: phyir / ting bsgom / de nyid cho 'phrul du
NK073(pu)006:3600: rang shar ba'i phyir sems yig 'bru gang yin pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3601: phyir / ting bsgom / rnam par gsal / ting
NK073(pu)006:3602: nge 'dzin rnam gsum la grangs nges pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK073(pu)006:3603: phyir / ting bsgom / rnam par gsal / dang / go rim nges pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3604: dgos ched dang gsum gyis bstan te //
NK073(pu)006:3606: gsum bas mang yang mi dgos nyung yang ma chog ste /
NK073(pu)006:3607: ngo bo la snang stong dbyer med gsum dang /
NK073(pu)006:3609: lam pas blo sbyangs pa la'ang de dang mthun pas gsum du nges pa'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK073(pu)006:3611: ma h+aa bas stong pa chen po'i ngang las snying rje chen po'i nyams mi 'gags par 'char /
NK073(pu)006:3612: de la rig pa'i cho 'phrul du 'char ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3615: de las sprul sku 'char bas na go rim nges pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3617: de ting gi dgos ched ni /
NK073(pu)006:3618: gang gis glang chen myos 'dra'i sems /
NK073(pu)006:3619: mnyam par bzhag pas brtul nas su /
NK073(pu)006:3620: zhes pas rig pa gzung 'dzin gyi chang gi myos
NK073(pu)006:3621: pas glang po che smyon pa 'dra bas mtho ris
NK073(pu)006:3622: dang thar pa'i cha thams cad brlag par byed pa
NK073(pu)006:3623: ste / glang rdzis lcags kyus bzung ste dul nas gar bsgyur dbang yod pa dang 'dra bar /
NK073(pu)006:3625: de ting la mnyam par bzhag ste de la brtan
NK073(pu)006:3626: na rig pa cir yang dbang bsgyur du yod pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3627: dgos ched do // kun tu snang gi dgos ched ni /
NK073(pu)006:3628: yongs la snyoms pas snying rje'i yum /
NK073(pu)006:3629: zhes pas rig pa gsal la 'gags pa med pa
NK073(pu)006:3630: chos thams cad mnyam pa'i ngo bo phyogs zhen mi
NK073(pu)006:3632: chos thams cad dang mi phyed cing dbyer med pa'i don gyis snying rje zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:3633: de nyid chos thams cad bskyed pa'i bdag nyid du
NK073(pu)006:3634: gyur pas dkyil 'khor yang snang ba'i gzhi yin pas
NK073(pu)006:3635: yum mo // rgyu ting gi dgos ched ni /
NK073(pu)006:3636: thabs las thabs byung thabs bsam yas /
NK073(pu)006:3638: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin ma 'gags pa nyid thabs rgyu'i ye ger snang /
NK073(pu)006:3639: de las thabs byung ste gzhal yas khang 'og gzhi dang bcas par grub pa la /
NK073(pu)006:3640: thabs bsam yas brten pa gtso 'khor rgyan dang bcas
NK073(pu)006:3641: pa 'od zer dang bcas pa snang ba'i dgos ched
NK073(pu)006:3642: do // rim gyis bskyed cing zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3643: thabs byung ston te rgyu yi ge las byung ba'i
NK073(pu)006:3644: rim brtsegs ni nam mkha' nas ri rab kyi bar
NK073(pu)006:3646: bzhugs gnas gzhal yas khang yang so so'i gzhung bzhin
NK073(pu)006:3647: du rim gyis rig pa snang bar byas pa la
NK073(pu)006:3649: cing zhes te 'og ma'i mgo 'dren te /
NK073(pu)006:3650: thabs bsam yas brten pa lha'i 'khor lo ni /
NK073(pu)006:3651: dkyil 'khor rim gyis bkod ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:3652: gnas der rgyu'i yi ge las /
NK073(pu)006:3655: dkyil ni gtso bo 'khor mang nyung rnams gsang gnas nas 'don rta rim gyis bkod do //
NK073(pu)006:3657: ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3658: sku gsung thugs gsum byin gyi brlab pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3659: ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs pa rnams byas nas /
NK073(pu)006:3660: mchod bstod kyi bar mchod pa'i cho 'phrul rnams rdzogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3662: de lta bu'i ngang la rgyun du gnas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3663: rim gyis bskyed pa'ang ston no //
NK073(pu)006:3664: de ni nar ma'i lugs so //
NK073(pu)006:3666: bsnyen bsgrub rnam pa bzhi'i dus su lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rim gyis bris te bkod /
NK073(pu)006:3667: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor rim gyis bsgom ste bkod /
NK073(pu)006:3668: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rim gyis spyan drangs nas bstim ste bkod nas /
NK073(pu)006:3669: mchod bstod dang bzlas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3670: sgrub pa chen po'i bar rnams la ni bsgom pas zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3671: de ltar lam gyi gzhi lta ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3672: lam rang gi ngo bo ting nge 'dzin gyis bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:3673: sgrub pa'i gzhi dam tshig ni /
NK073(pu)006:3674: bla med mi spang bla ma bkur //
NK073(pu)006:3675: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad //
NK073(pu)006:3676: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK073(pu)006:3677: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK073(pu)006:3679: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang che //
NK073(pu)006:3680: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:3681: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha che //
NK073(pu)006:3682: dag pa'i sno chu mi dor ro //
NK073(pu)006:3685: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni /
NK073(pu)006:3686: gcig la'ang bcu phrag lnga ru dbye /
NK073(pu)006:3687: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis la'ang //
NK073(pu)006:3688: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye /
NK073(pu)006:3691: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi /
NK073(pu)006:3692: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas pas /
NK073(pu)006:3693: zhes pas rim pa bzhin du mdor bsdu na /
NK073(pu)006:3695: de las spros na rtsa ba lnga /
NK073(pu)006:3697: de las spros na sum brgya drug cu ste /
NK073(pu)006:3698: dam tshig rgyas bsdus dgu las gsum du dbye ba 'di rtsa rgyud kyi lung gis khas blangs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3699: yang na man ngag gzhung gis sgegs rdor gyi gsal bakra'am /
NK073(pu)006:3700: s+thi ra ma ti'i nyer brgyad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3702: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK073(pu)006:3704: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs sgom bsgral //
NK073(pu)006:3705: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK073(pu)006:3706: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK073(pu)006:3708: yul dang 'phrad pas spyod pa lnga po dang /
NK073(pu)006:3709: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa lnga la sogs pa ni spyir bstan la /
NK073(pu)006:3710: khyad par du ni lam gyi spyod pa rnams te /
NK073(pu)006:3711: dad brtson gyi spyod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3712: shes rab dang mthun pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3715: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK073(pu)006:3716: rnam smin m+aum du shis par bya /
NK073(pu)006:3718: tshogs kyi spyod pa rnams so //
NK073(pu)006:3721: 'dir rtogs su rung ba'i rten gyi gang zag gcig
NK073(pu)006:3722: gis bla ma tshad dang ldan pa gcig la dbang
NK073(pu)006:3723: zhus / gdams ngag tshul bzhin du ma nos nas /
NK073(pu)006:3724: lam gyi gzhi ma lta ba yin pa rtogs pa 'ding dang ldan pa sngon du song //
NK073(pu)006:3725: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum rim pa bzhin du goms pa la /
NK073(pu)006:3726: brten nas gong ma'i gong ma la zhugs te /
NK073(pu)006:3727: spros pa'i dkyil 'khor la brtan pa thob nas ting
NK073(pu)006:3728: nge 'dzin 'gal rkyen rnam pa thams cad du med
NK073(pu)006:3729: na / las kyi sgrib pa phra ba'ang ma lus par dag ste /
NK073(pu)006:3730: de'i ngos nas tshogs lam chen po dang skal pa mnyam /
NK073(pu)006:3731: de nas cho ga lnga la sogs pa'i tshogs kyi
NK073(pu)006:3732: yan lag rnams tshang nas mnyams 'jug la rab brtson
NK073(pu)006:3733: zhes pas / dam tshig mnyams par tshogs kyi gzhung bzhin du bsgrub pa byas na /
NK073(pu)006:3735: 'bring bcu gnyis sam bcu bzhi'am bcu drug gis rig 'dzin gyi mchog grub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3736: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK073(pu)006:3737: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK073(pu)006:3738: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK073(pu)006:3740: tshe dbang dang rnam smin gnyis ka'i thob tshul lo //
NK073(pu)006:3741: thob tshul de gnyis kyis zag pa med pa mngon du byas te /
NK073(pu)006:3742: dbugs phyin pa ni nyon mongs pa'i sgrub pa gtan nas dag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3743: de nas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin sgom lam
NK073(pu)006:3744: pa shes bya'i sgrib pa phra rags rnams dag nas
NK073(pu)006:3745: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3747: blo dman ring ltar thogs na'ang lo stong drug brgyas mthar lam la sbyar te /
NK073(pu)006:3748: de'ang dbang po'i bye brag gis /
NK073(pu)006:3749: brgya dor gcig mar mthar 'gro ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:3751: tshe dbang rig 'dzin thob cing phyag rgya chen po
NK073(pu)006:3752: la mi gnas pas mthar lam du sbyor ba dang
NK073(pu)006:3753: / lo brgya tsam gyis mthar lam la sbyor ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:3754: shes rab kyi rtsal mtho dman gyis dabye'o //
NK073(pu)006:3756: lha dang mi dang tshangs pa yis /
NK073(pu)006:3757: skye ba rnam dang 'dzin mod kyang /
NK073(pu)006:3759: mi'i rgyal po la sogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:3761: tshangs pa'i 'dzin rten du gnas pa ni gzhan don mdzad pa'i ngor ro //
NK073(pu)006:3762: de la ni tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3763: brgya tsam gyis mthar lam la sbyor ro //
NK073(pu)006:3764: zag bcas kyi lus kyis zag med tshe dbang la sbyor ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:3767: de la skyes 'jig med pa'i lus kyis 'bras bu la sbyor ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:3769: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyis bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3770: mthar lam skyes bu la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis dbang bskur nas /
NK073(pu)006:3771: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad dang sku gsung
NK073(pu)006:3772: thugs dbyer med mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul yang khyad par
NK073(pu)006:3773: med pa ni / rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lnga lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3774: rjes su rnal 'byor gsum gyi dang po lta ba bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3775: de'i yang dang po 'jug pa'i sgo ni /
NK073(pu)006:3778: de ston bar byed pa'i theg pa //
NK073(pu)006:3779: lung a nu yo ga ste /
NK073(pu)006:3780: don dbyings dang ye shes skad cig ma la lhun
NK073(pu)006:3781: gyis grub kyang rgyu 'bras tsam du ston pa ni
NK073(pu)006:3782: 'jug sgo'o // yul de'i yul can shes rab kyi 'bring lung gi don de nyid rtogs nus la /
NK073(pu)006:3783: brtson 'grus dang brtul zhugs dang spyod pa dang yo
NK073(pu)006:3784: byad rnams ma h+aa bzhin du ched du'ang mi 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:3785: rdzogs pa chen po bzhin du gtan rag mi las
NK073(pu)006:3786: pa lta bu'ang ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:3787: 'on kyang 'tshogs pa'i rgyud longs spyod pa ma h+aa dang mthun no //
NK073(pu)006:3788: lta ba ni don dam par skye 'gag med pa'i zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3789: 'dir tha snyad la don dam pa zhes brjod kyang
NK073(pu)006:3790: 'og ma rnams kyi don dam pa dang mi 'dra
NK073(pu)006:3791: ste // chos thams cad kyi de kho na nyid
NK073(pu)006:3792: chos kyi dbyings la tha snyad du don dam pa
NK073(pu)006:3793: ste // zhes bya ste / shes bya thams cad
NK073(pu)006:3794: kyi don mthar thug pa'i ngo bo gzhi'i dus na
NK073(pu)006:3795: ma rtogs pa 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kyi 'byung
NK073(pu)006:3796: ste // zhes bya ste / gzhi / lam gyi
NK073(pu)006:3797: dus na lam pa rnams dmigs par bya ba'i yul
NK073(pu)006:3798: lam gong du 'phags shing 'bras bu la sbyor rab
NK073(pu)006:3799: ste // zhes bya ste / gzhi / nus pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3800: gzhi / 'bras bu chos kyi sku thams cad mkhyen
NK073(pu)006:3801: pa'i ye shes thams cad kyi 'byung khungs su bzhugs
NK073(pu)006:3802: pa la ni don zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:3803: de nyid dngos gzhi thams cad dang bral /
NK073(pu)006:3804: de'i dbang gis dus gsum du mi g.yo la der
NK073(pu)006:3805: cir yang char ba'i bdag nyid du gyur pas ni
NK073(pu)006:3806: dam pa ste ngo bo chos kyi dbyings so //
NK073(pu)006:3807: chos kyi dbyings nyid rgyu rkyen thams cad dang bral
NK073(pu)006:3808: bzhin skad cig ma dmigs pa'i skye bar ma grub
NK073(pu)006:3809: / der 'gags par snang ba 'ang mi gnas pas na skye 'gags med ces te /
NK073(pu)006:3810: chos kyi dbyings kyi zhabs sdud do //
NK073(pu)006:3811: yang ye shes kyi mgo 'dren te /
NK073(pu)006:3813: chos kyi dbyings nyid mi 'gags par snang ba'i 'gro
NK073(pu)006:3814: ba'i ngo bo la snod bcud dang las dkar nag
NK073(pu)006:3815: dang bde sdug la sogs rnams dang /
NK073(pu)006:3816: lam pa'i ngor lta spyod sgom pa la sogs pa lam gyi chos dang /
NK073(pu)006:3817: 'bras bu la rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyer lnga la
NK073(pu)006:3818: sogs pa rnams gsal la 'gags pa med pa'i ngos
NK073(pu)006:3819: nas ye shes zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3820: de ni chos kyi dbyings nyid med la zad mi shes stong la thams cad 'byung ste /
NK073(pu)006:3821: de nyid gsal la 'gags pa med pa rang byung
NK073(pu)006:3822: gi ye shes rang rig pa nyid yin pas ma
NK073(pu)006:3823: h+aa ba bzhin rig pa'i cho 'phrul snang zhes kyang
NK073(pu)006:3825: rig pa nyid rgyu rkyen dang bral ba rang snang
NK073(pu)006:3826: ba las skye zhes bya ba'i tha snyad gdags gzhi
NK073(pu)006:3827: med la / de nyid kyi ngang las ma 'gags
NK073(pu)006:3828: pa gtan nas dag pas 'gags pa med pa'i zhes
NK073(pu)006:3829: med la / te / ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:3830: lha dang lha mo zhes pas phung po lnga rigs lnga'i ngo bo dang /
NK073(pu)006:3831: 'byung ba lnga yum lnga'i ngang nyid de lha mo dang /
NK073(pu)006:3832: khams dang skye mched sems dpa' dang sems ma'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:3833: gsal ba'i ngos nas ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3834: dang gi sgras sems dpa' dang sems ma'i dkyil 'khor rnams kyang bsdus la /
NK073(pu)006:3836: de ltar lta ba bstan na sa /
NK073(pu)006:3838: rnam par mi rtog pa'i don zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:3839: gong ma lta bu bzhir bzhugs pa las /
NK073(pu)006:3840: tha snyad kyi rnam pa gang du'ang mi rtog ste /
NK073(pu)006:3841: rig pa'i ye shes gsal la 'gags pa med pa phyi nang chos sna tshogs su gsal bas ni /
NK073(pu)006:3842: med pa'i rnam par mi rtog /
NK073(pu)006:3843: snang tsam nyid na chu dang gsher ba bzhin chos
NK073(pu)006:3844: kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral
NK073(pu)006:3845: ba'i ngang las ma g.yos pas med pa'i mthar mi
NK073(pu)006:3846: rtog / de lta bu'i don lhun gyis grub pa
NK073(pu)006:3847: la ni yod med dang snang stong zang ngan la
NK073(pu)006:3848: sogs pa'i phyogs 'dzin gyi mtha' ma spang bral ba
NK073(pu)006:3849: tsam la dbu ma zhes brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:3850: de nyid ni gzhi'i bdag nyid med la zad mi
NK073(pu)006:3851: shes stong la thams cad 'byung chos kyi dbyings kyi
NK073(pu)006:3853: phyogs zhen gyi ched 'dzin phra ba'i phra ba'ang mi
NK073(pu)006:3854: mnga' bas ni nam mkha' nam mkha' las mi 'da'
NK073(pu)006:3855: ba bzhin no // gzhi de nyid ma h+aa bzhin
NK073(pu)006:3856: ting nge 'dzin rim bskyed kyi zhen pa med de
NK073(pu)006:3857: mtsho dwangs pa la gzugs brnyan shar ba bzhin ma
NK073(pu)006:3858: ba bzhin no // 'gags pa'am / lhag pa'i kun rdzob tu 'phags pa zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:3859: longs sku zhi ba dang khro bo gsal la ma 'dres pa mtha' gnyis kyis mgos pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3861: gdul bya'i ngo bo la snang zhing lam pa'i rig
NK073(pu)006:3862: pa'i ngo bo mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i tshul du grub
NK073(pu)006:3863: pa'o // yang zhes pas gong gi gnyis kyang gcig ste /
NK073(pu)006:3865: gzhi bstan te chu zla lta bu la /
NK073(pu)006:3866: yang gis ni gzhi can bstan te gzugs brnyan lta
NK073(pu)006:3867: bu rigs lnga gcig tu 'tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor zhi
NK073(pu)006:3869: khro bo nga brgyad la sogs pa rkyen sngags kyi stobs kyis gsal ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:3870: so so ra sku mdog dang phyag mtshan rgyan dang cha lugs ma 'dres par gsal te /
NK073(pu)006:3871: yi ge mngon du byung na yang /
NK073(pu)006:3874: don gyi ngo bo la dug gsum du mi 'gyur nas 'gal rkyen spangs mthun rkyen brten pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:3875: zhing zhes pa gang zhe na brten pa lta bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:3876: mnyam la ma 'dres zhes pa gong gi dbu ma chos kyi dbyings las kyang ma g.yos /
NK073(pu)006:3878: gsal ba gnyis gcig tu tshogs pa'i rig pa la phyogs zhen gyi 'dzin pa med pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:3879: dbyings ye shes mnyam pa nyid du lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:3880: pa'i ngang las ma g.yos la lam pa'i ngor sku'i
NK073(pu)006:3881: mtshan nyid rten dang brten par bcas pa rnams so
NK073(pu)006:3882: sor gsal ba la ma 'dres pa zhes brjod do
NK073(pu)006:3883: // yang mnyam la ma 'dres zhes brjod pas 'dir
NK073(pu)006:3884: spyod pa tshogs bsgrub la lam stegs mi 'cha' ste
NK073(pu)006:3885: // / spyod pa'i ngo bo dang po 'jug pa'i
NK073(pu)006:3886: ting nge 'dzin nas slob pas ting nge 'dzin dang
NK073(pu)006:3887: // / / spyod pa dang phyi nang gi chos
NK073(pu)006:3888: thams cad phyogs zhen dang bral ba mnyam la ma
NK073(pu)006:3889: 'dres pa'i dgongs pa nyid thog mthar dgongs pa 'ba'
NK073(pu)006:3890: zhig gis 'bras bu la sbyor bar byed bas na
NK073(pu)006:3892: des na 'di la zag bcas zag med kyi lam
NK073(pu)006:3893: gyi thad so rnams yod kyang zag med spyod pa
NK073(pu)006:3895: lta ba ni dbyings ye shes dbyer med rtogs /
NK073(pu)006:3896: ting nge 'dzin la'ang de ltar bsgom ste mthar phyin pa nyid 'bras bur bzhed do //
NK073(pu)006:3897: dam tshig ni ma h+aa'i dam tshig rnams kyi thog tu lung gi brtul zhugs kyi dam tshig dang /
NK073(pu)006:3899: bdud lnga las bzlog pa la sog pa rnams so //
NK073(pu)006:3901: ma h+aa bzhin ched du'ang mi len yang bdag gzhan
NK073(pu)006:3902: gyi don nam dgos pa'i skabs su ma h+aa'i spyod
NK073(pu)006:3903: pa rnams thun mong yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:3904: lta sgom gnyis rdzogs pa chen po'i rjes su zhugs /
NK073(pu)006:3905: spyod pa ma h+aa'i rjes su zhugs pas rjes su rnal 'byor smos so //
NK073(pu)006:3907: skyes bu rab kyi tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor ba'ang yod la /
NK073(pu)006:3909: tha mas yang phyi ma la sbyor te tshe gcig gis 'bras bu la sbyor zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:3911: bdal ba chos nyid kyi sa sku lnga lhun grub
NK073(pu)006:3912: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:3916: log par rtog pa 'jig rten lta ba bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:3917: ma rtog pa phyal pa dang rgyang 'phen gnyis grub mtha' la ma zhugs pa so so'i skye bo'o //
NK073(pu)006:3918: de yang lam rim 'jug gi dbang du na phal
NK073(pu)006:3919: pa'i sems brgyad skye bar byed pa'i gzhi yin la
NK073(pu)006:3920: / lam rang gi ngo bo'i dus su log rtog spang byar bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:3922: mur thug pa dang mu stegs pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:3924: log pa'i grub mtha' khrid kyang chad par lta ba
NK073(pu)006:3925: byang chub kyi myu gu skems par byed pas spang
NK073(pu)006:3928: rim 'jug gi dbang du phal pa'i sems brgyad mthar
NK073(pu)006:3929: phyin pa'i dbang du sbyong bya yin pas 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:3930: tshol ba la zhugs pa yin te /
NK073(pu)006:3931: mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud las /
NK073(pu)006:3932: mu stegs can la smad mi bya //
NK073(pu)006:3933: rnam par snang mdzad ring ba'i rgyu //
NK073(pu)006:3935: 'bras bu tshol ba bzhugs pa'i ring ba'i rgyu yin
NK073(pu)006:3936: kyang thog tu mi phebs pas lam gong ma rnams
NK073(pu)006:3937: kyi spang bya'o // phyogs rtogs dman pa gnyis kyang
NK073(pu)006:3938: rim 'jug gi ngos nas lam gyi ngo bo te
NK073(pu)006:3939: de nyid la ma brten par gong ma mthong ba'i
NK073(pu)006:3940: kyi spang bya'o // thabs med pas / skas dang
NK073(pu)006:3941: mtshungs kyang de nyid la zhen na lam gyi gol
NK073(pu)006:3942: sa yin par thag bcad do //
NK073(pu)006:3943: de bzhin du theg pa'i bye brag rnams 'og ma 'og ma la brten te /
NK073(pu)006:3944: gong ma gong ma mthong bas lam rim yang yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3945: de nyid la chags na gong ma'i gol sa yang yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:3946: mar 'dod pa myos zho la chags zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:3947: des na 'dir rim par bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:3948: rim 'jug gi lam gyi ngo bo ste /
NK073(pu)006:3949: 'og ma 'og ma la brten nas gong ma gong ma mthong ba sa bcu bgrod pa lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:3950: gcig char ba'i lam gyi gol sar bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3951: lam rim pa bzhin du 'og ma rnams ched 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:3952: phra rags kyi rim pa dang lta ba mtho dman
NK073(pu)006:3954: 'o na gsang sngags ni tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas /
NK073(pu)006:3955: zhes pa la rim 'jug dang khyad cis dbye na /
NK073(pu)006:3957: gsang sngags su zhugs nas dbang po rab kyi yang rab kyi dbang du btang ba yin la /
NK073(pu)006:3958: de lta bu'i don khyad par 'phags pa de sngon
NK073(pu)006:3959: du tshogs mang po ma bsags pa la mi snang
NK073(pu)006:3960: te / tshogs lam mthar ma phyin na sprul pa'i sku mi mthong la /
NK073(pu)006:3961: mthong lam mngon du ma byas tshe longs sku mi mthong ba bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:3962: des na gsang sngags mthong rtogs kyi skal ba dang
NK073(pu)006:3963: ldan pa ni sngon du tshogs mang po bsags pa
NK073(pu)006:3964: // rgyud dang bla ma rnams kyis gsal la /
NK073(pu)006:3966: sangs rgyas grangs med sngon mchod pas /
NK073(pu)006:3967: da ltar bcom ldan mtshan thos so //
NK073(pu)006:3969: des na rgyud tshod mtho dman gyi tshogs bsags pa'i ngo bo rnams theg pa 'og ma rnams so //
NK073(pu)006:3970: tshogs ma bsags par sangs rgyas ni /
NK073(pu)006:3971: a ti'i ston pa kun tu bzang pos kyang ma gsungs so //
NK073(pu)006:3972: des na rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK073(pu)006:3973: theg pa 'og ma rnams kyis bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:3974: mthar thug pa'i ngo bo 'di mthong ba'i thabs dbang
NK073(pu)006:3975: po'i bye brag dang bstun te 'og ma rnams su
NK073(pu)006:3976: snang ba'o // 'di nyid ni sku lnga lhun grub
NK073(pu)006:3977: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa gcig char
NK073(pu)006:3978: du ston pas lam mthar phyin pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:3979: de dang 'dra ba'i spyod yul lo //
NK073(pu)006:3981: des na gong ma'i zhabs sdud dang 'di nyid kyi mgo 'dren dang /
NK073(pu)006:3982: 'di nyid theg pa rnams kyi 'bras bu'i ngo bor bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:3983: da ni dkyus la 'jug par bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3984: rdzogs pa chen po'i tshul ni zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:3986: phyi nang gi chos thams cad rang snang kun tu
NK073(pu)006:3987: bzang po'i dgongs pa lhun gyis grub pa la lam
NK073(pu)006:3988: rim gyis bgrod pa dang bral bas /
NK073(pu)006:3989: rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:3991: tshul zhes pas nyams su len pa'i rten gyi gang zag bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:3992: gang zag blo rab 'bring dgur phyes pa'i rab kyi yang rab sbyangs yun ring zhing /
NK073(pu)006:3993: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu mthar phyin te lung man chad
NK073(pu)006:3994: la sbyangs pa phul du byung ba shes rab spobs
NK073(pu)006:3995: pa'i 'phangs mtho ba snod kyi yon tan kun rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:3996: pa / dbang dang dam tshig tu 'dzoms pas /
NK073(pu)006:3997: bla ma srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ba sbyangs
NK073(pu)006:3998: pa phul du byung ba shes rab dag pa'i dge
NK073(pu)006:3999: ba'i bshes gnyen dang ngo bo nyid kyis mjal ba
NK073(pu)006:4000: sa bcu pa dang skal pa mnyam pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4001: des 'jug par bya ba'i yul rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4002: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das zhes pa nas /
NK073(pu)006:4003: bsgom pa'i ste zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:4004: de yang 'jig rten nyon mongs pa rgyu 'bras kyis
NK073(pu)006:4005: bskyed pa'i 'khor ba'i chos skye 'jig ma lus pa
NK073(pu)006:4006: thams cad dang / 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'bras
NK073(pu)006:4007: bu mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos ye shes rgyu
NK073(pu)006:4008: 'bras bu snang ba'i sku rigs rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK073(pu)006:4010: chos ma lus pa thams cad dbye med pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4011: chos rnam pa gnyis po de ye nas byang chub
NK073(pu)006:4012: sems kyi ngang las ma 'gag pa dang ma dmigs
NK073(pu)006:4013: pa dang bden pa dbyer med kyi ngo bor sangs
NK073(pu)006:4014: rgyas te / dper na rdzas kyi dngos po bum pa lta bu la skad cig ma gcig la /
NK073(pu)006:4015: mis sa la sogs pa'i bum par mthong la /
NK073(pu)006:4016: lhas rin po che'i bum par mthong la /
NK073(pu)006:4017: rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i skyes bus de nyid ma
NK073(pu)006:4018: 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dbyings dang ye shes
NK073(pu)006:4019: dbyer med kyi ngang lhun gyis grub la /
NK073(pu)006:4020: de nyid kyi ngang la snang stong gang gi'ang zhen phyogs gi bral ba ni chos kyi dbyings so //
NK073(pu)006:4021: de mi 'gags pa'i rtsal las sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:4022: skye 'gro phyi nang gzugs rnams thams cad ni //
NK073(pu)006:4023: sku mchog mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:4025: snang ba thams cad snang la ma dmigs ngang gis
NK073(pu)006:4026: mi gnas de la phyogs su zhen pa med pas
NK073(pu)006:4027: gzung 'dzin gyis ma gos pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4028: ngan pa mi mnga' mas phyags dang dus kun nas kun tu bzang ste /
NK073(pu)006:4030: sgra skad rab 'bring tha ma lus pa //
NK073(pu)006:4031: gsung dbyangs mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor zab /
NK073(pu)006:4033: mi 'gags pa'i ngos nas sgra skad kyi bye brag thams cad dam /
NK073(pu)006:4035: rang bzhin med pa thams cad kun tu bzang mo'i ngang las mi 'gags par rang snang /
NK073(pu)006:4036: ngo bo dbyings las ma g.yos de dbyer med pa
NK073(pu)006:4037: nyid mtshan nyid thams cad las 'das te phyogs zhen
NK073(pu)006:4039: rtogs su snang ba'i ngos nas /
NK073(pu)006:4042: kun tu bzang po'i gsung ngo /
NK073(pu)006:4043: thams cad byang chub sems su ro gcig pas //
NK073(pu)006:4044: thugs mchog mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:4046: sku snang ba mi 'gags pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4048: grangs pa gnyis dbyer med pa nyid ni phyogs zhen mi mnga' bas thugs zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4049: chos thams cad de'i ngang du 'dus pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4050: dbye ba mi mnga' ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:4051: ris su 'dzin pa med pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4052: dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:4053: thams cad kyi 'byung gzhir gyur pa'i ngos nas thugs su bstan pa yang /
NK073(pu)006:4054: sku gsum gnyis bkag pa'am rdul phra rab kyis bshig
NK073(pu)006:4055: pa'am de las gzhan pa lta bu ma yin te
NK073(pu)006:4056: / de nyid thugs su lhun gyis grub pa de
NK073(pu)006:4057: ni tha snyad thams cad ma spang ngang gis dag
NK073(pu)006:4058: / pas na / kun tu bzang po'i thugs zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4060: thugs mi g.yo ba'i dkyil la sku gsung gnyis ma 'gags pa'i 'khor ram /
NK073(pu)006:4061: yang na sku'ang ma 'gags ma dmigs gsung thugs gnyis kyang ma 'gags pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:4062: ma dmigs pa'i 'khor gyis bskor ba 'am /
NK073(pu)006:4064: sku gsung thugs dbyer med pa de nyid phung po
NK073(pu)006:4065: khams dang skye mched du snang ba phung po la
NK073(pu)006:4067: khams la sogs pa phra ba'i 'khor gyis bskor ba'i rang bzhin nam /
NK073(pu)006:4068: ngo bo nyid la ni ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4069: de dag kyang lam pa'i blos bsgrub pa ma yin gyi /
NK073(pu)006:4070: mar ye nas snum pa ltar sus kyang ma byas par ye nas yin pa'i don rtogs nas /
NK073(pu)006:4072: rnal 'byor pas thos bsam sgom gsum gyis nyams su
NK073(pu)006:4073: myong nas rig pa yul bral mngon sum du gyur
NK073(pu)006:4074: pa'o // 'o na rtogs pas chog gam ce na mi chog ste /
NK073(pu)006:4075: rtogs pa zag bcas kyi mthong lam skad cig ma dang po yin la /
NK073(pu)006:4076: de'i don la lam pas rgyud du mi 'bral bar bsgom pa gces par gdams pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4077: tshig de ni gyur pa rdzogs pa chen po'i mdor bstan pa'am mgo 'dren pa'ang yin no //
NK073(pu)006:4079: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4081: rgyud nyid kyi lung gis bshad de /
NK073(pu)006:4083: khas blangs ba'i don nyid rgyud gsang ba'i snying po las bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:4084: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK073(pu)006:4085: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4086: chen po lnga ni yum lnga'i ngang nyid de /
NK073(pu)006:4087: zhes pa la sogs pa la rnams rtsa 'grel lta bu la yin kyang /
NK073(pu)006:4090: slob dpon gyi rgyas par bshad pa lta bu yin te //
NK073(pu)006:4091: de la rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK073(pu)006:4093: rdo rje ni chos kyi dbyings dus gsum du mi 'gyur bas rdo rje /
NK073(pu)006:4094: de gsal la 'gag pa med pa rang byung gi
NK073(pu)006:4095: ye shes su chos thams cad der 'dzom pas rdo
