NK073(pu)006:4096: rje / dbyings ye shes dbyer med pa mi phyed pa'i don gyis rdo rje ste /
NK073(pu)006:4097: don la rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'khor 'das
NK073(pu)006:4098: thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid mtha' thams cad dang
NK073(pu)006:4099: bral ba / mtshan nyid gang du ma grub pa nyid mtshan nyid thams cad par bzhugs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4100: de nyid rang snang ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:4102: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes 'du byed rnam par
NK073(pu)006:4103: shes pa lnga'o mi 'gags pa'i rtsal rang snang bas
NK073(pu)006:4106: gzugs kyi phung po'i yan lag rgyu'i gzugs bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4107: 'bras bu'i gzugs bcu gcig dang bco lnga /
NK073(pu)006:4108: tshor ba'i phung po'i yan lag /
NK073(pu)006:4111: btang snyoms su tshor ba la dbang po drug gi dbang du btang bas drug gsum bco brgyad /
NK073(pu)006:4112: 'du shes kyi phung po'i yan lag rgya che chung tshad med pa gsum /
NK073(pu)006:4113: 'du byed kyi phung po'i yan lag lnga bcu rtsa gcig ste /
NK073(pu)006:4114: phung po lnga yan lag dang bcas par /
NK073(pu)006:4116: rdo rje lta bu'i byang chub kyi sems las ma
NK073(pu)006:4117: g.yos shing byang chub sems nyid snang ba ni rgyu
NK073(pu)006:4118: 'bras sam / don rtogs lta bu ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4119: chu dang gzugs brnyan ltar dbyer med par lhun gyis grub pa'i gtan tshigs kyis /
NK073(pu)006:4120: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags /
NK073(pu)006:4121: zhes pa ma h+aa yo ga bzhin bsgyur bya sgyur byed lta bu ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4122: bshad pa'i gtan tshigs kyis snang tsam nyid na sangs rgyas lnga ru lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:4124: tshogs gnyis rdzogs te ma 'gags pa bsod nams /
NK073(pu)006:4125: mi 'dzin pa ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:4126: ye rdzogs chen po'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:4127: sangs rgyas kyang rdo rje lta bu'i byang chub sems
NK073(pu)006:4128: la phyogs zhen phra ba'i phra ba'ang mi mnga' bas
NK073(pu)006:4129: ni sangs / de nyid phyi nang gi phung po
NK073(pu)006:4130: mi 'gags par lhun gyis grub pa ni rang rig
NK073(pu)006:4132: lnga zhes pa phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas te /
NK073(pu)006:4137: rnam par shes pa rdor sems dang lnga ru grags /
NK073(pu)006:4138: zhes pa nang pa'i rgyud thams cad du grags pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:4139: yang na phyogs thams cad du rgyas pa nam mkha'i
NK073(pu)006:4140: mthas gtugs pa thams cad rigs lngar lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:4142: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i gtan tshigs zhib mo ni rgyas bshad kyi skabs su 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK073(pu)006:4144: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai /
NK073(pu)006:4146: 'byung ba lnga yum lnga'i ngo bor bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:4147: 'byung ba lngas phung po lnga bskyed par byed pas kyang yum /
NK073(pu)006:4148: phung po lnga dang dbyer mi phyed pa'i don kyis kyang yum /
NK073(pu)006:4149: de las sangs rgyas spyan ma zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4150: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi yum /
NK073(pu)006:4151: chu ma ma k+ai ste rin po che'i rigs kyi yum /
NK073(pu)006:4152: me gos dkar mo ste pad+ma rigs kyi yum /
NK073(pu)006:4153: rlung dam tshig sgrol ma ste las kyi rigs kyi yum /
NK073(pu)006:4154: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma zhes pas rdo rje'i rigs kyi yum mo //
NK073(pu)006:4155: phung po dang 'byung ba de ltar sangs rgyas tsa
NK073(pu)006:4156: yan lag rnams sangs rgyas ma rgyas pa mi srid
NK073(pu)006:4157: pas / 'dam bu gcig khong stong na kun stong /
NK073(pu)006:4158: tshar bu gcig rkang rub na kun rkang rub /
NK073(pu)006:4160: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun /
NK073(pu)006:4161: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4162: skye mched ni dbang po la skye zhing yul la mched par byed pa bcu gnyis so //
NK073(pu)006:4163: khams ni byed pa med par mtshan nyid 'dzin pa
NK073(pu)006:4164: gcig gi spyod yul du gcig ma gyur pas na
NK073(pu)006:4165: khams / de rnams ni bco brgyad do //
NK073(pu)006:4166: de la mig gi skye mched gzugs kyi skye mched /
NK073(pu)006:4169: mig gi rnam par shes pa'i khams la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4170: rgyud de dag byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid /
NK073(pu)006:4172: phyi nang gi sems dpa' sems ma bcu drug ste /
NK073(pu)006:4173: mig rna ba sna lce'i rnam shes bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4174: sa'i snying po la sogs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4175: skye ba'i sgo mig la sogs pa'i dbang po bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4176: byams pa la sogs pa'i sems dpa' bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4177: mched pa'i yul gzugs la sogs pa bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4178: sgeg mo la sogs pa'i sems ma bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4179: dbang po la brten te 'byung ba'i dus bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4180: bdug spos ma la sogs pa'i sems ma bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4182: mtha' thug pa med pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyi rtog
NK073(pu)006:4183: tshogs de 'dam bu'i dpes gcig dag na kun dag
NK073(pu)006:4184: pa'o // de'ang rtog tshogs dang sems dpa' gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:4185: bzang ngan gnyis gral bstun pa lta bu'am /
NK073(pu)006:4186: ngan pa bcom nas bzang po bsgrubs pa lta bu'am /
NK073(pu)006:4187: ngan pa la bzang por 'gyur ba lta bu skabs 'dir ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4188: byang chub sems rdo rje lta bu ma 'gags pa'i
NK073(pu)006:4189: byin brlabs las chu'i gzugs brnyan ltar khams dang skye
NK073(pu)006:4190: mched du snang tsam nyid na /
NK073(pu)006:4191: de nyid byang chub sems dpar lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:4192: ma 'gags pa nyid la snang stong gi 'dzin pa mi mnga' bas byang /
NK073(pu)006:4193: khams dang skye mched ci ltar snang yang byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pas chub /
NK073(pu)006:4194: de nyid la phyogs zhe na phra ba'ang mi mnga'
NK073(pu)006:4195: zhing dus gsum du mi g.yo mi 'gyur bas sems
NK073(pu)006:4197: de nyid mtha' zag pa med pa'i rtog tshogs thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas //
NK073(pu)006:4198: sems kyi dbyings su lhun gyis grub pa la ni tha snyad du dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4199: nyid ni lam pa'i blos byas pa ma yin ye nas de ltar gnas zhe'o //
NK073(pu)006:4201: 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med pa'i khams gsum 'phral
NK073(pu)006:4202: du byas pa ma yin par ye nas ma 'dres
NK073(pu)006:4203: la yongs su rdzogs pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'ba'
NK073(pu)006:4204: zhing du rnam par dag pas 'khor ba'am gzung 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:4205: rdul phra rab tsam yang ma dmigs te /
NK073(pu)006:4206: gser gling ngam nyi ma'i snying po ltar gzung 'dzin ka nas dag par bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:4208: rgyud gsang ba'i snying po las byung ste /
NK073(pu)006:4210: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:4211: de'i nang du'ang sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin zhes pa mdor bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:4212: de rgyas par bshad pa la'ang nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4213: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad ces pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:4214: khams gsum 'khor ba'i chos rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4216: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa thams cad /
NK073(pu)006:4217: sems thog ma nas don dam pa'i rang bzhin ma
NK073(pu)006:4218: byung ma skyes pa'i chos nyid rig pa byang chub
NK073(pu)006:4219: kyi sems mtshan nyid thams cad dang bral ba ni
NK073(pu)006:4220: gong gi rdo rje'i bshad pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4221: gzhi de las phung po lnga la sogs pa ma 'gags par snang ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:4222: bya ba byed pa'i nus pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4227: nam mkhas go 'byed pa'i bya ba byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4228: gzugs kyi phung pos 'dzin pa'i bya ba byed /
NK073(pu)006:4231: 'du byed kyis myong ba'i bya ba byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4232: de la sogs pa'i khams dang skye mched rnams kyis so so'i bya ba byed pa rnams so //
NK073(pu)006:4234: de dag so so'i rtsal ma 'gags pa nus pa thogs med kyi mtshan nyid can no //
NK073(pu)006:4236: rig pa'i ye shes gsal la 'gags pa med pa
NK073(pu)006:4237: nyid du snang ba phung po khams dang skye mched
NK073(pu)006:4238: ste / snang bzhin du ma grub po chos kyi
NK073(pu)006:4239: dbyings las ma g.yos pa sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:4240: ste / pa rnams ni / bde bar gshegs pa yab yum bcu la sogs pa /
NK073(pu)006:4241: zhes pa 'dir yang lam lnga'i rim pa bzhin du
NK073(pu)006:4242: bgrod nas 'bras bu mngon du byas pa 'og ma'i
NK073(pu)006:4243: bder gshegs la ni mi bzhag gi /
NK073(pu)006:4245: nyid la gshegs pa rnam pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:4246: dang po ni ma 'gags pa dang ma dmigs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:4247: longs spyod gnyis dbyer med pa la ni bde bar
NK073(pu)006:4248: brjod la / de las dus gsum du 'gyur ldog mi mnga' ba la ni /
NK073(pu)006:4249: gshegs pa'am mthar son pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4250: nyid la gshegs pa ni bde bar zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4251: rdo rje lta bu'i rang rig pa'i ye shes la gzung 'dzin mi mnga' bas ni bde la /
NK073(pu)006:4252: de nyid kyi rtsal mi 'gags par snang bas na gshegs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4253: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams so //
NK073(pu)006:4254: yab ni phung po lnga ste mi 'gags pa'i mtshan nyid can no //
NK073(pu)006:4255: yum ni 'byung ba lnga ste phung po bskyed pa'i mtshan nyid can no //
NK073(pu)006:4256: sogs khongs su khams dang skye mched rnams sems dpa' dang sems ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:4257: gong du bde bar gshegs pa'i sgras ye nas yin gyi /
NK073(pu)006:4258: min pa la yin par ma bsgyur te /
NK073(pu)006:4259: dper na ngo mi shes pa 'ag'i mdun du gser
NK073(pu)006:4260: bzhag na gser ngo ma shes par rdor mthong la
NK073(pu)006:4261: / ngo shes pa'i dus su gser la gser du shes pa las /
NK073(pu)006:4262: ma rtogs pa'i snod ma btab pa bzhin du /
NK073(pu)006:4263: phung khams skye mched rnams snang stong dbyer med pa /
NK073(pu)006:4264: byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa las mi 'da' bas na /
NK073(pu)006:4265: rnam par dag pa la ni lha zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:4266: yul dang yul can gyi cha 'dzin pas ni yab yum zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4267: ma rtogs pas gzung 'dzin 'khrul par brtags kyang /
NK073(pu)006:4268: lha'i ngang las mi 'gyur ba ni gser la rdor mthong bas mtshon la /
NK073(pu)006:4269: de nyid de ltar ye nas yin pa'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:4270: de ngo shes pa'i thabs su rgyas par bshad na /
NK073(pu)006:4271: chos thams cad ni zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4272: 'khrul snang gi chos phung khams skyed mched byed pa
NK073(pu)006:4273: med par so so'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa thams cad
NK073(pu)006:4274: do // de dag ni chos kyi dbyings yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:4276: ngo bo nyid kyis ma 'gags pa ni sku /
NK073(pu)006:4277: ma dmigs pa ni ye shes /
NK073(pu)006:4278: des na khams blangs pa'i sku gsung thugs dkyil 'khor
NK073(pu)006:4279: gyi rang bzhin du de la der 'dzin mi mnga'
NK073(pu)006:4280: bas gsung 'dzin dag pa'i dbang gis mya ngan 'das
NK073(pu)006:4282: de nyid so sor bstan pa gang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:4283: chen po lnga ni yul lnga'i ngang nyid ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:4285: de'ang gong du mdor bstan gyi skabs su dang po yab bstan la /
NK073(pu)006:4286: 'dir dang po yum bstan pas dgos pa ci zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:4287: gong du ni dang po dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'am /
NK073(pu)006:4288: rtsa ba lta bur gyur pa'i don gyis dang po yab bstan la /
NK073(pu)006:4289: 'dir ni phung khams skye mched rnams 'byung ba lnga
NK073(pu)006:4290: la snang bas des na gzhi'i phyir dang po yum
NK073(pu)006:4291: bstan to // chen po zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4292: khyab che ste nam mkhas gar khyab du khyab /
NK073(pu)006:4293: las kyi nus pa che ste khams gsum gyi chos thams cad snang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:4294: nam mkhas khams gsum gyi go 'byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4295: sas khams gsum brtan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4296: chus khams gsum sdud pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4297: mes smin par byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4298: rlung gis g.yo zhing bskyod pas las thams cad 'grub cing chud mi za bar byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4299: lnga ni 'byung ba lnga po yum ni chos thams cad mi phyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4301: de nyid rigs kyi yum chen mo lnga yi ngang nyid ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:4302: 'byung ba ni nam mkha' nyid bshad pa'i don dang
NK073(pu)006:4303: ldan pa las gsal zhing go 'byed pa ni las
NK073(pu)006:4305: byang chub sems las ma g.yos /
NK073(pu)006:4307: kun tu bzang mo zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4308: gzung 'dzin gyi skyon mi mnga' bas so //
NK073(pu)006:4309: yang na dbyings phyug ma zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4310: 'byung ba bzhi dang des bskyed pa'i phyi nang gi
NK073(pu)006:4311: chos thams cad snang ba'i gzhi 'am rgyur gyur pas
NK073(pu)006:4313: thams cad de'i ngang las dbyer med cing mi gnyis pas na dbang phyug ma zhes kyang bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4314: de nyid ni rdo rje'i rigs kyi yum ste /
NK073(pu)006:4315: rdo rje ni skye 'jig med pa dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba /
NK073(pu)006:4316: chos kyi dbyings shin tu dag pa'i ye shes /
NK073(pu)006:4317: ye shes thams cad kyi bdag nyid yin pas rdo rje rigs kyi yum mo //
NK073(pu)006:4318: ma 'gags par 'byung ba sar snang ba nyid spyan zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4319: sa dngos su mthong zhing rtag brtan la thams cad bskyed pa'i gzhir gyur pa ltar /
NK073(pu)006:4320: ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med pa nyid byang chub
NK073(pu)006:4321: sems su lhun gyis grub pa nyid dus gsum du
NK073(pu)006:4322: ma 'gyur ba de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi yum
NK073(pu)006:4323: ste / thams cad mkhyen pa'i che yon thams cad snang ba'i gzhir gyur pas /
NK073(pu)006:4325: chu ni thams cad skyod cing sdud pa'i las dang /
NK073(pu)006:4326: rgyun mi chad pa dang mnyen pas gar yang drangs
NK073(pu)006:4327: du btub ste de nyid ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer
NK073(pu)006:4328: med pa m+aa m+aa k+ai ste /
NK073(pu)006:4329: chu'i bshad pa gsum gyis m+aa ma k+ai'i gtan tshigs 'grub po //
NK073(pu)006:4330: de nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi ngo
NK073(pu)006:4331: bo rin po che'i rigs yon tan gyi bdag nyid
NK073(pu)006:4332: kyi yum mo // me ni me nyid ma gtogs
NK073(pu)006:4333: par gzhan thams cad bsreg par byed pas mi gnas
NK073(pu)006:4334: kyi yum mo // pa dang / smin cing brtas par byed pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4335: de nyid ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med pa byang
NK073(pu)006:4336: chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa nyid gos dkar
NK073(pu)006:4338: gdul bya'i yon tan thams cad smin cing brtags par
NK073(pu)006:4339: byed kyang gzung 'dzin gyi nyes spyod gyis ma gos
NK073(pu)006:4340: pas kha dog dkar ba la skyon med pa bzhin
NK073(pu)006:4341: / gos dkar mo zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4342: gsum pad+ma'i rigs so sor rtog pa'i rigs kyi yum ste /
NK073(pu)006:4343: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes spyi dang rang gi
NK073(pu)006:4344: mtshan nyid gnyis kyi ngos nas mtha' gnyis kyi skyon
NK073(pu)006:4346: gdul bya'i don smin cing brtan par byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4347: rlung ni dngos po med kyang gzhan bskyod cing sgrol ba'i las dang ldan /
NK073(pu)006:4348: de nyid ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med pa ni sgrol ma zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4349: rang gi ngo bo mtshan nyid thams cad dang bral
NK073(pu)006:4350: yang gdul bya sgrol ba'i phrin las rgyun mi chad
NK073(pu)006:4351: la / de nyid bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las kyi rigs kyi yum ste /
NK073(pu)006:4352: mdzad pa'i phrin las rgyun mi chad kyang phyogs su
NK073(pu)006:4353: 'dzin pa rdul phra rab tsam yang mi mnga' ba
NK073(pu)006:4354: nyid kyis / bdag don mthar phyin cing gzhan don mur sgrubs pas sgrol ma'o //
NK073(pu)006:4356: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang dang lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang gnyis las /
NK073(pu)006:4357: 'dir lhun gyis grub pa nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:4358: 'byung ba lngar snang tsam nyid na yum lngar lhun grub tu bzhugs la /
NK073(pu)006:4359: de nyid la snang stong gi dri ma phra ba'am
NK073(pu)006:4360: mi mnga' la mnyam pa nyid du lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:4361: pa nyid do // phung po lnga ni rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas /
NK073(pu)006:4363: gzugs la sogs pa lnga rnam grangs mang po gcig
NK073(pu)006:4364: tu 'tshogs pa la ni phung po zhes bya ste
NK073(pu)006:4365: / de dag mi 'gags par snang ba gser ma
NK073(pu)006:4366: shes pa dang 'dra bar ngo bo nyid kyis rigs
NK073(pu)006:4367: lnga'i sangs rgyas su lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:4368: gzugs kyi phung po rnam par snang mdzad ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:4369: gzugs chen bco lnga dang so so'i chos ma 'gags
NK073(pu)006:4370: par snang zhing phung po bzhi yang yang snang ba'i
NK073(pu)006:4371: rten du gyur pas de nyid ma 'gags ma dmigs
NK073(pu)006:4372: dbyer med pa / byang chub sems su rtogs pa
NK073(pu)006:4373: ni don dang mthun pa'i ming rnam par snang mdzad
NK073(pu)006:4374: de rigs lnga la sku'i rigs te ma 'gags pa'i
NK073(pu)006:4375: dbyer med pa / ngos nas so // tshor ba ni rin chen 'byung ldan te /
NK073(pu)006:4376: yul dang yul can tshor ba'i rnam grangs drug gsum
NK073(pu)006:4377: bco brgyad rnams ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med pa
NK073(pu)006:4378: byang chub sems su gsal la /
NK073(pu)006:4379: de nyid de'i dbang gis bde sdug 'dzin pa ris dang bral ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:4380: rtog pa med pas rin po che dang 'dra ste /
NK073(pu)006:4381: bco brgyad mi 'gags par snang bas dgos pa skong
NK073(pu)006:4382: bar byed pa ni rin po che las dgos 'dod
NK073(pu)006:4383: 'byung ba ste / de nyid rigs ni rin po
NK073(pu)006:4384: che'i rigs te bde bar gshegs pa'i yon tan thams
NK073(pu)006:4385: 'byung ba ste / cad ni / dbyings rig pa
NK073(pu)006:4386: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las cir yang snang ba'o
NK073(pu)006:4388: rgya che chung tshad med pa gsum gsal la ma
NK073(pu)006:4389: 'gags ngo bo sems las ma g.yos te /
NK073(pu)006:4390: dbyer med pa byang chub sems su 'das pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4391: pad+ma'i rigs te pad+ma 'dam na gnas kyang 'dam gyi
NK073(pu)006:4392: nyes pas mi gos pa dang 'dra bar so sor
NK073(pu)006:4393: rtog pa'i ye shes kyis chos spyi dang rang gi
NK073(pu)006:4394: mtshan nyid lhun gyis grub bas mtha' gnyis kyis mi
NK073(pu)006:4395: gos te / 'du shes gsal la ma dmigs pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK073(pu)006:4396: de la ni snang ba mtha' yas zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4397: snang ba ma dmigs pa nyid khams gsum gyis 'du shes cir yang lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4398: 'du byed lnga bcu rtsa gcig ma 'gags par snang /
NK073(pu)006:4399: ngo bo ma dmigs byang chub sems su lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:4400: grub pa ni 'khor 'das dbyer med pa'i ngo bo
NK073(pu)006:4401: ste de nyid don yod grub pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4402: ma 'gags par snang bas gzhan don lhun gyis grub la /
NK073(pu)006:4403: ma dmigs pas bdag don lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:4404: dbyer med pa don gnyis skad cig la rdzogs la /
NK073(pu)006:4405: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:4406: des na mthong snang gi chos bya ba byed nus
NK073(pu)006:4407: pa'i mtshan nyid 'dzin nus pa thams cad ni ngo
NK073(pu)006:4408: bo nyid kyi sku'i mdzad pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4409: ched du ma mdzad par bdag gzhan gyi bya ba thams cad 'grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4410: de ni don gnyis kyi bdag gzhan gyi bya ba thams cad mthar phyin pas /
NK073(pu)006:4412: rnam par shes pa'i phung po ni rnam shes tshogs
NK073(pu)006:4413: brgyad du ma 'gags par snang ba ngo bo dgu
NK073(pu)006:4414: pa las ma g.yos te dbyer med pa nyid ni
NK073(pu)006:4415: rdo rje ste / tshogs brgyad ci ltar snang yang
NK073(pu)006:4416: rnam shes dgu pa dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba
NK073(pu)006:4417: rdo rje ste / dang / tshogs brgyad ma 'gags
NK073(pu)006:4418: kyang de nyid dgu pa'i ngang du 'joms pa dang
NK073(pu)006:4419: rdo rje ste / dang / / gnyis po chu
NK073(pu)006:4420: dang gsher ba ltar mi phyed pa'i don gyi na
NK073(pu)006:4421: rdo rje ste / dang / / rdo rje ste
NK073(pu)006:4422: / dus gsum du mi 'gyur bas na rigs so
NK073(pu)006:4423: rdo rje ste / dang / / rdo rje ste
NK073(pu)006:4424: / // ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa mtha'
NK073(pu)006:4425: gnyis su mi g.yo bas mi bskyod pa zhes bya
NK073(pu)006:4426: rdo rje ste / dang / / rdo rje ste
NK073(pu)006:4427: / // ste / rang rig byang chub kyi sems
NK073(pu)006:4428: dgu pa'i ngo bo nyid gzhi dag pa la phyogs
NK073(pu)006:4429: 'dzin mi mnga' bas chos kyi dbyings shin tu dag
NK073(pu)006:4432: lnga pa nyid ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i don der phyogs zhen mi mnga' bas sangs la /
NK073(pu)006:4433: mtha' dang bral ba'i ye shes phung pos gar khyab tu rgyas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4434: des na ma rtogs pa'i dus su phung po dang
NK073(pu)006:4435: 'byung ba dbyer med du bzhugs pas yab yum du
NK073(pu)006:4436: smos la / de nyid bshad pa'i chos rnams kyis ye nas dbyer med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4437: de ltar 'byung ba dang phung po de ltar yin phan chod du /
NK073(pu)006:4438: de las snang ba'i phung po dang khams dang skye mched rnams kyang /
NK073(pu)006:4439: byang chub sems su snang ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:4441: rnams par shes pa bzhi ni zhes pa mig rna sna lce bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:4442: byang chub sems dpa' bzhi ni /
NK073(pu)006:4443: sa'i snying po spyan ras gzigs nam mkha'i snying po rdo rje can bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:4444: de yang gdos pa can dod bsnyams pa lta bu'am /
NK073(pu)006:4445: ngan pa bsheg nas bzang por byas pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:4446: mi 'dra ba las 'dra bar bcos pa'am /
NK073(pu)006:4447: ma h+aa pa bzhin lta bu ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4448: mig gi rnam par shes pa byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po ste /
NK073(pu)006:4449: de la mig gi rnam par shes pa ni gzugs 'dzin rig cing gcod pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4450: de rnams ma 'gags ngo bo ma dmigs te dbyer med pa nyid sa'i snying po zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4451: sa ni yon tan thams cad bskyed pa'i gzhi rten yin la /
NK073(pu)006:4452: de nyid spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral bas snying po zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4453: yon tan gyi bdag nyid phyag na rin po che'i myu gu bsnams pa'i don no //
NK073(pu)006:4454: des na mig gi rnam shes dbyer med pa byang
NK073(pu)006:4455: chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa la sa snying
NK073(pu)006:4456: zhes bya'o // rna ba'i rnam shes ni sgra 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:4457: gyi shes pa nyid ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med
NK073(pu)006:4458: pa nyid gsung gi lam ste /
NK073(pu)006:4460: de yang spyan ras gzigs ni de bzhin gshegs pa
NK073(pu)006:4461: thams cad kyi gsung gi ngo bo nyid thugs rje'i
NK073(pu)006:4462: spyan ras kyis mthar thug pa med pa'i 'gro ba
NK073(pu)006:4463: la gzigs pa dang tshul mthun pa rna ba'i rnam
NK073(pu)006:4464: shes kyis kyang thag ring ba'i sgra gcod pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4465: sna'i rnam shes ni dri'i bye brag gcod pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4466: ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med pa nyid byang chub sems la /
NK073(pu)006:4467: de nyid ni nam mkha'i snying po ste /
NK073(pu)006:4468: nam mkha' ni chos thams cad kyi go 'byed kyang ngo bo ma grub pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:4469: dri'i bye brag rnams kyang so sor ma 'dres par
NK073(pu)006:4470: myong ba yod kyang gzugs su grub pa med pas
NK073(pu)006:4471: lce'i rnam shes ni ro'i bye brag rnams gcod pa'i
NK073(pu)006:4472: ngo bo ste / ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med pa byang chub sems las ma g.yos la /
NK073(pu)006:4473: de nyid ni phyag na rdo rje ste /
NK073(pu)006:4474: ro'i bye brag rnams chos kyi dbyings su 'jogs shing de nyid las mi 'gyu bas so //
NK073(pu)006:4475: byang chub sems dpa' bzhi zhes pa rnam shes bzhi chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pas byang /
NK073(pu)006:4476: rnam shes bzhi de nyid du lhun gyis grub pas chub /
NK073(pu)006:4477: de dbyer med pa nyid dus gsum du mi 'gyur bas sems /
NK073(pu)006:4478: des mtha' gnyis 'joms pas dpa' ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:4480: rang bzhin zhes pas chu mthong tsa na gsher ba
NK073(pu)006:4481: dus mtshungs pa dang 'dra bar rnam shes bzhi byang
NK073(pu)006:4482: chub sems dpa' bzhi'i ngo las ma 'da' bar bstan
NK073(pu)006:4483: to // yul bzhi ni mdzes pa'i lha mo bzhi'i rang bzhin zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:4484: yul ni rnam par shes pa'i yul du gyur pa ste //
NK073(pu)006:4490: rnam shes bzhi'i dgos pa skong bar byed pas so //
NK073(pu)006:4491: de yang rnam par shes pa bzhi byang chub sems kyi ngang las ma 'das tsa /
NK073(pu)006:4492: yul dang yul can snga phyi med pa gcig char
NK073(pu)006:4493: du grub pa nyid byang chub sems su grub pa
NK073(pu)006:4494: yin pas / yul bzhis so sor rnams pa ma 'gags par snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:4495: de ngo bo chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos de
NK073(pu)006:4496: dbyer med pa byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:4497: pa'i ngang phyogs zhen gyi nyes pa mi mnga' bas
NK073(pu)006:4499: gzung 'dzin ka nas dag pas lha /
NK073(pu)006:4500: rnam par shes pas spyod par bya ba'i yul du
NK073(pu)006:4501: gyur cing mnyes pa'i stoms dang ldan pas na mo
NK073(pu)006:4502: // de yang sgegs mo ni gzugs kyi bye brag
NK073(pu)006:4503: thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i ngang
NK073(pu)006:4504: las ched 'dzin gyi skyon dang bral bas sgegs mo'o
NK073(pu)006:4505: // // sgra'i bye brag thams cad ma 'dres la
NK073(pu)006:4506: yongs su rdzogs pa byang chub sems su lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:4507: grub pa nyid rnam par shes pa'i mnyes pa bskyed
NK073(pu)006:4508: par byed pas dbyangs mkhan ma /
NK073(pu)006:4509: dri'i bye brag rnams ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:4510: pa byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa nyid
NK073(pu)006:4511: rig pa la mdzes pa rgyun mi chad pa phreng
NK073(pu)006:4512: ba ma / ro'i bye brag rnams ma 'dres la
NK073(pu)006:4513: yongs su rdzogs pa nyid byangs chub sems su lhun
NK073(pu)006:4514: gyis grub pa bde ba'i ye shes kyis lce'i rnam
NK073(pu)006:4515: par shes pa'i dgos pa skong bar mdzad pas gar
NK073(pu)006:4516: ba ma / ma'o // de dag kyang rnam par shes pa la brten te yul gcod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4517: yul la brten te rnam par shes pa skye bas
NK073(pu)006:4518: yab yum du rgyun mi chad par ngo bo nyid
NK073(pu)006:4519: kyi bzhugs so // rang bzhin ni bshad zin to //
NK073(pu)006:4520: dbang po bzhi ni mig la sogs pa bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:4521: byang chub sems dpa'i rang bzhin zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4522: byams pa la sogs pa bzhi'o //
NK073(pu)006:4523: de la mig gi dbang po zar ma'i me tog
NK073(pu)006:4524: kha phye ba lta bu ma 'dres la yongs rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:4525: byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa nyid byang
NK073(pu)006:4526: chub sems dpa' byams pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4528: de na g+han+d+he bsnams pa yang khrus dang gtsang sbra
NK073(pu)006:4529: ste lus kyi bya ba shas che pa'i tshul lo
NK073(pu)006:4530: // rna ba'i dbang po gro rna gcus pa 'dra ba ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK073(pu)006:4531: sems kyi dbyings su gsal ba nyid sgrib pa rnams sel te /
NK073(pu)006:4532: gsung gis shes bya'i brda 'phrad cing 'gro ba'i mun
NK073(pu)006:4533: pa sel ba po ti'i phyag rgya yang rtags so
NK073(pu)006:4534: // sna'i dbang po zangs kyi mo khab gshib pa 'dra ba ma 'dres /
NK073(pu)006:4535: yongs rdzogs byang chub sems su lhun gyis rdzogs par rtogs pa nyid kun tu bzang po ste /
NK073(pu)006:4536: byang chub sems la mngar 'dzin mi mnga' ba'i don dang mthun pa'i mtshan no //
NK073(pu)006:4537: mnyam pa nyid la che ba'i yon tan rgyun mi chad pa'i rtags su rin po che'i snye ma'o //
NK073(pu)006:4538: lce'i dbang po zla ba bkas pa lta bu ma
NK073(pu)006:4539: 'dres yongs rdzogs byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:4541: phyogs su 'dzin pa'i zug rngu mi mnga' bas 'jam la /
NK073(pu)006:4542: de nyid kyis dpal du gyur pas na'o //
NK073(pu)006:4543: de ltar dbang po bzhi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs byang chub sems lhun gyis grub tsa /
NK073(pu)006:4544: dbang po la brten te dus byung ba dus bzhi ni yul du dag ste /
NK073(pu)006:4550: dbang po mnyes par byed pas so //
NK073(pu)006:4551: bshad pa bzhin gyi lha mo bzhi ni /
NK073(pu)006:4556: dus 'das pa dang dbyings kyi khams ma 'dres yongs
NK073(pu)006:4557: rdzogs byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa dbang
NK073(pu)006:4558: po mnyes par byed pas na lha mo ste spos
NK073(pu)006:4559: me ma'o // da ltar dang dbyar gyi khams ma
NK073(pu)006:4560: 'dres yongs rdzogs nyid rig pa la lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:4561: pa lha mo me tog ma'o //
NK073(pu)006:4562: 'byung ba dang ston ma 'dres yongs rdzogs byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa mar me ma'o //
NK073(pu)006:4563: ma 'ongs pa dang dgun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs lhun gyis grub pa dri chab ma'o //
NK073(pu)006:4564: de dag 'phral du byas pa ma yin /
NK073(pu)006:4565: ye nas de ltar bzhugs pas na rang bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:4569: de las byung ba'i byang chub sems /
NK073(pu)006:4570: khro bo bzhi'i rang bzhin zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4571: dbang po rnam shes brgyad pos ni /
NK073(pu)006:4572: yul gcod kyang 'jam pa dang snyoms pa'i tshul gyis bya chub sems dpa' zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:4573: 'dir lus kyi dbang yul gyis yul gcod pa ni stobs che ste /
NK073(pu)006:4574: 'di'i dus su gzhan ma rnams 'gag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4575: mi gnas par mdzad pas khro bo zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4576: de la lus kyi dbang po ni gsang ba'i rdo rje'o //
NK073(pu)006:4577: rnam par shes pa ni yul la reg pa reg shes so //
NK073(pu)006:4578: yul ni rdo rje'i yul lo //
NK073(pu)006:4579: de na dbang po dang yul du 'dzom pa'i dus
NK073(pu)006:4580: su rnam par shes pa dang gsum 'dzom pa las
NK073(pu)006:4581: byung ba ni gsum 'dus ba'i reg pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4582: ngo bo byang chub sems su'o //
NK073(pu)006:4583: khro bo bzhi'i rang bzhin zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4584: bzhi po ma 'dres yongs rdzogs byang chub sems su
NK073(pu)006:4585: lhun gyis grub pa nyid ma 'gags par snang ba
NK073(pu)006:4587: lus kyis dbang po dngos su snang ba sku gshin rje gshed /
NK073(pu)006:4588: rnam shes dngos po dang bral ba thugs stobs po che /
NK073(pu)006:4589: yul bde ba mi 'gags pa'i gnas gsum rta mgrin /
NK073(pu)006:4590: gsum 'dus pa'i reg pa byang chub sems nyams su myong ba'i tshe rtog tshogs /
NK073(pu)006:4591: gzhan ma thams cad nub pa'i las dang ldan pas phrin las bdud rtsi 'khyil pa /
NK073(pu)006:4592: de dag kyang ma h+aa yo ga bzhin sku la
NK073(pu)006:4593: brtsi ba ma yin la sku spong ba'ang ma yin
NK073(pu)006:4594: te / ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas so //
NK073(pu)006:4595: khro bo rab brjod pa ni las ma 'gags pa'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:4596: yul khro mo bzhi ni rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi
NK073(pu)006:4597: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi don la mtshan yum mi
NK073(pu)006:4598: pham la sogs pa bzhir 'dogs so //
NK073(pu)006:4599: de ltar rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas tsa /
NK073(pu)006:4600: de'i rtsa ba ni yid kyi shes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4601: yid kyi rnam par shes pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4602: byang chub sems rdo rje yid kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4603: yid ni skad cig tu mi gnas par dngos po
NK073(pu)006:4604: med bzhin kun tu rgyu ba las rnam par shes
NK073(pu)006:4605: pa ni / drug po 'gag pa'i de ma thag
NK073(pu)006:4606: pa phyi nang gi chos thams cad la gcod pa'o
NK073(pu)006:4607: pa ni / // yid la'ang gnyis te kun tu
NK073(pu)006:4608: tshol ba'i yid ni shes pa yul la rtog cing
NK073(pu)006:4609: 'jug pa nyid kyi yul can no //
NK073(pu)006:4610: gtan la 'bebs pa'i yid ni shes pa brtags nas gcod de 'di yin zhes gtan la phab pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4611: de gnyis kyang ma go rting tsam min pa yun med de skad cig ma gcig go //
NK073(pu)006:4612: byang chub sems rdo rje zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4613: yid kyi shes pa ma 'gags par snang ba rtog
NK073(pu)006:4614: tshogs bzhi bcu zhe gnyis ci ltar 'char yang chos
NK073(pu)006:4615: kyi dbyings las ma g.yos te der 'dzin dang bral
NK073(pu)006:4616: bas byang / 'on kyang thams cad de nyid du lhun gyis grub pas chub /
NK073(pu)006:4617: de dbyer med pa'i ngang las rang rig rang byung
NK073(pu)006:4618: gi ye shes chen po ye nas 'od gsal ba'i
NK073(pu)006:4619: ngo bo nyid la dus gsum du 'gyur ba med
NK073(pu)006:4620: bas sems / ting nge 'dzin des chos thams cad 'joms pas kyang rdo rje /
NK073(pu)006:4621: ngo bo mi 'gyur bas kyang rdo rje /
NK073(pu)006:4622: dbyer med phyed pas kyang rdo rje /
NK073(pu)006:4624: rdo rje yid ste rang byung ye shes rdo rje nyid yid kyi shes pa gsal bar snang /
NK073(pu)006:4625: yid rdo rje ste yid kyi shes pa gsal ba nyid skye 'jig med pa rdo rje lta bu /
NK073(pu)006:4626: de'i ngo bo ni rtog tshogs bzhi bcu bshad pa
NK073(pu)006:4627: bzhin ma 'dres yongs rdzogs mtha' thams cad dang bral
NK073(pu)006:4628: ba'i ngang la phyogs zhen mi mnga' ba la tha
NK073(pu)006:4629: snyad du kun tu bzang po zhes bya yi /
NK073(pu)006:4630: don la kun tu bzang po zhes bya ba'i gdags gzhi dang yang bral lo //
NK073(pu)006:4631: rang bzhin ni ye nas yin pa'i don no //
NK073(pu)006:4632: de ni mi 'gags pa shas che ba yin la /
NK073(pu)006:4633: rang bzhin ni yul chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma
NK073(pu)006:4634: byas pa kun tu bzang mo'i rang bzhin te zhes
NK073(pu)006:4635: pa yul ni yid kyi yul lo //
NK073(pu)006:4637: chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas gnyis so //
NK073(pu)006:4638: de la 'dus byas ni kun rdzob kyi chos ste /
NK073(pu)006:4639: 'byung ba bzhis bskyed pa'i rtog pa bzhi bcu lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:4640: 'dus ma byas ni don dam par rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:4645: 'gog pa la so sor brtags pa'i 'gog pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4646: so sor brtags min gyi 'gog pa ste shes par zad /
NK073(pu)006:4647: des na yul gnyis po de ma 'gags ma dmigs
NK073(pu)006:4648: dbyer med pa byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:4649: pa la dus dang gnas skabs kun tu gzung 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:4650: gyi zhen pa dang bral bas bzang zhes bya ste
NK073(pu)006:4652: yid kyi yul yin pa'i ngos nas tha snyad du mo zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4653: de'i rang bzhin las mi 'da' bas na rang bzhin te /
NK073(pu)006:4654: nyon mongs pa drug thub pa drug tu 'dus pas gong gis basgre'o //
NK073(pu)006:4655: des na rtog pa'i chos de rnams la ma 'gags
NK073(pu)006:4656: par snang ba la phyogs 'dzin bral ba sku mi
NK073(pu)006:4658: rang bzhin med pa nyid phyogs 'dzin dang bral ba gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo //
NK073(pu)006:4659: de dbyer med pa nyid phyogs 'dzin thams cad dang
NK073(pu)006:4660: bral ba thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK073(pu)006:4661: ste / rdzogs pa chen po'i ngo bo kun tu
NK073(pu)006:4662: bzang po dang bzang mo dbyer med pa nyid mthong
NK073(pu)006:4663: snang gi chos da lta nyid nas yin zhes brjod
NK073(pu)006:4664: ste / pa'i don to // rgyu yi theg pa
NK073(pu)006:4665: dag gis mthong snang gi chos 'di ni don dam
NK073(pu)006:4666: pa'i bden pa min te sems can la 'khrul par
NK073(pu)006:4668: des ni sku gsung thugs kyi rgyas pa'i rgyas pa bshad nas /
NK073(pu)006:4669: de yang ye nas yin pa'i don rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4670: de dag kyang ye nas mngon par rdzogs par zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4671: smos pa'i rtog tshogs rnams sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil
NK073(pu)006:4672: 'khor du bstan pa de dag kyang min pa las
NK073(pu)006:4673: yin par bsgyur ba ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4674: nam mkhar ye nas stong gsal du gnas pa ltar
NK073(pu)006:4675: ma 'gags pa sku ma dmigs pa ye shes su
NK073(pu)006:4677: mngon par rdzogs zhes pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4678: dbang po'i mngon sum du gnas pa nyid ma byas
NK073(pu)006:4679: ma rtsal bar rang rig pa'i mngon sum du tshogs
NK073(pu)006:4680: gnyis ma bsags par rang rdzogs te /
NK073(pu)006:4681: ma 'gags pas ni chad pa'i mtha' las rgyal bar mngon zhing bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs la /
NK073(pu)006:4682: ma dmigs pas ni rtag pa'i mtha' las rgyal bar mngon zhing ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pas /
NK073(pu)006:4683: de nyid kyi ngang las phyogs zhen mi mnga' bas sangs /
NK073(pu)006:4684: don des mtha' dbus med par lhun gyis grub pas rgyas te /
NK073(pu)006:4685: de ni 'bras bu'i ngo bor tshogs ye rdzogs chen po'i gtan tshigs kyang ston to //
NK073(pu)006:4687: de ltar bu'i rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid ye nas zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4689: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams /
NK073(pu)006:4690: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyi /
NK073(pu)006:4692: des na rten gyi gang zag gis gser 'gyur rtsi
NK073(pu)006:4693: ltar da lta lam gyi gnas skabs su bsgrubs nas
NK073(pu)006:4694: bshad pa'i don rnams snang ba byas pa lta bu
NK073(pu)006:4695: ma yin te yin pa'i don bstan pa de kho
NK073(pu)006:4696: na'o // dbyer med pa rgyas par bshad pa ni gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:4697: bstan pa'i ngos nas don gtan la phab pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4698: de ltar phyogs bcu dus gsum zhes pas la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4699: gong du bstan pa sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK073(pu)006:4700: de yang ye nas yin pa'i don bstan pa de
NK073(pu)006:4701: ltar na mtha' thug pa med pa'i 'jig rten gyi
NK073(pu)006:4702: khams thams cad de rtog pa ji snyed pa thams
NK073(pu)006:4703: cad bshad pa'i don du lhun gyis grub pas /
NK073(pu)006:4704: phyogs kyi dbang du na bcu dang /
NK073(pu)006:4705: dus kyi bsdus na gsum dang /
NK073(pu)006:4706: gnas kyi bsdus na khams gsum dang /
NK073(pu)006:4707: sog khongs su snod 'byung ba bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:4708: bcud 'gro ba ris drug la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:4709: tha snyad thams cad dang de bsdus nas 'dus byas zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4710: kun rdzob 'byung ba dang 'byung ba las gyur pa thams cad dang /
NK073(pu)006:4712: don dam pa'i ma bshad pa'i 'dus ma byas bzhi po'am /
NK073(pu)006:4713: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos smos pa de dag thams cad /
NK073(pu)006:4714: rang gi sems las gud na med /
NK073(pu)006:4716: rang zhes bya ba ni bshad pa'i chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:4717: rtsa lo dang bral ba'i tshul gyis byang chub sems
NK073(pu)006:4719: de la snang stong gi 'dzin pa dang bral bas du ma ma grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:4720: ris su 'dzin pa dang bral ba'i ngos nas bdag nyid chen po'i ngang la rang zhes bya yis /
NK073(pu)006:4721: gzhan pa la ltos pa'i rang rtsa lo'am /
NK073(pu)006:4722: rnal 'byor pa gcig gi snying kha la 'char ba lta bur ni mi brjod de /
NK073(pu)006:4723: rdzogs pa chen po'i don ni khyab bdal lhun grub
NK073(pu)006:4724: kyi ngang la rtsa lo mi mnga' bas bdag gzhan
NK073(pu)006:4725: gyi 'dzin pa ma spangs rang dag go //
NK073(pu)006:4726: sems ni bdag nyid chen po'i ngo bo de nyid /
NK073(pu)006:4727: 'dzin pa dang bral bar ye nas 'od gsal ba la sems zhes brjod kyi /
NK073(pu)006:4728: dmigs pa'i spros bral ni 'dir kun rdzob bo //
NK073(pu)006:4729: de bas na sems kyi chos nyid spros pa'i mtshan
NK073(pu)006:4730: ma thams cad dang bral ba'i ngang la rtogs ma
NK073(pu)006:4731: rtogs kyi 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:4732: de'ang lam pa'i snang ba yin la /
NK073(pu)006:4733: thams cad mkhyen pa rang ngo la ni nam mkhas
NK073(pu)006:4734: nam mkha' mi 'dzin pa dang 'dra bas tha snyad
NK073(pu)006:4735: ma grub kyang / lam pa'i ngos nas mya ngan
NK073(pu)006:4736: las 'das pa'i che yon rnams yid kyi yul du
NK073(pu)006:4737: byas pa'ang gnas skabs der yid kyi shes pa de
NK073(pu)006:4738: nyid du snang ba las ma gtogs pa ngo bo
NK073(pu)006:4739: la yul yul can gtan nas ma dmigs te /
NK073(pu)006:4740: gsal pa de nyid ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:4741: pa'i ngang la phyogs 'dzin ma spangs bral ba ni
NK073(pu)006:4742: sems nyid rnam par dag pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4743: des na mya ngan las 'das pa thams cad kyang rang sems snang ba ce'o //
NK073(pu)006:4744: khams gsum 'khor ba'i chos mtha' thug pa med pa
NK073(pu)006:4745: ni ci ltar snang yang yid kyi shes pa nyid
NK073(pu)006:4746: der snang ba las ma gtogs pa yul du ma
NK073(pu)006:4747: grub la / de nyid ma 'dres la yongs su
NK073(pu)006:4748: rdzogs pa nyid bshad pa bzhin sems su lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:4749: grub pas sems las gud na med de zhes bya'o
NK073(pu)006:4750: grub la / // de ni lam pa'i blo tshod kyi snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:4751: bshad pa'i tshig gi na yar ni /
NK073(pu)006:4752: 'khor 'das thams cad sems kyi chos nyid las gung na med de rtogs na sangs rgyas su gcig /
NK073(pu)006:4753: ma rtogs na sems can du gcig /
NK073(pu)006:4756: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK073(pu)006:4757: de ni lung gi tshad mar gzhal zhes bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:4758: de nyid lung gi tshad mar bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4760: chos thams cad sems su gcig pa'i don gong du ji skad bshad pa bzhin te /
NK073(pu)006:4761: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud las kyang 'di skad du ston te /
NK073(pu)006:4762: rang sems so sor rtogs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4763: sangs rgyas byang chub de nyid de /
NK073(pu)006:4765: du ma bral ba'i rang gi sems kyi chos thams
NK073(pu)006:4766: cad dbyer med pa'i ngo bo ni rtogs par bya
NK073(pu)006:4767: ba'i yul lo // so sor rtog pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4768: zhes pa yul can lam pa rnams kyi rang gi
NK073(pu)006:4769: shes rab kyi rtsal dang mthun par so sor snang
NK073(pu)006:4770: ba'i rtogs pa ni gang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:4771: sems kyi chos nyid kyi don rtogs pa mtha' phyin
NK073(pu)006:4772: nas de las skyed du bya ba med pa ni
NK073(pu)006:4773: sangs rgyas so // sems kyi chos nyid spros pa'i
NK073(pu)006:4774: mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba ma skyes pa'i
NK073(pu)006:4776: byang chub ste sa dang po'o //
NK073(pu)006:4777: sems kyi mtshan nyid bden pa dbyer med kyi don mngon du byas pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4778: byang chub sems dpa' ste bsgom lam pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4779: bden pa dbyer med kyi don la mnyam rjes kyi cha phra ba dang ma bral la /
NK073(pu)006:4780: so sor rtog pa ni byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ste mthar lam pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4781: zhar la sems kyi don skad cig ma dang rdul phra rab don dam du rtogs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4782: nyan thos rang rgyal te de ltar na rtogs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:4783: bye brag so sor mi 'dra ba rnams kyang sems
NK073(pu)006:4784: nyid 'od gsal rang byung gi ye shes chen po
NK073(pu)006:4785: de nyid la snang zhing de nyid du gcig pas
NK073(pu)006:4786: so // 'jig rten gsum pa'ang de nyid de /
NK073(pu)006:4789: bcas pa'i khams gsum po'ang sems nyid de la snang
NK073(pu)006:4790: zhing de nyid kyi ngang du dbyer med de rgyu
NK073(pu)006:4791: rkyen rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba phra rab kyi
NK073(pu)006:4792: dngos po thams cad kyang sems rnam par dag pa
NK073(pu)006:4793: de nyid du lhun gyis grub po /
NK073(pu)006:4794: 'byung ba che rnams de nyid de zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4795: khams gsum snod bcud 'grub par byed pa'i rgyu nam
NK073(pu)006:4796: mkha'i ngang las de nyid kyang rgyun chad med pa
NK073(pu)006:4797: dang / snod bcud thams cad snang bas /
NK073(pu)006:4798: 'byung ba chen po rnams ni lnga po de nyid
NK073(pu)006:4799: kyang sems de kho na nyid du dbyer med cing
NK073(pu)006:4801: zhes gong du bstan pa'i rgyud las 'byung ngo //
NK073(pu)006:4802: de ltar ma 'gags pa thams cad sems nyid du gcig par bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:4803: sems rang gi ngo bo nyid bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4805: zhes pa gong du bshad pa dang mthun par gsang ba 'dus pa las 'di skad du 'byung ste /
NK073(pu)006:4807: chos thams cad ni sems la gnas so //
NK073(pu)006:4808: zhes pa snang stong gi dngos po yid kyi yul du byas pa'i chos thams cad ni /
NK073(pu)006:4809: sems su gnas shing sems su dbyer med cing sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos med do //
NK073(pu)006:4810: dper na rgya mtsho dwangs pa la nyi zla gza'
NK073(pu)006:4811: skar gzugs brnyan gyi tshogs ci ltar 'char yang tshur
NK073(pu)006:4812: gcig cing tshur mi gnyis pa bzhin pas /
NK073(pu)006:4813: sems la gnas so zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4814: 'dir ma h+aa pa bzhin rtsa lo'am spro bsdu lta bu ni ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4815: dper rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan phar ka yang chu tshur
NK073(pu)006:4816: ka'ang chu dang mtshungs pas yul du snang ba yang
NK073(pu)006:4817: / sems yul can du snang ba'ang sems rang snang
NK073(pu)006:4818: bas gzhi dang gzhi can lta bu ma yin no
NK073(pu)006:4819: / // gnas zhes bya ba'ang de las mi 'da' zhing mi 'gyur ba'i don no //
NK073(pu)006:4820: sems nam mkha' la gnas so zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:4821: sems nyid ni nam mkha' dang dbyer med par bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:4822: nam mkha' ni kha dog dang /
NK073(pu)006:4825: yod med la sogs pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral /
NK073(pu)006:4826: don des sems dang nam mkha' chos dbyings gsum ye nas dbyer med pa'i ngo bo yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:4827: dpes mtshon pas sems nyid mtha' thams cad dang bral ba /
NK073(pu)006:4828: nam mkha' lta bur gnas so zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4829: nam mkha' ci la'ang mi gnas so zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4830: 'byung ba'i nam mkha' ni yod med dang rtag chad
NK073(pu)006:4831: dang kha dog dang dbyibs la sogs pa rnam grangs
NK073(pu)006:4832: mtha' can gyi chos ci la'ang dmigs pa dang bral
NK073(pu)006:4833: bas / ched 'dzin thams cad dang bral te mi gnas so zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4834: de bas na chos thams cad ni sems las gzhan
NK073(pu)006:4835: med la sems ni mtha' dang bral bas nam mkha'
NK073(pu)006:4836: lta bu yin la nam mkha' ni bya ba thams
NK073(pu)006:4838: de ltar bu'i don nyid ye nas yin no zhes rgyud las 'byung ba dang //
NK073(pu)006:4839: yang mdo sde'i lug gis kyang bstan te //
NK073(pu)006:4840: chos thams cad ni ngo bo nyid kyi stong pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4841: zhes pa la sogs pa sems kyi chos nyid gong
NK073(pu)006:4842: du bstan pa bzhin gyi gtan tshigs kyis sems nyid
NK073(pu)006:4843: rang snang ba'i // 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:4844: ni snang tsam nyid na rang bzhin med de ngo
NK073(pu)006:4845: bo nyid kyis ma skyes pas stong pa bdag med
NK073(pu)006:4846: rang snang ba'i // pa ste / rtsa ba sems nyid nas rnam par dag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4847: chos thams cad gdod nas rnam par dag pa'o zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4848: brjod pa'i chos thams cad ni byed pa pos ma
NK073(pu)006:4849: byas bskos pa pos ma bskos par rgyu rkyen dang
NK073(pu)006:4850: bral ba'i tshul gyis gzod ma nas chos nyid snang
NK073(pu)006:4851: ba las ma gtogs pa'i gnyis 'dzin mi mnga' bas
NK073(pu)006:4852: / rnam par dag pa ste nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:4853: brjod pa'i chos thams cad ni /
NK073(pu)006:4855: ngo bo nyid kyis sems kyi chos nyid du lhun
NK073(pu)006:4856: gyis grub pa la ma rig pa ka nas dag
NK073(pu)006:4857: cing gzung 'dzin gyi sgrib g.yog mi mnga' zhing dngos
NK073(pu)006:4858: po dang bral bas thams cad la thogs pa med
NK073(pu)006:4859: par 'jug ste / 'od gsal ba nyi ma'i snying po lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:4860: brjod pa'i chos thams cad ni yul can med pas 'dzin chags kyi gnas ma grub pa'i dbang gis /
NK073(pu)006:4861: chu'i rang bzhin gsher ba dang 'dra bar rang bzhin
NK073(pu)006:4862: nam ngo bo nyid kyis gzung 'dzin dang nyon mongs
NK073(pu)006:4863: pa gtan nas dag pas mya ngan las 'das pa
NK073(pu)006:4864: ste / 'byung ba bzhi'i bem po'i mtshan nyid lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:4865: gong gi gtan tshigs stong pa dang dag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4866: mya ngan las 'das pa'i gzhi lhun gyis grub pa des na /
NK073(pu)006:4867: brjod pa'i chos thams cad ni ye 'am /
NK073(pu)006:4868: thog ma nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4869: bsgrubs nas mya ngan las 'das pa ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4870: ye nas yin pa'i don gyis gnyis can thams cad
NK073(pu)006:4871: gnyis med du ro gcig pas ma 'gags pa dang
NK073(pu)006:4872: ma dmigs pa gnyis kyis mtha' gnyis las rgyal bar
NK073(pu)006:4873: mngon zhing tshogs gnyis kyang ma bsags par gcig rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:4874: su ye rdzogs chen po'i ngo bor bzhugs pa la
NK073(pu)006:4875: / chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral bas sangs /
NK073(pu)006:4876: rig pa'i ye shes gsal la ma 'gags la med pas rgyas /
NK073(pu)006:4877: ma 'gags pa sku ma dmigs pa ye shes su
NK073(pu)006:4878: lhun gyis grub pa sangs rgyas ye rgyas chen po'i
NK073(pu)006:4880: des ni dbyer med pa'i don rgyas par bshad la /
NK073(pu)006:4881: de nyid sa gcod dang sbyar bar yang shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4882: zhes brgyad stong pa las kyang gsungs so //
NK073(pu)006:4883: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i zhabs bsdu ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:4884: 'di ni rdzogs pa chen po'i tshul lo //
NK073(pu)006:4885: zhes pa sngon du song ba dang nye bar brjod pa gnyis las /
NK073(pu)006:4886: sngon du bshad pa'i don 'di ni rang bzhin ye
NK073(pu)006:4887: nas gnas pa'i don ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:4888: pa dbyer med pas chen po'i tshul lam gnas tshul
NK073(pu)006:4889: brjod pa'o // de nyid yin tshul gtan la phab pa'i ngos nas gzhir 'gro la /
NK073(pu)006:4890: phab pas shis pa'i ngos nas lta ba ste lam
NK073(pu)006:4891: du'ang 'gro bas lam gyi gzhi lta ba zhes kyang
NK073(pu)006:4892: brjod pa'o // de nas gong du rtogs nas bsgom pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4893: zhes brjod pas rtogs pa ni gzhi lam gnyis kyi mtshams sbyor yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4894: sgom pa yang 'di'i gnas skabs su gyur pa rdzogs pa chen po zhes brjod pas /
NK073(pu)006:4895: ma h+aa pa bzhin ting nge 'dzin gsum dang cho 'phrul bzhis bskyed de /
NK073(pu)006:4896: lam mi 'dra gcig bsgoms nas de la 'bras bu snang ba lta bu ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:4897: yin tshul gyi don shes pa lta ba sems thog tu phebs te /
NK073(pu)006:4898: nam mkha' nam mkha' mi sems pa ltar lhun gyis grub pa la ni gyur pa zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:4899: de'i ngang la ma shes pa shes par bya rgyu med ste /
NK073(pu)006:4900: ma goms pa goms par bya ba tsam la bsgom zhes brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:4902: rdzogs pa chen po'i tshul ni /
NK073(pu)006:4903: rtogs pa rnam bzhi lam gyi yid ches te zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4904: rdzogs pa chen po ni gong du bstan pa nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:4905: tshul ni don la 'jug tshul te /
NK073(pu)006:4906: ngo bo la 'jug bya 'jug byed med de 'dir
NK073(pu)006:4907: gyur pa rdzogs pa chen po yin pa'i ngos nas
NK073(pu)006:4909: rtogs pa rnam bzhi zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:4910: 'dir rdzogs pa chen po la gcig char du 'jug nas /
NK073(pu)006:4911: phyi nang gi chos thams cad kun tu bzang po'i
NK073(pu)006:4912: ngo bo sku gsum thugs mi zad brgyan gyi 'khor
NK073(pu)006:4913: lor lhun gyis grub ba'i gtan tshigs te rgyas par
NK073(pu)006:4914: 'chad do // lam gyi yid ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:4915: rtogs pa skad cig ma snga ma ni 'jug tshul gyi ngos nas lam yin la /
NK073(pu)006:4916: skad cig ma phyi ma la yid ches te /
NK073(pu)006:4917: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du lhun gyis grub nas
NK073(pu)006:4918: yul yul can med de de nyid du 'dzin pa'ang
NK073(pu)006:4919: med pa ni / yid kyi g.yo ba rgyun chad de mi 'byung ba yid ches zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4920: de ni rgyas bshad kyi mgo 'dren no //
NK073(pu)006:4921: rgyas par bshad pa la tshan don dang thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4922: de la rdzogs pa chen po ni zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4923: mdor bstan du bzhir byas pa'i gzhi de las dang po'i nyid bkar nas ston te /
NK073(pu)006:4924: gzhi gnas tshul ngo bo nyid lam pa rnams kyi shes par bya ba'i don no //
NK073(pu)006:4925: rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:4926: rdzogs pa ni 'khor 'das snang srid snod bcud kyi chos thams cad mi 'gags par snang ba /
NK073(pu)006:4927: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa ni dngos po so
NK073(pu)006:4928: so'i dgos pa bya ba byed pa'i cha nas bsod
NK073(pu)006:4929: nams kyi tshogs ma bsags par lhun grub tu rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:4931: chos kyi dbyings kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' dbyings las ma g.yos pas ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK073(pu)006:4932: de gnyis kyang chu dang mar gyi dpe bzhin du dbyer med pa la tshogs zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:4933: de yang lam pa'i blos byas pa ma yin /
NK073(pu)006:4934: ye nas tshogs bsags pa'ang rgyud mi chad pa'i tshogs
NK073(pu)006:4935: kyi ngo bo nyid du bzhugs pa la tshogs kyi
NK073(pu)006:4938: tshogs gnyis ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas gcig char rdzogs pas kyang chen po'o //
NK073(pu)006:4939: 'bras bu'i che yon thams cad kyang lhun gyis grub pas kyang chen po ste /
NK073(pu)006:4940: tshogs rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu gang yin zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:4941: 'bras bu'i chos lhun gyis grub pa'i don te /
NK073(pu)006:4942: zhes pas tshogs ye rdzogs chen po'i ngang rgyu'i dus
NK073(pu)006:4943: nas 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsung thugs lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:4945: rtog tshogs zhe gnyis ma 'gags pa sku'i dkyil 'khor /
NK073(pu)006:4946: ma dmigs pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor dbyer med pa ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK073(pu)006:4947: rgyun mi chad par 'char ba yon tan gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK073(pu)006:4948: so so'i bya ba byed pa phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK073(pu)006:4949: de dag la gzung 'dzin ngang gis mi gnas pas kun tu bzang po ste 'bras bu'i chos so //
NK073(pu)006:4951: rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i tshul gyis chos kyi dbyings mi 'gags pa'i rtsal las rang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:4952: ye nas de ltar yin pa'i don ni 'bras bu'i
NK073(pu)006:4953: ngo bo ye nas gnas pa'i tshul rtogs pa'i yul
NK073(pu)006:4954: lo // tshul rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4956: zhes te 'dir rtogs pa'i tshul yang ye nas yin pa'i don la lta bas rtogs par byed /
NK073(pu)006:4957: ting nge 'dzin gyis goms par byed /
NK073(pu)006:4958: mtha' phyin pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo bas theg pa
NK073(pu)006:4959: 'og ma rnams dang mi 'dra ba'i ngos nas don
NK073(pu)006:4960: la 'jug pa'i tshul bkar nas bstan no //
NK073(pu)006:4961: 'jug pa'i tshul lam pa'i ngor rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:4963: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:4964: don la 'jug pa'i tshul gyis rdzogs pa chen po'i don mngon du bya ba yang /
NK073(pu)006:4965: rtogs pa rnam bzhis gtan la dbab dgos te /
NK073(pu)006:4966: tshig dang yi ge la rag las pas /
NK073(pu)006:4968: yi ge sgras btags ming tshogs las //
NK073(pu)006:4969: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te /
NK073(pu)006:4971: mtshon pa'i tshig kyang rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs te /
NK073(pu)006:4973: rgyud gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK073(pu)006:4974: byin gyis rlabs dang mngon sum par /
NK073(pu)006:4975: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis /
NK073(pu)006:4976: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che /
NK073(pu)006:4978: rgyu gcig par rtogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4979: zhes pa la sogs te chos thams cad don dam par rgyu gcig pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4980: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam du rgyu gcig pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4981: dbyer med par rgyu gcig pa dang gsum mo //
NK073(pu)006:4982: yig 'bru'i tshul du rtogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4984: am o +amo gsum gyis sku gsung thugs dbyer med par rtogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4985: byin gyis rlabs par rtogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:4986: zhes pa gong gi gtan tshigs gnyis kyis chos thams cad 'bras bu'i ngo bor byin gyi brlabs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:4988: de nyid rig pa la gding du gyur nas rang
NK073(pu)006:4989: rig pa'i mngon sum du lhun gyis grub par rtogs
NK073(pu)006:4991: de las zhes pa gong du dbyes pa'i gzhi de las rgyu gcig pa bkar nas ston pas /
NK073(pu)006:4992: rgyu gcig par rtogs pa ni zhes pa gang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:4993: chos thams cad ma skyes pas zhes pa la sogs pas don dam ston te /
NK073(pu)006:4994: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos rnams
NK073(pu)006:4995: skye ba med pa chos kyi dbyings bdal ba chen
NK073(pu)006:4996: po las ma g.yos pa nyid /
NK073(pu)006:4997: rig pa byang chub kyi sems mtshan nyid thams cad
NK073(pu)006:4998: dang bral bas tha snyad du don dam par zhes
NK073(pu)006:4999: brjod la / de'i ngang las rgyu rkyen rtogs ma rtogs thams cad ma grub pa la ni /
NK073(pu)006:5000: ma skyes pa'i don gyis chos kyi dbyings /
NK073(pu)006:5001: ye shes rang snang ba'i ngo bos la du ma
NK073(pu)006:5002: dang so sor mtshan nyid 'dzin pa med de cha
NK073(pu)006:5003: shas su dbye ba ma grub pas na ma yin
NK073(pu)006:5005: de yang rtogs ma rtogs gyis ma rig pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5006: ye shes gnyis su snang yang snying po byang sems
NK073(pu)006:5007: nyi ma'i snying po 'dra ba la ma rig pa
NK073(pu)006:5009: de la ltos pa'i ye shes kyang ma dmigs pas
NK073(pu)006:5010: chos kyi dbyings su 'dzin pa ngang bral ba la
NK073(pu)006:5012: 'dir du ma gcig tu byas pa'i yul byas kyi shes pa gtan nas ma grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:5013: rtogs pa ston pa'i skabs yin no //
NK073(pu)006:5015: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5016: lam pa'i ngos nas gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:5017: dag pa'i kun rdzob rgyu rang byung gi ye shes
NK073(pu)006:5018: rtogs pa rang snang ba'i sku dang ye shes ma
NK073(pu)006:5019: 'gags pa rnams ni rig pa'i ye shes mtha' thams
NK073(pu)006:5020: cad dang bral zhing cir yang mi 'gags pa'i rtsal
NK073(pu)006:5021: dang / lta ba po'i ngor 'dzin pa las snang
NK073(pu)006:5022: bas de la der 'dzin gyis gzhi ma grub cing
NK073(pu)006:5023: dang / / dngos 'dzin dang bral bas kun rdzob ste /
NK073(pu)006:5024: de tsam du sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:5025: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku rang bzhin ma grub pa de nyid mi 'gags pa'i mtshan nyid ste /
NK073(pu)006:5026: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i mtshan nyid thams cad do //
NK073(pu)006:5027: de dag ni chos kyi dbyings yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:5029: ngo bo nyid kyis ma 'gags pa ni sku /
NK073(pu)006:5030: ma dmigs pa ni ye shes /
NK073(pu)006:5031: des na khas blangs pa'i sku gsung thugs dkyil 'khor
NK073(pu)006:5032: gyi rang bzhin du de la der 'dzin mi mnga'
NK073(pu)006:5033: bas gzung 'dzin dag pa'i dbang gis mya ngan 'das
NK073(pu)006:5035: de nyid so sor bstan pa gang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:5036: chen po lnga ni yul lnga'i ngang nyid ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:5038: de'ang gong du mdor bstan gyi skabs su dang po yab bstan la /
NK073(pu)006:5039: 'dir dang po yum bstan pas dgos pa ci zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:5040: gong du ni dang po dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'am /
NK073(pu)006:5041: rtsa ba lta bur gyur pa'i don gyis dang po yab bstan la /
NK073(pu)006:5042: 'dir ni phung khams skye mched khams rnams 'byung ba
NK073(pu)006:5043: lnga la snang bas des na gzhi'i phyir dang po
NK073(pu)006:5044: yum bstan to // chen po zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5045: khyab che ste nam mkhas gar khyab du khyab /
NK073(pu)006:5046: las kyi nus pa che ste khams gsum gyi chos thams cad snang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:5047: nam mkha' khams gsum gyi go 'byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5048: sas khams gsum brtan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5049: chus khams gsum sdud pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5050: mes smin par byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5051: rlung gis g.yo zhing bskyod pas las thams cad 'grub cing chud mi za bar byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5052: lnga ni 'byung ba lnga po yum ni chos thams cad mi phyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5054: de nyid rigs kyi yum chen mo lnga yi ngang nyid ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:5055: 'byung ba nam mkha' nyid bshad pa'i don dang ldan
NK073(pu)006:5056: pa las gsal zhing go 'byed pa ni las kyis
NK073(pu)006:5058: byang chub sems las ma g.yos /
NK073(pu)006:5060: kun tu bzang mo zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5061: gzung 'dzin gyi skyon mi mnga' bas so //
NK073(pu)006:5062: yang na dbyings phyug ma zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5063: 'byung ba bzhi dang des bskyed pa'i phyi nang gi
NK073(pu)006:5064: chos thams cad snang ba'i gazhi'am rgyur gyur pas dbyings
NK073(pu)006:5065: zhes bya la / thams cad de'i ngang las dbyer med cing mi gnyis pas na /
NK073(pu)006:5066: dbang phyug ma zhes kyang bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5067: de nyid ni rdo rje'i rigs kyi yum ste /
NK073(pu)006:5068: rdo rje ni skye 'jig med pa dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba /
NK073(pu)006:5069: chos kyi dbyings shin tu dag pa'i ye 'di nas
NK073(pu)006:5070: ma dpe la chad yod snyam dpe gzhan dang bsdur
NK073(pu)006:5071: dgos zhu / ba'i bya ba byed cing 'bras bu la spyor ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:5072: ma dag pa 'khrul snang rnams kyis so so'i bya ba byed pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5073: ka bas gdung 'degs bum pas chu skyor ba la
NK073(pu)006:5074: sogs pa so so'i bya ba byed pa la sogs
NK073(pu)006:5075: te / kun rdzob kyi cha ma lus pa ni
NK073(pu)006:5076: don dam phyogs lhung dang bral ba'i mtshan nyid tsam
NK073(pu)006:5077: te / mo // bya ba byed pa de ltar
NK073(pu)006:5078: snang tsam na yang sgyu ma ngo bo nyid med
NK073(pu)006:5079: te / mo // de / ma skyes pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5080: ye shes sgyu ma dang log rtog gnyis so sor
NK073(pu)006:5081: snang tsam nyid na sgyu ma'i gtan tshigs kyis rang
NK073(pu)006:5082: rgyud du grub pa med de /
NK073(pu)006:5083: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes rdzogs pa chen
NK073(pu)006:5084: po'i ngang la dngos po'i chos gtan nas ma grub
NK073(pu)006:5085: te / ma skyes pa ni skad cig ma gcig
NK073(pu)006:5086: la lhun gyis grub pas kun rdzob dang don dam
NK073(pu)006:5088: de lta bu'i don ni bshad pa rnams kyis don
NK073(pu)006:5089: thag chod par rig pa blo gting du son na
NK073(pu)006:5090: phyogs 'dzin gyi chos ma spangs ngang gis bral te
NK073(pu)006:5091: / sgro 'dogs chod pa'i mtha' tsam la yang mi gnas nas lta ba gding du son pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5092: na zhes pas gnas skabs de lta bu na rgyu
NK073(pu)006:5093: gcig pa rnam pa gsum rtogs pa rig pa la
NK073(pu)006:5094: gding du son pa rnal 'byor pa'i spyod yul yin
NK073(pu)006:5096: des ni don gyi ngo bo bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:5097: gong ma'i don de sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5098: de yang dbyer med par ston pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5099: yig 'bru'i tshul du rtogs pa ni zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5100: gong gi don de dpes pa lta bu yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5101: yig 'bru a o +amo gsum gyis sku gsung thugs gsum mtshon te /
NK073(pu)006:5102: lam pas de nyams su blangs pas 'jug pa'i tshul
NK073(pu)006:5103: du phyi nang gi chos thams cad sku gsung thugs
NK073(pu)006:5104: dbyer med pa'i ngang du rtogs pa ni gang zhe
NK073(pu)006:5105: na / thams cad ma skyes pa ni zhes pa la sogs pa te /
NK073(pu)006:5106: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngang las ma grub te /
NK073(pu)006:5107: 'khor ba'i chos btsal yang mi rnyed /
NK073(pu)006:5108: de'i ngang las ma skyes pa zhes bya ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:5109: yang sems kyi mtshan nyid 'khor 'das kyi chos kyi
NK073(pu)006:5110: ngo bo nyid yin kyang sems nyid de dag gang
NK073(pu)006:5111: gi'ang phyogs su song ba med de /
NK073(pu)006:5112: gtan tshigs des 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kyang sems nyid las ma byung ma skyes skye ba med /
NK073(pu)006:5113: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad sems nyid
NK073(pu)006:5114: kyi ngang las ma byung ma skyes skye ba med
NK073(pu)006:5115: de / don dam par ma skyes pa ni yi ge as mtshon ste /
NK073(pu)006:5116: a ni yi ge thams cad kyi khong na gnas
NK073(pu)006:5117: pa bzhin rang rig ma skyes pas chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:5119: a yig 'bru rnams su ma 'gags par 'char bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:5120: rig pa'i ye shes ma skyes pas rtogs ma rtogs kyis 'khor 'das kyi snang ba ma 'gags pa /
NK073(pu)006:5121: as mtshon la de nyid sku gsung thugs gsum la ni gsung gi rang bzhin te /
NK073(pu)006:5122: a ngo bo ma grub pa nyid yi ge'i tshogs
NK073(pu)006:5123: su snang ba bzhin sems kyi chos nyid mtha' gang
NK073(pu)006:5124: du'ang ma grub pa nyid chos thams cad du snang
NK073(pu)006:5125: la / snang yang rang gi ngo bos stong te /
NK073(pu)006:5126: gsum ni ngo bo ma grub bzhin cir yang mi 'gags par snang la /
NK073(pu)006:5127: snang tsam nyid na gang du'ang ma grub pa sgyu
NK073(pu)006:5128: sgyus stong pa bzhin ma skyes pa nyid sgyu mar
NK073(pu)006:5129: snang zhes pa la sogs pas sku bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:5130: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes rgyu rkyen dang
NK073(pu)006:5131: bral bas ma skyes pa nyid rtogs ma rtogs kyis
NK073(pu)006:5132: ye shes dang / log rtog sgyu mar snang zhing
NK073(pu)006:5133: kun rdzob tsam du dag ma dag gi bya ba
NK073(pu)006:5134: byed nus pa'i mtshan nyid can ni /
NK073(pu)006:5135: mtshon bya ste sku yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5136: 'di nyid mtshon byed ni ye ge o ste snga ma'i a nyid gzhi bzhag la /
NK073(pu)006:5137: na ro bsnan pas or gyur /
NK073(pu)006:5138: de bzhin du rig pa'i ye shes mtshan nyid thams
NK073(pu)006:5139: cad dang bral ba nyid ma g.yos pa las sgyu
NK073(pu)006:5140: ma'i mtshan nyid rang snang ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:5141: sku gsung thugs la ni sku'i rang bzhin te /
NK073(pu)006:5142: sku mi 'gags par snang ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK073(pu)006:5144: a o yi ges mtshon pa'i chos nyid ma g.yos
NK073(pu)006:5145: pa las sku mi 'gags par snang ba gnyis tshig
NK073(pu)006:5146: la snga phyi byung yang don la dbyer med pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5147: rtogs pa'i rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nyid
NK073(pu)006:5148: / sgyu ma ni rang bzhin ma grub bzhin du
NK073(pu)006:5149: snang bas dbyer med kyi rtogs pa mtshon pa'i tshig
NK073(pu)006:5150: / ste / de lta bu'i don rtogs pa'i rig
NK073(pu)006:5151: pa phyogs zhen mi mnga' zhing gsal la 'gags pa
NK073(pu)006:5152: med pa'i rang byung gi ye shes dbus mtha' med
NK073(pu)006:5153: / ste / ces pa / dbyer med du 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:5154: pa dang bral bas ni dbus mtha' med pa dang
NK073(pu)006:5155: / ste / ces pa / / snang stong gi
NK073(pu)006:5156: 'dzin pa dang bral bas ni mtha' med pa dang
NK073(pu)006:5158: mtha' med pa ni 'dir yul dang yul can ma
NK073(pu)006:5160: / rang gi ngo bo nyid mngon du gyur pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5161: lta ba yin pa'i gtan tshigs kyis gzhal bya sgyu
NK073(pu)006:5162: ma rnam gnyis kyis gar khyab du gzhal byed kyi
NK073(pu)006:5164: / rig pa khyab / de dbyer med pa byang
NK073(pu)006:5165: chub sems bde ba chen pos ni rtsa ba'am /
NK073(pu)006:5166: snying po ni ngo bo med pas ma grub la //
NK073(pu)006:5167: mtha' 'dir thugs 'dir ma thug gi mtha' med pa ni mtshon bya don te /
NK073(pu)006:5169: o ma 'gul ba las thig le ba snan pas
NK073(pu)006:5170: +amo du gyur te ka la tsi grub na gong
NK073(pu)006:5171: ma gnyis dbyer med pas chos thams cad thugs kyi
NK073(pu)006:5173: 'o na thugs ni gsal la 'gags pa med pa
NK073(pu)006:5174: ye shes lnga yin de 'dir ji lta mtshon zhe
NK073(pu)006:5175: na / +amo yi ge cha lngas mtshon te a
NK073(pu)006:5176: skye ba med pas mtshon pa'i bden pa dbyer med
NK073(pu)006:5177: rang byung gi ye shes nyid skye ba med pa
NK073(pu)006:5178: chos kyi dbyings shin tu rnam par dag pa'i ye
NK073(pu)006:5179: na / shes / na ro gsal la mi 'gags pa me long /
NK073(pu)006:5180: zla tshes gdul bya'i yid bzhin cir yang 'char ba so sor rtog pa /
NK073(pu)006:5181: thig le mnyam nyid ji lta ba dang ji snyed
NK073(pu)006:5182: pa gnyis dbyer med pa nyid las che ba'i yon
NK073(pu)006:5184: 'a rig pa'i ye shes cir yang mi 'gags par
NK073(pu)006:5185: 'char bas bya ba byed pa'i phrin las dang ldan
NK073(pu)006:5187: de lta bu'i rang bzhin ye nas yin pa de blo la gding du byas pa la rtogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5189: byin gyis rlabs par rtogs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5191: gzhal bya'i phung khams skye mched kyi chos thams cad yi ge gsum gyis mtshon te /
NK073(pu)006:5192: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK073(pu)006:5193: rdzogs pa chen po'i ngo bor byin gyis rlabs pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5194: mthu bstan te / dper ni dper na /
NK073(pu)006:5195: ras dkar po zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:5196: ras dkar po ras rang gi rang bzhin las mi
NK073(pu)006:5197: 'gyur te ma g.yos kyang kha dog dmar por byin
NK073(pu)006:5199: gang la yod na brtsod la yod /
NK073(pu)006:5200: de tshon gzhan la med pa bzhin du /
NK073(pu)006:5201: snod bcud kyi chos rtog tshogs bzhi bcu zhe gnyis
NK073(pu)006:5202: mtha' thug pa med pa thams cad chos nyid ma
NK073(pu)006:5203: skye ba gsum du sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5204: ma 'gags pa sku ru sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5205: dbyer med pa rang rig pa'i ye shes mtha' dbus
NK073(pu)006:5206: med pa thugs su sangs rgyas par byin gyis rlabs
NK073(pu)006:5207: zhes te / thos pa'i shes rab kyi yul yang ma yin /
NK073(pu)006:5208: bsam pa'i shes rab kyi yul yang ma yin /
NK073(pu)006:5209: sgom pa'i shes rab 'ba' zhig gi yul te /
NK073(pu)006:5210: rang rig pas mngon sum du nyams su myong bar
NK073(pu)006:5211: byed nus pa'i mthu yang gang la snang na bshad
NK073(pu)006:5212: pa'i rgyu gcig par rtog pa gding du gyur pa
NK073(pu)006:5213: dang / de'i 'grub byed kyi tshul yig 'bru'i tshul du rtogs pa gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:5214: dbyer med pa'i mthus rang rig pa'i mngon sum du
NK073(pu)006:5215: ras dkar po dmar por byin gyis rlabs pa ltar
NK073(pu)006:5216: / rtogs pa gding du gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5217: mngon sum par rtogs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5218: zhes pa mngon sum bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:5220: yid kyi dang rnal 'byor gyi dang /
NK073(pu)006:5221: rang rig pa'i mngon sum las /
NK073(pu)006:5222: dbang po mngon sum snang ba yul dang yul can
NK073(pu)006:5223: rtog tshogs su snang ba'i chos rnams gzhal bya ste
NK073(pu)006:5224: bzhi'o // yid kyi mngon sum ni /
NK073(pu)006:5225: thos bsam gyi dus su lung dang man ngag gi stobs kyis /
NK073(pu)006:5226: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis stobs zhugs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5228: bsam pa'i shes rab mthar phyin /
NK073(pu)006:5229: sgom pa'i shes rab mgo gzug /
NK073(pu)006:5230: rdzogs pa chen po'i don rgyan gyi 'khor lo rig
NK073(pu)006:5231: par gcig cing rang rig tu dbyer med par rtogs
NK073(pu)006:5232: kyang zhe yi 'dzin pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5233: gsum po ni 'di nyid kyi lam lta bu la /
NK073(pu)006:5234: 'di ni rang rig pa'i mngon sum ste /
NK073(pu)006:5237: phyogs 'dzin phra ba'ang mi gnas kyang nam mkhas nam
NK073(pu)006:5238: mkha' mi gtong ba ltar du gsum du mi g.yo
NK073(pu)006:5239: ba'o / chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par gnas pa de yang zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5240: ma 'gags pa 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye 'am thog ma nas /
NK073(pu)006:5241: rdzogs pa chen po'i skabs su bshad pa ltar sku
NK073(pu)006:5242: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lhun grub kyis
NK073(pu)006:5243: ye shes chen por sangs rgyas te ye nas de
NK073(pu)006:5244: ltar yin pa'i don gnas pa de yang /
NK073(pu)006:5245: lung dang man ngag dang bral ba yang ma yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5247: lung ni ston pa tshad ma kun tu bzang pos
NK073(pu)006:5248: gsungs pas theg pa thams cad kyi spyi lung rgyud
NK073(pu)006:5249: 'di nyid do // des ni gab pa'i gsang ba 'byin no //
NK073(pu)006:5251: de nyid la bden pa tshad du phyin pa'i bla ma rnams kyis mdzad pa'i gdams ngag ste /
NK073(pu)006:5252: lta phreng gi gzhung 'di nyid lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:5253: des ni sbas pa'i gsang ba 'byin te /
NK073(pu)006:5254: bral ba yang ma yin la zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5255: lung dang man ngag dang bral na /
NK073(pu)006:5256: rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtogs mi nus te mig
NK073(pu)006:5257: med pa'am sgron ma med pa'i mi mun pa'i nang
NK073(pu)006:5258: na 'gro ba bzhin bar ma dor chud za ste
NK073(pu)006:5259: / don rtogs par mi nus pas yin zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5260: bshad ma thag pa'i snang ba gnyis dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:5261: lung dang man ngag gi tshig tsam la brten pa yang ma yin zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5262: de nyid la mi brten kha med kyang tshig gi tha snyad tsam yin gyi /
NK073(pu)006:5263: yul du byas nas don du 'dzin pa la brten pa yang ma yin par /
NK073(pu)006:5265: 'dzub mos zla ba ston kyang zla ba ma mthong
NK073(pu)006:5266: bas 'dzub mo'i rtse mo la chags pas zla ba
NK073(pu)006:5268: lung dang man ngag gi tshig dang tha snyad thams cad don mthong ba'i khrid byed yin kyang /
NK073(pu)006:5269: thos pa'i shes rab dang bsam pa'i shes rab kyi
NK073(pu)006:5270: yul so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab tsam la don
NK073(pu)006:5271: du byas nas lta ba rtogs par mno ba ni
NK073(pu)006:5272: / sags pa sngon po'i r+ts+wa dang mtshungs pas ma yin par zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5273: rang gi rig pas bla'i gteng du zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5275: gzhal bya'i yul dang gzhal ba'i gtan tshogs dang grub
NK073(pu)006:5276: mtha' thams cad rang rig pa la snang rang rig
NK073(pu)006:5277: par gcig / de'i yang phyogs zhe na thams cad
NK073(pu)006:5278: dang bral ba'i tshul gyis lhun gyis grub cing tha
NK073(pu)006:5279: snyad rnams spangs pa med par rang dag pa la
NK073(pu)006:5280: ni rig pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5281: blo ni so so skye bo'i yul yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5282: des ma reg cing mthong ba'i yul du ma gyur
NK073(pu)006:5283: pas reg cing rtogs dkar ba la ni gting tu
NK073(pu)006:5284: zhes bya ste / rdzogs pa chen po'i don bden
NK073(pu)006:5285: pa dbyer med kyi ngang la lhun gyis grub nas
NK073(pu)006:5286: yul dang yul can gyi zhe 'dod thams cad ma
NK073(pu)006:5288: snyam blo'i rgyu ba chad pa la ni mi 'gyur bas yid ches zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5289: deng sang gi gang zag blo rtsing pos thos bsam
NK073(pu)006:5290: gyi she rab kyis don spyi yid kyi yul du
NK073(pu)006:5291: byas nas / 'dzin pa rlom sems dang bcas pa ni yid ches pa zhes mi bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5292: zhe 'dod 'dzin pa spang blang gi phyogs bskyor spang blang gi blo rnams 'byung bas /
NK073(pu)006:5293: yid ma ches pa'i nang na'ang gtso bo ste /
NK073(pu)006:5294: 'khor ba la rta rnga 'gros gang gis kyang cang ma dpags la /
NK073(pu)006:5296: ci bzhin pa zhes rnam rtog de phyir rtog bsgom pa //
NK073(pu)006:5297: bde ba chen po 'dod pas chags pa'i nad yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5299: 'on kyang de nyid spang bya ma yin te dang po 'jug pa'i lam yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5300: de nyid la rlom sems dang bcas pas chags na
NK073(pu)006:5301: gong ma'i sgrib byed yin pas rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK073(pu)006:5303: de nyid spangs sems dang bcas kyang skyon che ste de'i dus su bla ma gal che'o //
NK073(pu)006:5304: don de nyid ni rang rig pa'i mngon sum du
NK073(pu)006:5305: byas pas rig pa yul dang bral bas rtogs zhes
NK073(pu)006:5306: bya'o // lam gyis yid ches pas rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5307: lam gyis yid ches pa zhes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5308: gong du bshad pa'i rtogs pa rnam bzhi nyid //
NK073(pu)006:5309: lung dang man ngag la brten pas /
NK073(pu)006:5310: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du yid ches shing don rig pa nyid de /
NK073(pu)006:5311: theg pa mchog gi lam nyams su blangs pa'i rnal
NK073(pu)006:5312: 'byor pa rnams kyis rtogs par bya ba'i thabs kyi
NK073(pu)006:5313: lam gyi ngo bo yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5314: de yang mtshan nyid pa ltar bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rgyu'i dus su bsgrubs pas /
NK073(pu)006:5315: phyis grangs med gsum na 'bras bu sku gsum gzhan nas 'byung ba'i dus sam /
NK073(pu)006:5316: bskal pa la sogs pa la ltos pa lta bu ni ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5317: 'dir ni rang gi mngon sum du rtogs shing yid ches pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5319: rten gyi ga nga zag rnal 'byor pas rang rig
NK073(pu)006:5320: pa'i shes rab kyi mngon sum du phyi nang gi
NK073(pu)006:5321: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan
NK073(pu)006:5322: gyi 'khor lor sangs rgyas par bshad pa ltar rtogs
NK073(pu)006:5323: te / yid ches gding du gyur pa thob bya
NK073(pu)006:5324: gzhan na med pa'i skad cig ma dang po ni
NK073(pu)006:5325: rtogs pa'i lta ba ste rgyu yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5326: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin la goms te rig pa
NK073(pu)006:5327: yul bral gyi ye shes skyed du bya ba med
NK073(pu)006:5328: pa nyid mngon du gyur tsam gzhi mngon du gyur
NK073(pu)006:5329: / lam mthar phyin pa 'bras bu rang snang ba la yid ches pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5331: gong 'og kun gyi sa gcod kyang dkyus bzhin du spyar bar bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5332: rtogs pa bzhi'i don lam gyis yid ches pa nyid /
NK073(pu)006:5333: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum kar bstan pas /
NK073(pu)006:5334: 'bras bu'i lam du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5335: de la mtshan nyid gsum gyi don mthar phyir par 'gyur te /
NK073(pu)006:5339: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK073(pu)006:5340: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK073(pu)006:5341: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags /
NK073(pu)006:5342: zhes pas gong du rtogs pa bzhi'i yid ches pa nyid /
NK073(pu)006:5343: 'og ma ltar rgyus 'bras bu bsgrub pa nyid 'bras
NK073(pu)006:5344: bu dus la ltos pa ma yin par bstan te
NK073(pu)006:5345: / rtogs pa'i rig pa de nyid la /
NK073(pu)006:5348: 'bras bu goms pa'i mtshan nyid rnam pa gsum gyis
NK073(pu)006:5349: lam pa rnams kyi don 'bras bu mthar phyin par
NK073(pu)006:5350: 'gyur te / rtogs pa bzhi'i tshul du rig pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5353: gong du bstan pa ltar rtogs pa bzhi'o don la
NK073(pu)006:5354: 'jug pa'i tshul du thos bsam la brten nas chos
NK073(pu)006:5355: thams cad sku gsung thugs rgyan gyi 'khor lor rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:5356: pa chen po'i ngang du rig pa thag chod ste
NK073(pu)006:5357: / yid ches pa'i skad cig ma dang po la ni shes pa'i mtshan nyid ces te /
NK073(pu)006:5358: 'og ma las dpags pa'i thun mong ma yin pa'i shes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5360: lta ba'i ngo bo ste de nyid 'di nyid kyi
NK073(pu)006:5361: lam gyi gzhi yin pas mtshan nyid do zhes bya
NK073(pu)006:5364: zhes pa phyi nang gi chos thams cad rdzogs pa
NK073(pu)006:5365: chen po'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub pa la
NK073(pu)006:5366: ni ldan pa'i zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:5367: de'i don bshad pa bzhin rtogs pa la ni dkyil 'khor gyis zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5368: lta ba rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor ba'i byed pa ston te /
NK073(pu)006:5369: 'o na 'dir lta ba'i gnas skabs su yid ches pas zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:5370: shes bya'i babs su lhun gyis grub pas yul yul
NK073(pu)006:5371: can med par thag chod pa'i ngo bo nyid la
NK073(pu)006:5373: dper na chu rnyogs ma lan gcig dwangs kyang rnyogs
NK073(pu)006:5374: ma'i nang na 'dug pa'i dbang gis rkyen dang 'phrad
NK073(pu)006:5376: 'dir rtogs pa'i skad cig la rnyogs ma dwangs pa
NK073(pu)006:5377: dang 'dra bar yul bral gyi ye shes mngon du
NK073(pu)006:5378: gyur kyang / thog ma med pa'i mu nas log rtog la goms pa'i dbang gis /
NK073(pu)006:5379: rkyen gyi rnyogs ma dang 'dra ba'i rgyu bas sgribs pas /
NK073(pu)006:5380: de mi gnas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:5381: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5382: de la yang nas yang du goms par byed pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5384: zhes pa rgyu'i mtshan nyid rtogs pa bzhis mnyam rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:5385: kyi don nyams su len pa de la yang nas
NK073(pu)006:5386: yang du goms par byed pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5388: bsgom pa'i gnas skabs na nyid mi yengs mtshan mi gnyid cing /
NK073(pu)006:5389: ci la'ang mi blta de la zhen par bya /
NK073(pu)006:5390: zhes pa'i don nyams su lon pa las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:5391: goms par byed pa zhes bya na /
NK073(pu)006:5392: bya byed la 'phags gyin 'dar 'dug byed pa //
NK073(pu)006:5394: rtogs pa sngon du song bu'i dbang gis zhen 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:5395: rdul phra rab tsam yang med pa'i ngang las gyin
NK073(pu)006:5396: 'dar mi g.yo ba gnas pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5397: de la ni g.yo thos brtan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5398: phyi nang gi drod rtags rnams sa chod mtho dman gyis 'char ba ni rgyas par shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5399: de lta bu lhun grub kyi ngang la yul yul
NK073(pu)006:5400: can med par mi g.yo ba la ni bsgom pa
NK073(pu)006:5401: zhes bya ste / ngo bo la 'og ma bzhin
NK073(pu)006:5402: zhe 'dod kyis bsgrub pa med pas kyang de nyid
NK073(pu)006:5403: nyams su blang pa la lam zhes bya bas /
NK073(pu)006:5405: goms pa las 'bras bu snang ba la rkyen zhes
NK073(pu)006:5406: gdags kyi ngo bo la rkyen du ma grub pa'o
NK073(pu)006:5407: // de ni 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa la ma rig pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5408: yun ni rten gyi gang zag gi shes rab kyi rtsal gyi dbang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:5412: shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba'i dkyil 'khor las /
NK073(pu)006:5413: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la rgyun du mi 'da' bar byed pa la ni /
NK073(pu)006:5415: goms pa'i mthu mngon du gyur pa ni 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid do zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5416: de ltar bsgoms pas goms pa stobs su gyur te 'dir /
NK073(pu)006:5417: sa lam gyi brtsi ba med kyang yid la bya
NK073(pu)006:5418: ba thams cad dang bral ba ting nge 'dzin stobs
NK073(pu)006:5419: su gyur te / shes bya'i sgrib pa dang cha
NK073(pu)006:5420: mthun pa ched 'dzin rags pa dang phra ba dang
NK073(pu)006:5421: phra ba'i phra ba rnams mi gnas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5422: ma thu ni nus pa stobs su gyur pa ste gong nas gong du snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:5424: lam gyi rtsol ba zad pa nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor mngon du gyur pa yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5425: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5426: klog yangs nam mkha' snying po la /
NK073(pu)006:5427: sprin med nyi ma 'bum gyis bdal /
NK073(pu)006:5429: lam mthar phyin pa nyid la 'bras bu zhes brjod kyi /
NK073(pu)006:5430: ngo bo la 'bras bu thob bya thob byed gtan nas med de /
NK073(pu)006:5431: de nyid la 'dir lam pa'i ngos 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5435: goms pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid mthar phyin pa nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5436: de la 'dir rtogs pa'i ngang la mtshan nyid gsum du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5437: lam gzhan ma rnams la dgos 'brel tshang bar mchis na /
NK073(pu)006:5438: 'di la tshang ngam mi tshang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:5441: mtshan nyid gsum gyis zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:5442: gong du mtshan nyid gsum de'i 'brel ba dang zhes pa shes pa'i mtshan nyid la /
NK073(pu)006:5443: dgos pa dang zhes pa 'grub pa'i mtshan nyid te /
NK073(pu)006:5444: dgos pa'i yang dgos pa zhes 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ston te mdor bsdus pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5445: de la zhes pa mtshan nyid gsum gyi gzhi de la 'brel ba bkar nas ston pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5446: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:5447: gzhal bya'i yul du gyur pa khams gsum 'khor ba rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa thams cad dang /
NK073(pu)006:5448: rnam par byang ba'i chos su btags pa sku dang
NK073(pu)006:5449: ye shes kyi rnam grangs thams cad ye'ang thog ma
NK073(pu)006:5450: nas byed pa pos ma byas bsgyur ba bos ma
