NK073(pu)006:5451: bsgyur te / gong du bstan pa ltar snang ba thams cad ni sku'i bdag nyid /
NK073(pu)006:5452: rang bzhin med pa ni gsung gi bdag nyid /
NK073(pu)006:5453: de dbyer med pa ni thugs kyi bdag nyid dam /
NK073(pu)006:5454: ngo bo nyid lhun gyis grub ste chu gsher ba'am /
NK073(pu)006:5455: gser ser ba dang mtshungs la /
NK073(pu)006:5456: rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid kyis lhun grub gyi ye shes la phyogs zhen mi mnga' bas sangs /
NK073(pu)006:5457: mtha' dbus med par khyad gdal bas rgyas /
NK073(pu)006:5460: sangs rgyas kyi don dam pa'am ngo bo nyid de
NK073(pu)006:5461: med la zad mi shes stong la thams cad 'byung
NK073(pu)006:5462: ba'i bdag nyid zad 'phel med pa nor bu rin
NK073(pu)006:5463: po che dang mtshungs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5464: nam mkha'i dbyings dang mtshungs te thams cad kyi gazhi'am ngo bo nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:5466: rtogs ma rtogs gang ltar yang gong du bstan pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5467: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK073(pu)006:5468: // byin ni dbyings kyi cha yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5469: brlabs ni snang ba'i cha ste /
NK073(pu)006:5470: ma 'gags pa thams cad ye nas 'bras bu'i ngo
NK073(pu)006:5471: bo yin te de gnyis kyang byung khams sam rtsa
NK073(pu)006:5472: lo lta bu ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5473: chu dwangs pa bzhin gzugs brnyan du snang la /
NK073(pu)006:5474: gzugs brnyan nyid chur snang bzhin zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:5475: de ni ye nas tshul yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5476: de ni chos thams cad de nyid du gcig pa
NK073(pu)006:5477: la bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa zhes kyang bya'o
NK073(pu)006:5478: // don rtogs pa ni zhes pa yin tshul gyi don te /
NK073(pu)006:5479: rtogs pa bzhi'i tshul gyis rig pa la gdeng du gyur ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:5480: shes pa'i mtshan nyid ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:5481: gong ma'i gzhi lta bu'i ngo bo mngon sum du rtogs shing yid ches pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5482: rgyu 'bras med kyang 'dir tshig gi tha snyad du shes pa'i mtshan nyid ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5483: de ni shes pa'i mtshan nyid de las 'bras bu 'byung pas de las 'byung ba dang 'brel pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5484: de lta bu shes pa'i mtshan nyid de ni 'bras
NK073(pu)006:5485: bu bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas rdzogs pa spyir
NK073(pu)006:5486: chibs kyi sa mngon du snang ba'i rgyu yin /
NK073(pu)006:5488: nyams su blang ba rang gi ngo bo ste /
NK073(pu)006:5489: de'i don ni shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba yin la de dang 'brel pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5491: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum ka'ang 'brel te /
NK073(pu)006:5492: 'brel pa gnyis ni gong du bstan la 'dir rtogs
NK073(pu)006:5493: pa bzhi'i brjod byed kyi tshig gis mtshon nas grub
NK073(pu)006:5494: mtha' rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lnga rtogs
NK073(pu)006:5495: pas brjod bya dang brjod byed du'ang 'brel /
NK073(pu)006:5496: de nyid gzhi ma shes par byed pa lta ba dang 'brel /
NK073(pu)006:5497: shes pa nyid la brten te lam goms pa snang bas lam dang 'brel /
NK073(pu)006:5498: de nyid mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i 'brel pa yin pas /
NK073(pu)006:5499: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i 'brel pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5500: des shes pa'i mtshan nyid kyis 'brel ba bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:5501: da 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid kyi dgos pa bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5504: 'dir bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin spyod pa gnyis gcig gis gcig bskyed cing /
NK073(pu)006:5505: gcig gi gsos su gcig gyur te ched byas dang bral ba'i spyod pas /
NK073(pu)006:5506: ched 'dzin dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi gsos su 'gyur la /
NK073(pu)006:5507: dgos pa de mnga' bas mdzad pa ci mdzad kyang
NK073(pu)006:5508: mthar mi 'gyur ba'i thog tu gsos su 'gyur te
NK073(pu)006:5509: / lta sgom spyod pa gsum dbyer med pa gcig char du lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5510: 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa la dgos te rgyu
NK073(pu)006:5511: rkyen 'dzom pa'i myu gu 'tsho rdzi dang bcas par
NK073(pu)006:5512: chad dang bral ba nyid 'bras bu smin pa bzhin
NK073(pu)006:5513: no // des na kun nas nyon mongs pa rgyu 'bras su bcas pa rnams dang /
NK073(pu)006:5514: rnam par byang ba'i chos ye shes rgyu 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:5515: bcas pa rnams log rtog can gyi ngo la tha
NK073(pu)006:5516: dad kyang / rtogs pa bzhis mngon du byas pas shes pa'i mtshan nyid mngon du song bas /
NK073(pu)006:5517: sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:5518: rin po che gser gling ltar spang blang gi chos
NK073(pu)006:5519: rdul phra rab tsam yang ma dmigs pa ni dgongs
NK073(pu)006:5521: dgongs pa de dag dang ldan pa'i skyes bus spyod pa ci ltar spyad na /
NK073(pu)006:5523: sman lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5525: phyi pas dang du blang bar bya ba gtsang bar
NK073(pu)006:5526: byas pa'i kan ta ka'i la sogs pa'i sman lnga
NK073(pu)006:5527: dang / phyi pas spang nang pas dang du blangs pa'i bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:5528: sogs khongs su nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:5530: dag pa dang ma dag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5531: gtsang ba dang mi gtsang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:5532: bzang ba dang ngan pa la sogs pa'i khyad par
NK073(pu)006:5533: gyi ming du btags te gnyis su snang ba thams
NK073(pu)006:5534: cad dgongs pa'i ngos nas ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5536: zhes pa ye 'ang thog ma nas byas chos dang bral te /
NK073(pu)006:5537: chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la rang
NK073(pu)006:5538: byung gi ye shes chen po bkag pa med par
NK073(pu)006:5539: sku gsung thugs lhun gyis grub pa dbyer med pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5540: lta ba lhun gyis grub pa la /
NK073(pu)006:5541: rnal 'byor pas ting nge 'dzin yang sku gsang thugs
NK073(pu)006:5542: gsum dbyer med pa'i mnyam pa chen po'i ngang las
NK073(pu)006:5543: ma g.yos shing dgongs pa dang mthun pa'i spyod pas
NK073(pu)006:5544: / bshad pa'i spyod pa rnams sems nyid mnyam pa
NK073(pu)006:5545: nyid kyi ngang du lhun gyis grub pas blang dor
NK073(pu)006:5546: med pas ci la'ang thogs pa med par spyod cing
NK073(pu)006:5547: zhe 'dod dang bral ba'i tshul gyis /
NK073(pu)006:5548: shugs 'byung du nyams su lon pa ni lta ba'ang mi 'gags pa'i spyod par shar /
NK073(pu)006:5549: spyod pa'ang ma g.yos pa lta ba'i ngang las mi
NK073(pu)006:5550: 'da' ste de dbyer med pa lta ba'ang spyod pa
NK073(pu)006:5551: / spyod pa'ang lta bar dbyer med par lhun gyis grub pa la ni /
NK073(pu)006:5552: lta spyod mgo 'byor ba ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5553: 'bras bu snang ba'i rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid 'bras
NK073(pu)006:5554: bu thob pa'i grogs byed pas rkyen zhes bla dgas
NK073(pu)006:5555: su btags so // dgongs pa'i nges tshig bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5556: lta spyod mgo 'byor pa de ni lam mthar phyin
NK073(pu)006:5557: pas bla na med pa'i spangs mkhyen lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:5558: pa'i sangs rgyas rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi sa mngon
NK073(pu)006:5559: du snang bas na 'grub pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5560: rgyu yin pa'i phyir zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5561: 'dir rgyu dang rgyu'i rgyu gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:5563: ting nge 'dzin la ni rgyu zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5564: bshad pa'i lta spyod mgo 'byor pa nyid nyams su
NK073(pu)006:5565: blang ba mthar phyin pa nyid lam yin pa'i phyir
NK073(pu)006:5566: mthar phyin pa'i don 'bras bu la dgos pas na
NK073(pu)006:5568: dgos pa'i yang dgos pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5569: zhees pa ni 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid de /
NK073(pu)006:5570: dgos pa'i lam la de la'ang dgos pa ni 'bras bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:5571: 'bras bu med pa'i lam ni btsal bas tshi chad pa'i lam ste mu stegs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5572: 'dir gzhan bya ba ldabs pa lta bur spyod kyang
NK073(pu)006:5573: gong ma ni lta spyod mgo 'byor pas nyams su
NK073(pu)006:5574: len te lam gyi skabs yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5575: 'dir ni goms pa mthar phyin te blang dor med par 'bras bu'i ngo bor bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:5576: de la kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5578: sman lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa khyad par du btags pa thams cad ces pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5579: rkyen gyi skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:5580: de dag kyang ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5581: ye'am thog ma nas ma 'dres yongs rdzogs lhun grub
NK073(pu)006:5582: tu sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor
NK073(pu)006:5583: lor sangs rgyas pa'i ngang la mnyam pa chen po'i
NK073(pu)006:5584: zhes pa / kun rdzob tu lha dang lha mor mnyam /
NK073(pu)006:5585: don dam par rig pa byang chub sems su mnyam /
NK073(pu)006:5586: phyi'i yul chen po lnga yul lngar mnyam /
NK073(pu)006:5587: nang gi sems rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar mnyam la /
NK073(pu)006:5588: de lta bu'i ngang la snang stong ngam mtha'i skyon ngang gis mi gnas pas chen po /
NK073(pu)006:5589: de nyid ni chos thams cad bdag nyid chen po'i ngang du lhun gyis grub pas kyang chen po'o //
NK073(pu)006:5591: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du blang dor med ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:5592: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs su
NK073(pu)006:5593: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:5594: pa la blang bya'i chos ma dmigs pas /
NK073(pu)006:5595: de la ltos pa'i dor bya'ang med par mngon du gyur pa'i dus su /
NK073(pu)006:5596: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyis 'khor lor lhun gyis grub ste 'bras bur lhags pa'i tshe /
NK073(pu)006:5597: de nyid dam par 'dzin pa dang bral bas tha snyad tsam du mthar phyin zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5598: de lta bu'i dus su srid gsum gyi ngo bo
NK073(pu)006:5599: spang bya'i chos khams gsum 'khor ba nyid spangs pa
NK073(pu)006:5600: med par ye nas yin pa'i don lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:5601: bas 'bras bu bla na med pa'i spangs mkhyen lhun
NK073(pu)006:5602: gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin las 'khor
NK073(pu)006:5604: mya ngan las 'das pa zhes bya ba'ang ma dmigs pas /
NK073(pu)006:5605: 'khor ba spangs pa med par rang dag pa la mya ngan las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5608: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub /
NK073(pu)006:5610: dkyil 'khor la gnas dkyil 'khor nyid ni /
NK073(pu)006:5611: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ye nas yin pa'i don dang /
NK073(pu)006:5612: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:5613: mthar phyin pa nyid lhun gyis grub pa yin pas
NK073(pu)006:5615: rgyan du dkyil 'khor ma lus thogs /
NK073(pu)006:5617: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo mngon du gyur pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5618: 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ma 'gags par snang ba ni
NK073(pu)006:5619: chos kyi sku lnga la sogs pa'i sku lnga dang
NK073(pu)006:5620: / chos skye med rig pa'i gsung la sogs te gsung lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:5621: rdo rje'i thugs la sogs te thugs lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:5622: zhing khams dang gzhal yas la sogs te yon tan lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:5623: phrin las rnam pa lnga ste nyer lnga la sogs
NK073(pu)006:5624: te gdul bya'i grangs bzhin zad pa med pa ni
NK073(pu)006:5625: yon tan gyi ngos nas rnam grangs so //
NK073(pu)006:5626: ngo bo ni rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK073(pu)006:5627: lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid chos thams cad kyi
NK073(pu)006:5628: ngo bo rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyer lnga la yang
NK073(pu)006:5629: mi phyed pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:5631: nam mkha'i ngang las 'byung ba'i cho 'phrul mi zad ste /
NK073(pu)006:5632: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid thams cad par bzhugs pa'i dpes
NK073(pu)006:5633: sku lnga lhun grub rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i
NK073(pu)006:5634: dgongs pa rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi sa lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:5635: grub pa ni gdul bya ma zad par du gdul
NK073(pu)006:5637: spyir 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa la sogs pa gsum /
NK073(pu)006:5638: don dam nges pa'i theg pa'ang bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK073(pu)006:5640: gser mig tu g.yu bcug na mi 'dra ba gnyis gcig gis gcig brjid phyungs te mdzes pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:5641: chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang
NK073(pu)006:5642: bral ba nyid kun la byams snyoms pa'i ngang las
NK073(pu)006:5643: rig pa'i ye shes gsal la 'gags pa med pa
NK073(pu)006:5644: / thams cad 'dzoms shing gcod de mi gnas pa
NK073(pu)006:5645: mdzad pas las gnyis dus gcig tu 'tshogs pa ni
NK073(pu)006:5646: / / gcig gi rgyan du gcig che bas ni
NK073(pu)006:5647: sku'i mdzad pa bsam gyi mi khyab pa thams cad
NK073(pu)006:5650: gdul byed kyi mdzad pa rgyun mi chad par 'char bas kyang 'khor lo //
NK073(pu)006:5651: de gdul bya'i rgyud la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas kyang 'khor lo //
NK073(pu)006:5652: des gdul bya'i rgyud kyi zhen pa bcod pas kyang 'khor lo ste /
NK073(pu)006:5653: mngon du gyur pa ni zhes pa las kyi bya ba zad pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5654: 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa dang dus gcig pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5655: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi
NK073(pu)006:5656: zhes pa thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du
NK073(pu)006:5657: lhun gyis grub nas rang rig mtha' dbus bral ba
NK073(pu)006:5658: nam mkha' lta bu las 'das nyams med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5659: 'bras bu'i ngo bo de ni dgos pa lam gyi
NK073(pu)006:5660: yang dgos yin pas na 'bras bu 'ang 'dogs zhes
NK073(pu)006:5661: bya'o // yang gsung sgros gcig la ma zad pa 'bras bu'i rnam grangs nyer lnga'i chos sku dang /
NK073(pu)006:5663: chos kyi dbyings shin tu rnam par dag pa'i ye shes dang gsu ni ngo bo mi zad pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5664: gzhan nyer gsum ni rnam pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5665: gdul bya ma zad bar du 'dul byed mi zad pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5666: nyer lnga po chos kyi dbyings kyi snang ba yin pas rgyan /
NK073(pu)006:5667: dus res mo med pa lhun grub tu 'char bas 'khor lo'o //
NK073(pu)006:5668: gong ltar rtogs pa bzhi mtshan nyid gsum gyis lam
NK073(pu)006:5669: mthar phyin nas 'bras bu mngon du byas pa la
NK073(pu)006:5671: bsnyen sgrub bzhis lam mthar phyiin par bzhed de /
NK073(pu)006:5673: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK073(pu)006:5674: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen pos //
NK073(pu)006:5676: de la yang spyi lam gyi bsnyen grub bzhi dang /
NK073(pu)006:5677: zag bcas zag med so so'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi bzhi dang /
NK073(pu)006:5678: ting nge 'dzin tshom re re'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i mdor bstan ni /
NK073(pu)006:5679: gsang ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi la sogs pa bstan na /
NK073(pu)006:5680: 'dir tshang ngam ma tshang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:5682: de la bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i mdor bstan no //
NK073(pu)006:5683: de la bsnyen pa dang zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5684: gong du bstan pa'i rtogs pa bzhi mtshan nyid gsum gyi tshul gyi dgos 'brel gsum 'dzom ste /
NK073(pu)006:5685: gzhan gyi glan ka bral ba dang ldan pa'i don
NK073(pu)006:5686: gyis 'bras bu mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK073(pu)006:5687: lhun gyis grub pa'i gzhi de la 'dir bsnyen sgrub
NK073(pu)006:5688: bzhi tshang ste / bsnyen pa dang zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5689: ngo bo rtogs pa med pa'i mtshan nyid kyis rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don shes pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5691: ma 'gags pa phung po lnga ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi don du gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5692: sgrub pa ni 'byung ba lnga snang la ma dmigs pa rdzogs pa chen po'i ngo bor rtogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5693: sgrub pa chen po ni de gnyis yab yum thams
NK073(pu)006:5694: cad shes rab dbyer med pa'i ngang la byang chub
NK073(pu)006:5695: sems khams dang skye mched thams cad ma 'gags pa
NK073(pu)006:5696: bral / ma dmigs pa lcam gyi tshul du snang
NK073(pu)006:5697: grags kyi chos thams cad sku gsung thugs mi zad
NK073(pu)006:5698: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo kun tu bzang po nyid
NK073(pu)006:5699: du bsgrub bya'i ngo bo'am don lhun gyis grub par
NK073(pu)006:5700: bral / 'gyur bas ste / des na rnal 'byor la brtson par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5702: gong ma lta bu'i don rtogs nas so //
NK073(pu)006:5703: des mi chog pas rnal 'byor ni ting nge 'dzin
NK073(pu)006:5704: te yin pa'i don rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa
NK073(pu)006:5705: de'i ngang las mi 'da' bar bsgoms pas /
NK073(pu)006:5706: goms pa drag dal gyis brtson par 'bad par gdams so //
NK073(pu)006:5707: rgyas par bshad pa'i bsnyen pa ni bzhir dbyer pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5708: gzhi de las bsnyen pa bkar nas bstan pa ni
NK073(pu)006:5710: gsang ba'i thig le dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK073(pu)006:5712: rang rig snying po byang chub sems thams cad mkhyen pas kyang dmigs pa'i yul du ma gyur cing /
NK073(pu)006:5713: spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba nyid
NK073(pu)006:5714: la khams dang skye mched 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pas
NK073(pu)006:5716: des na byang chub sems zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:5717: bshad pa'i rang rig pa nyid phyogs zhen gyi chos mi mnga' bas byang /
NK073(pu)006:5718: ma 'gags pa'i chos thams cad de las ma g.yos pas chub /
NK073(pu)006:5719: de nyid dbyer med pa'i rig pa byang chub sems
NK073(pu)006:5720: ni dngos por ma grub sgrib g.yog thams cad dang
NK073(pu)006:5721: bral la khyab / rang gi ngo bo mi 'gyur ba bzhis sems can te shes pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5722: rig pa de nyid du son pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5723: de ni bsnyen pa'i mdor bstan pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5724: ste zhes pa rgyas pa rab bshad pa'i mgo 'dren te /
NK073(pu)006:5725: byang chub sems shes pa'i ngo bo de yang chos thams cad ces te /
NK073(pu)006:5726: snod bcud 'khor 'das gzung yul te tha snyad gdags su rung ba thams cad sdud do //
NK073(pu)006:5727: de dag ni ye nas sangs rgyas zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5728: nam mkha' 'byed pa med par ye nas stong gsal
NK073(pu)006:5729: yin pa'i dpes ye'am thog ma nas 'khrul chos ci
NK073(pu)006:5730: ltar snang yang / byang chub sems kyi ngang las gtan nas snang ma myong ste /
NK073(pu)006:5732: lhun grub kyi ye shes chen po phyogs 'dzin dang bral bas rgyas te /
NK073(pu)006:5733: chos thams cad de'i rang bzhin du ye nas yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5734: lam gyi bsgrub cing zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5735: de lam pa rnams kyi blos zhe 'dod kyis bsgrub cing /
NK073(pu)006:5736: theg pa 'og ma pa bzhin chos de dag la
NK073(pu)006:5737: mi mthun pa dang gnyen po'i ngos nas bcos su
NK073(pu)006:5738: med de / nang pa par yang /
NK073(pu)006:5742: gnyen pos bcos pa'i thabs kyang /
NK073(pu)006:5743: 'dir gzung 'dzin zhen pa kho na bas /
NK073(pu)006:5744: de lta bu la mi gnas pa'i don mngon du byas pa ni mi rtogs pa zhes so //
NK073(pu)006:5745: des na mchog gi theg pa 'di'i skabs su dper
NK073(pu)006:5746: na byis pa yi ge bslab pa ka kha nas
NK073(pu)006:5747: gzhung rtsal rdzogs klog mthar phyin pa'i bar te /
NK073(pu)006:5748: ka kha nyid la rtsal 'byongs pa min pa ka
NK073(pu)006:5749: kha rgyur byas nas bzhag ste 'bras bu logs su
NK073(pu)006:5751: 'dir gzhi'i gnas tshul gyi don ngo bo nyid kyi
NK073(pu)006:5752: sku rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po mthar phyin pa
NK073(pu)006:5753: nyid 'bras bu thob bya'i ngo bo yin pas lam
NK073(pu)006:5754: gyi rtsol ba zad pa nyid la 'bras bu zhes
NK073(pu)006:5755: brjod do // des na kun brtags can gyi ngo
NK073(pu)006:5756: la snang ba'i gzung 'dzin nyid ma bshig ma sbyangs
NK073(pu)006:5757: brjod do // ma bcos par / thun mong ma
NK073(pu)006:5758: yin pa'i lung man ngag gnyis kyis bshad pa'i byang
NK073(pu)006:5759: chub sems yin tshul gyi don rtogs pa'i gnas skabs
NK073(pu)006:5760: na 'bras bu yul du re ba'i rtsol ba dang
NK073(pu)006:5761: brjod do // ma bcos par / bral / lam
NK073(pu)006:5762: gnyen po sgrub pa'i rtsol ba dang bral bar rig
NK073(pu)006:5764: phyogs zhen med pa ni rtogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5765: de nyid bshad pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo la bsnyen pas na bsnyen pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5766: tha ma pa la gzung 'dzin gyi zhen pa rtogs pa'i ngos la dag pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5767: ma h+aa yo ga'i gnas skabs na bsnyen pa lta ba shes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5768: nye bsnyen de'i ngang las bdag nyid lhar byas pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5769: sgrub pa yum bskyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5770: sgrub pa chen po yab yum rol nas sras lcam dral gyi dkyil 'khor la bkod pa brjod pas /
NK073(pu)006:5771: 'dir de dag gong gi mtshan nyid gsum mthar phyin
NK073(pu)006:5772: pa'i bar la ngo bo gcig kyang bsnyen sgrub bzhi
NK073(pu)006:5773: tshang bar so sor gsal bar byas pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5775: nye ba'i bsnyen pa bdag nyid lhar shes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5777: mthar phyin pa'i don mngon du snang ba las bsnyen
NK073(pu)006:5778: pa bas kyang nye bas na nye ba'i bsnyen pa
NK073(pu)006:5779: zhes bya ste / bdag nyid lhar shes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5781: don byang chub sems rang snang ba phung po lnga
NK073(pu)006:5782: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas sku gsung thugs su ngo sprod
NK073(pu)006:5783: pa ste / de yang rgyud las /
NK073(pu)006:5784: chen po rigs kyi de bzhin te /
NK073(pu)006:5786: chen po ni 'byung ba lnga las snang ba'i phung
NK073(pu)006:5787: po lnga'i nang du khams gsum gyi chos ma lus
NK073(pu)006:5788: pa thams cad 'dus pas gtso bo lta bu bas
NK073(pu)006:5790: rigs kyi de bzhin ni ma 'dres yongs rdzogs nyid rigs lnga'i sku gsung thugs su snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:5792: chos thams cad phung po lngar ma 'dus pa med pas /
NK073(pu)006:5794: lhar shes pa ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK073(pu)006:5795: skabs su bshad pa bzhin rigs lnga'i sku gsung thugs
NK073(pu)006:5796: ma zad ba rgyan gyi 'khor lo rtogs pa rig
NK073(pu)006:5797: pa la chud pa la ni shes pa zhes bya
NK073(pu)006:5800: de yang zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5801: mdor bstan du bshad pa'i don de yang /
NK073(pu)006:5802: snod bcud kyi chos thams cad ye 'am thog ma
NK073(pu)006:5803: nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin bshad pa yin pas
NK073(pu)006:5804: na / dper na chu thams cad gsher ba las
NK073(pu)006:5805: ma 'das pas gtsang po'ang gsher ba las ma 'das
NK073(pu)006:5806: na / pa bzhin / bdag nyid kyang zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5807: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nyid gsal la ma 'gags pa phung po lnga ste /
NK073(pu)006:5808: de'ang phyogs bcu'i phung po ma lus pa rnams gzug
NK073(pu)006:5809: chen bco lnga dang tshor ba drug gsum bco brgyad
NK073(pu)006:5810: la sogs pa mtshungs pas dbyer med pas kyang /
NK073(pu)006:5812: des na phung po la du ma med pas phung
NK073(pu)006:5813: po lnga 'ang ye 'am thog ma nas lha'i rang
NK073(pu)006:5814: bzhin te / gzugs kyi phung po ma 'gags ma
NK073(pu)006:5815: dmigs dbyer med pa byang chub sems su lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:5816: grub pa ni phyogs 'dzin mi mnga' bas rnam par
NK073(pu)006:5817: dag pa la lha zhes brjod de /
NK073(pu)006:5818: des na rang bzhin zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5819: tshor ba la sogs pa bzhi po la'ang des bsgre ste phyogs zhen mi mnga' ba sangs /
NK073(pu)006:5820: rig pa mtha' dbus bral bas rgyas pa yin gyi /
NK073(pu)006:5821: rnal 'byor pas da lta kho nar lam gyi zhe 'dod kyi bsgrubs pa ma yin par rtogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5822: des ni gong ma las lam pa'i blos nyams su
NK073(pu)006:5823: len pa shas che bas mthar phyin pa la nye
NK073(pu)006:5824: bas nye ba'i bsnyen pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5825: sgrub pa ni yum bskyed pa ste zhes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5826: 'dir yang yab dang yum du 'dzom yul dang yul
NK073(pu)006:5827: can du 'dzom pas gcig yod na gcig med mi
NK073(pu)006:5828: srid pa dang / phung po lnga gong ltar rtogs
NK073(pu)006:5829: pas des bskyed par byed pa'i 'byung ba lnga yum
NK073(pu)006:5830: lngar mi rtogs mi srid ste /
NK073(pu)006:5831: dus gcig rtogs kyang so sor gsal ba'i dbye ba'i
NK073(pu)006:5832: ngos nas bstan pa'i phyir yang sgrub pa zhes bya
NK073(pu)006:5833: ba dang / yang sgrub pa chen po 'bras bu'i
NK073(pu)006:5834: ngo bo mthar phyin pa nyid bsnyen pa dang sgrub
NK073(pu)006:5835: pa gnyis 'dzom pa la snang gi /
NK073(pu)006:5836: ya bral la mi snang bas sgrub pa chen po la nye bas sgrub pa zhes bya /
NK073(pu)006:5837: yum ces pa 'byung ba lnga ni 'khrul snang la yang yum ste /
NK073(pu)006:5841: chu sdud cing brtas par byed pa'i yum /
NK073(pu)006:5842: rlung gis g.yo ste bar ma dor chud mi za ste mi rul ba'i yum /
NK073(pu)006:5844: yum bzhi nam mkha' la snang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:5845: lnga po nyid ma 'gags pa sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo //
NK073(pu)006:5846: ma dmigs pa dang dbyer med pa ni gsung dang thugs rgyan gyi 'khor lo ste /
NK073(pu)006:5847: de lta bu rig pa'i ngang las snang zhing mi
NK073(pu)006:5848: 'gags pa rig pa las ma g.yos shing phyogs su
NK073(pu)006:5849: zhen pa med pa'i dgongs pa rtogs pa nas /
NK073(pu)006:5850: mthar thug pa'i bar du bsgom pa'i stobs kyis 'phar ba la bskyed pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5854: 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum //
NK073(pu)006:5856: 'byung ba lnga ma 'dres yongs rdzogs nyid thams cad bskyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:5857: thams cad dang mi phyed pa'i don gyis thabs shes rab nyid las shes rab /
NK073(pu)006:5858: yab yum gnyis las yum ste /
NK073(pu)006:5859: las dang ngo bo gnyis kyis so //
NK073(pu)006:5861: 'khor 'das dbyer med byang chub sems bde ba chen
NK073(pu)006:5862: po bsnyen pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i ngo bo nyid
NK073(pu)006:5863: ni / tha snyad kyi mtshan nyid thams cad dang
NK073(pu)006:5864: bral te mtha' thams cad kyis stong pas kyang yum
NK073(pu)006:5865: ni / / mtshan nyid med pa nyid mtshan nyid thams cad pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pas kyang yum /
NK073(pu)006:5866: de'i dbang gis ma rtogs 'khor ba'i chos su snang la /
NK073(pu)006:5867: rtog pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos su snang ste 'khor 'dus su snang bas kyang yum /
NK073(pu)006:5868: 'khor 'das dang snod bcud dang yod med dang gnyis
NK073(pu)006:5869: su snang ba thams cad de'i ngang las gnyis su
NK073(pu)006:5870: med pas ni / chen mo'i nam mkha'i zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5871: stong la gsal mtha' thams cad dang bral /
NK073(pu)006:5872: mtha' dbus med ris su mi 'dzin pas na nam mkha' la /
NK073(pu)006:5874: chos thams cad kyi gazhi'am rtsa ba lta bu med
NK073(pu)006:5875: la zad mi shes stong la thams cad 'byung ba'i
NK073(pu)006:5877: ma zhes pa thams cad des bskyed pa'i ngang las nam mkha' nyid ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:5878: 'byung ba'i nam mkha'i mtshan nyid ni stong gsal go 'byed pa nyid du snang la /
NK073(pu)006:5880: 'go ma'i mgo 'dren gong ma'i zhabs sdud de /
NK073(pu)006:5881: zhabs sdud na nam mkha'i nyid 'byung ba dang 'byung
NK073(pu)006:5882: ba las gyur pa'i chos thams cad skye zhing snang
NK073(pu)006:5883: bar byed pas na yum chen mo //
NK073(pu)006:5884: mgo 'dren na nam mkha'i nyid mi 'gags pa'i ngang las yum chen mo bzhir snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:5886: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung bzhir snang zhing ci byed na bya ba byed de /
NK073(pu)006:5887: sas brtan pa'i bya ba byed /
NK073(pu)006:5890: rlung gis g.yo zhing bskyod pa'i bya ba byed pa'i yum zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:5891: bya ba bzhi po byed pa'i ngang las chos thams cad bskyed pas na yum /
NK073(pu)006:5892: snang ba'i chos thams cad mi phyed pas na yum de yang ye nas yin zhes pas /
NK073(pu)006:5893: kun brtags kyi ngo la 'khrul snang las kyi bya bar brtags kyang /
NK073(pu)006:5894: ngo bo nyid las rang bzhin gyis bde bar gshegs
NK073(pu)006:5895: pa'i yum lnga'i ngang nyid de ma 'gags pa'i ngos
NK073(pu)006:5896: nas 'byung ba lnga'i mdzad pa la thog ma dang
NK073(pu)006:5897: tha ma med / ngar 'dzin dang rlom sems med /
NK073(pu)006:5898: skyo ba dang dub pa med cing snga phyi rgyun
NK073(pu)006:5899: chad pa med pas ngo bo nyid kyi mdzad pa
NK073(pu)006:5900: chen po'o // de yang ma 'gags par snang ba ni sku /
NK073(pu)006:5901: rang bzhin med pa ni gsung /
NK073(pu)006:5902: dbyer med pa ni thugs te /
NK073(pu)006:5903: yum gyi sku gsung thugs ye nas yin par rtogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5904: 'khrul ba bdag gis 'byung ba lnga ni bem po yin la /
NK073(pu)006:5905: sems can gyi las kyi snang ba ste 'khrul pa'i spyod yul lo ce na /
NK073(pu)006:5906: rig pa yul can med pa'i 'byung ba yul yod
NK073(pu)006:5907: pa med ste ma rtogs pa'i dus su yang thams
NK073(pu)006:5908: cad yid kyi shes pa 'ba' zhig tu 'dus pa
NK073(pu)006:5909: yid mi dmigs pa'i shes rab /
NK073(pu)006:5910: rang byung gi ye shes su lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK073(pu)006:5911: gzhal bya thams cad rang byung ye shes spro bsdu
NK073(pu)006:5912: dang bral ba'i tshul gyis rang snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:5913: gzhal bya gzhal byed med pa'i dus su lta ba shes pa rtogs pa'i mgo zug pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:5914: des na dngos po gcig la mthong snang tha dad ste 'phrul chos bem por snang bas dang /
NK073(pu)006:5915: ye shes yul bral gyi snang ba gnyis dngos po'i
NK073(pu)006:5916: chos gcig la skad cig ma gcig la mtshung par
NK073(pu)006:5917: ldan no // des na yul lnga'i dkyis 'khor du
NK073(pu)006:5918: lhun gyis grub pa ni sgrub pa chen po la
NK073(pu)006:5919: kha thag nye bas sgrub pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:5921: 'bras bu'i ngo bo yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis /
NK073(pu)006:5922: snod bcud kyi chos rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK073(pu)006:5923: rnams rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sku gsung
NK073(pu)006:5924: thugs kyi 'khor lor sangs rgyas pa 'bras bu'i ngo
NK073(pu)006:5925: bo bas chen po zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5927: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs /
NK073(pu)006:5928: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams /
NK073(pu)006:5929: zhes bshad pa'i nye bsnyen dang /
NK073(pu)006:5930: sgrub pa gnyis yab yum du 'byor ba'i rtsal las /
NK073(pu)006:5931: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:5932: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams /
NK073(pu)006:5934: khams dang skye mched lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor
NK073(pu)006:5935: nyid de mngon du gyur pas de bshad pa ni
NK073(pu)006:5936: / thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:5938: phung po lnga thabs kyi ngo bo dang /
NK073(pu)006:5939: 'byung ba lnga shes rab kyi ngo bo dang /
NK073(pu)006:5940: yang rags par snang ba thabs dang /
NK073(pu)006:5941: rang bzhin med pa shes rab gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:5942: gang ltar na 'ang dung dang dkar ba'am /
NK073(pu)006:5943: chu dang gsher ba bzhin mgo mnyam du grub la
NK073(pu)006:5944: 'brel po ni de dag dang dus mtshungs par khams
NK073(pu)006:5945: dang skye mched lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du
NK073(pu)006:5947: phyi nang gi chos thams cad kun tu bzang po
NK073(pu)006:5948: dbye ba med pa'i sa mngon du gyur pa ni
NK073(pu)006:5949: sgrub pa chen po 'bras bu'i ngo bo ste mado'o
NK073(pu)006:5950: // rgyas pa la dang por kun gyi gzhi yum bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5951: de yang zhes pa bstan pa'i sgrub pa chen po
NK073(pu)006:5952: de yang chos dbyings kyi yum chen mo stong la
NK073(pu)006:5953: thams cad 'byung ba'i ngang las lnga yi zhes pa
NK073(pu)006:5954: / nam mkha' la sogs pa'i 'byung ba lnga sgrub
NK073(pu)006:5955: par bshad pa bzhin gyi don thabs dang shes rab
NK073(pu)006:5957: yang 'byung ba chen po lnga ma 'gags bar snang yang /
NK073(pu)006:5958: spyi yum chos dbyings kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing
NK073(pu)006:5959: de las bya ba byed pa dang bcas pa'i yum
NK073(pu)006:5960: chen mo lnga / rang bzhin med pa rnam par dag pa'i shes rab dang zhes te /
NK073(pu)006:5961: thabs shes rab gnyis las shes rab bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:5962: de nyid rnam thar sgo gsum las stong pa nyid du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:5963: yum gyi mkha' stong pa nyid las /
NK073(pu)006:5965: spyi yum chos kyi dbyings gsal zhing go 'byed pas
NK073(pu)006:5966: mkha' dang de nyid dngos po'i chos ma grub pas
NK073(pu)006:5967: stongs / de'i ngang las snang ba'i yum nam mkha'
NK073(pu)006:5968: dbyings phyug ma 'byung ba bzhi gsal zhing go 'byed
NK073(pu)006:5969: stongs / pas mkha' / dngos po'i chos kyi stong pas stong pa nyid /
NK073(pu)006:5970: de las snang ba'i 'byung ba bzhi snod bcud kyi chos thams cad bskyed pas yum /
NK073(pu)006:5971: phung po la sogs pa gsal zhing go 'byed pas mkha' /
NK073(pu)006:5972: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi ngang las snang
NK073(pu)006:5973: stong gi ltos pa'i chos kyi dngos pos dben pas
NK073(pu)006:5974: / rnam thar stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK073(pu)006:5975: yab dang smon pa med pa mtshon pa ni phung po lnga'i zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:5976: 'byung ba las snod ba'i gzugs kyi phung po la
NK073(pu)006:5977: sogs ba lnga ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi mthar gnyis
NK073(pu)006:5979: lhun grub kyi ye shes kyis mtha' dbus med par
NK073(pu)006:5980: rgyas pa nyid rgyud kyi lung gis bshad pa yin
NK073(pu)006:5981: pas / de nyid ni thabs shes rab gnyis las /
NK073(pu)006:5982: thabs te 'byung ba lnga nyid ma 'gags par snang ba'i sgo nas so //
NK073(pu)006:5983: yab yum gnyis las yab ste /
NK073(pu)006:5984: 'byung ba dang dbyer med pa ste 'byung ba las
NK073(pu)006:5985: spyod par bya ba'i ngo bo nyid du bzhugs pa
NK073(pu)006:5986: dang / 'byung ba nyid de'i rang bzhin yin pas mi phyed pa'i don gyis so //
NK073(pu)006:5987: smon pa med par zhes pa de ltar phung po
NK073(pu)006:5988: dang 'byung ba dbyer med kyang dus mtshungs par grub
NK073(pu)006:5989: pas yul dang yul can med pas smon pa med
NK073(pu)006:5990: pa dang / 'byung ba dang phung po dbyer med
NK073(pu)006:5991: pa nyid ma 'gags ma byung dbyer med pa nyid
NK073(pu)006:5992: byang chub sems su dbyer med pa la bdag nyid
NK073(pu)006:5993: chen po'i don gyi yul chos ma grub pas smon
NK073(pu)006:5995: des ni thams cad bdag nyid la lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:5996: pas 'bras bu longs su mi re bas smon pa
NK073(pu)006:5998: don de yang lam blos byas pa ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:5999: ye 'am thog ma nas phung po dang 'byung ba
NK073(pu)006:6000: thabs shes rab yab dang yum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:6001: su zung du 'brel par ye bzhugs chen po yin
NK073(pu)006:6003: 'dir gzhi dang gzhi can smos kyang brjod pa'i ngos nas yin gyi /
NK073(pu)006:6004: ngo bo la ni skad cig ma snga phyi dang
NK073(pu)006:6005: bral bas dus mtshungs te 'gro 'ong dang bral bas
NK073(pu)006:6007: des na sgrub pa chen po'i gzhi stong pa nyid smos pa med pa dang gnyis bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:6008: sgrub pa chen po rang gi ngo bo mtshan ma med pa'i don mthar phyin pa bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:6009: de yang sgrub pa chen po'i don gyi ngo bo ni /
NK073(pu)006:6010: byang chub kyi sems sprul pa lcam dral /
NK073(pu)006:6012: 'dir yang ma h+aa bas thabs shes rab bsrub pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6013: kun rdzob byang chub sems las sras lcam dral 'phro
NK073(pu)006:6015: 'dir byang chub sems ni bshad pa ltar phung po
NK073(pu)006:6016: dang 'byung ba dbyer med pa nyid rig pa byang
NK073(pu)006:6017: chub sems las ma g.yos bzhin ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:6018: kyi don la phyogs 'dzin mi mnga' bas byang /
NK073(pu)006:6019: ma 'dres pa'i chos thams cad de nyid du lhun gyis grub pas chub /
NK073(pu)006:6020: de dbyer med pa rig pa rang byung gi ye
NK073(pu)006:6021: shes byang chub sems bdal ba chen po zhes bya
NK073(pu)006:6022: ste / phung po dang 'byung ba dbyer med pa
NK073(pu)006:6023: nyid ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med phyogs zhen gyi
NK073(pu)006:6024: mtshan ma phra ba'i phra ba'ang mi mnga' ba la
NK073(pu)006:6025: ste / brjod do // des na rgyud kyi tshig gi bshad pa nyid kyang de'o //
NK073(pu)006:6027: med bzhin du mi 'gags par 'char zhing de nyid gang du'ang ma grub pa med pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6028: phung po dang 'byung ba byang chub sems su dbyer
NK073(pu)006:6029: med pa'i rtsal las snang ba'i rnam shes bzhi dang
NK073(pu)006:6035: snang la ma grub chos kyi dbyings su lhun gyis grub pa sprul pa lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:6036: lcam dral ni de nyid la snang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6037: slar dgos pa skor ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:6038: de yang dang po dgos pa skong ba bshad na /
NK073(pu)006:6039: sprul pa'i tshogs rnam shes bzhi ni yab /
NK073(pu)006:6040: yul bzhi ni yum la sogs pa bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:6041: de'i ngos nas mi phyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6043: mnyes pa phul ba'i don gyis yab yum zhes kyang bya /
NK073(pu)006:6044: 'dir phung po 'byung ba byang chub sems su lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang las snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:6045: chu'i kha dog thams cad chu las ma g.yos pa dang mtshungs /
NK073(pu)006:6046: las kyi sgo nas yab yum du snang yang byang
NK073(pu)006:6047: chub sems su lhun grub kyi ngang la gcig char
NK073(pu)006:6048: du shar bas lcam dral zhes smos so //
NK073(pu)006:6050: thabs shes rab dbyer med pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK073(pu)006:6052: ma h+aa yo ga ba ltar dngos por 'dzin bcas kyi sbyor ba lta bu ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:6053: nam mkha' ltar ye nas de'i rang bzhin pas /
NK073(pu)006:6055: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK073(pu)006:6056: bdag nyid chen po'i lhag pa yi thugs kyi ye shes lnga lta zhing /
NK073(pu)006:6058: bshad ma thag pa'i don ni /
NK073(pu)006:6059: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6060: ma 'gags pa dang ma dmigs pa dang dbyer med pa gsum /
NK073(pu)006:6061: sku gsung thugs kun tu bzang po'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:6062: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab des khyab pas dkyil 'khor la /
NK073(pu)006:6063: bdag nyid chen po ni thams cad de nyid la du ma dang cha shas med pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6065: de nyid mtshon pa'i ngos nas ye shes lngar yang lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:6066: sku gsung thugs dbyer med pa'i don nyid mtshan ma'i
NK073(pu)006:6067: 'dzin pa thams cad dang bral ba chos dbyings ye
NK073(pu)006:6068: shes / gsal la 'gags pa med pa me long ye shes /
NK073(pu)006:6069: phung khams skye mched cir yang snang ba so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK073(pu)006:6070: chos dbyings ye shes las ma g.yos pa mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK073(pu)006:6071: mi 'gags pa'i mdzad pa thams cad kyis bya ba
NK073(pu)006:6072: byed pa dang ngo bo chos dbyings las ma g.yos
NK073(pu)006:6074: de lta bu de yang lam gyis bcos pa ma
NK073(pu)006:6075: yin ye nas dngos po'i mtha' la mi gnas pas
NK073(pu)006:6076: sangs / rig pa phyogs lhung dang bral ba'i don
NK073(pu)006:6077: lhun gyis grub pas rgyas pa'i don la mthong ba
NK073(pu)006:6078: med pa'i tshul gyis rtogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6079: don de lta bu lam pa'i blo la myong tshul ni /
NK073(pu)006:6080: sgyu ma las sgyu ma rol cing zhes /
NK073(pu)006:6082: snying po'i thig le mnyam sbyor bas //
NK073(pu)006:6084: snying po dang thig le gnyis phung po dang 'byung ba'am /
NK073(pu)006:6088: de dag ci ltar snang yang ma 'gags ma dmigs
NK073(pu)006:6089: dbyer med pas byang cub sems su lhun gyis grub
NK073(pu)006:6090: par ston te / sgyu ma la zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6091: snang yang ngo bo ma grub pas zhen pa med pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:6092: tha snyad kyi dbang du bshad pa'i yul gyi chos
NK073(pu)006:6093: rnams chos kyi dbyings mi 'gag pa'i rtsal las snang
NK073(pu)006:6094: / so so'i bya ba byed 'dod na'ang ngo bo
NK073(pu)006:6095: la grub pa ma mchis te chos kyi dbyings su
NK073(pu)006:6096: lhun gyis grub pas yul lam /
NK073(pu)006:6097: chos nyid sgyu ma lta bu la dbang po 'am
NK073(pu)006:6098: ye shes sgyu ma lta bur rol cing ma 'gags
NK073(pu)006:6099: ma dmigs dbyer med pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK073(pu)006:6102: lam pa'i dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'i ngo bo ste /
NK073(pu)006:6104: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo yis //
NK073(pu)006:6105: ye shes dgyes la mchod pa 'bul /
NK073(pu)006:6106: zhes pa ma 'gags ma dmigs dbyer med pa phyogs
NK073(pu)006:6107: zhen thams cad dang bral ba'i bde ba'i ye shes
NK073(pu)006:6108: cir yang 'char ba rol mo lta bu'i dgongs pa
NK073(pu)006:6110: gnyis 'dzin gyi zhan pa rdul phra rab tsam yang
NK073(pu)006:6111: mi mnga' bas ye shes dgyes pa zhes bya ste
NK073(pu)006:6112: / de nyid bul ba med par mnyes pa'i mchog yin pa la ni bde mchog ces te /
NK073(pu)006:6113: ma 'gags pa ni ma 'dres pa'i bde ba la /
NK073(pu)006:6114: ma dmigs pa ni yongs su rdzogs pa'i bde ba /
NK073(pu)006:6115: de ni longs spyod gnyis te ma bkag pas bde zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:6116: de nyid rang rig byang chub sems su gcig cing 'dzin pa thams cad dang bral bas mchog go //
NK073(pu)006:6118: 'khrul ba log rtog sgyu ma'i chos thams cad ma
NK073(pu)006:6119: bsgyur ma bcos bar snang stong dbyer med pa ye
NK073(pu)006:6120: shes sgyu ma'i rgyun la lhun gyis grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:6121: skad cig ma gcig dang ngo bo nyid kyi rgyun nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:6122: bde ba'i dus nyid na zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6124: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyis /
NK073(pu)006:6126: zag pa'i rgyud gzung 'dzin rang byung gi ye shes su dag pas de ma 'gags par snang bas /
NK073(pu)006:6127: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyun yang ma 'gags pa ni bsod nams kyi tshogs /
NK073(pu)006:6128: mi 'dzin pa ni ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK073(pu)006:6130: tshogs gnyis kyis 'khor 'das kyi bde ba gnyis dbyer
NK073(pu)006:6131: med par bdag nyid chen po'i ngang la gcig tu
NK073(pu)006:6132: lhun gyis grub pa'i gding las mi 'da' ba'i dus
NK073(pu)006:6133: de nyid kyi gnas skabs na /
NK073(pu)006:6134: rnam par thar pa'i sgo mtshan ma med pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6135: sgyu ma la sgyu ma rol cing bde mchog sgyu ma'i rgyun la gnas pa'i tshe skabs na /
NK073(pu)006:6136: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par dngos po'i mtshan
NK073(pu)006:6137: mas ma gos mi 'gags pas stong pa'i mtshan mas
NK073(pu)006:6138: ma gos la / de dbyer med pas mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6141: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang ba //
NK073(pu)006:6142: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor bsam yas mchog /
NK073(pu)006:6143: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NK073(pu)006:6144: de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK073(pu)006:6146: rang byung gi ye shes snang bzhin ma grub par rang snang ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:6149: de nyid dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub cing de la der 'dzin dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:6152: sems nyid gsang ba'i ngo bo spros pa dang bral
NK073(pu)006:6153: ba'i thig le mi 'gags pa'i rtsal dang ldan pas
NK073(pu)006:6154: dbyings te / de ni phyogs dus kyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dngos gzhir brjod pas /
NK073(pu)006:6155: 'dir mtshan ma med pa'i don mthar phyin pa'i ngang la mi dmigs zhes smos pas /
NK073(pu)006:6156: bshad pa'i snang stong gi mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i ngo bo nyid la /
NK073(pu)006:6157: rtogs pa'i don gyi yul yul can /
NK073(pu)006:6158: snang ba stong pa gnyis can gyi dngos po gang
NK073(pu)006:6159: yang ma grub pa'i dbang gis dmigs pa thams cad
NK073(pu)006:6160: dang bral ba la mi dmigs pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:6161: ched du mi dmigs pa la ni 'dir mi brjod do //
NK073(pu)006:6162: nam mkha' ni dngos gzhi dang bral yang gsal zhing gos byed la /
NK073(pu)006:6163: dus gsum du mi 'gyur yang ngar 'dzin rtsa ba nas zad do //
NK073(pu)006:6164: dpe de ltar rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i rig pa
NK073(pu)006:6165: phyogs zhen dang bral ba nyid gsal ba ni mthas
NK073(pu)006:6166: ma sgrib pa'o // go 'byed pa ni cir yang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6167: phyogs zhen bral ba nyid kyi ngang dus gsum du
NK073(pu)006:6168: mi 'gyur zhing der 'dzin bral ba la ni snyoms
NK073(pu)006:6170: de yang yul gcig la yul can gcig gis dmigs
NK073(pu)006:6171: nas snyoms pa lta bu la ni mi bya ste
NK073(pu)006:6172: / rtogs pa mthar phyin lam bskyed du bya rgyu
NK073(pu)006:6173: med rdzogs pa chen po'i don mngon du gyur nas
NK073(pu)006:6174: lhun grub kyi rig pa spros pa'i mtha' dbus dang
NK073(pu)006:6175: phyogs kyi mtha' dbus rnams dag ste /
NK073(pu)006:6176: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab lhun grub tu gyur nas deng 'dzin dang bral te /
NK073(pu)006:6177: sa bcu pa'i shes bya'i sgrib pa phra ba'i phra
NK073(pu)006:6178: ba ltar zhe 'dod phra ba'ang mi gnas pa la
NK073(pu)006:6179: ni don dam par ngo bo nyid kyis btang snyoms
NK073(pu)006:6180: chen po'o // des na dkyus kyi sgyu ma nas gzung ste /
NK073(pu)006:6181: 'di'i bar ni sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin dbang po
NK073(pu)006:6182: rno brtul dang brtson 'grus drag na skyed du bya
NK073(pu)006:6183: ba myur bral gyi bye brag ste /
NK073(pu)006:6184: de rnams sgrub pa chen po'i dngos grub len pa'i thabs lta bu yin la /
NK073(pu)006:6185: snyoms pa ni dngos grub mngon du byas pa lta bu kho na'o //
NK073(pu)006:6186: des na sgrub pa chen po 'bras bu mngon du byas ba'i don ni /
NK073(pu)006:6188: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa ni //
NK073(pu)006:6189: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK073(pu)006:6190: ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong ba //
NK073(pu)006:6191: dbang bsgyur mchog nyid dam pa yin //
NK073(pu)006:6193: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK073(pu)006:6194: rgyan du dkyil 'khor ma lus thogs //
NK073(pu)006:6196: ngo bo nyid kyi snyoms pa chen po la /
NK073(pu)006:6199: chu klu chen po 'brub pa'i dus su chu'i 'gal
NK073(pu)006:6200: rkyen thams cad chu'i dpung du gyur la gzhan gang
NK073(pu)006:6201: gis kyang bar bcad du med pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:6202: 'dir rang byung gi ye shes phyogs ltung dang bral
NK073(pu)006:6203: ba zher 'dzin med pa stobs su zhugs pa'i tshe
NK073(pu)006:6204: / gzung 'dzin zhen pa'i chos nyid byang chub sems
NK073(pu)006:6205: su rtogs pa thams cad rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang
NK073(pu)006:6206: las ma gtogs pa gang yang mi rnyed ste gser
NK073(pu)006:6208: lhun gyis grub ste khams gsum gyi chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:6209: rang snang gi kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs
NK073(pu)006:6210: gsum du lhun gyis grub ste bdag zhal bdag gis
NK073(pu)006:6211: mthong ba la yul dang yul can med pa'i dbang
NK073(pu)006:6212: gis rang snang du gsal lo //
NK073(pu)006:6213: de'ang phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i chos thams cad dbang
NK073(pu)006:6214: po'i mngon sum nyid rang rig pa'i mngon sum du
NK073(pu)006:6216: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyis tshogs gnyis gcig char rdzogs pa ma 'gags pa sku /
NK073(pu)006:6219: rtogs pa med par snang ba yon tan /
NK073(pu)006:6220: bya ba byed pa'i cha thams cad phrin las te /
NK073(pu)006:6221: chos thams cad rang snang gi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK073(pu)006:6222: bdag nyid du lhun gyis grub pa ni bdag zhal
NK073(pu)006:6224: 'khor 'das dbyer med rig pa la rang dbang bsgyur
NK073(pu)006:6225: ba nyid phyogs zhen thams cad dang bral bas mchog
NK073(pu)006:6227: bsnyen pa ye nas gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK073(pu)006:6228: nye bsnyen dang sgrub pa nyams su blang ba'i dkyil
NK073(pu)006:6229: 'khor nyid kyis sgrub pa chen po rang bzhin lhun
NK073(pu)006:6230: gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor phyi nang gi chos thams
NK073(pu)006:6231: cad rtogs pa lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du
NK073(pu)006:6232: rdzogs pas lhun gyis grub ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6233: rgyan du dkyil 'khor ma lus thogs zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6234: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams
NK073(pu)006:6235: cad rtogs pa lhun gyis grub pas thams cad ma
NK073(pu)006:6236: 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par rang snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:6237: gzung 'dzin 'khor ba'i chos rdul phra rab tsam yang mi snang ba ni nam mkha'i dbyings bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:6238: 'o na 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i dus su
NK073(pu)006:6239: 'og ma rnams la ni bdud bzhi btul ba yin
NK073(pu)006:6240: na / de tshang ngam mi tshang zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:6241: tshang par bstan pas bdud bzhi yang btul /
NK073(pu)006:6244: phung po dang nyon mongs pa'i bdud dang /
NK073(pu)006:6245: 'chi bdag dang lha'i bu'i bdud las /
NK073(pu)006:6246: nye ba'i bsnyen pa'i skabs su bdag nyid ltar shes
NK073(pu)006:6247: pa phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su rtogs
NK073(pu)006:6248: pa nyid mthar phyin pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:6249: sgyu ma la sgyu ma rol /
NK073(pu)006:6250: zhes pa la sogs pas thams cad bdag nyid chen
NK073(pu)006:6251: po'i ngang du lhun gyis grub te yul yul can
NK073(pu)006:6252: med de gzung 'dzin ka nas dag pas nyon mongs
NK073(pu)006:6253: pa'i bdud bcom / sgyu ma'i rgyud la bde ba'i dus nyid na /
NK073(pu)006:6255: rig pa'i ye shes skad cig ma'i rgyun las grol
NK073(pu)006:6256: te ngo bo nyid kyi rgyun la skye 'gags ma
NK073(pu)006:6257: dmigs pas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK073(pu)006:6258: yab yum thabs shes rab ye nas zung du 'brel /
NK073(pu)006:6260: gnyis can gyi chos ma dmigs te yul yul can dang bral bas /
NK073(pu)006:6261: gnyen po med pas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom mo //
NK073(pu)006:6262: des na rtogs pa'i dus nas kyang bdud bcom pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6263: mgo zug 'bras bu mthar phyin pa dang bdud bcom
NK073(pu)006:6265: mtha' phyin pa'i don grub bo //
NK073(pu)006:6267: lam gyi bya ba zad ngo bo nyid kyi sku mngon du gyur /
NK073(pu)006:6268: rang snang kun tu bzang po lhun gyis grub pa ni don zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6269: bsgrub bya'i ngo bo sgrub pa chen po mngon du snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6270: 'o na bshad pa'i don gyis 'khrul pa rdul phra
NK073(pu)006:6271: rab tsam yang ma dmigs pa thams cad dkyil 'khor
NK073(pu)006:6272: 'ba' zhig tu lhun gyis grub pas thugs rje 'gags
NK073(pu)006:6279: bdud gcig btul bas thams cad thul te gzhan don
NK073(pu)006:6280: gyi mdzad pa mi 'gags pa de'i rtsal yin pa
NK073(pu)006:6281: dang / yang don grub ces pas /
NK073(pu)006:6282: rang don gzhan don dus gcig la grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:6283: rang don grub shas che chung gis gzhan gyi snang ba yang /
NK073(pu)006:6284: de bzhin shar bas rang don lhun gyis grub nas /
NK073(pu)006:6285: gzhan don phyogs med du 'char bar bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6287: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor bas //
NK073(pu)006:6290: sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK073(pu)006:6291: bya byed med pa'i dkyil 'khor spyod /
NK073(pu)006:6293: chos thams cad rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil
NK073(pu)006:6294: 'khor du rdzogs pa de rtogs pa mthar phyin pa
NK073(pu)006:6295: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du sbyor
NK073(pu)006:6297: 'gro drug rang byung byang chub sems su lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:6298: grub pa'i yul dang bral ba'i thugs rje chen po'i
NK073(pu)006:6299: gtan tshigs kyis / phyogs bcu'i dus gnas so //
NK073(pu)006:6300: sa'i mtshan nyid thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su
NK073(pu)006:6301: rdzogs pa gsal bas thabs kyi mdzad pa gang yang
NK073(pu)006:6305: mdor na gdul bya nyid kyang thugs rje'i mdzad pa mi 'gags pa'i snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6306: des na phyogs dus kyis bsdus pa'i chos ma lus
NK073(pu)006:6307: pa gdul bya 'dul thabs rnams dang bcas pa rnams
NK073(pu)006:6311: 'o na de ltar mdzad pa la rtog pa mnga' 'am snyam na /
NK073(pu)006:6312: gdul bya gdul byed mdzad pa thams cad byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub pas /
NK073(pu)006:6313: sgyu ma'i chu las sgyu ma'i mis sgyu ma'i 'gro
NK073(pu)006:6314: ba bton pa ltar snang yang byas pa med bzhin
NK073(pu)006:6315: don byed mkhan dang yul dang mdzad pa gsum du
NK073(pu)006:6316: mi rtog par mdzad pa mi 'gog pa'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:6317: bya ba byed med par dkyil 'khor spyod /
NK073(pu)006:6319: des ni rtogs pa bzhi la bsnyen sgrub bzhi tshang ba'i tshul bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:6320: de la 'di'i dkyus su bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6321: rtog pa bzhi ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i rtogs tshul kho na ste /
NK073(pu)006:6323: rtogs pa bzhi yi gtan tshigs kyis //
NK073(pu)006:6324: snang srid phyi nang chos rnams kun //
NK073(pu)006:6325: mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor ston //
NK073(pu)006:6327: des mchog pa med kyang lam pa'i ngor rtogs pa bzhi /
NK073(pu)006:6328: mtshan nyid gsum du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6330: dgos 'brel gsum ni mtshan nyid gsum /
NK073(pu)006:6331: gzhi lam 'bras bur 'brel ba'i mtshan nyid bstan la /
NK073(pu)006:6332: spyir gang zag gcig gi cha rkyen du des chog la /
NK073(pu)006:6333: bsnyen sgrub ni gsang sngags spyi gzhung dang mthun pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6334: de la mos pa rnams kyi don du theg pa 'di nyid la'ang tshang bar bstan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6335: dkyil 'khor 'jug pa'i dpe bzhi ni shas che bar lam pa'i blo ngor /
NK073(pu)006:6336: de ltar khog don bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:6338: chos thams cad gdod ma nas zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6340: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK073(pu)006:6342: rang byung gi ye shes la snang grags kyi chos
NK073(pu)006:6343: thams cad sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK073(pu)006:6345: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor yin te /
NK073(pu)006:6346: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sku dang ye shes su gdod ma nas lhun gyis grub pas /
NK073(pu)006:6347: de'i ngang la 'khor ba ma dmigs pa'i phyir mya
NK073(pu)006:6348: ngan 'das pa zhes gdags gzhi bral bas phyogs zhen
NK073(pu)006:6349: gtan nas mi mnga' bas rnam par dag pa zhes
NK073(pu)006:6350: bya ste / chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:6351: ston pa dang bstan pa dbyer med de gsal la
NK073(pu)006:6352: 'gags pa med pa rang byung ye shes kyi ngos
NK073(pu)006:6353: nas ni ston pa zhes brjod la /
NK073(pu)006:6354: chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang
NK073(pu)006:6355: bral bas chos thams cad la khyab cing thams cad
NK073(pu)006:6356: de las mi gnyis pa'i ngang las gzhal yas zhes
NK073(pu)006:6357: bya ste / de yang 'dir gzhal yas khang gtso che bar smos pa lta bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:6359: rin po che la rtog pa med cing ris su
NK073(pu)006:6360: mi snyed kyang dgos 'dod 'byung ba bzhin chos kyi
NK073(pu)006:6361: dbyings la rtog pa mi mnga' zhing yon tan ris
NK073(pu)006:6362: su ma rnyed kyang rtogs ma rtogs kyis dgos pa
NK073(pu)006:6363: skong bas yid bzhin zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:6364: de nyid rtags su gsal ba ma 'gags par snang
NK073(pu)006:6365: ba longs sku chen po'i ngo bo gang du'ang ma
NK073(pu)006:6366: grub bzhin du gdul bya'i snang bas cir yang 'char
NK073(pu)006:6367: bas yid bzhin / rang rig byang chub sems de
NK073(pu)006:6368: lta bu nyid gsal la mi 'gags pa kha dog
NK073(pu)006:6369: dang dbyibs su snang ba la ni gzhan yas khang
NK073(pu)006:6370: bas yid bzhin / zhes bya ste // de yang don rtog gnyis las /
NK073(pu)006:6371: don rig pa rang byung gi ye shes chen po
NK073(pu)006:6372: lam pa rnams kyis gzhal du med cing thams cad
NK073(pu)006:6373: mkhyen pas kyang ngo bo 'di lta bu zhes mi
NK073(pu)006:6374: dpog pas / gzhal yas khang ni de nyid rig
NK073(pu)006:6375: pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo nyid du bzhugs pas
NK073(pu)006:6376: dpog pas / so // rtags gzhal yas ni /
NK073(pu)006:6377: ston pa'i dgongs pa rig pa'i ye shes nyid ma
NK073(pu)006:6378: 'gags pa rin po che la sogs pa'i kha dog
NK073(pu)006:6379: dang dabyingabasa su snang ba ni gzhan yas khang gi
NK073(pu)006:6381: rang rig nyid mtha' bral bas de snang ba'i gzhal yas khang yang mtha' bral te /
NK073(pu)006:6382: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab tu khyab pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6383: gdul bya'i blos mi dpog ste /
NK073(pu)006:6384: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba 'ba' zhig go //
NK073(pu)006:6385: khang ni ston pa'i ngo bo rig pa'i ye shes de las mi 'da' ste /
NK073(pu)006:6386: bskal par brgyugs kyang 'byung sa ma rnyed pas gtan tshigs des rgya yongs su ma chad ste /
NK073(pu)006:6387: chos kyi dbyings rgya ma chad pas thams cad khyab 'dal ba ni ngo bo'o //
NK073(pu)006:6388: rnam pa ni ye shes kyi snang ba pas ston
NK073(pu)006:6389: 'khor so so'i snang ba bzhin du lhun grub tu
NK073(pu)006:6390: bzhugs pa'o // des kyang gong gi rang bzhin rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:6391: pa chen po las lhag pa gzhan zhig ston pa
NK073(pu)006:6392: bzhugs pa'o // ma yin te / de nyid 'dir
NK073(pu)006:6393: gzhal yas la mos pa rnams kyi snang ba la
NK073(pu)006:6395: 'khor lo ces pas gdul bya'i ngos nas bcud bstan pa lta bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:6396: snod bstan pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang las bcud
NK073(pu)006:6397: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du bstan pa
NK073(pu)006:6398: bzhin ma 'gags pa rtogs pa'i chos rnams rtog pa
NK073(pu)006:6399: rgyu rkyen 'dus pa las snang ba de tsam na
NK073(pu)006:6400: gong du bshad pa bzhin snang ba sku /
NK073(pu)006:6403: rgyan gyi 'khor lo gsum rang bzhin gyis ye nas
NK073(pu)006:6404: de ltar yin pas dus skabs na rtog tshogs thams
NK073(pu)006:6405: cad de bzhin du lhun gyis grub pas zhen pa
NK073(pu)006:6406: phra ba 'ang ma dmigs pas rin po che gser
NK073(pu)006:6408: lam pa'i blos byas pa ma yin pa gser gling ye nas ser ba dang 'dra'o //
NK073(pu)006:6409: bla na med pa'i zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6410: don de lta bu gang gi 'og tu ma gyur
NK073(pu)006:6411: te dman pa gnyis kyi spyod yul ma yin pa
NK073(pu)006:6412: lta yang cang ches te kun tu 'od kyi sa
NK073(pu)006:6414: 'khor ba spang bya 'das pa blang byar sgrub phyir ro //
NK073(pu)006:6415: gsang sngags phyi nang lnga pos kyang mi rtogs te /
NK073(pu)006:6416: phung po khams skye mched lcags lta bu la /
NK073(pu)006:6417: sku dang ye shes 'gyur rtsi lta bus bgyur bar
NK073(pu)006:6418: bzhed pa'i bsgyur bya sgyur byed dang der 'dzin dang
NK073(pu)006:6420: des na theg pa 'dir ni yin tshul gyi don
NK073(pu)006:6421: mngon du gyur pa las ma gtogs pa'i bsgyur bya
NK073(pu)006:6422: sgyur byed kyi phyogs zhen med pas theg pa gang
NK073(pu)006:6423: gis kyang ma reg pas na bla na med pa'o
NK073(pu)006:6424: // de lta bu la ni ye ge nas pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6425: ngos nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya
NK073(pu)006:6426: // / byed mkhan med la rgyu rkyen bral bas
NK073(pu)006:6427: ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya ste
NK073(pu)006:6428: // / / don la ma 'dres yongs rdzogs so //
NK073(pu)006:6429: rdzogs pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa yang /
NK073(pu)006:6430: zhes pa'i blo ngo la so sor rtogs pa'i shes
NK073(pu)006:6431: rab kyi don spyi yid kyi yul du bya ba
NK073(pu)006:6432: ni / 'jug pa dang po yin la /
NK073(pu)006:6433: bsam ba'i shes rab kyis dbyod pa'i shes rab mthar
NK073(pu)006:6434: phyin te yul yul can med par rdzogs pa chen
NK073(pu)006:6435: po'i don gyi ngo bo rig pa gding du gyur
NK073(pu)006:6436: kyang / mthong bya mthong byed med pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6437: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6438: lta ba gtan la phebs pa ste 'jug pa gnyis pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6439: rtogs pa'i don las ma yengs par sgom pa'i gnas
NK073(pu)006:6440: skabs su 'dres shing goms par byed pa ni 'jug
NK073(pu)006:6441: pa gsum pa'o // goms pa mngon gyur lam gyi
NK073(pu)006:6442: btsal ba zad btsal bya btsal byed kyi chos phra
NK073(pu)006:6443: ba'ang mi gnas pas rang rig byang chub sems snang
NK073(pu)006:6444: stong gi phyogs lhung thams cad ma spangs ngang gis
NK073(pu)006:6445: pa gsum pa'o // dag pa nyid / nam mkhas
NK073(pu)006:6446: nam mkha' la 'dzin pa med pa bzhin du snyoms
NK073(pu)006:6447: pa chen por gyur pa ni 'jug pa mthar phyin
NK073(pu)006:6448: pa ste mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6451: de la yang tshul bzhi'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad na /
NK073(pu)006:6453: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor yin //
NK073(pu)006:6456: thabs kyi theg pa'i gnas skabs ni mig phye ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6457: thabs mkhas che dang mang yas yangs /
NK073(pu)006:6459: bshad pa nyid kyi theg pa don ston par byed pa gsang sngags nang pa /
NK073(pu)006:6460: de las kyang nye ba theg pa thams cad kyi spyi lung gsang ba'i snying po 'di nyid do /
NK073(pu)006:6461: gzhung ni dbu nas zhabs kyi bar lam gyi dgos
NK073(pu)006:6462: pa rgyud kyi dngos po bdun gsal bar ston pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6463: brjod byed kyi tshig 'di nyid do //
NK073(pu)006:6464: thos pa ni nyams thog tu lung son pa'i dam pa la /
NK073(pu)006:6465: slob ma rgyud nyid du smos pa'i mtshan nyid dang
NK073(pu)006:6466: ldan pas dad pas kun nas slong pa'i ma yengs
NK073(pu)006:6467: par rna ba'i dbang po la brgyud nas rig pa
NK073(pu)006:6468: ma yengs pas sgra spyi la brten sgra rang gi
NK073(pu)006:6469: mtshan nyid kyis don spyi la gcod pa'i gnas skabs
NK073(pu)006:6472: dper na skyes bu gcig mig long nas dngos po
NK073(pu)006:6473: gang yang mthong ba'i nus pa med pa mig mkhan
NK073(pu)006:6474: gyis phyes nas mig gi skyon dag pa'i skad cig
NK073(pu)006:6475: la dngos po gang la'ang thogs pa med par rang
NK073(pu)006:6476: 'jug pa'i nus pa dang ldan pa dang 'dra bar
NK073(pu)006:6477: / thos pa'i shes rab kyis don spyi yid kyi
NK073(pu)006:6478: yul du byas pa tsam de mig phye ba dang
NK073(pu)006:6479: / 'dra bar / bsam pa'i shes rab kyi skabs
NK073(pu)006:6480: su don rang gi mtshan nyid la 'jug pa'i rgyu
NK073(pu)006:6481: nus pa thogs med dang ldan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6482: des na mdor bstan pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i gzhal
NK073(pu)006:6483: yas khang chen po la rten gyi gang zag dang
NK073(pu)006:6484: 'jug pa'i mig phye ba dang 'dra ste /
NK073(pu)006:6486: bsam pa'i shes rab ston te /
NK073(pu)006:6487: don rtogs ni dkyil 'khor mthong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6489: bsam pa'i shes rab kyis yang nas yang du gdar sha chod par bsam ste /
NK073(pu)006:6491: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po mnyam pa nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes nyid /
NK073(pu)006:6493: de nyid la blo rig pa gdeng du gyur te
NK073(pu)006:6494: gzhal bya gzhal byed gtan tshigs thams cad thag chod
NK073(pu)006:6495: pa'i ngo bo bshad pa nyid la dbyer med nas
NK073(pu)006:6496: phyogs su 'dzin pa'i zhe 'dod ngang gis mi gnas
NK073(pu)006:6497: pa la ni rtogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6498: bsam pa'i shes rab mthar phyin pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6500: de nyid mig phyes na dpe dkyil 'khor mthong ba dang 'dra bar /
NK073(pu)006:6501: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor shes rab kyi spyan gyis
NK073(pu)006:6502: mthong bya mthong byed med par mngon du gyur pa'o
NK073(pu)006:6505: rtogs nas goms par byed pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6506: dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6507: rtogs pa'i don sgro 'dogs chod kyang /
NK073(pu)006:6508: sngon log rtog la goms pa'i dbang gis chu'i rnyogs
NK073(pu)006:6509: ma dang 'dra ba'i gzugs 'dzin zhen pa'i gyong ma
NK073(pu)006:6510: sangs pas de dag par byed pa la ni /
NK073(pu)006:6512: de yang 'og ma bzhin bsgyur bya dang sgyur byed
NK073(pu)006:6513: dang mi mthun pa dag gnyen po ma yin te
NK073(pu)006:6514: rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid la dus rgyun du 'da'
NK073(pu)006:6515: nyams med par gyi na 'da' mar gnas pa la
NK073(pu)006:6516: tha snyad du goms par byed ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6517: rtsol bas ma spags pa'i tshig go //
NK073(pu)006:6518: de la ni g.yo thob brtan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6519: drod dang rtags dang cho 'phrul dang mngon shes rnams kyang skabs de'i mtho dman la snang ste /
NK073(pu)006:6520: lam ring thung yang brtsi ba med pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6521: gang zag gi shes rab dang brtson 'grus kyi stobs so //
NK073(pu)006:6522: dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'o zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6523: dpe'i dkyil 'khor du zhug pa'i cho ga rdzogs pa
NK073(pu)006:6524: bzhin 'dir rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rtogs pa bzhi'i
NK073(pu)006:6526: de la lta ba ni rgyu shes pa tsam la
NK073(pu)006:6527: nyams su myong bar ni ting nge 'dzin gyi byed
NK073(pu)006:6529: des ni rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa bstan to //
NK073(pu)006:6530: de 'jug pa bzhi'i tha ma ni /
NK073(pu)006:6531: mnyam sbyor yin zhes pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6532: zhugs nas mngon du gyur pa ni dngos grub chen po thob pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6534: thos bsam sgom gsum gyis mnyam par sbyor ba mthar phyin /
NK073(pu)006:6535: ting nge 'dzin gyis zhugs te goms pa mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6536: phyi nang gi chos thams cad kun tu bzang po'i
NK073(pu)006:6537: rol pa sku gsung thugs lhun gyis grub pa mngon
NK073(pu)006:6538: du gyur nas yul dang yul can med de bdag
NK073(pu)006:6540: bdag nyid chen po lhun gyis grub phyogs zhen phra ba'i ba'ang mi mnga' ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:6541: gzhi ji bzhin pa nyid du gyur pa ni dngos grub chen po thob pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6543: dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid mngon sum du
NK073(pu)006:6544: grub pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK073(pu)006:6545: don rang snang ba la ni tha snyad du thob
NK073(pu)006:6547: sgrub pa chen po'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:6549: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub /
NK073(pu)006:6550: 'di ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos /
NK073(pu)006:6551: zhes pa snod bcud thams cad kun tu bzang po'i ngang du lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6552: rgyu las ma byang rkyen gyis ma skyed pas /
NK073(pu)006:6554: chos kyi dbyings dngos gzhi thams cad dang bral ba
NK073(pu)006:6555: nyid mi 'gags pa'i rtsal las sku gsung thugs kyi
NK073(pu)006:6557: snang bzhin du chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa dus gcig /
NK073(pu)006:6558: de'i ngang du lhun gyis grub ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:6559: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab thams cad rang bzhin
NK073(pu)006:6560: rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du lhun gyis grub la
NK073(pu)006:6561: / thugs rje dang mdzad pa mkhyen pa thams cad
NK073(pu)006:6562: res mos bral bas lhun grub tu bshad pa bzhin
NK073(pu)006:6563: / te / 'di'i skabs su gdul bya yang mdzad pa nyid mi 'gags pa'i rtsal lo //
NK073(pu)006:6564: don de ni phyogs bcu na bzhugs shing dus bzhir
NK073(pu)006:6565: gshegs pa'i rgyal ba ma lus mi lus lus pa
NK073(pu)006:6567: 'dir yang rtogs pa bzhi las gzhan du ma song ste /
NK073(pu)006:6568: rtogs pa bzhi'i don nyid 'jug tshul 'di lta bu
NK073(pu)006:6569: la dga' ba rnams kyi ngor 'di nyid bstan to
NK073(pu)006:6570: // des yan chad du gyur pa rdzogs pa chen po bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:6571: skol mdo dang sbyar ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:6572: spyi rdzogs pa chen po'i 'bras bu gcig char 'jug
NK073(pu)006:6573: pas rim par bsgrang du med kyang 'dir theg pa
NK073(pu)006:6574: gzhan gyi zla dang gang zag gi 'jug ngor dbye
NK073(pu)006:6575: nas 'jug pa'i sgo dang gang zag gnyis bstan na
NK073(pu)006:6576: / rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ni gzhi nas tshul /
NK073(pu)006:6577: rtogs pa bzhi shes pa'i mtshan nyid dang 'bral ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6578: bsnyen pa dang mig phye ba dang dkyil 'khor mthong ba rnams ni lta ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6580: dgos pa dang nye bsnyen sgrub pa gnyis dang dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa rnams ni sgom pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6581: 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid dang yang dgos dang sgrub pa
NK073(pu)006:6582: chen po dang dngos grub chen po thob pa ni
NK073(pu)006:6583: 'bras bu'o // spyod pa ni ngo bo nyid kyi
NK073(pu)006:6584: spyod pa 'khor 'das kyi mi 'gags pa thams cad
NK073(pu)006:6585: 'bras bu'o // yin la / lam pa'i spyod pa
NK073(pu)006:6586: ni dug gsum byang chub kyi lam du shar ba'i
NK073(pu)006:6587: spyod pa la sogs pa'i spyod pa lnga'o //
NK073(pu)006:6589: rdzogs pa chen po ni ched du bya ba thams
NK073(pu)006:6590: cad dang bral nas bsrung ba'i dngos po ma grub
NK073(pu)006:6591: pa dang / mi 'gags pa theg pa brgyad po'i dam tshig rnams de nyid du shar ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6592: mdor bstan na mnyam pa'i dmi tshig gcig gam /
NK073(pu)006:6598: yun ni sa lam rim gyis bgrod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6599: bral bas lam rim bstan du med kyang 'dir sngar
NK073(pu)006:6600: gyi sbyangs pa dang shes rab dang brtson 'grus su
NK073(pu)006:6601: ldan na / tshe gcig gis rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyis mngon du snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:6602: gdams pa brjod pa la gnyis kyi /
NK073(pu)006:6603: dang po skal ldan gyi mtshan nyid bstan pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:6604: dngos dang yul khyad par can de yul can kyang khyad par can du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6605: de ltar tshul 'di ni rdzogs pa chen po'i don zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:6606: gong du bstan pa'i rtog pa bzhi nas /
NK073(pu)006:6607: dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i dpe bzhi'i bar /
NK073(pu)006:6608: rdzogs pa chen po'i don la 'jug pa'i tshul 'di
NK073(pu)006:6609: ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang snang kun
NK073(pu)006:6610: tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs su rdzogs la /
NK073(pu)006:6611: de yang ma 'gags pa dang ma dmigs pa dbyer
NK073(pu)006:6612: med pa ched 'dzin thams cad dang bral bas chen
NK073(pu)006:6613: po ste / mthar phyin pa ni de las thob
NK073(pu)006:6614: bya dang rtogs bya dang goms bya ma mchis pas
NK073(pu)006:6615: po ste / na / mthar phyin pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6616: chos thams cad de las mi 'da' ste lam snang der lhun gyis grub pa'i don no //
NK073(pu)006:6617: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6618: yi ge ni brtags pa dang brjod pa dang tha snyad ste /
NK073(pu)006:6619: phyi nang ngam snod bcud dam 'khor 'das sam mtho
NK073(pu)006:6620: ris ngan song dam gnyis can du btags pa thams
NK073(pu)006:6621: cad ngo bo la ma grub ste /
NK073(pu)006:6622: sgra tsam tha snyad tsam du zad pas yi ge'o //
NK073(pu)006:6623: 'khor lo ni rgyun chad med par snang ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:6624: de ltar yi ges mtshon pa'i phyogs bcu mtha' thug pa med pa'i mi 'gags pa'i tshogs rnams /
NK073(pu)006:6625: sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor rdzogs la /
NK073(pu)006:6627: dbyer med pa thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor
NK073(pu)006:6628: lor rdzogs te phyogs thams cad sku gsung thugs su
NK073(pu)006:6629: gsal ba'o // de la'ang yul yul can ni ma dmigs so //
NK073(pu)006:6631: de lta bu'i ngang las ma 'gags pa bsod nams /
NK073(pu)006:6632: mi 'dzin pa ye shes kyi tshogs /
NK073(pu)006:6633: dbyer med pa chen po ste tshogs ye rdzogs che po'i ngang la /
NK073(pu)006:6634: sa zhes pa ni thams cad der 'dus shing de
NK073(pu)006:6635: las snang ste de nyid las mi 'gyur bas so
NK073(pu)006:6636: // de'i ngang las yul yul can med /
NK073(pu)006:6637: 'jug bya 'jug byed med par rang snang du lhun gyis rtogs pa 'jug pa zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:6638: de ni yul khyad par can du bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:6639: yul des yul can yang khyad par can du bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6641: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK073(pu)006:6642: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK073(pu)006:6643: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK073(pu)006:6644: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK073(pu)006:6645: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK073(pu)006:6647: lhag pa'i shes rab rnam par dag pa dang ldan
NK073(pu)006:6648: pa gang zhig rdzogs pa chen po'i don yul khyad
NK073(pu)006:6649: par can gong ma la mos pa tsam gyis kyang
NK073(pu)006:6650: / sangs rgyas kyi 'khor ma lus pas phyogs kun
NK073(pu)006:6651: nas kun tu 'bras bu la reg ma thag yin
NK073(pu)006:6652: / pas / nye ba'i sras su dgongs pas bar ma dor mi 'dor zhes bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:6653: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK073(pu)006:6654: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas pas //
NK073(pu)006:6655: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK073(pu)006:6658: bskal pa grangs med pa gsum sbyangs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6659: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod cing bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:6660: gsang chen rdzogs pa chen po'i don mthong bar nus
NK073(pu)006:6662: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK073(pu)006:6663: 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK073(pu)006:6664: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK073(pu)006:6665: bsnyen nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK073(pu)006:6667: drug gi 'jig rten phyogs bcu na 'das pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6668: da ltar gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i sangs rgyas ril gyis
NK073(pu)006:6669: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don 'di rnyed nas
NK073(pu)006:6670: gzod sangs rgyas par gyur pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo'o
NK073(pu)006:6674: 'byung dang ma 'ongs pa'i dus gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6675: rgyal ba thams cad 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6676: tshe / rdzog pa chen po la brten dgos zhe'o //
NK073(pu)006:6677: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK073(pu)006:6678: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6679: rdzogs pa chen po'i don gsang chen nges pa nyid
NK073(pu)006:6680: gong du rgyu rkyen 'bras bu mtshan nyid gsum du
NK073(pu)006:6681: btags kyang ngo bo rdzogs pa chen po nyid du
NK073(pu)006:6682: gcig pas 'bras bu lam zhes so //
NK073(pu)006:6683: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK073(pu)006:6684: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK073(pu)006:6685: btsal kyang rgyal bas mi brnyed so //
NK073(pu)006:6687: rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa rdzogs pa chen po 'di nyid la /
NK073(pu)006:6688: 'di las lhag pa'i logs su btsal na rgyal bas kyang mi brnyed ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:6689: kun gyi phyag rgya chen po mchog /
NK073(pu)006:6691: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi lam yang 'di
NK073(pu)006:6692: yin te 'di ma rtog bar du lam bgrod dgos
NK073(pu)006:6693: la / 'di ma thob par du bsgrub dgos pas /
NK073(pu)006:6695: des yul gyi yon tan bstan nas //
NK073(pu)006:6696: yul can gyi yon tan ni //
NK073(pu)006:6697: thos bsam sgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK073(pu)006:6699: sbyangs pa mthar phyin pa'i stobs kyis dngos po thams
NK073(pu)006:6700: cad kyi de kho na nyid shes pa ni rdzogs
NK073(pu)006:6702: de ni shes rab kyi mig dang ldan pa rnams kyis bzung ngo //
NK073(pu)006:6703: snod ldan dang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK073(pu)006:6704: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK073(pu)006:6706: snod dang ldan pa'i mtshan nyid ni rdzogs pa'i gzhung nas bshad pa rnams yin la /
NK073(pu)006:6707: gzhan yang ngang ring ba tshul shes pa rang bzhin bzang ba brtan pa /
NK073(pu)006:6708: lus dang longs spyod gtong ba rnams ni sngon du sbyangs 'phro stobs su gyur pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6709: rgyud kyi khungs de nyid dkyus la sbyar na /
NK073(pu)006:6711: rgyud kyi mtshan nyid de rnams dang ldan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6712: sbyangs pa'i stobs kyis bsod nams dang ye shes las skyes la /
NK073(pu)006:6713: blo rtsal rab ni rab 'bring gsum phyes pa'i tha ma gsum las kyang 'das /
NK073(pu)006:6715: rab kyi yang rab phyi nang gi chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:6716: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pa chen po'i ngo bo kun
NK073(pu)006:6717: tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs su rtogs pa'i rtsal
NK073(pu)006:6718: dang ldan pa la rab ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:6719: rten gyi gang zag de lta bu des chos thams
NK073(pu)006:6720: cad ye gnas pa'i ngo bo bshad pa'i don gyis
NK073(pu)006:6721: sangs rgyas pa'i gazhi'am don la /
NK073(pu)006:6722: gnas tshul bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas par rtogs par
NK073(pu)006:6723: rtogs pa yul dang yul can dbyer med pa'i ngang
NK073(pu)006:6724: la / goms pa drag dal zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6725: rtogs pa'i ngang las ting nge 'dzin gyis rgyun du
NK073(pu)006:6726: gnas pa ni brtson 'grus che na goms pa drag
NK073(pu)006:6727: ste 'bras bu la myur du phyin /
NK073(pu)006:6728: brtson 'grus chung na dal te phyi mar phyin /
NK073(pu)006:6729: yang na goms pa drag pa ni gcig char rtogs /
NK073(pu)006:6730: dal ba ni rim gyis pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6732: goms pa drag dal zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6733: rtogs pa'i ngang la bar chad med pa'i lam du
NK073(pu)006:6734: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis 'grod pa la
NK073(pu)006:6735: ni goms pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6736: mig lam du 'gro ba yang gzhan du skad cig
NK073(pu)006:6737: tsam yang mi yengs nas lam du gom pa drag
NK073(pu)006:6738: dal gyis 'gro / zhes pa dang 'dra bar /
NK073(pu)006:6739: yid la bya ba thams cad dang bral ba'i tshul
NK073(pu)006:6740: gyis ting nge 'dzin la rgyud du mi yengs pa
NK073(pu)006:6741: la ni / 'gro ba yin zhes bya /
NK073(pu)006:6742: don des ni rtogs pas mi chog 'bras bu ting
NK073(pu)006:6743: nge 'dzin gyis myong bar nan tan du gdams pa'o
NK073(pu)006:6744: // phal gyi bya ba ma yin no //
NK073(pu)006:6746: blo rab bshad pa bzhin lam ma gtogs pa dgur
NK073(pu)006:6747: dbyer ba'i shes rab brgyad po man chod kyi spyod
NK073(pu)006:6749: gzhan yang snod kyi skyon rnams dang ldan pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6750: brtson 'grus zhan pa la sogs pa rnams kyi spyod yul ma yin no //
NK073(pu)006:6752: snod ngan pa'i mtshan nyid kyang /
NK073(pu)006:6754: gzhan du nam yang sbyin mi bya //
NK073(pu)006:6755: rmongs la 'phyar bas gal te byin //
NK073(pu)006:6756: dus min par ni srog zad nas //
NK073(pu)006:6757: bsreg dang sbrebs la yun ring gnas //
NK073(pu)006:6759: gzhan du gong ma'i yon tan rnams la bzlog pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6760: skyon dang ldan pa rnams la ni nam yang mi
NK073(pu)006:6761: sbyin te / rang gi snying 'byin nyes dang bsdos te gsang ngo //
NK073(pu)006:6763: byin pa'i nyes dmigs ni go sla'o //
NK073(pu)006:6764: phal gyi thog te zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6765: bsod nams ma bsags pa shes rab rnam gsum la
NK073(pu)006:6766: ma sbyangs pas rig pa ma 'byongs pa bcud 'di'i
NK073(pu)006:6767: snod kyi skal bar mi ldan pa la ni phal
NK073(pu)006:6768: kyis zhes bya'o // thos te zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6769: de lta bu la don bstan te thog kyang snod
NK073(pu)006:6770: bcud du mi 'dzom pas blo la mi shongs te
NK073(pu)006:6771: / dpen na nyan thos kyis nyan thos go yang
NK073(pu)006:6772: don 'di nyid mi go ba bzhin pas rang gis
NK073(pu)006:6773: / ma go / ma go ba'i dbang gis ji ltar bsam kyang nges shes mi skye ste /
NK073(pu)006:6774: bden zhing bzang bar zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6775: theg pa 'di'i tshig bden par yid la mi 'byor ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6777: snang srid kun tu bzang por ston pa la tshig bden par yid ches par yang mi 'gyur la /
NK073(pu)006:6778: don bzang bar yang yin ches par mi 'byung /
NK073(pu)006:6781: rang gis ma go ba'i dbang gis thabs kyi theg
NK073(pu)006:6782: pa 'di la ci ltar bsam kyang 'di chos kyi
NK073(pu)006:6783: gnas tshul yin pas bden pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6784: lam nye zhing 'jigs pa med pas yid ches par mi 'gyur ro //
NK073(pu)006:6785: yid ma ches pa'i skyon bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6786: yid ma ches pa dang zhes pa bshad pa bzhin pas /
NK073(pu)006:6787: phal zhes pa blo dman pa rnams sdud ste /
NK073(pu)006:6788: de dag gi blo la dka' zhing zhes pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6789: rang gis ma rtogs pas so //
NK073(pu)006:6790: des na rang shes rab chung ba'i nyams dang sbyar nas tshig bden pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6791: don bzang bar yang ma shes /
NK073(pu)006:6792: gnas tshul yin pas bden pa dang lam nye zhing
NK073(pu)006:6793: 'jigs pa med pas bzang bar ma shes pa'i rang
NK073(pu)006:6796: shes rab can rdzogs pa chen po rtogs pa'i skal
NK073(pu)006:6797: ba dang ldan pa rnams de dang 'dra snyam ste
NK073(pu)006:6798: / rgyu nges 'bras bu ni rdzogs pa'i don phyi
NK073(pu)006:6799: nang gi chos thams cad 'bras bu'i ngo bo yid
NK073(pu)006:6800: / pa dang / theg pa 'di nyid chos kyi gnas tshul yin pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6801: lam nye zhing 'jigs pa med pa rnams yang brdzun zhes chos la ma dad de /
NK073(pu)006:6802: de rtogs pa'i skyes bu la'ang ma dad de /
NK073(pu)006:6804: rdzogs pa chen po mnyam pa nyid kyi don mngon sum du rtogs pa la yang mi bden te /
NK073(pu)006:6805: chos min te des na shes rab chung bas thabs
NK073(pu)006:6806: kyi theg pa ma go na de la skyon bzhi
NK073(pu)006:6807: 'byung ste / ma dad pas dam pa'i chos spong ba nyid kyi chos la skur pa btab dang /
NK073(pu)006:6808: de rtogs pa'i skye bu yang mi bden snyam nas 'phags pa la skur pa btab pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6809: thabs kyi theg pa ni 'bras bu'i ngo bo yin
NK073(pu)006:6810: pa las de la ma dad pa ni 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:6813: rgyu bsgrub pa la don med de /
NK073(pu)006:6814: de'i 'bras bu ni ngan song kha brgyud par 'gyur nas thar ba'i skal pa med do //
NK073(pu)006:6815: de bas na de dag chud mi gnas pa'i phyir gsang bar gsungs so //
NK073(pu)006:6816: sun 'byin pa'i blo skye bar 'gyur zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6818: mnyam pa nyid ces bya ba sun 'byin te /
NK073(pu)006:6819: mngon sum du mi mnyam pa bkod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6820: snang srid kyi chos rang snang 'bras bu yin pa sun 'byin te /
NK073(pu)006:6821: 'khrul ba gzung 'dzin yin par bkod pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6822: blang dor med par sun 'byin te /
NK073(pu)006:6823: khyi phag la sogs pa'i 'thad pa bkod pa la
NK073(pu)006:6824: sogs blo la de lta bu skye bar 'gyur bas
NK073(pu)006:6826: gong ma'i don rnams brjod nas chos la skur ba 'debs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6827: de lta bu rten gyi gang zag gi ngos nas
NK073(pu)006:6828: gang zag la 'ang skur pa 'debs par 'gyur bas
NK073(pu)006:6829: / de ltar byas pas dper na glang bu brag la 'phras na rmig pa khrag gis gang /
NK073(pu)006:6830: sgo nga gnas du 'phags na rting pas la grub
NK073(pu)006:6831: pa dang 'dra bar bshad pa bzhin kho lhung pa'i
NK073(pu)006:6833: bsreg dang sbrebs la yun ring gnas nas ngan song kha brgyud de thar daka'o //
NK073(pu)006:6834: de bas na blo dman de dag gi don du rab tu gsang te mi bstan pa'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:6835: gsang ba'i theg pa zhes bka' stsal to //
NK073(pu)006:6838: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba che //
NK073(pu)006:6839: gsang chen sbyor bas dngos grub thob //
NK073(pu)006:6842: gsang sngags gsang bar bya ba yang //
NK073(pu)006:6843: gsang sngags skyon yod ma yin te //
NK073(pu)006:6844: las 'phro ngan dang skal med la //
NK073(pu)006:6845: de la shin tu gsang bar bya //
NK073(pu)006:6847: de la sogs te gsang sngags phyi nang rnams na
NK073(pu)006:6848: gsang ba'i thabs su lus brda' dang ngag brda' dang
NK073(pu)006:6849: snod brtags pa la sogs pa rgyas par bka' stsal
NK073(pu)006:6851: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK073(pu)006:6852: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin /
NK073(pu)006:6854: blo dman rnams rim pa bzhin du don bya bar bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6855: de bas na chos thams cad /
NK073(pu)006:6856: ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6858: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa /
NK073(pu)006:6859: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas /
NK073(pu)006:6860: zhes pa rdo rje slob dpon theg pa dgu la mkhas dgos par bstan te /
NK073(pu)006:6862: gsang sngags phal gyi blo la shongs dka' ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6863: ma shongs nas skur ba btab na thon pa'i thabs
NK073(pu)006:6864: med pas gzhan du gsang dgos pa'i gtan tshig de
NK073(pu)006:6865: bas na / rdo rje slob dpon gyis slob ma
NK073(pu)006:6866: rnams 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye 'am thog
NK073(pu)006:6867: ma nas chos kyi dbyings sam sku gsung thugs kyi
NK073(pu)006:6868: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa'i don la
NK073(pu)006:6869: bas na / / shes rab rnams gsum gyis blo sbyangs nas /
NK073(pu)006:6870: rtogs pa thag chod pa'i blo ma skyes kyi bar du theg pa 'og ma pas zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6871: lha dang mi'i theg pa dge ba bcu dang /
NK073(pu)006:6872: rgyu 'bras mi bslu ba'i chos spyod nyan thos rang rgyal dang /
NK073(pu)006:6873: rgyu'i theg pa chen po dang gsang sngags phyi pa
NK073(pu)006:6874: gsum ste bdun gyi sgo nas gdul bya rnams kyis
NK073(pu)006:6875: so sor rang rang gi blo tshod dang bstun pa
NK073(pu)006:6876: de'i theg pa de bstan nas /
