NK073(pu)006:6877: 'gro don byas na ji srid bdag 'dzin dang ma bral gyi bar du rgyu 'bras mi bslu /
NK073(pu)006:6878: des nag po rnams mi spyod pas ngan song gi sgo khegs /
NK073(pu)006:6879: chos spyod dkar po rnams spyad pas mtho ris su rgyu 'bras mi bslu ste /
NK073(pu)006:6880: khang bzang nas khang bzang du 'gro ba dang 'dra
NK073(pu)006:6881: bar gyur nas gdul bya'i bya ba chud mi gsan
NK073(pu)006:6882: ba'i gtan tshigs de bas na /
NK073(pu)006:6883: slob dpon gyis theg pa kun la mkhas par bya dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6884: slob dpon gyis ces pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6885: rdo rje slob dpon gyis bzung ba kun gyis kyang /
NK073(pu)006:6886: khams gsum 'khor ba'i skyon dang zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6887: rgyu rkyen ngo bo mtshan nyid rnams shes par byas nas /
NK073(pu)006:6888: slob ma de la skrags nas skyo ba skye pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6889: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyu rkyen mtshan nyid ngo
NK073(pu)006:6890: bo yon tan rnams shes par byas nas bshad de
NK073(pu)006:6891: slob mas go nas brod pa bskyed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6892: theg pa thams cad la mkhas par bya ba yin gyi /
NK073(pu)006:6894: dkyus 'di nyid du bstan pa'i mu stegs yan chad
NK073(pu)006:6895: theg pa dgu'i lta spyod sgom pa la sogs pa
NK073(pu)006:6896: skol mdor dbyes pa thams cad la mkhas par byas
NK073(pu)006:6897: na / slo ma la yang blo tshod dang sbyar
NK073(pu)006:6898: ba'i theg pa de dang de bstan nas chud mi
NK073(pu)006:6899: za bas chos grwa'i slob dpon chen pos theg pa
NK073(pu)006:6900: kun la mkhas par bya ba yin gyi /
NK073(pu)006:6902: phyogs 'ga' shes pas slob dpon gyi sa bzung du mi rung bar /
NK073(pu)006:6904: gdul bya blo che chung gi 'tshams tshad du ston dgos pa'i gtan tshigs des na /
NK073(pu)006:6905: slob dpon gyi phyogs 'ga' zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6906: theg pa che chung gang yin pa'i phyogs 'ga' dang /
NK073(pu)006:6907: gcig shes pas ni don ston mi nus par gsungs te /
NK073(pu)006:6908: de ni bla ma dam pa bde bar gshegs pa chen pos kyang /
NK073(pu)006:6914: dgu bstan bcos dang bcas pa las 'byung bas na rgyas cher zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6917: phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i rgyud dang /
NK073(pu)006:6918: de la sogs ste gsang sngags phyi nang kun dang /
NK073(pu)006:6919: sogs pa brgyad kyis gtan la dbab pa'i mdo sde la sogs pa'i mdo sde rnams dang /
NK073(pu)006:6920: gzhung 'di nyid la sogs pa'i bstan bcos rnams las 'byung ngo //
NK073(pu)006:6921: spyod pa bstan pa la gnyis kyi mdo ni /
NK073(pu)006:6922: lta ba'i khyad par gyis zhes pa sogs pa 'jig rten dang 'das pa'i lta ba'i khyad par dang /
NK073(pu)006:6923: 'jig rten pa rang la'ang lta ba yod med kyi khyad par dang /
NK073(pu)006:6924: 'das pa'i theg pa dgu so so'i lta ba ni
NK073(pu)006:6925: ris mi 'dra ba'i gong 'og gi khyad par gyis
NK073(pu)006:6928: yang na srung ste rnam par dag pa lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:6931: spyod pa shes che ba'i ngos nas sam /
NK073(pu)006:6932: yang na gang yin yang dngos su nyams su blang bde ba'i ngos nas so //
NK073(pu)006:6935: gong gi lta ba'i khyad par bzhin du spyod pa'ang de ltar snang ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:6936: des na so so'i spyod pa rnams su 'gyur ro //
NK073(pu)006:6937: spyod pa yod med kyi khyad par spyir bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6938: dka' thub med pa ni zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6939: bsrung ba spyod pa nyams su blang rgyu med pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6940: 'jig rten phyal pa mur thug go //
NK073(pu)006:6941: dka' thub yod pa ni rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK073(pu)006:6943: 'bras bu tshol ba la zhugs kyang log par song ba'i mu stegs te /
NK073(pu)006:6944: 'khor ba las mi 'da' bas 'jig rten gyi dka' thub ce'o //
NK073(pu)006:6945: gzhan yang 'chad par 'gyur ba'i nyan thos te /
NK073(pu)006:6946: theg pa dman pa gnyis kyi dka' thub dang /
NK073(pu)006:6947: gzhan don ched du gnyer ba byang chub sems dpa'i dka' thub /
NK073(pu)006:6948: phal la med cing theg pa thams cad kyi mthar thug bla na med pa'i dka' thub po //
NK073(pu)006:6950: rgyas par dka' thub med pa gnyis ni /
NK073(pu)006:6951: de la phyal pa ni zhes pa la logs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6952: gong du byung gdab pa'i gzhi de las phyal ba bkar nas bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6953: rgyu 'bras la rmongs pas zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6954: dge ba spyod pas mtho ris kyang mi shes /
NK073(pu)006:6955: mi dge ba spyad pas kyang ngan song yang mi shes /
NK073(pu)006:6956: tshe snga ma dang phyi ma 'adi'ang rgyu 'bras kyi bya ba rnams la blo ma zhugs te /
NK073(pu)006:6957: mgo rmongs pa ni ma rtos pa'i phyir zhe 'dod med pas sgrub pa med ste /
NK073(pu)006:6958: des na 'grub byed kyi dka' thub med do //
NK073(pu)006:6960: tshe phyi ma med de 'jig rten 'di kho na yin la mtha' chad par lta ste /
NK073(pu)006:6961: 'di snang ba'ang stes dbang gis spang la sha mong
NK073(pu)006:6962: skye ba'i tshul du glo bur skye bas phyi ma'i
NK073(pu)006:6963: 'bras bu med pas 'dir rgyus bskyed pa med ste
NK073(pu)006:6964: / log par rdzogs pa'i phyir dam du bca' dka' thub med ste /
NK073(pu)006:6965: dka' thub yod pa'i rgyang 'phen ni /
NK073(pu)006:6966: tshe snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bras la blo ma
NK073(pu)006:6967: zhugs kyang tshe 'di la gzhan pas dpag pa'i khyad
NK073(pu)006:6971: rigs rgyud 'phen po bsgrub pa'i phyir gtsang sbra zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:6974: khrus dang 'jig rten gyi lha la bsang la sogs pa byed pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:6975: gzhan yang rgyal rigs dang bram ze'i rigs so so
NK073(pu)006:6976: nang du mi nyams par bya ba'i sha mi za
NK073(pu)006:6977: ba dang / kha 'phro bsrung ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6978: gdol pa las phyogs bsrung ba rnams sogs khongs su bsdu ste /
NK073(pu)006:6979: des kyang las dkar nag ni rgyu 'bras dang tshe
NK073(pu)006:6980: snga phyi'i byed pa rnams ma rtogs te nag pa
NK073(pu)006:6982: dkar ba la blang ba'ang med pas yang dag pa'i don las rgyang ring du song ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6983: tshe 'di'i phan pa bsgrub pa'i spyod pa'i brtul zhugs can pas ma rtogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:6985: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:6986: log par rtogs pa'i nyams pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:6987: bdag rtag pa gcig yod pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:6988: 'gro ba kun gyi lus kyi khong na bdag ces bya ba'i rtag pa /
NK073(pu)006:6989: che na sgo nga ba tsam /
NK073(pu)006:6990: chung na yungs 'bru tsam yod pa de ma dag pa'i dus su ngan song gsum du snang la /
NK073(pu)006:6991: dag na 'bras bu thob par blta bas grogs ngan pa'i stobs kyis de dag par bya ba'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:6994: rang gi lus sdug bsngal gyis sun 'byin cing smra phabs te ngo bo gang yin na /
NK073(pu)006:6996: phyogs bzhir me bzhi btang ste stong nas nyi mas gdung pa dang lngas dag par re ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6997: sogs khongs su lo sar pa'i khyags kyis khrus byed na dag par blta ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:6998: gzhan yang dbyug gu gsum pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7003: gzhan yang khyii'i brtul zhugs te mu stegs pa la
NK073(pu)006:7004: log lta ma gtogs pa'i mi dge ba dgu bsrung
NK073(pu)006:7005: / bla gab med pa la sogs pa'i gtsang sar bsdud /
NK073(pu)006:7006: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig tu byas pas ma 'phros
NK073(pu)006:7007: pa'i dbang gis mig rnon la sogs pa'i mngon shes
NK073(pu)006:7008: phra ba yod pas khyi dang bya la sogs pa
NK073(pu)006:7009: shi nas lhar skye bar mthong ste /
NK073(pu)006:7010: der skye ba'i rgyu snga ma'i dge ba'i las kun
NK073(pu)006:7011: gzhi la yod pa ni ma mthong zhing ma shes
NK073(pu)006:7012: pas / spyod pa de nyid kyi stobs kyis skye bar mthong bas /
NK073(pu)006:7013: nyal thabs la sogs pa khyi'i spyod pa rnams 'chang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:7014: steg la gnas te bya'i spyod pa 'chang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:7015: nya bzhin du chu la 'phyong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7016: de dag ni kho'i 'bras bu sgrub pa'i lam du mthong bas na dka' thub dang /
NK073(pu)006:7017: tha mal pa brtul nas spyod pa de dag nyams su blang ba la zhugs pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:7018: rgyu 'bras re yang spyod pa de las 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:7019: mi 'byung bas na log pa'i spyod pa zhes bya'o
NK073(pu)006:7021: nyan thos dang dman pa gnyis /
NK073(pu)006:7022: rang nyid khams gsum gyi sdug bsngal ma bzod nas
NK073(pu)006:7023: de las 'da' ba'i thabs kyi tshul khrims dang spyod
NK073(pu)006:7024: pa la dka' thub ces bya ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:7026: lung sel sogs pa thams cad tshig 'di bzhi las 'phros pas thams cad kyi rtsa ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7027: sdig pa thams cad mi bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:7029: sdig pa ni rgyu lus ngag yid gsum brlab pa
NK073(pu)006:7030: dang dang bcas pa'i las sdig sdig lta bu'i mtshan
NK073(pu)006:7031: nyid can gyis 'bras bu ngan song gsum du mnar
NK073(pu)006:7032: bas na sdig pa zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:7033: thams cad ni rten gyi sgo nas lus ngag yid
NK073(pu)006:7034: gsum du 'dus pa thams cad ngo bo'i sgo nas
NK073(pu)006:7036: phra rags kyi sgo nas rags pa mi bsad pa lta bu /
NK073(pu)006:7037: phra ba srog chags phra ba'i phra ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:7040: rang don du mi bya ba lta a cang yang ches te /
NK073(pu)006:7041: gzhan don du 'gyur yang mi bya ba ni dge
NK073(pu)006:7042: sdig gi rnam pa kun rdzob dang don dam so
NK073(pu)006:7044: rang zhi ba 'ba' zhig gis kun nas bslang bas so //
NK073(pu)006:7045: de ni sdom pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK073(pu)006:7046: dge ba phun tshogs par spyod /
NK073(pu)006:7048: rgyud dge ba rnam par dka' bdag nyid can bdag gzhan la byams pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7049: snyoms pa nyid 'bras bu dge ba mtho ris dang thar par snang bas so //
NK073(pu)006:7050: phun sum tshogs pa ni dge ba bcu la sogs te rang don du 'gyur la /
NK073(pu)006:7051: gzhan la mi gnod pa'i ngo bo phra rags tshogs
NK073(pu)006:7052: par spyad de de la ni shes rab ces bya'o
NK073(pu)006:7054: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul /
NK073(pu)006:7056: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims dang spyod pa thams cad
NK073(pu)006:7057: kyi rtsa ba ni rang gi sems 'dus ba tshul
NK073(pu)006:7058: bzhin ma yin pa yid la mi byed pa 'ba'
NK073(pu)006:7059: zhig ste / dper na shing rta blan dka' ba /
NK073(pu)006:7060: srab ni so sor thar 'di yin /
NK073(pu)006:7062: shing rta mi sdod par rgyug pa la mthun pa'i 'dzer bu btab na ni sdod la /
NK073(pu)006:7063: mi mthun pa'i 'dzeng bu btab na ni 'gro ba bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:7064: bdag gi sems rta rgod dang 'dra ba de gang la ba'i phyir /
NK073(pu)006:7065: so sor thar pa'i 'dul ba dang 'dra ba nyid
NK073(pu)006:7066: kyis rang sems 'dul bar byas pa ni rtsa ba'ang
NK073(pu)006:7067: yin la / yon tan nam 'bras bu'ang yin /
NK073(pu)006:7068: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin /
NK073(pu)006:7070: brjod byed kyi tshig gsum po de'ang des mtshon pa'i
NK073(pu)006:7071: tshul khrims gsum po dang 'di ni sprul pa'i sku
NK073(pu)006:7072: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i ngo bo yin
NK073(pu)006:7073: te / de'ang ston pa 'jig rten du byon ma thag tu gsung ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7075: dge ba bcu la sogs pa'i rnam par dgar ba'i chos thams cad dang /
NK073(pu)006:7076: mi dge bcu la sogs pa rnam par gnag pa'i
NK073(pu)006:7077: chos thams cad kun rdzob tu yang tha dad de
NK073(pu)006:7078: / dge ba kun rdzob kyis mtho ris /
NK073(pu)006:7079: sdig pa kun rdzob kyis ngan song /
NK073(pu)006:7080: don dam par yang tha dad ste /
NK073(pu)006:7081: rdul phra rab dag skad cig mar mtshungs pas des na so sor yod par lta bas /
NK073(pu)006:7082: dge ba'i ni spyad ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:7083: gtan tshigs gong mas dge ba ni dang du blang zhing spyod /
NK073(pu)006:7084: mi dge ba ni gzhan don du 'gyur na'ang spong bas bsrung ba'i tshul khrims kyi dka' thub dang /
NK073(pu)006:7085: tha mal pa las brtul zhing rang gi spyod pa'i dngos po sdom pa la zhugs pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7086: des na phyogs rtogs zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:7087: don dam pa ji bzhin pa ma rtogs pa'i phyogs chos so //
NK073(pu)006:7088: byang chub sems dpa'i dka' thub ni /
NK073(pu)006:7089: zhes pa snying rje chen pos khams gsum gyi sdug bsngal ma bzod de /
NK073(pu)006:7090: de dag gi ched du sa bcu rim pa bzhin
NK073(pu)006:7091: bgrod nas bdag gzhan gyi don gcig char du spyod
NK073(pu)006:7092: pa la ni / byang chub sems dpa' zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:7093: de'i spyod pa dang tshul khrims thun mong du bstan pas so //
NK073(pu)006:7094: dka' thub ni byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa las zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:7095: de ston par byed pa'i gzhug nyi shu pa las /
NK073(pu)006:7096: rkyen du 'tsham par don mi byed /
NK073(pu)006:7098: gzhan don byed par khas blangs te spyod pa la zhugs na pha rol pa'i don du gyur pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7099: rkyen du 'tsham pa'i nus pa rang la yod bzhin
NK073(pu)006:7100: du de'i don mi byed pa ste sdig pa'i las
NK073(pu)006:7101: byed pa mi bkag nas byed du bcug pa lta
NK073(pu)006:7102: bu / dge ba'i las la mi bskul nas 'phyal bar bzhag pa lta bu dang /
NK073(pu)006:7103: yang rkyen du 'tsham par zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:7104: theg pa chen pos don mi byed nas theg chung
NK073(pu)006:7105: la sbyor na'ang de dag byang chub sems dpa'i ltung
NK073(pu)006:7106: ba'o // yang mi 'dul bzhin du 'dul bar byed na'ang rkyen du mi 'tsham te ltung ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7107: mdor na gzhan don du 'gyur na ci yang nyams su blang ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:7108: ded dpon snying rje can gyis mi nag mdung thung
NK073(pu)006:7109: can ma bsad na byang chub sems las nyams pa
NK073(pu)006:7110: las / bsad pas mnyams pa'ang rkyen du 'tsham par don byed pa yin la /
NK073(pu)006:7111: ma bsad na mi byed pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7112: rdzu 'phrul bsdigs la sogs mi byed /
NK073(pu)006:7113: ces pa la sogs pa mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bstan
NK073(pu)006:7114: nas bsdigs pa la sogs pa rnams kyis yul de
NK073(pu)006:7115: dge ba la 'khor ba'i skabs su thabs /
NK073(pu)006:7116: nus pa yod pa la de ltar mi byed pa /
NK073(pu)006:7117: byang chub sems dpa'i ltung ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7118: sogs khongs su brid pa dang barngana pa sbyin pa
NK073(pu)006:7119: dang thabs ci'i sgo nas kyang 'gro ba rnams dge
NK073(pu)006:7121: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa yin pa la /
NK073(pu)006:7122: de dag mi byed na byang chub sems dpa'i 'gal ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7123: don des na byang chub sems dpa'i dka' thub ni gzhan don du 'gyur ba 'ba' zhig yin la /
NK073(pu)006:7124: der 'gyur na ci'ang nyams su blang zhe'o //
NK073(pu)006:7126: snying rjer ldan dang byams phyir dang /
NK073(pu)006:7128: snying rje ni thams cad kyi rgyu rkyen 'bras bu
NK073(pu)006:7129: rnams kun nas kun tu sdugs bsngal gyi rgyun par
NK073(pu)006:7130: gnas pa la gdung ste ma bzod nas sems 'phrog
NK073(pu)006:7132: sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyis de dag sdug bsngal dang bral te bde ba la bkod pa'i rnam pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7133: des na byang chub sems dpa' la bsam pa de gnyis dang ldan pa'i dbang dang /
NK073(pu)006:7134: sems dge ba la nyes pa med ces pas sems dge ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:7135: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu thams cad kyi ngos nas gzhan
NK073(pu)006:7136: la bsam pa bzang po gnag chos dang bral ba
NK073(pu)006:7137: dung lta bu yod pas rtsa ba des /
NK073(pu)006:7139: bsam pa dkar na sbyor ba gnag kyang sla bas /
NK073(pu)006:7140: dper na rgyal po me lta bu ste /
NK073(pu)006:7141: sems can gyi don du 'gyur na mi dge ba spyad pa'i nyes pas mi gos te /
NK073(pu)006:7142: rngon pa dang smad 'tshong ma'i sgrungs bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:7144: gzhi snying rje chen pos kun tu zin na 'gro
NK073(pu)006:7145: ba'i don du spyod pa'i chos thams cad rnam pa
NK073(pu)006:7146: dge ba dang / mi dge ba gang spyod kyang
NK073(pu)006:7147: gzhan gyi don du 'gyur bas rang gi sdom pa
NK073(pu)006:7149: mdor na lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo nas ci
NK073(pu)006:7150: byed kyang snying rjes gzhi bzung nas 'gro ba'i don
NK073(pu)006:7152: rang don la rag ma las pa lta bu'o //
NK073(pu)006:7153: gsang sngags kyi spyod pa la gnyis kyi /
NK073(pu)006:7154: mnyam pa'i spyod pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:7155: bla na med pa'i dka' thub ni /
NK073(pu)006:7157: 'dir gsang sngags phyi nang drug tu yod pa la /
NK073(pu)006:7158: ma phyes pa ni spyir gsang sngags tsam lta spyod mnyam pa nyid /
NK073(pu)006:7159: dbyer med par phyogs mthun pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7160: 'di nyid bstan pas 'go ma rnams kyang shugs kyis shes pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7161: dkyus thad ka zhar la bstan pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7162: bla na med pa'i gsang sngags kyi theg pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:7163: theg pa gang gis kyang ma reg pa mthar thug
NK073(pu)006:7164: pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo nye bar rdzogs pa chen
NK073(pu)006:7165: po'o // de'i mi 'gags pa bsrung ba dang spyod pa thun mong du bstan pa la ni /
NK073(pu)006:7167: ngo bo ni gnyis can thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi nang du lhun grub pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7168: dam tshig chen po'i mdo las /
NK073(pu)006:7170: 'bras bu mnyam pa nyid 'ba' zhig ston pas dam tshig chen po'o //
NK073(pu)006:7171: de'i mdo ni gsang ba'i snying po'i dam tshig gi le'u bcu dgu pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7172: sangs rgyas theg par rab nges na /
NK073(pu)006:7174: 'bras bu'i theg pa 'di sangs rgyas zhes bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:7175: phyi nang gi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du
NK073(pu)006:7176: sangs rgyas pa kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs
NK073(pu)006:7177: su da lta nyid du ston pas lam dang 'bras
NK073(pu)006:7178: bu gnyis ka mthar phyin pa'i don gyis cig char
NK073(pu)006:7179: du skyol bar byed pas na theg pa rab nges
NK073(pu)006:7180: na zhes pa / ngo bo dang /
NK073(pu)006:7182: rnam grangs ni dam tshig gi gzhung rnams ma nyams par nyams su lon pa'i stobs kyis /
NK073(pu)006:7183: ting nge 'dzin kyang ci ltar dmigs pa bzhin du btub pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7184: rtogs pa bzhi dang mnyam pa bzhis chos thams cad
NK073(pu)006:7185: kun tu bzang po'i dgongs par lhun gyis grub pa
NK073(pu)006:7186: la 'gyur ldog mi mnga' ba ni nges pa zhes
NK073(pu)006:7187: bya ste / gnas skabs de'i tshe na /
NK073(pu)006:7188: nyon mongs 'dod lnga kun spyod kyang /
NK073(pu)006:7190: spang bya nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:7191: 'gro ba kun gyi longs spyod pa'i 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang /
NK073(pu)006:7192: kun gyi sgras 'og ma rnams kyis gnag pa'i las su bltas pa'i mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK073(pu)006:7193: mtshams med pa lnga la sogs pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7194: de dag mi 'gags pa'i ngos nas spyod kyang /
NK073(pu)006:7196: ched 'dzin dang bral ba nam mkha' lta bu'i blo
NK073(pu)006:7197: 'chong ba'i skyes bu la spyod kyang ma gos te
NK073(pu)006:7198: / de'i dpe ni pad+ma la ni 'dam bzhin te /
NK073(pu)006:7200: pad+ma 'dam na gnas kyang 'dam gyi nyes pas ma gos te /
NK073(pu)006:7201: kha dog phun sum tshogs la /
NK073(pu)006:7202: ma gos par ma zad 'dam na gnas pa nyid
NK073(pu)006:7203: kyis pad+ma'i dri dang kha dog gsal bar byed pa
NK073(pu)006:7204: dang 'dra bar / 'dam dang 'dra ba'i bshad pa'i
NK073(pu)006:7205: 'khor ba'i chos rnams la spyod kyang nyes pa'i gzhi
NK073(pu)006:7207: gzung 'dzin dag pa nam mkha' bzhin pas mi gos la /
NK073(pu)006:7208: der ma zad nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs pa
NK073(pu)006:7209: 'khor ba'i chos rnams rang byung gi ye shes su
NK073(pu)006:7210: gsal ba ni pad+ma 'dam gyis bskyed pa dang 'dra
NK073(pu)006:7211: la / de la che ba'i yon tan thams cad rang snang ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7212: de la tshul khrims phun sum tshogs /
NK073(pu)006:7214: de lta bu'i rten gyi gang zag de la nyan thos kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK073(pu)006:7216: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7217: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig rnams kyi 'bras bu mngon
NK073(pu)006:7218: du byas pa dgongs pa la rdzogs pa ni mthar
NK073(pu)006:7219: thug pa med pa'i bsrung ba thams cad rig pa
NK073(pu)006:7220: nyid las mi gzhan pas rnam grangs rdzogs pas phun
NK073(pu)006:7223: tshul khrims phun sum tshogs zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:7225: sdom pa'i tshul khrims ni dgongs pa de lta bu
NK073(pu)006:7226: mnga' bas bshad pa ltar las dang nyon mongs pa
NK073(pu)006:7228: zhes yang byas pa med pa nyid kyi dgongs pa
NK073(pu)006:7229: nyams su lon pa ni nyes pa rtsa ba nas
NK073(pu)006:7230: bral nas sdom pa'i tshul khrims /
NK073(pu)006:7231: gzhan don du 'gyur na rtsa ba bzhi la sogs
NK073(pu)006:7232: la gang yang spyod pas gzhan gyi don du 'gyur
NK073(pu)006:7233: ba ni don byed pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK073(pu)006:7235: rdzogs pa chen po'i sku gsung thugs las mi nyams pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:7236: dge ba chos sdud pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK073(pu)006:7238: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye'am gdod ma nas
NK073(pu)006:7239: mnyam pa bzhi'am gnyis kyi ngo bo chos kyi dbyings
NK073(pu)006:7240: mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin las 'das nyams med
NK073(pu)006:7241: pa ste / khams gsum rang rig nyid du gsal ba'i phyir na /
NK073(pu)006:7242: 'og ma bzhin yul dang yul can gyi snying rjes kyang lhag par bsten du med ste /
NK073(pu)006:7243: ngo bo nyid kyi snying rje chen po la 'bral ba med pas so //
NK073(pu)006:7244: gzhi de las zhe sdang ni spang du med do zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:7245: zhe sdang mnar sems dgu dang ldan pa'i mtshan nyid kyang /
NK073(pu)006:7246: rig pa byang chub sems su gcig ste yul med pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7247: nam mkha' dngos por mi snang ba bzhin zhe sdang gtan nas ma grub pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7248: ma 'gags par snang ba nyid kyang sems nyid kyi ngang du rang bzhin med pa /
NK073(pu)006:7249: mdor na gtan nas ma grub pa la ni spang du med ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:7250: 'o na chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du gyur
NK073(pu)006:7251: na theg pa chen po'i lam gyi ngo bo snying
NK073(pu)006:7252: rje ye med pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:7253: ma yin par bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:7254: de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams la zhes pa la sogs te /
NK073(pu)006:7256: gong ma mnyam pa nyid kyi don no //
NK073(pu)006:7257: ma rtogs pa ni don nyams su ma myong ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7259: gtan nas ma rtogs pa khams gsum gyi sems can rnams sam /
NK073(pu)006:7260: ci bzhin par ma rtogs pa blo'i rim pa'i bye
NK073(pu)006:7261: brag gis theg pa brgyad po rnams la thugs rje
NK073(pu)006:7264: spyir khams gsum gyi sems can la thugs rje mi 'byung ba ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:7265: rang rang gi blo rtog gi snang ba don byed
NK073(pu)006:7266: nus pa rgyun mi chad pa'ang ngo bo nyid kyi
NK073(pu)006:7268: de nyid rtogs pa dang dbyer med pa'i mdzad pa shar ro //
NK073(pu)006:7269: nye bar theg pa brgyad po la thugs rjes mi 'byung ba'ang ma yin te /
NK073(pu)006:7270: theg pa brgyad po ma 'gags pa dang theg pa
NK073(pu)006:7271: so so'i rten gyi gang zag rnams kyi blo ngo
NK073(pu)006:7272: la bya ba mthar phyin par mdzad pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:7273: rgyud chad med pa'i thugs rje ste /
NK073(pu)006:7274: bar mtshams med par 'byung ba rgyun mi chad pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7275: de ltar mthar thugs pa rdzogs pa chen po'i dka' thub dang brtul zhugs bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:7276: zhar la gsang sngags lnga po'i dka' thub dang brtul zhugs bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:7277: ji ltar na ye nas rnam par dag pa rtogs pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:7279: shes bya lta ba'i ngo bo ye ji ltar yin
NK073(pu)006:7280: pa'i don de spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dang
NK073(pu)006:7281: bral ba'i ngang la phyogs zhen mi mnga' ba'i dag
NK073(pu)006:7282: pa'i lta bu'i ngo bo rtogs pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:7284: lung a nu yo ga dbyings dang ye shes rgyu 'bras su rtogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7285: ma h+aa yo ga pas thabs dang shes rab su rtogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7286: yo ga pa dag gis yul sems stong pa mnyam nyid kyi rtogs pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7287: kri ya chos thams cad rig pa mtha' bral gyi
NK073(pu)006:7288: rtogs pa dang mthun bzhin du bsrung ba'i tshul khrims
NK073(pu)006:7290: spyod pa'i khyad par gyi brdul zhugs kyang rtogs pa dang mthun pa de ltar /
NK073(pu)006:7291: rnam par dag pa zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:7292: kri ya bdag spyod ched 'dzin gyi ngos nas rnam par dag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7293: u pa ya de dang mthun pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7294: yo ga pa lus gar dang phyag rgya /
NK073(pu)006:7296: sems ting nge 'dzin la sems med pa'i rnam par dag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7297: ma h+aa pa dag thabs dang shes rab dang blang
NK073(pu)006:7298: dor med pa'i don nyams su len pa nyid kyis
NK073(pu)006:7299: blang dor gnyis 'dzin rnam par dag pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7300: a nu de dang mthun yang ma h+aa bzhin du
NK073(pu)006:7301: de nyid du 'dzin pa dang bral ba ni rnam
NK073(pu)006:7302: par dag pa zhes bya ste spyod pa'o //
NK073(pu)006:7303: des na nyams su blang ba'i ngos nas brtul zhugs zhes bya la /
NK073(pu)006:7304: nyams su blangs te mthar phyin pa'i ngos nas dka' thub ces bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:7305: des na bshad pa'i tshig rkang gnyis po des gsang sngags phyi nang gi spyod pa rnams bstan la /
NK073(pu)006:7306: thugs rje mi 'byung ba phyin chod kyi sbyis /
NK073(pu)006:7307: thugs rje 'byung ba'i ngo bo theg pa dgu kun
NK073(pu)006:7308: gyi rang rang gi rtogs pa dang mthun pa'i sdom
NK073(pu)006:7309: pa dang spyod pa rnams shes par bya'o //
NK073(pu)006:7310: des na rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK073(pu)006:7311: mthar thug pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo bcud dam pa
NK073(pu)006:7312: yin pa yid bzhin gyi nor gyi nor bu rin
NK073(pu)006:7314: theg pa kun gyis bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu yin pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7315: de nyid mi 'gags pa las gdul bya'i blo tshod
NK073(pu)006:7316: dang mthun pa bzhin du theg pa rnams snang bar
NK073(pu)006:7317: bstan pa ni / rgyud nyid las /
NK073(pu)006:7318: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK073(pu)006:7319: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK073(pu)006:7323: zhabs kyi don slob dpon nyid kyi smon lam min /
NK073(pu)006:7324: lta ba'i phreng ba'i gsang ba 'di /
NK073(pu)006:7326: lta ba ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa bcu gsum ste /
NK073(pu)006:7327: don las mtshan du stsal ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7328: phreng ba ni dpe las mtshan du gsol ba ste /
NK073(pu)006:7329: phreng ba dang thag pa gcig la brgyus kyang rdog
NK073(pu)006:7330: pa rnams so sor ma 'dres pa dang 'dra bar
NK073(pu)006:7331: / chos mnyam pa nyid phreng thag lta bu las
NK073(pu)006:7332: lta ba bcu gsum po rgyun chags su gral rim
NK073(pu)006:7333: ma nor bar yod pas so //
NK073(pu)006:7334: yang na phreng ba ni mdzes pa yin /
NK073(pu)006:7335: de dang 'dra bar gdul bya rnams so so rang
NK073(pu)006:7336: rang gi blo ngo la rig pa tshim zhing mdzes
NK073(pu)006:7337: pa'i bya ba byed pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:7338: des na g.yu thang bzhin du gong mas 'og ma
NK073(pu)006:7339: sun mi 'dod so sor theg pa rang rang gi
NK073(pu)006:7340: ngo bo bkod par nges so //
NK073(pu)006:7341: gsang ba 'di zhes pa gnyis te /
NK073(pu)006:7342: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:7344: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba ni /
NK073(pu)006:7345: bshad pa dang 'chad pa bzhin pas /
NK073(pu)006:7346: rtogs pa'i skal ldan pas phal gyi spyod yul ma yin pas so //
NK073(pu)006:7347: don des na snod du ma gyur pa la yang gsang bas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:7348: 'di zhes bya ba ni brjod bya brjod byed gnyis kyi ngo bo ston pas so //
NK073(pu)006:7349: 'o na lta ba'i phreng ba zhes smos na /
NK073(pu)006:7350: gsang ba 'di zhes pa rdzogs pa chen po la bzhag pa ci yin zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:7351: 'di'i rgyud kyi khungs kyi gzhung spyi yang gsang bar bsdu ba dang /
NK073(pu)006:7352: lta ba'i rnam grangs bstan pa kun kyang rdzogs pa chen po mthong ba'i thabs yin pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7353: lta ba rnams spyir bstan nas /
NK073(pu)006:7354: dmigs kyis rdzogs pa chen po bsal bas so //
NK073(pu)006:7355: dmur long rang phye'i mig rnyed ltar /
NK073(pu)006:7357: dper na sems can ma khong nas mig long bas
NK073(pu)006:7358: mthong snang gi dngos po ci yang mig gi yul
NK073(pu)006:7359: du ma gyur pa nyid snga ma'i las ngan pa
NK073(pu)006:7361: las bzang po sad pa'i mgo mnyam pas de'i stobs
NK073(pu)006:7362: kyis mig rang phyi ste mig rnyed par gyur na
NK073(pu)006:7363: skad cig ma gcig la phyi nang gi chos thams
NK073(pu)006:7364: cad brda 'phrad pa rim pa bzhin du skye mi
NK073(pu)006:7365: dgos pa ltar / 'dir dmus long dang 'dra ba'i
NK073(pu)006:7366: thog ma med pa'i mu nas ma rig pa gnyis
NK073(pu)006:7367: kyis shes rab kyi mig long ste /
NK073(pu)006:7368: las gsum gyi bag chags kyis bsnan te bsgribs pas /
NK073(pu)006:7369: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don rang dang skad cig tsam ma bral yang /
NK073(pu)006:7370: zur tsam yang ma mthong ba'i skabs su /
NK073(pu)006:7371: las bzang po sad pa dang 'dra ba'i bskal pa
NK073(pu)006:7372: zhing gi rdul snyed du gsum la blo sbyangs te
NK073(pu)006:7373: / dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa'i gang zag yang
NK073(pu)006:7374: rab kyis las ngan pa dag pa dang 'dra ba'i
NK073(pu)006:7375: ma rig pa gtan nas dag mig rang phye ba
NK073(pu)006:7376: dang 'dra ba'i rtogs pa'i shes rab rang las 'khrungs
NK073(pu)006:7377: te rang gi rang ngo shes /
NK073(pu)006:7378: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don gcig char mngon
NK073(pu)006:7379: du gyur pa'i shes rab thabs kyi rtsal 'chang ba
NK073(pu)006:7381: bshad ma thag pa'i rig pa nyid chos thams cad gang du'ang mi dmigs pa'i shes rab dang /
NK073(pu)006:7382: ci yang mi 'gags pa'i thabs te /
NK073(pu)006:7383: de dbyer med du byang chub sems su lhun gyis
NK073(pu)006:7384: grub pa skad cig la rtogs par nus pa'i rtsal
NK073(pu)006:7385: 'chang ba de ni skyes mchog ces bya ste /
NK073(pu)006:7386: bshad pa nyid kyi bsags pa dang sbyangs pa mthar thugs pa las snang bas na skyes /
NK073(pu)006:7387: 'dir theg pa nyid kyi snod du gyur pas na mchog yod na zhes pa /
NK073(pu)006:7388: dkon pa ste lam la zhugs pa khri tsam gyi nang na yang /
NK073(pu)006:7389: 'di rtogs su rung ba'i gang zag gcig tsam las
NK073(pu)006:7390: dkon pas na de lta bu yod na gzhung 'di
NK073(pu)006:7392: de ltar 'phrad pa tsam gyis snod bcud 'dzom pas
NK073(pu)006:7393: rig pa la mjal ba the tshom mi za ste
NK073(pu)006:7394: / dper na me long g.ya' dag pa la bzhin 'phrad pa bzhin no //
NK073(pu)006:7395: 'o na gzhan gyi bsngo ba 'gro ba yongs la bsngo na /
NK073(pu)006:7396: 'di ltar bsngo ba ci zhe na /
NK073(pu)006:7398: 'di nyid kyis 'gro ba yongs la bsngo ba'ang yin te /
NK073(pu)006:7399: dper na ri dbang gi rgyal po yod na dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pa bzhin /
NK073(pu)006:7400: 'dir bsngo ba bzhin gyi snod bcud 'dzom na 'gro don phyogs med du 'char ba'o //
NK073(pu)006:7402: ri dbang gi rgyal po sems can gyi mdun du snang bar gyur cig byas kyang /
NK073(pu)006:7403: spyod yul du ma gyur pas mi snang la /
NK073(pu)006:7404: zag med mthong ba rnams kyi spyod yul du gyur cig ces brjod na /
NK073(pu)006:7405: de bzhin du 'gyur bas slob dpon nyid rtsal chen
NK073(pu)006:7406: rdzogs pa'i skyes bu shes rab kyi 'phang mtho ba'i
NK073(pu)006:7407: mdzad pa'o // mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK073(pu)006:7408: lta ba phreng ba ces pa /
NK073(pu)006:7409: don dang dpe gnyis las btags pa ste bshad zin to //
NK073(pu)006:7411: tshig don ma lus pa'i tha tshig go //
NK073(pu)006:7414: // rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don //
NK073(pu)006:7415: til mar bzhin du chos kun la //
NK073(pu)006:7416: gsang ba bzhi yin chod nas gab //
NK073(pu)006:7417: ston byed drug pa kun bzang gis //
NK073(pu)006:7418: spyi lung gsang ba'i snying por bstan //
NK073(pu)006:7419: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK073(pu)006:7420: gang zag ras chod can don du //
NK073(pu)006:7421: brda' dang zur gyis sbas pa las //
NK073(pu)006:7422: sbyangs pa mthar phyin rtsal chen rdzogs //
NK073(pu)006:7423: lhun grub stobs mnga' pad+ma bas //
NK073(pu)006:7424: sbas pa'i don rnams 'di ru bstan //
NK073(pu)006:7425: de don bshes gnyen 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK073(pu)006:7426: bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs dkyil na //
NK073(pu)006:7427: mtsho dwangs nyi zla gza' skar ram //
NK073(pu)006:7428: nyi ma'i snying po bzhin du gsal //
NK073(pu)006:7429: zhabs kyi ldul la reg pa yi /
NK073(pu)006:7430: ban ldom dpyid chung dbyar ring la //
NK073(pu)006:7431: sbyangs bsags mthar phyin dpon ston gyis //
NK073(pu)006:7432: gzhan don gtso cher bskul ma btab //
NK073(pu)006:7433: sdebs sbyor spangs te nu ru'i lugs //
NK073(pu)006:7434: ci nus tsam du dbyes pa las //
NK073(pu)006:7435: nongs pa gong ma rnam la bshags //
NK073(pu)006:7436: ngal ba'i dge rtsal 'gro ba rnams /
NK073(pu)006:7438: rigs bdag nyid dang dbyer med shog /
NK073(pu)006:7439: dam med rnams dang ma 'phrad cig /
NK073(pu)006:7440: theg pa'i 'byung gnas bstan pa'i rgya mtsho che //
NK073(pu)006:7441: don gyi bcud 'dus gsang ba'i man ngag le'u //
NK073(pu)006:7442: rtogs dka' the tshom zhus pa'i tshig bkrol ba //
NK073(pu)006:7443: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bus dkyus su bkod //
NK073(pu)006:7444: dus kyi mnar ba'i 'gro ba'i blo ngo la //
NK073(pu)006:7445: lon par dkar bas dkyus kyi tshig sbram rnams //
NK073(pu)006:7446: gsal bar byas kyang nyid kyis nyid bkrol ba //
NK073(pu)006:7447: ma gtogs gzhan pa'i spros pa phal cher bcad //
NK073(pu)006:7448: 'di nyid rtogs pas rgyud don mthar phyin te //
NK073(pu)006:7449: yul bral ye shes chen po mngon gyur shog //
NK073(pu)006:7450: lta ba'i phreng ba'i bshad pa /
NK073(pu)006:7451: rgyud don rin po che snang byed ces bya ba
NK073(pu)006:7452: kahbana rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa rdzogs so
NK073(pu)006:7454: gzhi rgyud gdod nas rnam dag 'od gsal gshis //
NK073(pu)006:7455: thabs grol rtogs goms bgrod byed lam gyi rgyud //
NK073(pu)006:7456: 'bras rgyud nyer lnga'i bdag nyid rdo rje sems //
NK073(pu)006:7457: dbyer med gter chen bla mar phyag bagyi'o /
NK073(pu)006:7459: 1 / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas ma lus pa'i //
NK073(pu)006:7460: thugs bskyed smon lam pan grub zhal 'dzom pas //
NK073(pu)006:7461: gangs ljongs gsang sngags bstan pa'i klung rdol ba //
NK073(pu)006:7462: snga 'gyur rnying ma zhes byar grags pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:7464: 2 / de yi rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i pha nor dbyig /
NK073(pu)006:7465: yo ga gsum gyi don bsdus rtsa ba'i rgyud //
NK073(pu)006:7466: sgyu 'phrul gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK073(pu)006:7467: bka' gter bstan pa rgya mtsho'i nang gi mdzod /
NK073(pu)006:7469: 3 / tan+t+ra bco brgyad la sogs rgyud kun kyang //
NK073(pu)006:7470: 'di las byung zhing 'di la gzhol bas na //
NK073(pu)006:7471: bsang sngags chu bo bzhi yi 'byung gnas te //
NK073(pu)006:7472: rgyud kyi rgyal po theg pa'i yang rtse yin /
NK073(pu)006:7474: 4 / bstan pa'i 'byung khung lung rnams spyi yi 'grel //
NK073(pu)006:7475: rgyal ba'i dgongs phug 'bras bu'i mthar thug pa //
NK073(pu)006:7476: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad gshegs pa'i shul //
NK073(pu)006:7477: rnal 'byor che rnams bgrod pa'i lam po che /
NK073(pu)006:7479: 5 / che ba brgyad ldan gsang ba'i snying po yi //
NK073(pu)006:7480: gab pa'i man ngag mtha' drug tshul bzhi yi //
NK073(pu)006:7481: bcing kun ston pa rdo rje'i thugs mdzod nas //
NK073(pu)006:7482: rnam par 'byed po sangs rgyas gnyis pa ste /
NK073(pu)006:7484: 6 / man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba zhes byar grags //
NK073(pu)006:7485: de yang man ngag snyan brgyud zab mo nas //
NK073(pu)006:7486: rgyud don 'grel mdzad spob pa mtha' yas te //
NK073(pu)006:7487: de gsungs bdud rtsi'i stobs rtsal rab rgyas pa /
NK073(pu)006:7489: 7 / gsang bdag dpa' bo rdo rje rgyal matshan gyis //
NK073(pu)006:7490: phyi rabs 'gro la brtse ba chen po yis //
NK073(pu)006:7491: snga na med pa'i legs bashad 'di phyungs te //
NK073(pu)006:7492: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i nyi ma gsal bar byas /
NK073(pu)006:7494: 8 / de phyir rin thang lci ba'i chos kyi mdzod //
NK073(pu)006:7495: 'di la chos spyan ldan kun gzigs mdzod dang //
NK073(pu)006:7496: rmong pa'i mun pa drung nas 'byin byas te //
NK073(pu)006:7497: mtshan nyid gsum po mngon sum rtogs par nges /
NK073(pu)006:7499: 9 / de bas phyogs dus kun tu 'chad spel dang //
NK073(pu)006:7500: thos bsam sgom pa'i rnal 'byor byed po kun //
NK073(pu)006:7501: 'og min gnas su gsang bdag ston 'khor dang //
NK073(pu)006:7502: tha mi dad pa'i phrin las dbang 'byor phyir /
NK073(pu)006:7504: 10 / dad dang 'dun pa lhag bsam dang ldan pas //
NK073(pu)006:7505: kahthoga shar gnas seng+ge g.yu rdzong du //
NK073(pu)006:7506: 'bad pas spar du bzhengs pa'i legs tshogs rgyun //
NK073(pu)006:7507: snying po'i bstan la zungs su smin pa dang /
NK073(pu)006:7509: 11 / dpal ldan bla ma'i thugs dgongs yongs su rdzogs //
NK073(pu)006:7510: bstan 'dzin skyes bu'i zhabs pad rtag tu brtan //
NK073(pu)006:7511: bstan pa'i snying po bshad dang sgrub pa 'phel //
NK073(pu)006:7512: bstan pa phyogs dus kun tu rgyas gyur cig 12 /
NK073(pu)006:7513: bdag dang bdag la 'brel thogs sems can kun //
NK073(pu)006:7514: lam mchog zab mo 'di la spyod pa dang //
NK073(pu)006:7515: 'gal rkyen kun zhi mthun rkyen phun tshogs te //
NK073(pu)006:7516: don gnyis 'byor pa rgya mtsho rgyas par shog 13ces
NK073(pu)006:7517: pa'ang 'di nyid kyi rtsa ba dang 'brel pa chos
NK073(pu)006:7518: kyi 'byung khungs bcas spar du bsgrubs cing legs par
NK073(pu)006:7519: grub pa'i tshe spar byang smon tshig bcu gsum sa
NK073(pu)006:7520: yi grangs ldan 'di nyid snga 'gyur ba'i gral 'thar
NK073(pu)006:7521: skyes pa'i rmong btul gyi na ba pad+ma thugs rje'i
NK073(pu)006:7522: dbang phyug gzhan phan mtha' yas pas lcags pho 'brug
NK073(pu)006:7523: gi lo'i hor zla gsum pa'i yar tshes bcu bzhi
NK073(pu)006:7524: nyi ma me bzhi'i 'grub sbyor bzang po dang ldan
NK073(pu)006:7525: pa'i snga dro'i 'char bris pa phyogs dus kun tu
